NK058(si)001:1463: phyi nang med cing sangs rgyas kyi sa'i yon tan
NK058(si)001:1464: thams cad der ma tshud pa med pas kun tu
NK058(si)001:1465: yang nang du gyur pa mtshon pa'i phyir /
NK058(si)001:1466: gzhal yas khang de yang ye shes kyi 'od lnga
NK058(si)001:1467: rab tu dwangs pa'i rang bzhin de bzhin gshegs pa
NK058(si)001:1468: nyid kyi thugs rje'i ngang las snang bas phyi zhing
NK058(si)001:1469: khams su snang ba dang nang gtso 'khor du snang
NK058(si)001:1470: ba thams cad kyang nyid kyi rang bzhin las gzhan
NK058(si)001:1471: pa'i chos tha dad du grub pa med par ngo
NK058(si)001:1472: bo'i gnas lugs la dus dang rnam pa kun tu
NK058(si)001:1473: yang chos sku kun tu bzang po'i ngang las ma
NK058(si)001:1474: g.yos par 'dus pas nang spros pa dang bral ba
NK058(si)001:1475: nyid du ye nas gyur pa na zhes so //
NK058(si)001:1476: gnyis pa khri'i bkod pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK058(si)001:1477: theg pa 'og mas nyam mi nga zhing /
NK058(si)001:1478: mi 'jigs pa bzhi mtshon pa'i phyir dbus su seng ge rin po che'i khri dang ldan pa'o //
NK058(si)001:1479: nga sangs rgyas zhes zhal gyis bzhes pa rtogs pa dam 'cha' ba /
NK058(si)001:1480: sgrib pa mtha' dag spangs zhes spang ba dam 'cha' ba /
NK058(si)001:1481: dug gsum rang gas thar ba la bar du gcod ces bgegs dam 'cha' ba /
NK058(si)001:1482: lam zab mo bsgoms pas 'khor ba las nges par 'byung zhes lam dam 'cha' ba la /
NK058(si)001:1483: don la gnas pa'i rgol ba med pas mi 'jigs pa bzhi ste /
NK058(si)001:1485: rang gzhan don du ye shes dang //
NK058(si)001:1486: spangs dang nges 'byung gegs byed rnams //
NK058(si)001:1487: ston mdzad mu stegs gzhan dag gis //
NK058(si)001:1488: mi bardzi khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK058(si)001:1490: theg pa 'og mar mi chud pa'i don 'dir shong
NK058(si)001:1491: zhing theg la stobs kyi rnam pa bcu mnga' ba'i
NK058(si)001:1492: brdar shar du glang po che'i khri dang ldan pa'o
NK058(si)001:1493: // spyod yul gyi gnas dang gnas ma yin pa dang /
NK058(si)001:1494: 'gro ba'i las kyi rnam par smin pa dang /
NK058(si)001:1495: bsam gtan dang ting nge 'dzin dang rnam par grol ba dang /
NK058(si)001:1496: gdul bya'i mos pa sna tshogs dang /
NK058(si)001:1497: khams sna tshogs dang dbang po mchog dang mchog ma yin pa dang /
NK058(si)001:1498: 'gro ba rgyud lnga dang thar pa gsum du 'gro ba'i lam dang /
NK058(si)001:1499: rang bzhin gyi skye ba sngon gyi gnas rjes su dran pa dang /
NK058(si)001:1500: sems can gyi 'chi 'pho skye ba dang /
NK058(si)001:1501: zag pa zad pa mkhyen pa bcu la sgrib byed
NK058(si)001:1502: dam rang rang gi mi mthun phyogs bcu 'joms pas
NK058(si)001:1503: stobs bcu ste / de nyid las /
NK058(si)001:1504: thabs dang skyabs dang dag pa dang //
NK058(si)001:1505: theg chen nges par 'byung ba la //
NK058(si)001:1506: sems can rnams ni rab bslu ba'i //
NK058(si)001:1509: gdul bya thams cad myur du grol bar byed cing
NK058(si)001:1510: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi la mnga' brnyes pa'i
NK058(si)001:1511: brdar lhor cang shes pa rta'i khri dang ldan pa'o
NK058(si)001:1516: dpyod pa ste 'gro ba'i yid dang mthun par sprul pa bkye nas don mdzad pa ni /
NK058(si)001:1519: dpyod pa'i ting 'dzin spong ba yi //
NK058(si)001:1520: 'du byed rnams ni rkang pa bzhis //
NK058(si)001:1522: snang ba thams cad dbang du byed cing dbang bcu
NK058(si)001:1523: mnga' ba'i brdar nub tu rma bya rin po che'i
NK058(si)001:1527: 'gro ba'i sems shes pa sems dang /
NK058(si)001:1528: nam mkha' mdzod la mnga' brnyes pas yo byad dang /
NK058(si)001:1529: gzhan gyi las dman bzang por bsgyur bas las dang /
NK058(si)001:1530: ji ltar 'dul ba der sprul pa lhun grub tu 'byung bas skye ba dang /
NK058(si)001:1531: sngon dang phyi ma'i bskal pa rgya mtshor dgongs pa bzhin 'grub pas smon lam dang /
NK058(si)001:1532: gdul bya'i mos pa bzhin don mdzad pas mos pa dang /
NK058(si)001:1533: bzhed na 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad yungs 'bru
NK058(si)001:1534: gcig tu bcu ste 'jig rten chung ba'am yungs 'bru
NK058(si)001:1535: che bar mi mngon pa la sogs pa ston pas
NK058(si)001:1536: rdzu 'phrul dang / me long lta bu la sogs
NK058(si)001:1537: pa'i ye shes chen po lnga la mnga' brnyes pas
NK058(si)001:1538: don mdzad pa'i phyir ye shes dang /
NK058(si)001:1539: ji lta ba dang ji snyed pa ma lus pa
NK058(si)001:1540: mngon sum du mkhyen pas chos la dbang ba ste
NK058(si)001:1542: yo byad skye ba tshe la dbang //
NK058(si)001:1543: ye shes chos dang sems dang las //
NK058(si)001:1544: rdzu 'phrul smon lam chos rnams kyis //
NK058(si)001:1545: khams gsum kun gyi dbang phyug rgyal //
NK058(si)001:1547: phrin las sna tshogs kyis 'gro ba 'dul zhing thogs
NK058(si)001:1548: pa med pa'i ye shes gsum dang so so yang
NK058(si)001:1549: dag rig pa bzhis don mdzad pa'i brdar byang du
NK058(si)001:1550: nam mkha' lding ste shang shang gi khri dang ldan
NK058(si)001:1551: pa'o // thogs pa med pa'i ye shes gsum ni /
NK058(si)001:1554: da ltar byung ba'i dus la ma chags ma thogs
NK058(si)001:1555: pa'i ye shes kyi gzigs pa 'jug pa gsum mo
NK058(si)001:1557: chos thams cad kyi ngo bo rgyu dang 'bras bu mtha' dag mkhyen pas chos dang /
NK058(si)001:1558: de'i don brjod tshul du mas ston pas tshig dang /
NK058(si)001:1559: lha la sogs pa sems can gyi skad mkhyen pa ston pas skad dang /
NK058(si)001:1560: chos 'chad pa na 'khor ba la mi 'jigs pas
NK058(si)001:1561: spobs pa so so yang dag rig pa bzhi ste
NK058(si)001:1563: rten dang brten pa bshad bya dang //
NK058(si)001:1564: gsung dang mkhyen pa 'chad byed la //
NK058(si)001:1565: blo gros rtag thogs mi mnga' ba'i //
NK058(si)001:1566: legs ston khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK058(si)001:1568: gzhan yang gdan de dag gi nges pa 'ga' zhig rin po che dbang gi rgyud las 'byung ba /
NK058(si)001:1569: sku ni mi 'jigs bdud bzhi rab tu 'joms //
NK058(si)001:1570: de grub rtags su seng ge'i khri la bzhugs //
NK058(si)001:1571: thugs ni stobs bcu mi dge bcu rnams 'dul //
NK058(si)001:1572: de grub rtags su glang chen khri la bzhugs //
NK058(si)001:1573: yon tan rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhis chags med bgrod //
NK058(si)001:1574: de grub rtags su rta mchog khri la bzhugs //
NK058(si)001:1575: gsung ni dbang bcu mthar phyin rgyal ba'i tshul //
NK058(si)001:1576: de grub rtags su rma bya'i khri la bzhugs //
NK058(si)001:1577: las ni phrin las rnam bzhis skye bzhi sgrol //
NK058(si)001:1578: de grub rtags su mkha' lding khri la bzhugs //
NK058(si)001:1580: sems nyid dang chos sku ye nas rang bzhin gyis
NK058(si)001:1581: 'od gsal zhing thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa
NK058(si)001:1583: nyes pa'i skyon thams cad kyis gos pa med pa'i brdar sna tshogs pad+ma ste /
NK058(si)001:1584: de dag gi rgyu 'dod rgu 'byung ba'i rin po che las grub pa'i gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK058(si)001:1585: de yang khri lnga'i steng na pad+ma dang nyi zlas
NK058(si)001:1586: spras pa ni gtso bo rnams kyi gdan yin la
NK058(si)001:1587: / 'khor la ni so so'i gnas su pad+ma dang nyi zla'i gdan re re'o //
NK058(si)001:1588: gnyis pa ston pa phun sum tshogs pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:1593: gang gi rigs yin ngos gzung ba /
NK058(si)001:1594: gzhan gyi log rtog dgag pa'o //
NK058(si)001:1596: spyir de bzhin nyid du mngon par byang chub pa 'bras bu'i skabs su dbye na rigs lnga ste /
NK058(si)001:1602: de dag kyang re re zhing sku dang /
NK058(si)001:1606: phrin las kyi rigs lnga lnga ste nyi shu rtsa lnga'o //
NK058(si)001:1607: de bzhin du rigs lnga sku gsung thugs su dbye bas rigs brgya dang /
NK058(si)001:1610: grangs med pa'i bar du 'gyur te /
NK058(si)001:1612: rigs ni rnam lnga rab dbye bas //
NK058(si)001:1613: brgya stong bye ba grangs med de //
NK058(si)001:1614: nam mkha' bzhin du bsam las so //
NK058(si)001:1616: de ltar rigs so sor dbye na /
NK058(si)001:1617: dkyil 'khor de'i gtso bo ni rigs de nyid kyis bsdus pa'i thugs kyi rigs te /
NK058(si)001:1619: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor rnams la ni //
NK058(si)001:1620: rigs bdag thugs te rigs kyi gtso //
NK058(si)001:1622: yang de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi thugs rnam par snang mdzad mthing ga /
NK058(si)001:1623: sku rdo rje sems dpa' dkar po /
NK058(si)001:1624: gsung snang ba mtha' yas dmar po /
NK058(si)001:1625: yon tan rin cen 'byung ldan ser po /
NK058(si)001:1626: phrin las don yod grub pa ljang gu'o //
NK058(si)001:1627: rdo rje'i rigs la thugs mi bskyod pa mthing ga /
NK058(si)001:1628: sku rnam par snang mdzad dkar po /
NK058(si)001:1629: gzhan rnams so so'i mdog go /
NK058(si)001:1630: pad+ma'i rigs la gsung gi thugs snang mtha' mthing ga /
NK058(si)001:1631: gsung gi sku rnam par snang mdzad dkar po /
NK058(si)001:1632: gsung gi gsung mi bskyod pa dmar po /
NK058(si)001:1633: gsung gi yon tan dang phrin las ser ljang ngo //
NK058(si)001:1635: rin po che'i thugs rin 'byung mthing ga /
NK058(si)001:1636: yon tan mi bskyod pa ser po /
NK058(si)001:1637: gzhan gsum so so'i mdog go //
NK058(si)001:1638: las kyi rigs la las kyi thugs don grub mthing ga /
NK058(si)001:1639: phrin las mi bskyod pa ljang gu /
NK058(si)001:1640: gzhan ni so so'i mdog go //
NK058(si)001:1641: dbye ba 'di ni thun mong ma yin pa'i rgyud kyi dgongs pa'o //
NK058(si)001:1642: de'i tshe thugs kyi rigs kyi ye shes kyang me
NK058(si)001:1643: long lta bu gtso la gzhan bzhi bzhis mtshon pa
NK058(si)001:1644: ste / de bzhin gshegs pa'i skabs su thugs rnam snang me long ye shes /
NK058(si)001:1645: thugs kyi sku mi bskyod pa chos dbyings ye shes /
NK058(si)001:1648: phrin las don yod bya grub /
NK058(si)001:1649: rdo rje'i rigs la thugs mi bskyod pa me long ye shes /
NK058(si)001:1650: sku rnam snang chos dbyings ye shes /
NK058(si)001:1651: zhes pa'i tshul gyis gsungs so //
NK058(si)001:1652: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni //
NK058(si)001:1653: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK058(si)001:1654: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:1655: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid //
NK058(si)001:1657: 'gro ba'i rtog tshogs byang chub sems //
NK058(si)001:1658: zhes pa la sogs pas ma dag pa 'khor ba'i
NK058(si)001:1659: gnas skabs na yang ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin du
NK058(si)001:1660: ye nas sangs rgyas par 'dod de /
NK058(si)001:1661: re zhig zab mo'i mdo sde sdong po bkod pa las kyang /
NK058(si)001:1662: gang zhig bdag dang sangs rgyas rnams //
NK058(si)001:1663: rang bzhin mnyam par rab gnas shing //
NK058(si)001:1664: mi gnas len pa med pa de //
NK058(si)001:1665: de dag bde bar gshegs par 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:1666: gzugs dang tshor ba 'du shes dang //
NK058(si)001:1667: rnam par shes dang sems dpa' dag /
NK058(si)001:1668: grangs med de bzhin gshegs pa rnams //
NK058(si)001:1669: de dag thub pa chen por 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:1671: dri ma med pa'i mdo las kyang /
NK058(si)001:1672: 'jig tshogs la blta ba ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i gdung ngo //
NK058(si)001:1674: skam sa las pad+ma mi skye'i /
NK058(si)001:1676: 'dus ma byas mngon du byas pa rnams las bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi sems mi skye'i /
NK058(si)001:1677: 'jig tshogs la blta ba ri bo lta bu bskyed
NK058(si)001:1678: na bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi sems skye
NK058(si)001:1679: bar 'gyur bar / de bas na nyon mongs pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i gdung ngo //
NK058(si)001:1681: thabs kyi zhags pa'i bsrung ba med pa'i dam tshig gi skabs las kyang /
NK058(si)001:1682: 'di ltar gti mug ni rnam par mi rtog pa'i khongs su 'dus pas /
NK058(si)001:1683: spang blang med pa'i mtshan nyid ni sku de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs so //
NK058(si)001:1684: zhe sdang ni chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos bzhin
NK058(si)001:1685: du gdug pa 'dul ba'i mtshan nyid rdo rje'i rigs
NK058(si)001:1686: so // nga rgyal ni chos mnyam pa nyid la
NK058(si)001:1687: sran tshugs pa'i mtshan nyid rin po che'i rigs so
NK058(si)001:1688: so // // 'dod chags ni chos thams cad la mnga' brnyes pa'i mtshan nyid pad+ma'i rigs so //
NK058(si)001:1689: phrag dog ni chos mnyam par ma rtogs pa rnams
NK058(si)001:1690: la las dge sdig yod phyir 'gro ba'i don byed
NK058(si)001:1691: pa'i mtshan nyid las kyi rigs so //
NK058(si)001:1694: gzugs kyi gti mug nyid bstan pa //
NK058(si)001:1695: blun pas bcings pa'i ngo bo'o //
NK058(si)001:1696: tshor ba 'dod pas myos bstan pa //
NK058(si)001:1697: nga rgyal gyi ni ngo bo'o //
NK058(si)001:1699: dngos po la ni chags pa'i mtshan //
NK058(si)001:1700: 'du byed rtag tu phrag dog ste //
NK058(si)001:1701: rtse gcig bdag nyid bstod pa'o //
NK058(si)001:1702: rnam shes zhe sdang zhes bstan te //
NK058(si)001:1703: rgyu dang 'bras bur rab tu grags //
NK058(si)001:1704: 'di dag bde gshegs lnga yi rigs //
NK058(si)001:1706: rin chen sems las phyir gyur pa'i //
NK058(si)001:1707: sangs rgyas med cing sems can med //
NK058(si)001:1708: ces pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK058(si)001:1709: 'o na 'gro ba'i khams rnams ma dag pa sna tshogs su snang ba ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK058(si)001:1710: ye nas dag cing dri ma med kyang /
NK058(si)001:1711: glo bur kun tu btags pa'i rtog pas sbags pas
NK058(si)001:1712: las dang bde sdug sna tshogs su kun gzhi la
NK058(si)001:1713: nus pa sna tshogs bzhag pa las byung ba'o //
NK058(si)001:1715: thams cad pa ste kun gyi rten yin par /
NK058(si)001:1717: kun gzhi kun gyi rten yin te //
NK058(si)001:1718: srid pa dang ni de bzhin du //
NK058(si)001:1719: rnam par byang ba'i gzhi ma'ang yin //
NK058(si)001:1721: de yang ma dag pa 'khor bar snang dus de'i rten byed cing dbyer med pa bzhin yod kyang /
NK058(si)001:1722: dag pa'i chos kyi de nyid chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes bya bar ming gyur pa'o //
NK058(si)001:1723: de nyid la ni ye shes kun brten to //
NK058(si)001:1724: 'khor ba'i kun gzhi la ni kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa dang /
NK058(si)001:1727: sgo lnga'i rnam shes brten to //
NK058(si)001:1728: 'di dag mdo rgyud la lar sbyangs shing gnas gyur pas ye shes lngar dag par 'dod do //
NK058(si)001:1729: kun gzhi chos dbyings ye shes su gnas gyur /
NK058(si)001:1730: de bzhin du kun gzhi'i rnam shes me long ye shes /
NK058(si)001:1731: nyon yid so sor rtog pa /
NK058(si)001:1733: sgo lnga'i rnam shes bya ba grub pa'i ye shes su gnas gyur pa'o //
NK058(si)001:1734: de bzhin du gzugs rnam snang /
NK058(si)001:1738: rnam par shes pa'i phung po mi bskyod par gnas gyur cing /
NK058(si)001:1743: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug mar gnas gyur la /
NK058(si)001:1744: dbang po dang yul rnams ni sems dpa' dang sems ma'i ngo bor gnas gyur cing /
NK058(si)001:1745: sgo gsum 'dzin pa dang bcas pa sgo bar gnas gyur par grags kyang /
NK058(si)001:1747: snam bu tshos kyis bsgyur ba lta bu'i sbyang gzhi
NK058(si)001:1748: sbyong byed gnas gyur pa lta bu mi 'dod de
NK058(si)001:1749: / spang blang dang sbyong bsgyur las 'das pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:1750: de bas na ye nas ye shes su yin pa
NK058(si)001:1751: la yin par shes pas 'khor ba'i kun rtog ye
NK058(si)001:1752: shes su grol ba chab rom chur zhu ba'i tshul
NK058(si)001:1753: gyis / 'khor ba nyid myang 'das su grol bar 'dod do //
NK058(si)001:1754: de'ang da lta kun tu btags pa'i dri mas sel
NK058(si)001:1755: du gyur pas dag kyang ma dag pa ltar snang
NK058(si)001:1756: ba nyid gnad zab mo la goms pas kun rtog
NK058(si)001:1757: phung po dang bcas pa ye shes su gyur nas
NK058(si)001:1758: / dri ma spangs nas dbyings su dag pa ni dper na /
NK058(si)001:1759: gser dang 'dres pa'i dngul chu'i gong bu re zhig
NK058(si)001:1760: mar gsar ram dngul chu'i rnam par snang gi gser
NK058(si)001:1761: du mi snang yang me dang 'phrad pa'i rkyen kyis
NK058(si)001:1763: dngul chu'i rnam par mar gsar gyi kha dog nyid rang yal du song ba bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:1764: de bas na me la cher bsregs pa na 'dzam bu chu bo'i gser ltar snang ngo //
NK058(si)001:1765: de bzhin du lam zab mo goms pas nyon mongs
NK058(si)001:1766: pa las grol ba'i 'phags pa rig 'dzin gyi gnas
NK058(si)001:1767: skabs dang / lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin sangs rgyas kyi sar shes par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:1768: gnyis pa gang gi rigs yin ngos gzung ba ni /
NK058(si)001:1769: skabs 'di'i dkyil 'khor ni rdo rje'i rigs su byas nas /
NK058(si)001:1770: gtso bo mi bskyod par snga rabs pa dag gi bshad kyang /
NK058(si)001:1772: dbus su rigs kyi bdag po mtshon byed kyi gdan 'khor lo dang seng ge byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK058(si)001:1773: yum kyang nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK058(si)001:1774: zhi ba'i mdangs las 'phros pa'i khro bo'i skabs su
NK058(si)001:1775: yang gtso bo bud+d+ha he ru ka byung ba'i phyir
NK058(si)001:1776: dang / dkyil 'khor 'di yang ye shes rang snang
NK058(si)001:1777: ba gzhi la gtso 'khor ma 'khrugs par 'chad cing
NK058(si)001:1778: snang ba'i skabs yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK058(si)001:1779: slob dpon chen po pad+mas 'di'i sgrub thabs dang dbang bskur ba'i cho ga las kyang /
NK058(si)001:1781: me long ye shes rnam dag cing //
NK058(si)001:1782: rnam par snang mdzad bcom ldan 'das //
NK058(si)001:1783: dbyings kyi dbang phyug phyag rgya yis //
NK058(si)001:1784: rigs kyi bu la dbang bskur ro //
NK058(si)001:1785: zhes pa'i yi ges kyang gnod la /
NK058(si)001:1786: thun mong ma yin pa'i rgyud kyi sde tshan gcig
NK058(si)001:1787: pa 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i 'grel pa pad+ma
NK058(si)001:1789: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi bdag nyid rnam par snang mdzad mthing ga dang /
NK058(si)001:1790: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyi bdag nyid mi bskyod pa dkar por gsungs pa dang 'gal lo //
NK058(si)001:1791: 'o na rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes bshad pas mi bskyod par 'thad do //
NK058(si)001:1794: lha mo sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes bshad pas gtso
NK058(si)001:1795: bo lha mor thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon spangs
NK058(si)001:1797: des na rdorje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ni rigs thams cad kyi spyi'i sgrar bshad kyi /
NK058(si)001:1798: mi bskyod pa kho nar 'chad pa ma yin te /
NK058(si)001:1800: rdo rje sems dpa' rigs rnams kun gyi bdag /
NK058(si)001:1801: rigs dang dkyil 'khor kun gyi bdag por shog /
NK058(si)001:1802: ces pas dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo gang yin rdo rje sems dpar btags pa'i tshul dang gcig go //
NK058(si)001:1804: gzhi bstod la sogs pa ni bod ma yin pas yid brtan mi rung ngo //
NK058(si)001:1806: dbus su rnam par snang mdzad gtso //
NK058(si)001:1807: zhes pa'ang ma mthong bar zad do //
NK058(si)001:1808: de bas na 'dir de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs kyi
NK058(si)001:1809: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor yin pas gtso bo ni rnam
NK058(si)001:1810: par snang mdzad thugs kyi lha yin la /
NK058(si)001:1811: mi bskyod pa sku rdo rje'i bdag nyid do //
NK058(si)001:1812: gsum pa gzhan gyi log rtog dgag pa ni /
NK058(si)001:1814: gzugs ni rnam par snang mdzad nyid //
NK058(si)001:1815: tshor ba rin chen 'byung ldan la //
NK058(si)001:1816: 'du shes snang ba mtha' yas te //
NK058(si)001:1817: 'du byed don yod grub pa nyid //
NK058(si)001:1818: rnam par shes pa mi bskyod pa //
NK058(si)001:1820: sku mdog kyang mthing gar bshad pas 'gal lo zhe na /
NK058(si)001:1822: kye bzhin bzang da dung thun mong dang thun mong
NK058(si)001:1823: ma yin pa'i rgyud sde gong 'og la blo kha
NK058(si)001:1825: de lta na'ang khyed cag rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang zhes pa dang /
NK058(si)001:1826: mthing ga dang zhes pa'i sgra tsam la 'khrul bar zad de /
NK058(si)001:1827: 'dir ni 'og min rdo rjee dbyings dang /
NK058(si)001:1828: snying ga na 'od gsal gyi dam pa rigs brgya
NK058(si)001:1829: 'od lnga'i klong na de nyid dang tha dad med
NK058(si)001:1830: par yod par rang lugs 'jug pa ste /
NK058(si)001:1831: snying gi dgongs pa'i rgyud las /
NK058(si)001:1832: rnam par snang mdzad mthing ga phyag na 'khor lo
NK058(si)001:1833: bsnams pa yum nam mkha' dbyings phyug ma dang zhal
NK058(si)001:1834: sbyar nas sangs rgyas kyi sku drug phrag gcig tu
NK058(si)001:1836: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po zhes pa dang /
NK058(si)001:1837: mthing gar gsungs pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs kyi thugs kyi rigs yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:1838: gzhan las rnam snang gzugs te sku'i rigs dang mi
NK058(si)001:1839: bskyod pa thugs su bshad pa ni thun mong ba'i
NK058(si)001:1841: rigs lnga spyi tsam dang sku'i sku'i dkyil 'khor la
NK058(si)001:1842: sogs pa rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor las gzhan du 'phros
NK058(si)001:1844: gzhan yang nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma ni
NK058(si)001:1845: sems nyid rang bzhin gyis dag pas go 'byed pa
NK058(si)001:1846: yin la / rnam par shes pa ni sna tshogs
NK058(si)001:1847: su gsal zhing 'char bas rnam par snang mdzad de
NK058(si)001:1848: me long gi gzugs brnyan 'dzin pa lta bu'i ye
NK058(si)001:1849: yin la / shes so // sangs rgyas spyan ni
NK058(si)001:1850: mi g.yo zhing rtog pa med pas gti mug dang
NK058(si)001:1851: chos mthun pa'i phyir chos kyi dbyings kyi spyod yul
NK058(si)001:1852: sa'i khams kyii sra ba'i cha gzugs kyi phung pos
NK058(si)001:1853: bsdus pa ni gzhan du mi 'pho bas mi bskyod
NK058(si)001:1855: tshul 'di ni rgyud sde gong ma'i rnam bshad de gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa'o //
NK058(si)001:1856: de bas na gtso bo rnam par snang mdzad la
NK058(si)001:1857: rigs kyi 'khor tshom bu rnams kyis bskor ba'i dkyil
NK058(si)001:1859: de la kun gyi thugs rjes mnga' bdag ston pa
NK058(si)001:1860: kun tu bzang po yab yum dkyil 'khor 'di'i phyogs
NK058(si)001:1861: gang na yod pa yin zhe na /
NK058(si)001:1862: kha cig na re khyams na byin gyis rlob pa'i tshul du bzhugs zer ro //
NK058(si)001:1863: de ni ma yin te 'khor du thal ba dang /
NK058(si)001:1864: gtso bo mthar gnas pa thun mong dang thun mong
NK058(si)001:1865: ma yin pa'i dkyil 'khor gang las kyang mi 'byung
NK058(si)001:1866: ba'i phyir na rigs pa ma yin no //
NK058(si)001:1867: de bas na 'di ltar yin te /
NK058(si)001:1868: chos sku'i gnas skabs na rang byung gi ye shes
NK058(si)001:1869: chen po nyid dmigs sam spros pa'i yul las 'das
NK058(si)001:1870: par bzhugs pas kun tu bzang po yab yum zhes
NK058(si)001:1871: bya'o // de skad du dpal sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las /
NK058(si)001:1872: sems dpa' sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK058(si)001:1873: rdo rje sems dpa' bde ba'i mchog /
NK058(si)001:1874: gsang ba mchog gi dgyes pa na //
NK058(si)001:1875: thams cad bdag nyid rtag tu bzhugs //
NK058(si)001:1877: slob dpon chen po bi ma la'i rin po che'i sgron ma las /
NK058(si)001:1878: mi gnas chos dbyings dkyil 'khor na /
NK058(si)001:1879: kun bzang yab yum zhes bya'o //
NK058(si)001:1880: de las longs sku bzhengs pa na /
NK058(si)001:1881: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas yin par grags //
NK058(si)001:1882: sprul pas 'gro don spyod pa na //
NK058(si)001:1883: rdo rje sems dpa' rdo rje 'dzin //
NK058(si)001:1884: grangs med dpag gis mi lang ngo //
NK058(si)001:1885: zhes gsungs pa ltar longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:1886: du rang snang ba'i tshe rigs lnga'i gtso bo nyid
NK058(si)001:1887: rnam snang ste kun bzang yab yum mo //
NK058(si)001:1888: dmigs pa la dga' bas bsgom pa'i tshe de'i ton pa kar bsgom pa'i rim pa yang gsungs so //
NK058(si)001:1891: de nyid rigs rnams lngar snang yang //
NK058(si)001:1892: yang dag grub pa gcig pu nyid //
NK058(si)001:1893: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du sbyar //
NK058(si)001:1895: de las sprul pas 'gro ba 'dul ba na phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK058(si)001:1897: spyan ras gzigs la sogs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:1898: thub pa drug gi rol pa dpag tu med pa snang ngo //
NK058(si)001:1899: khyams su dgod par gsungs pa'i byed pa dang /
NK058(si)001:1900: bya ba gnyis ni gdangs thams cad 'char ba'i gzhi'i kun bzang yab yum zhes bya ste /
NK058(si)001:1901: bar do la sogs par thog mar chos dbyings rnam
NK058(si)001:1902: dag gi gdangs snang stong gnyis kyi rnam pa de
NK058(si)001:1904: rim gyis zhi khro'i lha so so'i tshom bu 'char ba'i gzhir gyur pa ste /
NK058(si)001:1905: khyams su gsungs pa'i don ni gtso bo'i thugs ka ste /
NK058(si)001:1906: rgyab mdun ni zhal sbyar nas bzhugs tshul gyi ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK058(si)001:1907: de bas na gzhi'i gtso bo ni dbus kyi gtso bo nyid yin la /
NK058(si)001:1908: gdangs kyi yab yum gnyis ni de'i thugs ka na
NK058(si)001:1909: gnas pa ste snang stong gnyis su med pa'i ye
NK058(si)001:1910: shes yin no // tshul 'di ni thun mong ma yin pa'i rgyud dang /
NK058(si)001:1912: sgrub thabs kyi yi ge chen po rnams las byung ba yin no //
NK058(si)001:1913: da lta gnas kyang zhi ba snying ga yin te nyi zla kha sbyor gyi rgyud las /
NK058(si)001:1914: tsit+ta rin chen gzhal yas na //
NK058(si)001:1915: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK058(si)001:1916: sku ni snang ba rang bzhin med //
NK058(si)001:1917: cha phra 'od gsal snying khar bzhugs //
NK058(si)001:1919: khro bo lnga bcu rtsa brgyad ni spyi bo na yod de /
NK058(si)001:1921: gdangs kyi khrag 'thung lnga bcu brgyad //
NK058(si)001:1922: dung khang b+han+d+ha'i gzhal yas na //
NK058(si)001:1924: tshul 'di ni slob dpon gyi bde gshegs 'dus pa'i bskyed rdzogs 'bring po'i las byang las /
NK058(si)001:1925: zhi ba lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor na //
NK058(si)001:1927: b+han+d+ha smug nag 'bar ba'i khang bzang du //
NK058(si)001:1928: mthu chen bdud kyi rgyal pos sgo bcad brtsigs //
NK058(si)001:1929: rngams pa'i khro bo rnams kyi gzer gyis btab //
NK058(si)001:1930: dregs pa lha chen brgyad kyi ka gdung bcas //
NK058(si)001:1931: gdug pa'i klu chen brgyad kyis rab tu gtams //
NK058(si)001:1932: gza' chen kha bad rgyu skar mig tshags byas //
NK058(si)001:1934: b+han+d+ha ni mgo ste skra smug nag can no //
NK058(si)001:1935: gzhan ni mtshog gsang gnyis dang ltag gsang gnyis kyi sdud sgo dang rtsa'i gnas so //
NK058(si)001:1937: gnyis pa gzhung gi don la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:1938: gtso bo'i bzhugs tshul dang phyag mtshan thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK058(si)001:1939: yab yum so sor bshad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:1941: sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin 'gro ba thams cad la
NK058(si)001:1942: dus rtag tu gzigs shing rgyab kyis mi phyogs pa'i
NK058(si)001:1943: mtshon byed du dwangs shing 'od kyi rang bzhin phyi
NK058(si)001:1944: nang gsal ba'i sku de yang rags par ma grub
NK058(si)001:1945: cing thugs rje chen po'i rang bzhin gyi phyogs mtshams
NK058(si)001:1946: steng 'og gang nas bltas kyang zhal bstan par snang
NK058(si)001:1947: gi 'di ni mdun dang 'di ni rgyab tu snang
NK058(si)001:1948: ngo zhes 'gro ba phal pa la mthong ba ltar
NK058(si)001:1949: med pa tshom bu'i 'khor thams cad la mdun gyis
NK058(si)001:1950: gzigs pas phyogs thams cad du zhal gyi dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:1952: sku la skyes bu chen po'i mtshan bzang po sum
NK058(si)001:1953: cu rtsa gnyis dang dpe byad bzang po brgyad cus
NK058(si)001:1954: ye shes dang yon tan phun sum tshogs pa mnga'
NK058(si)001:1955: ba'i mtshon byed du ldan pa'o //
NK058(si)001:1957: thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK058(si)001:1960: mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis ni ye shes bcu drug gi rtsal sems dpa' bcu drug dang /
NK058(si)001:1961: de'i yul chos dbyings bcu drug gi rtsal sems ma bcu drug ste sum cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK058(si)001:1962: dpe byad brgyad cu ni sems dpa' bcu drug po
NK058(si)001:1963: re re la'ang ye shes lnga'i rtags rigs lnga lngas
NK058(si)001:1964: dbu rgyan gyi rigs lnga brgyad cu'o //
NK058(si)001:1965: yum bcu drug la dbu rgyan med de /
NK058(si)001:1966: chos dbyings mtshon pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:1967: de dag mtshan dper 'jog pa ni /
NK058(si)001:1968: 'khor phun sum tshogs pas gtso bo'i rang bzhin yang bkod pa mdzes shing phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK058(si)001:1969: me tog gi ze'u 'bru dang 'dab mas me tog gis bkod pa mdzes par byed pa lta bu'o //
NK058(si)001:1970: gnyis pa thun mong gi mtshan dpe la gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:1971: mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis ni /
NK058(si)001:1973: phyag zhabs 'khor los mtshan dang rus sbal zhabs //
NK058(si)001:1974: phyag dang zhabs sor d+r+wa bas 'brel ba dang //
NK058(si)001:1975: phyag dang zhabs bcas 'jam zhing gzhon sha chags //
NK058(si)001:1976: 'di yi sku ni bdun dag mtho ba dang //
NK058(si)001:1977: sor mo ring dang rting yangs sku che drang //
NK058(si)001:1978: zhabs 'bur mi mngon spu ni gyen du phyogs //
NK058(si)001:1979: byin pa e na ya 'dra phyag ring mdzes //
NK058(si)001:1980: 'doms kyi lba ba sbubs su nub pa'i mchog /
NK058(si)001:1981: pags pa gser mdog pags pa srab pa dang //
NK058(si)001:1982: spu ni re re nas g.yas legs 'khrungs dang //
NK058(si)001:1983: zhal mdzod spus brgyan ro stod seng ge 'dra //
NK058(si)001:1984: 'di yi dpung pa'i mgo zlum thal gong rgyas //
NK058(si)001:1985: 'di la ro mi zhim pa'ang ro mchog snang //
NK058(si)001:1986: sku ni nya gro ta ltar chu zheng gab //
NK058(si)001:1987: gtsug tor dbur ldan ljags ring mdzes pa dang //
NK058(si)001:1988: tshangs dbyangs 'gram pa seng ge 'dra dang tshems //
NK058(si)001:1989: shin tu dkar dang tshad mnyam thags bzang dang //
NK058(si)001:1990: grangs ni bzhi bcu tham pa tshang ba dang //
NK058(si)001:1991: spyan ni mthon mthing spyan rdzi ba mchog gi /
NK058(si)001:1992: 'dra ba 'di dag sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan //
NK058(si)001:1996: thub pa'i sen mo zangs mdog dang //
NK058(si)001:1997: mdog snum mtho dang sor mo rnams //
NK058(si)001:1998: zlum rgyas byin gyis phra ba dang //
NK058(si)001:1999: rtsa mi mngon dang mdud pa med //
NK058(si)001:2000: long bu mi mngon zhabs mnyam dang //
NK058(si)001:2001: seng ge glang chen bya dang ni //
NK058(si)001:2002: khyu mchog stabs gshegs g.yas phyogs dang //
NK058(si)001:2003: mdzes gshegs drang dang 'khril bag chags //
NK058(si)001:2005: gtsang dang 'jam dang dag pa'i sku //
NK058(si)001:2006: mtshan ni yongs su rdzogs pa dang //
NK058(si)001:2007: sku yi kho lag yangs shing bzang //
NK058(si)001:2008: gom snyoms pa dang spyan gnyis ni //
NK058(si)001:2009: dag dang gzhon sha can nyid dang //
NK058(si)001:2010: sku zhum med dang rgyas pa dang //
NK058(si)001:2011: shin tu grims pa'i sku nyid dang //
NK058(si)001:2012: yan lag shin tu rnam 'byes dang //
NK058(si)001:2013: gzigs pa sgrib med dag pa dang //
NK058(si)001:2014: sku zlum skabs phyin ma rnyongs dang //
NK058(si)001:2015: phyang nge ba dang lte ba ni //
NK058(si)001:2016: zab dang g.yas phyogs 'khyil ba dang //
NK058(si)001:2017: kun nas blta na sdug pa dang //
NK058(si)001:2018: kun spyod gtsang dang sku la ni //
NK058(si)001:2019: sme ba nag bag med pa dang //
NK058(si)001:2020: phyag ni shing bal ltar 'jam dang //
NK058(si)001:2021: phyag ris mdangs yod zabs ring dang //
NK058(si)001:2022: zhal ni ha cang mi ring dang //
NK058(si)001:2023: mchu ni bim pa ltar dmar dang //
NK058(si)001:2024: ljags mnyen pa dang srab pa dang //
NK058(si)001:2025: dmar dang 'brug gi sgra nyid dang //
NK058(si)001:2026: gsung snyan 'jam dang mche ba zlum //
NK058(si)001:2027: rno dang dkar dang mnyam pa dang //
NK058(si)001:2028: byin gyi phra dang shangs mtho dang //
NK058(si)001:2029: mchog tu dag pa nyid dang ni //
NK058(si)001:2030: spyan yangs pa dang rdzi ma stug /
NK058(si)001:2032: smin mtshams ring dang 'jam pa dang //
NK058(si)001:2033: snum dang spu ni mnyam pa dang //
NK058(si)001:2034: phyag ring rgyas dang snyan mnyam dang //
NK058(si)001:2035: nyams pa rnam par spangs pa dang //
NK058(si)001:2036: dpral ba legs par 'byes pa dang //
NK058(si)001:2037: dbyes che ba dang dbu rgyas dang //
NK058(si)001:2038: dbu skra bung ba ltar gnag dang //
NK058(si)001:2040: mi gshor dri zhim skyes bu yi //
NK058(si)001:2041: yid ni 'phrog par byed pa dang //
NK058(si)001:2042: dpal gyi be'u dang bkra shis ni //
NK058(si)001:2043: g.yung drung 'khyil bas brgyan pa ste //
NK058(si)001:2044: sangs rgyas dpe byad bzang por bzhed //
NK058(si)001:2046: dpal gyi be'u man chad gcig yin cing gzhan ni so so'o //
NK058(si)001:2049: gdul bya'i 'jig rten bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams
NK058(si)001:2050: cad du lhun gyis grub pa'i sku gsung thugs mi
NK058(si)001:2051: zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo sna tshogs par kun
NK058(si)001:2052: tu snang ba'o // ji ltar snang na chos kyi
NK058(si)001:2053: dbyings spros pa dang bral ba'i zhing khams su sku
NK058(si)001:2054: mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo chos sku kun
NK058(si)001:2055: bzang yab yum spros las 'das pa /
NK058(si)001:2056: gsung mi zad pa brjod du med pa dang mnyan
NK058(si)001:2057: du med pa dang ngo bo nyid med pa dang
NK058(si)001:2058: / thugs mi zad pa gtan du spros pa thams cad zhi zhing rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa'o //
NK058(si)001:2059: nam mkha'i khams kyi mtha' klas pa rang snang lhun stug po bkod pa'i zhing du ni /
NK058(si)001:2060: sku mi zad pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i mtshan dang
NK058(si)001:2061: dpe byad kyis brgyan pa nam mkha' dang mnyam pa
NK058(si)001:2062: / gsung mi zad pa zhal gyi dkyil 'khor las
NK058(si)001:2063: 'od 'phros pas brjod bya'i don khong du chud pa
NK058(si)001:2064: / / thugs mi zad pa ye shes lnga'i mtshan nyid du bzhugs pa'o //
NK058(si)001:2065: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten 'gro ba drug gi 'dul zhing nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa rnams su ni /
NK058(si)001:2066: sku mi zad pa gang la gang gis 'dul ba sangs rgyas dang /
NK058(si)001:2068: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas dang /
NK058(si)001:2075: dud 'gro la sogs pa rigs mthun pa dang mi mthun pa dang /
NK058(si)001:2080: skyed mos tshal la sogs pa sems can la phan
NK058(si)001:2081: pa 'byung ba de dang de'i gzugs tshad med pa
NK058(si)001:2082: dang / gsung mi zad pa 'gro ba so so'i skad dang /
NK058(si)001:2083: pad+mo dang dpag bsam gyi shing la sogs pa las
NK058(si)001:2084: sgra byung bas chos kyi gsung sna tshogs par sgrogs
NK058(si)001:2086: thugs mi zad pa ji lta ba dang ji snyed
NK058(si)001:2087: pa mkhyen pas 'gro ba'i don mdzad par snang ngo
NK058(si)001:2088: // de'ang sangs rgyas rnams kyi rnam par 'phrul pa
NK058(si)001:2089: bsam gyis mi khyab pas don mdzad pa yin pas
NK058(si)001:2090: 'di dang 'adi'o zhes blos bsam par nus pa ma
NK058(si)001:2091: // yin no // 'o na chos sku dang longs
NK058(si)001:2092: sku'i gsung mi brjod pa la gsung du ci gdags
NK058(si)001:2093: // yin no // she na / sgra dang tshig
NK058(si)001:2094: tu brjod pa'i mthar yang brjod med go bar bya
NK058(si)001:2096: de nyid kyis dngos su brjod med go bar mdzad pa dang /
NK058(si)001:2097: tshig thams cad yi ger 'dus la de nyid a
NK058(si)001:2098: skye ba med par 'dus pas gsung gi snying po
NK058(si)001:2099: a'i don ston pa nyid gsung mchog chen po ste
NK058(si)001:2101: rgyal ba'i sras po cang mi gsung //
NK058(si)001:2102: ma gsungs pa nyid rgya cher gsungs //
NK058(si)001:2104: gdul bya la snang ba'i sprul sku thub pas yan
NK058(si)001:2105: lag drug cu'i dbyangs kyis gsungs pa lta bu yang
NK058(si)001:2106: gdul bya'i snang ba dang sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje
NK058(si)001:2107: 'dzom pa las gsung du snang yang sgra brnyan ltar
NK058(si)001:2108: don la gsungs pa med de /
NK058(si)001:2110: ji ltar sgra brnyan gyi ni sgra //
NK058(si)001:2111: gzhan gyis rnam rig las byung ba //
NK058(si)001:2112: rnam rtog med cing gzo med pa //
NK058(si)001:2113: de ltar de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung //
NK058(si)001:2114: gzhan gyi rnam rig las byung ba //
NK058(si)001:2115: phyi dang nang na'ang gnas ma yin //
NK058(si)001:2118: de bzhin gshegs pa sku bltams nas gang gi mtshan
NK058(si)001:2119: mo la myang ngan las 'das pa de srid du
NK058(si)001:2120: tshig dang yi ger snang bas chos tshig 'bru gcig
NK058(si)001:2121: kyang ma gsungs te gdul bya'i snang bas go bar
NK058(si)001:2123: 'di kha cig gis sprul sku kho na la sbyor
NK058(si)001:2124: ba mi 'thad de bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams
NK058(si)001:2125: cad du sku gsung thugs snang bar bshad pa nyid
NK058(si)001:2126: dang 'gal lo // sprul sku'i sgras skabs 'dir thub
NK058(si)001:2127: pa drug kyang zin pas thub drug gi gleng gzhi
NK058(si)001:2128: zhar la smos pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:2129: bstan pa gcig la ston pa gnyis mi 'thad ces
NK058(si)001:2130: pa ni skabs su ma babs pa'i rgol ba ste
NK058(si)001:2131: / 'dir longs sku bzhi dang thub drug 'khor du bstan pas ston pa gnyis med do //
NK058(si)001:2132: thabs snying rje chen po dang shes rab stong pa
NK058(si)001:2133: nyid kyi ye shes mnga' ba'i brdar zhabs gnyis te
NK058(si)001:2134: zung du 'brel bas srid zhi'i mtha' la mi gnas
NK058(si)001:2135: pa'i brdar mnyam pa'i rang bzhin nyon mongs pa mtha'
NK058(si)001:2136: dag btul cing ye shes chen po'i ngo bor bzhugs
NK058(si)001:2137: pa nyid kyi brdar rdo rje'i skyil mo krung du
NK058(si)001:2138: bzhugs pa'o // 'dir kha cig yum dngos su ma bshad par 'dod pa ni mi 'atha da de /
NK058(si)001:2139: btsun mo dam pa snang ba'i dbyings yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:2140: ye shes lnga dbyings rnam par dag pa'i ye shes dang drug gi mtshon byed du phyag drug go //
NK058(si)001:2141: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las med pa'i ye
NK058(si)001:2142: shes las dgos 'dod sna tshogs 'byung bas rin po
NK058(si)001:2143: che'i rang bzhin du mtshon pa'i phyir rdo rje la
NK058(si)001:2144: sogs pa'i phyag rgya drug las 'od zer mu med
NK058(si)001:2145: pa 'bar ba can ni ser sna dang /
NK058(si)001:2150: shes rab 'chal ba drug 'joms pa'i barda'o //
NK058(si)001:2151: kha cig ni gtso bo la phyag drug /
NK058(si)001:2152: gzhan rnams la phyag gnyis par 'dod pa ni ma yin te /
NK058(si)001:2153: thun mong du gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:2154: de'ang rdo rje rin po che 'khor lo pad+ma rgya gram dril bu ste /
NK058(si)001:2155: rigs so so'i rtsa phyag gnyis kyi g.yas thams cad rang rang gi phyag mtshan /
NK058(si)001:2156: g.yon thams cad dril bu ste /
NK058(si)001:2157: thugs kar bsnol nas 'dzin pa gzhan rnams so sor brkyangs pa'o //
NK058(si)001:2158: sangs rgyas gsang ba ni phyag drug na rin po
NK058(si)001:2159: che 'bar ba zur brgyad pa drug bsnams par bzhed
NK058(si)001:2160: do // sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi
NK058(si)001:2161: 'khor lo bsam gyis mi khyab pa mnga' ba'i mtshon
NK058(si)001:2162: byed du dbu gsum dang ldan pa ni gtso bo'i
NK058(si)001:2163: rtsa zhal mthing ga g.yas dkar g.yon dmar /
NK058(si)001:2164: mi bskyod pa'i rtsa zhal dkar po g.yas mthing g.yon dmar /
NK058(si)001:2165: rin 'byung gi rtsa zhal ser po g.yas dkar g.yon dmar /
NK058(si)001:2166: 'od dpag med kyi rtsa zhal dmar po g.yas dkar g.yon mthing /
NK058(si)001:2167: don grub kyi rtsa zhal ljang gu g.yas dkar g.yon dmar ro //
NK058(si)001:2168: gnyis pa yab yum so sor bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:2172: thams cad ye nas lha'i dkyil 'khor du bstan pa dang /
NK058(si)001:2174: dang po ni rnam par snang mdzad la sogs rigs lnga'i mtshan nas mi brjod par /
NK058(si)001:2175: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang zhes pa la
NK058(si)001:2176: sogs pa phung po lnga'i mtshan nas brjod pa ci
NK058(si)001:2177: yin zhes snga rabs pa dag zer te /
NK058(si)001:2178: 'di yang ma phyed par snang ngo //
NK058(si)001:2179: phung po lnga la sogs pa rtog pa'i ming gis lha la brjod pa med de /
NK058(si)001:2180: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang zhes ldan chos
NK058(si)001:2181: phung po lnga las 'phags pa nyid bstan pa yin
NK058(si)001:2182: te / mya ngan las 'das pa chen po zhes brjod pa bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:2183: mya ngan gyi ming gis sangs rgyas la brjod pa
NK058(si)001:2184: ma yin gyi 'phags chos ngos gzung ba'i phyir dang
NK058(si)001:2186: 'dod chags chen po rjes chags pa //
NK058(si)001:2187: zhes pa'ang bde stong gnyis med kyi ye shes la brjod cing /
NK058(si)001:2189: zhe sdang rdo rje zhes pa la sogs pas me
NK058(si)001:2190: long ye shes la sogs pa dngos su bstan pa
NK058(si)001:2191: bzhin no // des na rgyal po'i sgra ni chen
NK058(si)001:2192: po ste rnam par snang mdzad la sogs pa yin
NK058(si)001:2193: bzhin no // zhing / 'khor gyi skabs su'ang byang
NK058(si)001:2194: chub chen po rdo rje thos pa la sogs pa
NK058(si)001:2195: gsungs pa la'ang shes par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:2196: gal te rtog pa'i sgras brjod na rnam par shes
NK058(si)001:2197: pa dang zhes brjod pa rigs kyi rgyal po zhes
NK058(si)001:2198: mi rigs so // khyad par 'phags chos su brjod
NK058(si)001:2199: pa ni 'khor ba'i gnas skabs na rnam par shes
NK058(si)001:2200: pa de bzhin gshegs pa de dag gi gdung ngam
NK058(si)001:2201: rigs su gnas pas brjod pa'o //
NK058(si)001:2202: de yang rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i sangs rgyas nyid
NK058(si)001:2203: yin kyang ma dag pa'i tshe 'gro ba'i phung po
NK058(si)001:2204: lnga rnam smin las grub pa ltar snang ngo //
NK058(si)001:2205: de las cung zad dag pa na dbang thob pa
NK058(si)001:2206: rnams kyi smon lam las grub pa'i lus la sogs
NK058(si)001:2207: par snang ngo // shin tu dag pa'i tshe rgyal ba'i sku dang ye shes su snang ngo //
NK058(si)001:2208: dper na chu gcig la'ang dmyal ba bas me dang /
NK058(si)001:2209: yi dwags kyis rnag khrag dang /
NK058(si)001:2210: mis dag cing 'dod yon du byed pa dang /
NK058(si)001:2213: zhing dag pa'i 'gro bas bdud rtsi'i chu klung dang /
NK058(si)001:2214: grub pas m+aa ma k+ai la sogs par snang ba nyid do //
NK058(si)001:2215: yang na dngul chu'i khams bzhin du'ang snang bar sngar brjod zin to //
NK058(si)001:2216: de'ang ma dag pa'i skabs na phung po lnga dang khams bco brgyad dang /
NK058(si)001:2217: skye mched bcu gnyis la sogs par snang ba nyid /
NK058(si)001:2218: dag pa'i tshe na rigs lnga'i sku dang /
NK058(si)001:2219: 'khor gyi sems dpa' sems ma la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor du snang ba'o //
NK058(si)001:2220: dper na mig la bad kan gyi skyon chags pa'i
NK058(si)001:2221: tshe dung ser por snang ba nyid dag pa'i tshe
NK058(si)001:2222: dkar por snang ba bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:2223: bad kan gyi tshe na'ang gzugs brnyan dung gi rnam
NK058(si)001:2224: pa mi 'dor ba bzhin du ma dag pa'i tshe'ang
NK058(si)001:2225: sangs rgyas kyi chos mthun rtsir yod do //
NK058(si)001:2226: ser por snang yang don la dkar po yin pa
NK058(si)001:2227: bzhin du phyi nang gi snang ba rtog tshogs dang
NK058(si)001:2228: bcas pa kun ma dag par snang yang don la
NK058(si)001:2229: dag pa sangs rgyas kyii zhing dang sku gsung thugs
NK058(si)001:2230: mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo nyid yin no
NK058(si)001:2231: // gnyis pa so sor dbye ba la lnga las /
NK058(si)001:2232: dang po rnam par shes pa'i phung po la dbye na brgyad de /
NK058(si)001:2233: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa me long dag pa'i
NK058(si)001:2234: ngos lta bu shes pa yul la ma 'phros la
NK058(si)001:2236: yid kyi rnam shes don spyi'i yul dang rjes kyi blos yul la spyod pa dang /
NK058(si)001:2237: nyon mongs ba can gyis yid dgag sgrub tu byed pa'i shes pa la sogs pa byed pa dang /
NK058(si)001:2238: sgo lnga'i rnam shes gzugs mthong ba la sogs pa rtog med lnga'o //
NK058(si)001:2239: de'ang mthong thos reg tshor gyi cha ni rtog med yin la /
NK058(si)001:2240: de la so sor shes pa ni yid la /
NK058(si)001:2241: de la dgag sgrub byed pa ni nyon yid do //
NK058(si)001:2242: sgo lnga dang yid shes tsam gyis ni las mi gsog la /
NK058(si)001:2243: nyon yid kyis kun gzhi'i steng du las gsog pa'o //
NK058(si)001:2244: kun gzhi ni de thams cad pa'i rten yin te rtog med lung ma bstan no //
NK058(si)001:2245: dper na gang du'ang rtog dpyod med cing gsal dwangs
NK058(si)001:2246: med pa'i shes pa rang so'i gnas skabs lta bu'o
NK058(si)001:2247: // des mtshon pa thams cad do //
NK058(si)001:2248: kun gzhi'i rnam shes ni shes pa gsal dwangs yul la ma 'phros pa'i gnas skabs so //
NK058(si)001:2249: sgo lnga ni yul de gsal bar snang ba'o //
NK058(si)001:2250: yid ni 'drer rung 'dzin pa tsam mo //
NK058(si)001:2251: nyon yid ni dgag sgrub tu skyes pa'o //
NK058(si)001:2252: 'dir ni kun gzhi'i rnam shes me long lta bu 'phags chos su bzung ngo //
NK058(si)001:2254: yul yid du 'ong ba la bde ba /
NK058(si)001:2256: bar ma la btang snyoms su skye'o //
NK058(si)001:2258: yul la 'jug pa rgya che ba /
NK058(si)001:2261: 'du byed la sems byung lnga bcu rtsa gcig ste /
NK058(si)001:2267: sems pa ste kun tu 'gro ba lnga dang /
NK058(si)001:2272: shes rab ste yul so sor nges pa lnga dang /
NK058(si)001:2279: brtson 'grus dang shin tu sbyangs pa /
NK058(si)001:2282: gti mug med pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba ste bcu gcig dge ba dang /
NK058(si)001:2288: the tshom ste drug rtsa ba'i nyon mongs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:2308: 'tshig pa ste nyi shu nye ba'i nyon mongs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:2312: dpyod pa ste bzhi ni gzhan du 'gyur ba'o //
NK058(si)001:2313: de rnams kyi nang nas tshor ba dang 'du shes las gzhan pa'i bzhi bcu rtsa dgu dang /
NK058(si)001:2314: ming dang mtshan ma la sogs pa mi ldan pa'i
NK058(si)001:2315: 'du byed 'khor 'das bskyed pa'i bya ba byed pa
NK058(si)001:2316: thams cad ni / bya ba grub pa'i ye shes
NK058(si)001:2317: kyi ngo bo don yod grub pa'i khyad par 'phags
NK058(si)001:2319: gzugs kyi phung po la dbye na bco lnga ste /
NK058(si)001:2323: rlung ste rgyu'i gzugs 'byung ba bzhi dang /
NK058(si)001:2328: reg bya ste yul lnga dang /
NK058(si)001:2333: lus kyi dbang po ste dbang po lnga dang /
NK058(si)001:2334: rnam par rig byed ma yin pa'i gzugs te bco
NK058(si)001:2335: lnga las rig byed ma yin pa ni chos kyi
NK058(si)001:2336: dbyings kyi ye shes mi bskyod pa dang gzhan bcu
NK058(si)001:2337: bzhi sangs rgyas spyan sogs kyis bsdus pa'i khyad par
NK058(si)001:2339: gnyis pa gzhung gi don la gnyis te //
NK058(si)001:2340: dbyings ngo bo nyid kyi gtso bo dang /
NK058(si)001:2341: rang bzhin tha mi dad pa'i 'khor ro //
NK058(si)001:2343: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK058(si)001:2344: de bzhin gshegs pa gzugs kyi rgyal po mi bskyod pa dang /
NK058(si)001:2345: de bzhin gshegs pa tshor ba'i rgyal po rin cen 'byung ldan dang /
NK058(si)001:2346: de bzhin gshegs pa 'du shes kyi rgyal po snang ba mtha' yas dang /
NK058(si)001:2347: de bzhin gshegs pa 'du byed kyi rgyal po don yod grub pa dang lnga'o //
NK058(si)001:2348: rigs lnga po de dag kun kyang sku mdog ni rim pa bzhin /
NK058(si)001:2349: me long lta bu'i ye shes 'gyur ba med pas rnam par snang mdzad mthing ga dang /
NK058(si)001:2350: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes dri ma thams cad dang bral bas mi bskyod pa dkar po dang /
NK058(si)001:2351: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes che ba'i yon tan
NK058(si)001:2352: du ma dang ldan pas rin cen 'byung ldan ser
NK058(si)001:2353: po dang / so sor rtog pa'i ye shes 'gro
NK058(si)001:2354: ba'i don la rjes su chags pas 'od dpag med
NK058(si)001:2355: le brgan te dmar po dang /
NK058(si)001:2356: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyis sems can gyi
NK058(si)001:2357: don sna tshogs su mdzad pas don yod grub pa
NK058(si)001:2358: ljang gu'i mdog tu gsal zhing 'tsher ba ni rigs
NK058(si)001:2359: lnga ka'i rang bzhin dwangs la bkrag dang gzi brjid
NK058(si)001:2360: che ba'o // de dag gi yum ni longs spyod
NK058(si)001:2361: par bya ba'i gzhi dang gtso bo'i yum du gyur
NK058(si)001:2362: pa dang yon tan gyis cho rigs btsun pas btsun
NK058(si)001:2363: mo gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pas dam pa'o
NK058(si)001:2364: che ba'o // // dbyings nam mkha'i rang bzhin ni
NK058(si)001:2365: chos nyid yangs shing yon tan gyi go 'byed pa
NK058(si)001:2366: la mi bsgribs pas gsal bar byed pa'i phyir snang
NK058(si)001:2367: ba'i ngo bo nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma
NK058(si)001:2368: che ba'o // // dang / sa ni brtan cing
NK058(si)001:2369: rten du gyur pa bzhin du ngo bo mi 'gyur
NK058(si)001:2370: zhing yon tan gyi rten byed pas sra ba'i dbyings
NK058(si)001:2372: chu ni gsher la skye bo'i gsos su gyur pa
NK058(si)001:2373: ltar 'gro ba'i rgyud brlan par byed pas mnyen pa'i
NK058(si)001:2374: dbyings te m+aa ma k+ai dang /
NK058(si)001:2375: me ni bsreg cing snang ba ltar nyon mongs pa
NK058(si)001:2376: bsreg cing shes bya thams cad gsal bar byed pas
NK058(si)001:2377: dro ba'i dbyings te gos dkar mo dang /
NK058(si)001:2378: rlung ni bskyod pa dang 'degs pa'i bya ba byed
NK058(si)001:2379: pa ltar 'gro ba'i don la thogs pa med cing
NK058(si)001:2380: nye bar 'tsho ba'i gzhir gyur bas bskyod pa'i dbyings
NK058(si)001:2381: te dam tshigs sgrol ma dang /
NK058(si)001:2382: de dag la sogs pa rigs kyi btsun mo'i tshogs
NK058(si)001:2383: ma lus mi lus lus pa med pa thams cad
NK058(si)001:2384: dang thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med par mnyam
NK058(si)001:2386: de dag gi rang bzhin nam bzhugs pa'i tshul lam grangs sam rnam grangs bstan pa ni /
NK058(si)001:2387: snang srid thams cad la ye nas 'du 'bral med par khyab cing /
NK058(si)001:2388: khyad par du longs sku'i snang bas yul chos kyi
NK058(si)001:2389: dbyings nam mkha'i mtha' klas pa kun tu sku gsung
NK058(si)001:2390: thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i snang ba
NK058(si)001:2391: chen pos kun tu mtha' yas par khyab pa ni
NK058(si)001:2392: / 'di lta ste dper na til gyi gang bu
NK058(si)001:2393: kha phye ba bzhin du go mtshams med par sku
NK058(si)001:2394: dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gyis gang nas thams
NK058(si)001:2395: cad kun tu khyab par bzhugs so //
NK058(si)001:2396: spyir snang srid thams cad la ye nas khyab kyang 'dir bde gshegs kyi snang ba la sbyar ro //
NK058(si)001:2397: tshul 'di ni bar gyi gsal byed de gong gi rigs lnga yab yum dang /
NK058(si)001:2398: 'og gi sems dpa' sems ma la sogs pa'i dkyil 'khor thams cad la shes par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:2400: ci'i phyir zhe na las dang po pas rtogs par dka' zhing bul chung ba'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:2401: gsum pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:2402: rang bzhin gyi 'khor ni gong du bstan zin cing /
NK058(si)001:2404: nang gi sems dpa' yab yum /
NK058(si)001:2407: dang po la'ang gnyis las yab bzhi ni /
NK058(si)001:2408: gtso bo rigs lnga'i rang bzhin bshad pa de nas sems dpa'i 'khor bshad par bya ste /
NK058(si)001:2409: de yang ston pa nyid byang chub chen po yin
NK058(si)001:2410: pa bzhin du rang snang ba'i thugs rje'i ngang las
NK058(si)001:2411: shar ba'i 'khor rnams kyang sgrib pa mtha' dag byang
NK058(si)001:2412: zhing yon tan ma lus pa thugs su chub pas
NK058(si)001:2413: sangs rgyas nyid yin pa'i phyir chen po sar gnas
NK058(si)001:2415: de yang rnam par shes pa'i sems dpa' bzhi la /
NK058(si)001:2416: rdo rje ni dbyings dang ye shes snang ba dang
NK058(si)001:2417: stong pa gnyis su med cing 'jig 'bral med pa
NK058(si)001:2418: ste / rdo rje rtse mo las /
NK058(si)001:2419: sra zhing snying po khog stong med //
NK058(si)001:2420: gcad dang gzhig par bya ba med //
NK058(si)001:2421: bsreg par byar med 'jig med pas //
NK058(si)001:2422: stong nyid rdo rjer brjod par bya //
NK058(si)001:2424: sgrib pa thams cad 'joms shing sgrib pas tshur mi gnod pa yin te /
NK058(si)001:2426: rdo rje'i rang bzhin sgrib pa kun //
NK058(si)001:2427: 'joms shing cis kyang mi tshugs la //
NK058(si)001:2428: rang byung ye shes lha yi lha //
NK058(si)001:2429: thams cad kun la 'bigs par byed //
NK058(si)001:2431: mig gi rnam shes kyis gzugs mthong ba las khyad
NK058(si)001:2432: par du 'phags pa sangs rgyas kyi spyan gyis yul
NK058(si)001:2433: lnga ga la 'jug cing chos nyid ro gcig tu
NK058(si)001:2434: gzigs pa'i cha nas mthong ba ste sa'i snying po
NK058(si)001:2435: dang / rna ba'i rnam shes kyis sgra thos pa
NK058(si)001:2436: las 'phags pas sangs rgyas kyi snyan gyis yul lnga
NK058(si)001:2437: ga la 'jug cing de bzhin nyid du ro gcig
NK058(si)001:2438: par gsan pa'i cha nas byang chub chen po rdo
NK058(si)001:2439: rje thos pa ste phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK058(si)001:2440: sna'i rnam shes kyi dri tshor ba las 'phags pa
NK058(si)001:2441: sangs rgyas kyi shangs kyi yul lnga ga la 'jug
NK058(si)001:2442: cing skye ba med par ro gcig tu tshor ba
NK058(si)001:2443: byang chub chen po rdo rje snom pa ste nam
NK058(si)001:2445: lce'i rnam shes kyis ro myong ba tsam las 'phags
NK058(si)001:2446: pa sangs rgyas kyi ljags kyi yul lnga ga la
NK058(si)001:2447: 'jug cing gnyis su med par ro gcig tu myong
NK058(si)001:2448: ba byang chub chen po rdo rje myong ba ste
NK058(si)001:2450: de dag gi yum bzhi yang rim pa bzhin du
NK058(si)001:2451: btsun mo mthong bar bya ba ye shes kyi snang
NK058(si)001:2452: ba'i yul gzugs te sgeg mo dang /
NK058(si)001:2453: de bzhin du mnyan par bya ba phreng ma dang /
NK058(si)001:2454: mnam par bya ba ni glu dbyangs ma dang /
NK058(si)001:2455: myong bar bya ba rol pa'i dga' ba ste gar ma dang bzhi'o //
NK058(si)001:2456: de ltar cung zad bsnol yang ming tsam ste don
NK058(si)001:2457: la nang gi sgeg mo bzhir 'dod pas mi 'gal
NK058(si)001:2458: lo // ji lta ba'i sgrar brjod na mnyan par bya ba sgra ste glu ma /
NK058(si)001:2459: mnam par bya ba dri ste bdug spos mar 'byung ngo //
NK058(si)001:2460: dbang po'i sems dpa' bzhi la mthong byed ni mig
NK058(si)001:2461: gi dbang po zar ma'i me tog lta bu las
NK058(si)001:2462: khyad par du 'phags pa rdo rje'i spyan sgrib pa
NK058(si)001:2463: med pas yul lnga 'dzin pa'i rten byed pa ste
NK058(si)001:2464: byams pa dang / thos byed ni rna ba'i dbang
NK058(si)001:2465: po gro ga gcus pa lta bu las 'phags pa
NK058(si)001:2466: snyan gyi dbang po nyams pa med pas yul lnga
NK058(si)001:2467: gsal ba'i rten byed pa ste sgrib pa rnam sel
NK058(si)001:2468: byams pa dang / dang / mnam byed ni sna'i
NK058(si)001:2469: dbang po zangs kyi mo khab gshibs pa lta bu
NK058(si)001:2470: las 'phags pa shangs kyi dbang po'i yul lnga la
NK058(si)001:2471: 'jug pa'i rten byed pa ste kun tu bzang po
NK058(si)001:2472: byams pa dang / dang / dang / myong byed
NK058(si)001:2473: ni lce'i dbang po zla ba phyed pa lta bu
NK058(si)001:2474: las 'phags pa gsung ro bro ba'i mchog mkhyen pas
NK058(si)001:2475: yul lnga la 'jug pa'i rten byed pa ste 'jam
NK058(si)001:2476: byams pa dang / dang / dang / dpal dang
NK058(si)001:2477: / de dag gi yum rnams kyang rim pa bzhin
NK058(si)001:2478: byams pa dang / dang / dang / dpal dang
NK058(si)001:2479: / / btsun mo 'das pa ni sngar grags pa'i
NK058(si)001:2480: chos zhig nas med pa las khyad par du 'phags
NK058(si)001:2481: pa snga ma'i chos ji bzhin pa mngon sum du
NK058(si)001:2482: gsal ba'i rang bzhin 'das pa'i dus la ma chags
NK058(si)001:2483: ma thogs pa'i ye shes gzigs pa 'jug pa'i mtshon
NK058(si)001:2484: byed du bdug spos mar snang ba dang /
NK058(si)001:2485: da ltar ni dbang po'i mngon sum la snang ba
NK058(si)001:2486: tsam las 'phags pa chos thams cad bskal don med
NK058(si)001:2487: par da ltar gyi dus la ma chags ma thogs
NK058(si)001:2488: pa'i ye shes gzigs pa la 'jug pa'i mtshon byed
NK058(si)001:2489: du me tog mar snang ba dang /
NK058(si)001:2490: ma byung ba ni ma 'ongs pa'i yul la mngon
NK058(si)001:2491: du ma gyur pa las khyad par du 'phags pa
NK058(si)001:2492: ma 'ongs pa'i chos rnams kyang skyu ru ra phyag
NK058(si)001:2493: mthil du bzhag pa bzhin du da ltar gzigs pas
NK058(si)001:2494: ma 'ongs pa'i dus la ma chags ma thogs pa'i
NK058(si)001:2495: ye shes gzigs pa la 'jug pa'i mtshon byed du
NK058(si)001:2496: snang gsal mar snang ba dang /
NK058(si)001:2497: 'byung bar ma nges pa'i tshogs dus bzhi mnyam pa
NK058(si)001:2498: nyid kyi ye shes te rang byung gi snang ba
NK058(si)001:2499: ji bzhin pa'i ngang nas 'pho 'gyur med pa'i chos
NK058(si)001:2500: nyid la bzhugs pa'i mtshon byed du dri chab mar
NK058(si)001:2502: de'ang 'das ma 'ongs da ltar mkhyen tshul ni me
NK058(si)001:2503: long gi ngos la pra phab pa'i snga rtags phyi
NK058(si)001:2504: rtags da ltar ba dang bcas pa 'char ba bzhin
NK058(si)001:2506: de skad du phal po che las /
NK058(si)001:2508: ji snyed ji bzhin mngon du gyur //
NK058(si)001:2510: sgo ba yab yum la gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:2511: yab ni gsang ba 'dus pa'i rgyud phyi ma las /
NK058(si)001:2512: mi 'jig rnam par mi shes pa //
NK058(si)001:2513: brjod med rnam par mi rtog pa //
NK058(si)001:2514: sangs rgyas byang chub ye shes 'di //
NK058(si)001:2515: shes na bde ba thob par 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:2516: zhes pa'i tshul dang mthun par bshad de /
NK058(si)001:2517: 'joms pa ni thabs dang chen po ni shes rab ste /
NK058(si)001:2518: de gnyis kyi rnam par 'phrul pa chen pos bdud
NK058(si)001:2519: dang gshin rje la sogs pa gdug pa can rnams
NK058(si)001:2521: de yang gsum las lus kyi cha'i reg pa'i tshor ba bskyed pa la /
NK058(si)001:2524: de gnyis 'phrad pa las reg bya shes pa lus
NK058(si)001:2525: kyi rnam shes te tha mal pa las khyad par
NK058(si)001:2526: du 'phags pa sangs rgyas kyi sku'i reg bya'i khams
NK058(si)001:2527: yul lnga la 'jug pa'i phyir bdud rtsi 'khyil ba
NK058(si)001:2531: ngag gi cha'i reg pa nyid sgrar bsgyur te gzhung
NK058(si)001:2532: du lus kyi gzhi dang por dngos su bstan pas
NK058(si)001:2533: ngag yid gnyis shugs la bstan to //
NK058(si)001:2534: de yang sgra'i shes pa skye ba la /
NK058(si)001:2537: de gnyis brjod pa'i rkyen tshogs pa las sgra'i shes
NK058(si)001:2538: pa snyan mi snyan bar ma gsum 'byung ba las
NK058(si)001:2539: khyad par 'phags pa sangs rgyas kyi gsung dbyangs sgrib
NK058(si)001:2540: pa thams cad dang bral ba yul lnga la 'jug
NK058(si)001:2541: pa'i mtshon byed du bdud rtsi 'khyil ba la sogs
NK058(si)001:2542: pa khro bo bzhir snang ngo //
NK058(si)001:2543: yid kyi tshe chos su bsgyur te /
NK058(si)001:2544: yid kyi yul chos kyi skye mched skye ba la /
NK058(si)001:2546: rig bya don spyi'i rnam pa sna tshogs pa yul /
NK058(si)001:2547: de gnyis 'phrad pa las bde sdug dgag sgrub la
NK058(si)001:2548: sogs pa'i shes pa skye ba las khyad par 'phags
NK058(si)001:2549: pa sangs rgyas kyi ye shes sgrib pa med pa
NK058(si)001:2550: don spyi'i 'dzin pa la mi ltos par mngon sum
NK058(si)001:2551: du gyur cing chags sdang thams cad dang bral ba'i
NK058(si)001:2552: mtshon byed du khro bo bzhi sgo bar ye shes
NK058(si)001:2553: kyi rtsal las rang snang ba de yang skye 'jig
NK058(si)001:2554: med pa dang / brjod du med pa dang /
NK058(si)001:2556: rnam pa med par rtogs pa'i ye shes bzhi'o //
NK058(si)001:2557: de dag gi yum bzhi ni rim pa bzhin ngo
NK058(si)001:2558: bo gzugs la sogs pa'i chos thams cad rtag par
NK058(si)001:2559: ma yin pa ste med bzhin du snang ba gzugs
NK058(si)001:2560: brnyan dang 'dra bar mtshon zhing rnam pa byams pa
NK058(si)001:2561: chen po dang sbyin pas sems can rnams sdud pa'i
NK058(si)001:2562: mtshon byed du lcags kyu ma'o //
NK058(si)001:2563: sgra la sogs pa'i chos thams cad chad par ma
NK058(si)001:2564: yin pa ste ngo bo rang rang gi snang ba
NK058(si)001:2565: ma dor ba smig rgyu dang 'dra bar mtshon zhing
NK058(si)001:2566: rnam pa snying rje chen po dang snyan par smra
NK058(si)001:2567: bas sems can rnams bsdud pa'i phyir zhags pa mar
NK058(si)001:2568: snang ba'o // yid kyi chos rnams la dgag sgrub
NK058(si)001:2569: kyi bdag tu gzung du med de ngo bo bdag
NK058(si)001:2570: tu grub pa ma yin pa rmi lam dang 'dra
NK058(si)001:2571: zhing rnam pa dga' ba chen po dang don mthun
NK058(si)001:2572: pas sems can rnams dbang du byed pa'i brdar lcags
NK058(si)001:2573: snang ba'o // sgrog ma'o // snang srid 'khor 'das
NK058(si)001:2574: thams cad kyi ngo bo dngos po dang mtshan mar
NK058(si)001:2575: grub pa ma yin te gdod ma nas rang bzhin
NK058(si)001:2576: med pa sprul pa dang 'dra zhing rnam pa don
NK058(si)001:2577: dpyod pa dang btang snyoms chen pos sems can rnams
NK058(si)001:2578: zhi ba la 'god pa'i mtshon byed du dril bu
NK058(si)001:2579: snang ba'o // sgrog ma'o // mar snang ba'o //
NK058(si)001:2580: de yang sangs rgyas kyis na dbang shes lnga po
NK058(si)001:2581: re res kyang yul lnga la 'jug par /
NK058(si)001:2583: dbang po lnga rnams gzhan gyur na //
NK058(si)001:2584: don kun 'jug dang thams cad kyi //
NK058(si)001:2585: yon tan brgya phrag bcu gnyis 'byung //
NK058(si)001:2587: mig gi dbang po la thog mar phyogs bzhi steng 'og gnyis te drug tu phye la /
NK058(si)001:2588: drug po re re la gdod phyogs bcur phye ba'i
NK058(si)001:2589: mig gi dbang pos shar phyogs kyi shar gyi gzugs
NK058(si)001:2595: phyogs lhag ma dgu la bzhi bzhi ste bzhi bcu /
NK058(si)001:2596: de bzhin du phyogs lhag ma lnga la'ang bcu bcur phye la bzhi bcu bzhi bcu ste /
NK058(si)001:2597: de ltar na bzhi bcu tshan pa drug la nyis brgya bzhi bcu ste /
NK058(si)001:2601: lus rnams la'ang rang rang gi yon tan bor la
NK058(si)001:2602: de bzhin du brtsis pa brgya phrag bcu gnyis te
NK058(si)001:2603: / 'di dag ni sangs rgyas kyi sa'i yon tan khyad par can no //
NK058(si)001:2604: de ltar rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi yab dang yum
NK058(si)001:2605: dang sems dpa' dang sems ma dang sgo ba yab
NK058(si)001:2606: yum la sogs pa dbus su snang ba ji lta
NK058(si)001:2607: ba bzhin du / phyogs bzhir rigs bzhi'i dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:2608: rang rang gi tshom bu'i 'khor 'bum phrag du mas
NK058(si)001:2609: ba bzhin du / bskor ba / lha'i bkod tshul
NK058(si)001:2610: gyi mang nyung dang rnam pa rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:2611: de lta bu'i tshogs nam mkha'i dbyings kun khyab par
NK058(si)001:2612: rjod kyis mi lang bar snang ba rnams dang rang
NK058(si)001:2613: bzhin gnyis su med par bzhugs te rang snang ye
NK058(si)001:2614: shes kyi rol pa gcig gis ngang las shar ba'i
NK058(si)001:2615: ba bzhin du / bskor ba / gnad kyis so
NK058(si)001:2616: // gsum pa ye shes kyi rang snang bkod pas
NK058(si)001:2617: don bsdu ba la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:2618: gang las bkod pa'i ngo bo /
NK058(si)001:2619: tshul ji ltar bkod pa'i tshul lo //
NK058(si)001:2621: gleng gzhi rgyas par bstan pa de nas de bzhin
NK058(si)001:2622: gshegs pa yab rnams yum btsun mo'i tshogs dang rang
NK058(si)001:2623: bzhin gnyis su med pa'i ngo bo gzhan gyi spyod
NK058(si)001:2624: yul du ma gyur pas gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor rang
NK058(si)001:2625: snang ba de dag nyid kyi gsang ba chen po
NK058(si)001:2626: 'di nyid / sku rdo rje dang gsung rdo rje
NK058(si)001:2627: dang thugs rdo rje dang yon tan rdo rje dang
NK058(si)001:2628: phrin las rdo rje las rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor rang
NK058(si)001:2629: snang ba'i don ston pa'i rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig
NK058(si)001:2630: 'di dag dgongs pa rang shar du ma brjod pa'i
NK058(si)001:2632: gnyis pa ji ltar phyung zhing rang snang du bkod pa la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:2633: rang snang gi dkyil 'khor de nyid gang gi ngang las bkod pa /
NK058(si)001:2635: de nyid gang gis bzhugs gnas yin ngos gzung ba'o //
NK058(si)001:2637: e chos sku'i ngang las e ma longs sku'i snang
NK058(si)001:2638: ba e ma hohsna tshogs su rang snang ba ngo
NK058(si)001:2639: mtshar ston pa'o // chos sku de bzhin nyid kyi
NK058(si)001:2640: dbyings nyid kyi ngo bo la dbang bsgyur ba longs
NK058(si)001:2641: sku ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub pa
NK058(si)001:2642: ni ston pa nyid kyi bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK058(si)001:2643: thugs rje'i ngang las byung ba'o //
NK058(si)001:2645: de lta bu'i zhing khams lhun stug po bkod pa
NK058(si)001:2646: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la rang snang ba nyid
NK058(si)001:2647: de sangs rgyas kyi ting 'dzin rnam par dag pa'i
NK058(si)001:2648: gzugs brnyan ye shes kyi sgyu ma rang bzhin gyis
NK058(si)001:2649: rnam par dag pa'i ngo bor gsal zhing snang ba
NK058(si)001:2650: ni zhes so // gsum pa ni /
NK058(si)001:2651: sangs rgyas kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs dang yon
NK058(si)001:2652: tan dang phrin las rnams nyes pa'i skyon cung zad
NK058(si)001:2653: tsam gyi'ang sel med pa'i bdag nyid /
NK058(si)001:2654: yon tan phun sum tshogs pa yid bzhin rin po
NK058(si)001:2655: che bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mnga' thang chen po
NK058(si)001:2656: mi zad par ldan pa ye shes rgyan gyi 'khor
NK058(si)001:2657: lo mnga' ba'i rang bzhin rdo rje mchog gi ngo
NK058(si)001:2658: bo 'du 'bral med pa dang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK058(si)001:2660: zhes sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig rgyud kyi rang bzhin du'o //
NK058(si)001:2661: 'di la kha cig sdud pa po'i rnam par sbyor
NK058(si)001:2662: ba ni mi 'thad de rdo rje gsang ba snying
NK058(si)001:2663: po'i rgyud yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:2668: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor thugs rje'i dkyil 'khor /
NK058(si)001:2675: gsal ba'i dkyil 'khor du bzhed do //
NK058(si)001:2676: de yang rdo rje'i tshig yin pas gang du'ang sbyar du rung mod kyi /
NK058(si)001:2677: 'on kyang skabs 'di ting nge 'dzin gsum dang /
NK058(si)001:2678: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la sogs pa lam gyi dkyil 'khor ston pa'i skabs ma yin zhing /
NK058(si)001:2679: sangs rgyas kyi rang snang lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil
NK058(si)001:2680: 'khor ston pa'i skabs yin pa'i phyir ma 'brel lo
NK058(si)001:2681: // kha cig gleng gzhi bsdus par 'dod pa de
NK058(si)001:2682: dag gis kyang gzhung gi phyogs tsam yang ma mthong
NK058(si)001:2683: // ba nyid do // gleng gzhi ston pa'i bkar bsdu ba ni /
NK058(si)001:2684: kha cig na re gleng gzhi ni sdud pa po'i
NK058(si)001:2685: tshig yin pas gleng slong pa man chad bka' yin
NK058(si)001:2687: sdud pa po nyid ston pa dang tha dad med pas kyang de'i gsung bka' yin la /
NK058(si)001:2688: ngan song sbyong bar dkyil 'khor phal cher gsang bdag gis gsungs pa'ang rgyud du bshad pa dang /
NK058(si)001:2689: gzhan yang snying rje pad+ma dkar po'i mdo las kyang /
NK058(si)001:2690: nga 'das pa'i tshe dge slong rnams bka' bsdu bar byed pa na /
NK058(si)001:2691: thog mar 'di skad bdag gis thos pa dus gcig na zhes pas gling slong zhig /
NK058(si)001:2692: ces gsungs pas 'dir yang chos mthun no //
NK058(si)001:2693: de ltar phun sum tshogs pa'i tshul brjod pa de
NK058(si)001:2694: dag gis gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid
NK058(si)001:2695: nges pa'i le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis yod pa las
NK058(si)001:2696: / rgyud 'byung ba'i lo rgyus dang nges pa sbyin
NK058(si)001:2697: pa dang gzhir gyur pa'i phyir gleng gzhi'i don yin
NK058(si)001:2698: / la / le'u ni pa rits+tsheta'i sgra las yongs
NK058(si)001:2699: su bcad pa'am dum bur byas pa la 'jug pas
NK058(si)001:2701: dang po'i ni le'u rnams kyi thog ma smos pa'i
NK058(si)001:2702: sgra de gral gyi 'go na gnas pa bzhin no
NK058(si)001:2703: // de'ang bam po ni kha mar blta la /
NK058(si)001:2704: le'u rnams ni kha yar blta ba yin pas na
NK058(si)001:2705: so so'i le'u re rdzogs par bstan pa'i mtha' tshig
NK058(si)001:2707: gnyis pa ston pa nyid rigs lngar bzhengs pa'i thugs
NK058(si)001:2708: rang byung gi ye shes gnyis su med pas chos
NK058(si)001:2709: thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par ched du brjod
NK058(si)001:2710: cing thugs rje g.yo ba'i tshul bstan pa ni /
NK058(si)001:2711: gleng bslang ba'i tshul gyis ston te /
NK058(si)001:2712: de'ang chos sku'i ston pa yab yum nyid longs skur
NK058(si)001:2713: snang ba'i thugs rang byung gi ye shes shes bya'i
NK058(si)001:2715: 'bebs byed rig pa ni yid rdo rje kun tu bzang po yab tu brjod la /
NK058(si)001:2716: yul shes bya ni bya ba mo kun tu bzang
NK058(si)001:2717: mo ste yum du btags pa ni 'og tu tshogs
NK058(si)001:2718: sgrub pa'i skabs su gzung yul yum dang 'dzin pa
NK058(si)001:2719: yab tu bshad pa bzhin yin la /
NK058(si)001:2720: yab yum gnyis su med pa ni blo yul gzhal
NK058(si)001:2721: pa'i tshe gnyis ka rig pa'i ngo bor gcig pa
NK058(si)001:2722: ste dper na / sems la lha sa'i don spyi lam gyis gzhal dus /
NK058(si)001:2725: de gnyis rang gi sems su ro gcig pa ni gnyis su med pa bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:2726: de ltar spyi'i go don yid la bzhag nas /
NK058(si)001:2727: da ni le'u gnyis pa'i gzhung don nyid brjod pa la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:2728: don gyi dgongs pa gleng bslang ba dang /
NK058(si)001:2729: de ma rtogs pa'i sems can la thugs rje g.yo ba'i tshul bstan pa'o //
NK058(si)001:2733: gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa gleng bslang ba'o //
NK058(si)001:2735: dgongs pa gleng bslang ba la 'jug pa'i rgyu dang /
NK058(si)001:2737: dang po ni gleng gzhi bstan pa de nas bcom
NK058(si)001:2738: ldan 'das rigs kyi gtso bo'i thugs rang byung gi
NK058(si)001:2739: ye shes yul 'byed par byed pa po gnyis su
NK058(si)001:2740: med pa'i tshul rdo rje yid yul du ma la
NK058(si)001:2741: 'jug pas kun tu ngo bo dbyings las ma g.yos
NK058(si)001:2742: pas bzang po phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas thams
NK058(si)001:2743: cad kyi dgongs pa ma lus pa 'dus pa'i rang
NK058(si)001:2744: bzhin gyi sku gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i tshul dus
NK058(si)001:2746: yul gyi rang bzhin ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i phyir
NK058(si)001:2747: btsun mo gtan la dbab par bya ba mo snang
NK058(si)001:2748: srid 'khor 'das kyi chos ma lus pa kun tu
NK058(si)001:2749: ste thams cad kyang ye nas dag pas bzang mo
NK058(si)001:2750: la 'byed pa'i blo 'jug par gyur to //
NK058(si)001:2751: blo zhugs pas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs
NK058(si)001:2752: pa ma lus pa thams cad thugs rang byung gi
NK058(si)001:2753: ye shes kun tu bzang po gcig gi rang bzhin
NK058(si)001:2754: du ngo bo dbyer med pas /
NK058(si)001:2755: nyid las gzhan pa'i chos ma gzigs nas de bzhin gshegs pa nyid /
NK058(si)001:2756: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la ched du brjod pa'i tshul 'di skad ces brjod par mdzad do //
NK058(si)001:2757: gnyis pa ni chos thams cad gdod nas dag pas e ma hohste ngo mtshar che ba'i don to //
NK058(si)001:2758: ji ltar na sangs rgyas dang sems can thams cad
NK058(si)001:2759: kyi rang bzhin ye nas skye ba med par sangs
NK058(si)001:2760: rgyas pas rdo rje ste chos nyid stong pa nyid
NK058(si)001:2761: dang chos can snang ba nyid kyi rang bzhin ni
NK058(si)001:2762: phung po'o // de'i yan lag ni rnam par shes pa la sogs pa'i phung po lnga ste /
NK058(si)001:2763: mi bskyod pa la sogs pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags pa'o //
NK058(si)001:2764: de bzhin du skye mched bcu gnyis dang khams bco
NK058(si)001:2765: brgyad po rnams kyi bye brag mang po kun kyang
NK058(si)001:2766: byang chub sems dpa' yab yum ste 'khor gyi dkyil
NK058(si)001:2767: 'khor nyid du ye nas gnas so //
NK058(si)001:2768: skye mched ni gzugs la sogs pa'i yul drug la
NK058(si)001:2769: mig la sogs pa dbang po'i shes pa drug skye
NK058(si)001:2770: zhing skad cig phyi mar rgyun mched par 'byed pas
NK058(si)001:2772: dbye na gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya chos te yul drug /
NK058(si)001:2773: mig rna ba sna lce lus yid de dbang po drug gi skye mched de bcu gnyis so //
NK058(si)001:2777: mig gis rnam par shes pa'i khams dang zhes yul drug /
NK058(si)001:2780: 'byung ba lnga yum lnga'i ngo bor sangs rgyas te
NK058(si)001:2781: sa dang chu ni sangs rgyas spyan ma dang m+aa
NK058(si)001:2782: ma k+ai'o // me dang rlung ni gos dkar mo dang dam tshig sgrol ma ste /
NK058(si)001:2783: nam mkha' ni dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma'o //
NK058(si)001:2784: de ltar phyi nang gi 'byung ba dang rtog tshogs
NK058(si)001:2785: kyis bsdus pa'i 'dod pa gzugs gzugs med pa'i srid
NK058(si)001:2786: pa gsum gyi ngo bo ma dag pa ltar snang
NK058(si)001:2787: ba 'di yang ye gdod ma nas sangs rgyas kyi
NK058(si)001:2789: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad dang mya ngan las 'das
NK058(si)001:2790: pa'i chos ma lus pa snang zhing srid pa'i chos
NK058(si)001:2791: so cog thams cad sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma
NK058(si)001:2792: yin te / sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan pa ma
NK058(si)001:2793: dag pa 'khor ba'i chos zhes bya ba rang mtshan
NK058(si)001:2795: btsal na sangs rgyas nyid kyis kyang rdul tsam zhig mi brnyes so ste mi rnyed do //
NK058(si)001:2796: sangs rgyas kyis ma rnyed pa ni don la med par go bar byed pa yin te /
NK058(si)001:2798: thams cad mkhyen pas gzigs pa log pa ni thams
NK058(si)001:2799: cad du med par go bar byed pa kho na
NK058(si)001:2801: ji skad du kun byed las /
NK058(si)001:2802: chos kun ma skyes kun byed nyid kyi ngang //
NK058(si)001:2803: ye nas sangs rgyas snying po kun byed la //
NK058(si)001:2804: yod med mi dmigs rang bzhin mnyam pa'i ngang //
NK058(si)001:2805: gdod nas gzhi rtsa bral ba'i chos nyid do //
NK058(si)001:2807: phyir mi ldog pa'i 'khor lo'i mdo las /
NK058(si)001:2808: chos kun ye nas sangs rgyas pas //
NK058(si)001:2809: byang chub nam mkha'i mtshan nyid do //
NK058(si)001:2811: de ltar snang ba'i chos nyid ye nas sangs rgyas
NK058(si)001:2812: pa'o zhes brjod pas de bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i
NK058(si)001:2813: tshogs dang bcas pa thams cad mnyes par gyur to
NK058(si)001:2814: // gnyis pa yum gyi dgongs pa chos nyid stong
NK058(si)001:2815: pa'i gnas lugs gtso bor gleng bslang ba la'ang gnyis
NK058(si)001:2816: // te / dgongs pas gleng bslang ba la 'jug pa'i rgyu dang /
NK058(si)001:2818: dang po ni blos yul gyi gnas lugs brjod pa
NK058(si)001:2819: de nas blo la snang ba'i yul rang bzhin gyis
NK058(si)001:2820: dag pa'i btsun mo gtan la dbab par bya ba
NK058(si)001:2821: mo rang snang ba'i chos kun tu bzang mos /
NK058(si)001:2822: yul can rig pa'i ye shes bcom ldan 'das kun
NK058(si)001:2823: tu bzang po dang yul yul can gnyis su med
NK058(si)001:2824: par gyur nas chos nyid stong pa nyid kyi gnas
NK058(si)001:2825: lugs 'di nyid ched du brjod pa'i ngo bor 'di
NK058(si)001:2828: chos nyid ngo mtshar bar bstan pa'i phyir kye ma hoh zhes so //
NK058(si)001:2829: ji ltar mtshar na rang snang gi zhing khams 'dis
NK058(si)001:2830: mtshon nas phyogs bcu'i stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i
NK058(si)001:2831: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad ye gdod ma nas
NK058(si)001:2832: stong pa nyid kyis phyir dben pa ni snod kyi
NK058(si)001:2833: 'jig rten stong pa nyid du bstan pa'o //
NK058(si)001:2835: gling bzhi ri rab dang bcas pa gcig lcags ri
NK058(si)001:2836: gnya' shing 'dzin dang mtho dman mnyam pas bskor ba
NK058(si)001:2837: 'dod pa dang gzugs kyi lha'i khang pas brgyan pa
NK058(si)001:2838: ni gling bzhi pa'i 'jig rten no //
NK058(si)001:2839: de stong gi mthar sum cu rtsa gsum gyi gnas
NK058(si)001:2840: dang mtho dman mnyam pa'i lcags ris bskor ba ni
NK058(si)001:2841: stong dang po'i spyi phud kyi 'jig rten no //
NK058(si)001:2842: de stong gi mthar gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi gnas
NK058(si)001:2843: dang mnyam pa'i lcags ris bskor ba ni stong gnyis
NK058(si)001:2845: de stong gi mthar bsam gtan dang po'i gnas dang
NK058(si)001:2846: mnyam pa'i lcags ris bskor ba ni stong gsum gyi
NK058(si)001:2847: stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams so //
NK058(si)001:2848: 'dir ni des mtshon pa'i zhing dang 'jig rten thams cad stong pa nyid de gzugs brnyan bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:2849: de na gnas pa'i bcud kyi sems can thams cad
NK058(si)001:2850: kyang stong bar bstan pa ni srid pa gsum ni
NK058(si)001:2851: ye nas dag pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams lhun
NK058(si)001:2852: stug po bkod pa'i rang bzhin du gnas shing /
NK058(si)001:2853: ye shes lnga'i rtsal gzung 'dzin du 'khrul dus dug
NK058(si)001:2854: lngar snang bas 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal bskyed pa'i phyir
NK058(si)001:2855: snyigs ma lnga nyid kyang ngo bo rang byung gi
NK058(si)001:2856: ye shes bde ba chen po dang ldan pa'i gnas
NK058(si)001:2858: 'di la kha cig dus la sogs pa'i snyigs mar 'chad pa ni phyin ci log go //
NK058(si)001:2859: 'gro ba'i phung po lnga nyid kyang snga ma bzhin ye nas mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i phyir /
NK058(si)001:2860: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs la bzang ngan dang
NK058(si)001:2861: blang dor gang du'ang ma grub pas mchog gi snying
NK058(si)001:2862: po mnyam pa nyid byang chub kyi rang bzhin yin
NK058(si)001:2863: pas na / de las gzhan du rgyal bas chos mi btsal te /
NK058(si)001:2864: thams cad sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin yin zhing /
NK058(si)001:2865: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma dag pa zhes bya
NK058(si)001:2866: ba'i chos log pa zhig btsal kyang rgyal bas gzhan
NK058(si)001:2867: mi brnyes so ste mi rnyed do //
NK058(si)001:2868: zhes yum gyi brjod pas chos thams cad ye nas
NK058(si)001:2869: sangs rgyas par de bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs
NK058(si)001:2870: dang bcas pa nyid kyis mkhyen to //
NK058(si)001:2871: gsum pa gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:2872: dgongs pa bslang ba la 'jug pa'i rgyu dang /
NK058(si)001:2874: dang po yul nyid yul can gyi ngo bo dang
NK058(si)001:2875: rig pa'i ye shes su rnam par dag pa de
NK058(si)001:2876: nas yab yum rig stong gnyis su med pa'i bdag
NK058(si)001:2877: nyid chen pos / 'khor 'das ye nas mnyam pa
NK058(si)001:2878: nyid du sangs rgyas pa'i phyir sems kyang sangs rgyas
NK058(si)001:2879: pa'i chos nyid du shes par byed pa rang byung
NK058(si)001:2880: gi ye shes su ye nas yin pa la yin
NK058(si)001:2881: pa'i bdag nyid du bskyed pa 'di gsungs so //
NK058(si)001:2882: de skad du'ang rmad byung rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK058(si)001:2883: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK058(si)001:2884: ye nas sangs rgyas yin pa la //
NK058(si)001:2885: yin par shes pa'i bdag nyid du //
NK058(si)001:2886: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK058(si)001:2888: gnyis pa ni chos thams cad ye nas skye 'gag spros pa'i yul las 'das shing /
NK058(si)001:2889: de rtogs pa'i blo yang ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin du bstan pa'i phyir /
NK058(si)001:2890: e ma hohchosa rnams kyi gnas lugs ngo mtshar zhing
NK058(si)001:2891: gzhan las rmad du byung ba nyid kyi chos nyid
NK058(si)001:2892: 'di ni / rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba zab mo'i don to //
NK058(si)001:2893: gang zhe na chos nyid gdod ma nas skye ba
NK058(si)001:2894: med pa'i ngang las snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus
NK058(si)001:2895: pa'i chos thams cad skyes bar snang ba rmi lam
NK058(si)001:2897: skyes par snang dus nyid na don la skye ba med pa'i ngo bo ni chos kyi dbyings so //
NK058(si)001:2898: de nyid rtogs pa'i blo ni chos dbyings ye shes so //
NK058(si)001:2899: de bzhin du tshig dang po gnyis 'og ma bzhi la yang sbyar nas /
NK058(si)001:2900: ye nas 'gag pa med pa'i chos nyid gdangs sna
NK058(si)001:2901: tshogs su 'char ba me long gi ngos lta bu
NK058(si)001:2902: las / chos can sna tshogs gzugs brnyan ltar snang ba thams cad 'gag pa ltar snang yang /
NK058(si)001:2903: 'gag par snang dus de nyid na gnas lugs 'gag pa med pa ni me long lta bu'o //
NK058(si)001:2904: de nyid rtogs pa'i blo ni me long lta bu'i ye shes so //
NK058(si)001:2905: chos thams cad ye nas gnas pa med pa nam
NK058(si)001:2906: mkha' lta bu'i ngang las 'di ltar snang ba'i chos
NK058(si)001:2907: sna tshogs pa thams cad gnas pa ltar snang yang
NK058(si)001:2908: / gnas par snang dus 'di nyid na don la gnas pa med pa ni mnyam pa nyid do //
NK058(si)001:2909: de nyid rtogs pa'i blo ni mnyam nyid ye shes so //
NK058(si)001:2910: sems nyid rang bzhin gyis dag pa dmigs pa dang
NK058(si)001:2911: mtshan ma med pa nam mkha' 'am rgya mtsho dngas
NK058(si)001:2912: pa'i dkyil lta bu'i ngang las rnam par rtog pa
NK058(si)001:2913: sprin nam gzugs brnyan ltar sna tshogs su shar ba
NK058(si)001:2914: thams cad dgag sgrub la sogs par dmigs pa ltar
NK058(si)001:2915: snang yang rnam rtog sna tshogs su dmigs par snang
NK058(si)001:2916: dus nyid na gzhi med rtsa ba dang bral bas
NK058(si)001:2917: dmigs pa dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i rtog pa rang
NK058(si)001:2918: bzhin gyis med pa ni so sor rtog pa'o //
NK058(si)001:2919: de nyid rtogs pa'i blo la so sor rtog pa'i ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK058(si)001:2920: chos thams cad gdod nas 'gro 'ong med pa sprul
NK058(si)001:2921: pa lta bu'i ngang las snang ba dang rig pa
NK058(si)001:2922: 'gro ba dang 'ong ba sna tshogs su snang yang
NK058(si)001:2923: / 'gro 'ong du snang ba nyid na rang gi
NK058(si)001:2924: ngo bo 'gro 'ong med par gnas pa ni bya
NK058(si)001:2925: / ba grub pa / de nyid rtogs pa'i blo ni bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK058(si)001:2926: de dag gi don kha cig gis dga' ba bzhi'i
NK058(si)001:2927: ye shes so zhes sbyor ba yang skabs dang 'brel
NK058(si)001:2928: bar ma mthong ste snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK058(si)001:2929: thams cad kyi gnas lugs ston pa'i skabs yin pa'i
NK058(si)001:2930: phyir ro // de ltar chos thams cad kyi rang
NK058(si)001:2931: bzhin ye nas dag pa'i tshul de skad ces brjod
NK058(si)001:2932: pas de bzhin gshegs pa yab snang ba thams cad
NK058(si)001:2933: phyir ro // dang / yum btsun mo'i tshogs stong
NK058(si)001:2934: pa thams cad kyang mnyam pa nyid du ye nas
NK058(si)001:2935: mnyes pas khyab par gyur to //
NK058(si)001:2936: gnyis pa de nyid ma rtogs pa'i 'gro ba la
NK058(si)001:2937: thugs rjee g.yo ba'i tshul bstan pa la bzhi ste
NK058(si)001:2938: / thugs rje 'jug pa'i yul sems can gyis ma rtogs par bstan pa dang /
NK058(si)001:2939: ma rtog pa'i rang bzhin bdag tu gzung bas 'khor bar 'khrul tshul /
NK058(si)001:2940: 'khrul par snang dus nyid nas bcing grol med pa'i don las ma 'das pa /
NK058(si)001:2941: de nyid bstan pa'i phyir thugs rje'i rol pa 'gyed pa'i tshul brjod pa'o //
NK058(si)001:2943: thugs rje 'jug pa'i rgyu bstan pa dang /
NK058(si)001:2944: ji ltar 'jug pa'i yul bstan pa'o //
NK058(si)001:2945: dang po ni chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs bstan
NK058(si)001:2946: pa de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad btsun
NK058(si)001:2947: mo'i tshogs dang bcas pas don 'di nyid bstan pa'i
NK058(si)001:2948: phyir ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK058(si)001:2949: gnyis pa ni ma rtogs pa'i sems can gyi tshogs
NK058(si)001:2950: la skyo ba'i tshul gyis e ma hohzhesa bos te
NK058(si)001:2951: chos thams cad rang bzhin gdod ma nas sangs rgyas
NK058(si)001:2952: pa'i don thog ma nyid nas ma rtogs par ye
NK058(si)001:2953: nas 'gro ba thams cad la gsang ba'i chos so
NK058(si)001:2954: // snang srid sna tshogs su snang ba 'di dang
NK058(si)001:2955: sku gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i chos nyid du ye
NK058(si)001:2956: nas gnas pa la ma dag 'khrul pa'i chos su
NK058(si)001:2957: snang bas rang bzhin gyis gsang ba'o //
NK058(si)001:2958: de lta bu'i don de nyid gzhan gyis sbas pa
NK058(si)001:2959: lta bu ma yin par snang stong 'du 'bral med
