NK058(si)001:8887: 'bras bu rgyal ba smin grub ngo mtshar ming tshogs bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK058(si)001:8888: 'dus ma byas nyid 'dus byas rdo rje dkyil 'khor 'byin pa'i dam //
NK058(si)001:8889: 'da' bar mi mdzad dbang med rgyu rkyen tshogs pa'i
NK058(si)001:8890: mthu chen yin hoh zhes pas yab yum gnyis su
NK058(si)001:8891: med par 'khril ba'i thugs ka nas yi ge sprin
NK058(si)001:8892: 'phros te / lha'i dkyil 'khor du gyur pas sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs /
NK058(si)001:8893: slar 'dus dkyil 'khor du byon par bsam zhing /
NK058(si)001:8894: tha ni sgyu 'phrul rdo rje nyid //
NK058(si)001:8896: ni thams cad zhig pa yin gyi bar brjod pas /
NK058(si)001:8897: rnam snang yab yum ni kun tu bzang po yab yum la thim par gyur /
NK058(si)001:8898: lha gzhan rnams ni rang rang gi gnas su bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK058(si)001:8899: de nas gtso bo'i thugs ka nas rig pa'i kun
NK058(si)001:8900: tu bzang po rkang pa'i long bu sprad cing lag
NK058(si)001:8901: pa thal mo sbyar te 'greng ba sems dpa'i rgyan
NK058(si)001:8903: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la lan gsum bskor ba byas te nub sgo nas me tog gtor zhing //
NK058(si)001:8904: sngon gyi thugs dam chen po ni //
NK058(si)001:8905: 'jig rten ma lus thams cad kun //
NK058(si)001:8906: rgyal ba'i zhing du sbyor bas na //
NK058(si)001:8907: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK058(si)001:8909: lha rnams kyis gnang ste thabs dang shes rab kyi 'od zer bdag la spros te /
NK058(si)001:8910: sems kyi rtog pa dang de las gyur ba'i lus ngag sbyangs te /
NK058(si)001:8911: gzung 'dzin gnyis dang bral ba'i rang bzhin 'od kyi gong bu gcig tu gyur pa la /
NK058(si)001:8912: lha rnams kyi sku gsung thugs kyi 'od zer +aahmh'u gi rnam par 'phros pa phog cing thim pas /
NK058(si)001:8913: 'od kyi gong bu de nyid sku gsung thugs gnyis
NK058(si)001:8914: su med pa'i rang bzhin yi ge h'u du gyur
NK058(si)001:8915: nas / gtso bo'i thugs kar thim pas gtso bo'i sku gzi byin dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK058(si)001:8916: de nas gtso bo yab yum gnyis su med pa'i
NK058(si)001:8917: byang chub kyi sems su gyur te yum gyi mkha'
NK058(si)001:8919: lha thams cad kyang rang rang gi gsang sngags kyi
NK058(si)001:8920: sgra dang bcas nas byang chub kyi sems la thim
NK058(si)001:8921: par gyur nas / dkyil 'khor gyi dbus seng ge
NK058(si)001:8922: dang nyi zla'i steng na de thams cad gcig tu
NK058(si)001:8923: gyur pa byang chub kyi sems kyi rang bzhin 'od
NK058(si)001:8924: kyi gong bu tsam zhig dmigs pa las /
NK058(si)001:8925: slar yang h'u dang m+aum du gyur te 'od zer
NK058(si)001:8926: gyi 'phro 'du las rdo rje dang dril bur gyur
NK058(si)001:8927: cing / de yongs su gyur pa las rnam par snang mdzad yab yum gyi skur bsam mo //
NK058(si)001:8928: de nas ma h+aa sh+au nya ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra
NK058(si)001:8929: swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham zhes pa la sogs
NK058(si)001:8930: pas ye shes lnga yi dbang bskur zhing sku gsung
NK058(si)001:8931: thugs yon tan phrin las lngas byin gyis brlab bo
NK058(si)001:8932: // de nas gtso bo yab yum gyi mkha' gsang rdo rje dang pad+mara byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK058(si)001:8933: sa ma ya hohs sbyor ba'i brdas bskul nas gnyis
NK058(si)001:8934: su med par snyoms par zhugs pa'i yab kyi byang
NK058(si)001:8935: sems yum gyi mkha' la spros pas mkha' gzhal yas
NK058(si)001:8936: khang du byin gyis brlabs pa'i nang na /
NK058(si)001:8937: lha rnams kyi snying po h'u dang la sogs pa so so'i sa bon rnams gsal btab la /
NK058(si)001:8938: lha so so'i gsang sngags brjod pa tsam gyis lha so so'i skur gyur te /
NK058(si)001:8939: dzahzhesa brjod pa tsam gyis yum gyi mkha' nas mdun gyi nam mkha' la skad cig gis bton te /
NK058(si)001:8940: +aahmh'u gis sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs /
NK058(si)001:8941: 'od zer gyi spro bsdus sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs te /
NK058(si)001:8942: rang rang gi gnas su bzhugs par bsam zhing /
NK058(si)001:8943: sngar bstan pa'i lha so so'i sngags rnams brjod cing gsal bar bskyed do //
NK058(si)001:8944: de'ang kun tu bzang po yab yum ni gtso bo'i thugs kar bsam zhing /
NK058(si)001:8945: thub drug ni phyi'i khyams la bzhugs par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:8946: gzhan ni ji skad smos pa bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:8948: de nas spyan drang ba ni /
NK058(si)001:8949: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK058(si)001:8950: mi dmigs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor las //
NK058(si)001:8951: dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK058(si)001:8952: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor la //
NK058(si)001:8953: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor bas //
NK058(si)001:8954: phyogs dus kun nas gshegs pa yi //
NK058(si)001:8955: bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor rab tu rdzogs //
NK058(si)001:8956: nye bar 'gyur ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK058(si)001:8957: e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aa na ma h+aa ka
NK058(si)001:8958: ru ni ka dri sha hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam
NK058(si)001:8960: 'og min nas dkyil 'khor chen po ji ltar bskyed
NK058(si)001:8961: pa lta bu mdun gyi nam mkhar byon pa la
NK058(si)001:8963: rig pa'i me tog dor ba ni /
NK058(si)001:8965: +aahbadz+ra sa ma ya +aah h'u badz+ra sa ma ya h'u /
NK058(si)001:8966: s+w+aa badz+ra sa ma ya s+w+aa /
NK058(si)001:8967: h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya h+aah zhes brjod pas /
NK058(si)001:8968: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor rnams kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las rnams dang /
NK058(si)001:8969: ting nge 'dzin gyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK058(si)001:8970: las rnams rang bzhin dbyer med par rtogs par bya
NK058(si)001:8971: ste / thams cad sems kyi rnam 'phrul ye nas dag pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:8972: 'di ni rig pa'i me tog dor ba zhes kyang bya /
NK058(si)001:8973: so so ma yin pa rig pa 'dun pa'i phyag ces kyang bya /
NK058(si)001:8974: rang snang gi dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i tshul zhes kyang bya'o //
NK058(si)001:8975: de nas lha'i sku rnams dbyer med du bstim pa'i phyir //
NK058(si)001:8976: ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK058(si)001:8977: yon tan phrin las rmad po che //
NK058(si)001:8978: de nyid du ni mnyam sbyor ba //
NK058(si)001:8979: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK058(si)001:8980: ces pas lha rnams dngos grub stsol ba la phyogs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:8981: badz+ra sa ma ya h'u gis ye shes pa dam
NK058(si)001:8982: tshig pa la chu la chu bzhag pa bzhin dbyer
NK058(si)001:8983: med du thim / badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam gyis
NK058(si)001:8984: rang nyid lha'i dkyil 'khor du 'tshang ma rgyas kyi
NK058(si)001:8985: bar la brtan par bzhugs par bsam /
NK058(si)001:8986: badz+ra sa ma ya hohs dbang du gyur cing dgyes par bsam mo //
NK058(si)001:8987: dzahmh'u bam hohs brtan zhing gsal bar gyur pa nyid /
NK058(si)001:8988: shin tu gsal bar gyur pa nyid //
NK058(si)001:8989: gdan la rdzogs dang sems dpa'i tshul //
NK058(si)001:8991: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK058(si)001:8994: gnyis pa ji ltar mchod pa la gsum las /
NK058(si)001:8995: dang po thun mong gi mchod pa ni sngags phyi pa rnams dang tshul mthun par /
NK058(si)001:8996: lha'i dkyil 'khor la bdag nyid gtso bo'i thugs ka nas las kyi sems dpa'i tshul du byung ste /
NK058(si)001:9002: smon lam 'debs pa la sogs bya'o //
NK058(si)001:9003: de'ang sems kyi rol pa tsam yin pa'i phyir na gnyis su med pa'i ngo bor shes par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:9004: gnyis pa thun mong ma yin pa'i mchod pa ni
NK058(si)001:9005: 'phrul dag'i lha rnams rang gi sprul pa'i longs spyod
NK058(si)001:9007: lha rnams kyi thugs ka nas 'dod yon gyi lha
NK058(si)001:9008: mo rnams spros te de dag gis mchod par bsam
NK058(si)001:9009: pa dang / phyogs bcu thams cad sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams dag par bsam zhing /
NK058(si)001:9010: longs spyod chen po rgyan gyis rol pa glu tshig
NK058(si)001:9011: rol mo'i sprin la sogs 'dod dgu phun sum tshogs
NK058(si)001:9012: pa'i mchod pa chen po rgyun mi 'chad par lhun
NK058(si)001:9013: gyis grub pa kun tu bzang po'i mchod sprin bsam
NK058(si)001:9014: gyis mi khyab pa sprul te /
NK058(si)001:9015: lha la lha rol pa'i tshul gyis mchod par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:9016: gsum pa bla na med pa'i mchod pa la yang /
NK058(si)001:9017: sbyor sgrol gnyis su med pa'i mchod pa /
NK058(si)001:9018: dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i mchod pa /
NK058(si)001:9019: glu ye shes phyag rgya'i mchod pa /
NK058(si)001:9020: dgyes pa chen po bstod pa'i mchod pa rnams gong 'og nas 'byung ba bzhin 'dir mchod cing /
NK058(si)001:9021: khyad par du bdud rtsi'i rjes la yum mtshan dang
NK058(si)001:9022: ldan pa dngos sam yid kyis bsam pa la sbyor
NK058(si)001:9023: ba'i brdas bskul ba'i pad+ma'i khyams su yungs 'bru tsam
NK058(si)001:9025: 'og min nas nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i dkyil 'khor spyan drang la bstim la /
NK058(si)001:9026: rol pa'i bde bas mchod par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:9027: de nyid yul sangs rgyas bde ba chen po la /
NK058(si)001:9028: mchod rdzas bde ba chen pos mchod pas /
NK058(si)001:9029: 'bras bu ye shes bde ba chen po sangs rgyas
NK058(si)001:9030: kyi dgongs pa da lta nyid la mngon du gyur
NK058(si)001:9031: pas bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs thams cad
NK058(si)001:9032: kyi nang nas mchog tu gyur pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:9033: de nas bzlas brjod kyi rim pa ni /
NK058(si)001:9034: lha rnams kyi thugs ka'i yi ge las 'od 'phros
NK058(si)001:9035: pa nam mkha'i dbyings kyi mtha' klas pa'i sems can
NK058(si)001:9036: la phog pas / sgrib pa thams cad sbyang ba la sogs pa las bzhi'i rim pas dmigs te /
NK058(si)001:9037: sems can rnams yi ger gyur thugs kar thim pa'i
NK058(si)001:9038: tshul gyis gtso bo nas sgo ba'i bar lha so
NK058(si)001:9040: yang na sngags kyi phreng ba lha so so'i sku'i
NK058(si)001:9041: dbyibs brgyud cing mkha' gsang nas 'khor ba'i 'od zer
NK058(si)001:9042: bde ba chen po 'phros pa sems can la phog
NK058(si)001:9043: pas / sgrib pa sbyangs te lha'i rang bzhin du
NK058(si)001:9044: gyur pa slar 'dus snying gar thim pa tshul gyis
NK058(si)001:9046: 'khor gyi sa bon tsam phyogs gcig tu bzlas pa la brtson par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:9047: grangs ni 'dir mtha' gcig tu nges par ma gsungs te /
NK058(si)001:9048: ji tsam grub par gyur pa de srid du bzlas par 'dod do //
NK058(si)001:9049: spyir gtso bo la bye ba /
NK058(si)001:9050: 'khor rnams la khri phrag re res grangs kyi bsnyen
NK058(si)001:9051: pa grub par bzhed pas 'dir yang de'i rjes su
NK058(si)001:9052: 'brang bar bya'o // de'ang dus thams cad du lha'i
NK058(si)001:9053: dkyil 'khor las mi 'da' ba'i phyir thun rjes gsal
NK058(si)001:9054: btab pa'i ngang las phyag rgya bzhi'i don dang /
NK058(si)001:9055: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas lugs dran par byas te mnyam par bzhag nas /
NK058(si)001:9056: sems can gyi don du bsngo ba byas la langs
NK058(si)001:9057: te snang srid thams cad lha dang gzhal yas khang
NK058(si)001:9058: dang zhing khams su mos pas spyod lam gyi bya
NK058(si)001:9060: gsum pa dbang bskur zhing 'bras bu bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:9061: thun mong gi sngon du 'gro ba sbyin sreg bstan pa /
NK058(si)001:9062: slob ma gzhug cing dbang bskur ba /
NK058(si)001:9063: bskyed rdzogs bsgoms pa'i 'bras bu bstan pa'o //
NK058(si)001:9066: spyin sreg rnam pa bzhir gsungs te //
NK058(si)001:9067: sa dang rab gnas rnam gnyis dang //
NK058(si)001:9068: bde ba sbyin pa'i dus nyid do //
NK058(si)001:9070: sa chog gi tshe mtshan ma ngan na zhi ba /
NK058(si)001:9071: dkyil 'khor rab tu gnas pa'i tshe rgyas pa /
NK058(si)001:9073: slob ma sta gon gyi tshe rmi lam ngan na drag po'o //
NK058(si)001:9074: de'ang thab khung ni zhi ba la dkar zhing zlum pa ste /
NK058(si)001:9075: rtsig pa yin na zabs su khru gang yod pa'i
NK058(si)001:9076: kha khyer bang rim gsum la 'khor lo dang rdo
NK058(si)001:9077: rje ra ba dang mda' bzhi zhags pa dkar pos
NK058(si)001:9078: mtshan pa'o // bris pa yin na 'khor lo rtsibs
NK058(si)001:9079: brgyad pa'i mtha' ma dang seng mgo spel ma dang
NK058(si)001:9080: mda' bzhi zhags pa dkar pos mtshan pa'o //
NK058(si)001:9081: rgyas pa la gru bzhi ser po ste /
NK058(si)001:9082: rtsig na grub bzhi khru gang ba bang rim gsum gyi nang ma la rin po che'i sgrom bu /
NK058(si)001:9084: mtha' ma la zhags pa ser pos bskor ba'o //
NK058(si)001:9085: bris na rin po che zur brgyad pa rtse mo rin po ches mtshan pa'o //
NK058(si)001:9086: dbang la zla gam dmar po ste /
NK058(si)001:9088: rtsig na mda' bzhi gru bzhi dmar po'o //
NK058(si)001:9089: drag po la gru gsum nag po ste /
NK058(si)001:9090: bris na khro zhal gdengs pa /
NK058(si)001:9091: rtsig na mda' bzhi zhags pa nag pos bskor ba'o //
NK058(si)001:9092: bud shing yang kha dog so so'i dbyibs dang mthun par brtsigs te /
NK058(si)001:9093: sreg rdzas zhi ba la dkar gsum til dang kha zas dkar po'o //
NK058(si)001:9094: rgyas pa la mngar gsum zho dang 'bru sna tshogs ser po /
NK058(si)001:9095: dbang la skyur dang me tog bza' btung sna tshogs dmar po /
NK058(si)001:9096: drag po la tsha ba dug khrag ling+ga sna tshogs nag po'o //
NK058(si)001:9097: de nas thab dang sreg rdzas bsang sbyangs byas te /
NK058(si)001:9098: ye shes kyi me 'od las kyi kha dog can gyi dbus su t+r+aam h+r+aih+aahlasa /
NK058(si)001:9099: las gang byed kyi me lha ra skyes kyi steng na bgrang phreng /
NK058(si)001:9103: g.yon gun+d+he 'dzin pa so so'i mdog can du bskyed la /
NK058(si)001:9105: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK058(si)001:9106: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs 'byung po che //
NK058(si)001:9107: me lha drang srong bram ze mchog /
NK058(si)001:9108: 'di nyid du ni gshegs su gsol //
NK058(si)001:9109: ag+na ye e h+ye hi sa ma ya dza dzahs
NK058(si)001:9110: spyan drangs la dzahmh'u bam hohs bstim pa la mar
NK058(si)001:9111: khu dgang blugs bdun gyis byon zan phul nas mchod
NK058(si)001:9112: bstod byas te / me lha'i sngags des sreg rdzas lan bdun phul la bstod nas /
NK058(si)001:9113: me lha'i lto bar zhi rgyas gnyis la zhi ba'i lha /
NK058(si)001:9114: dbang drag la khro bo bskyed pa'am /
NK058(si)001:9115: ma bskyed kyang rung ste spyan drangs nas bzhugs par gyur pa la /
NK058(si)001:9116: byon zan dgang blugs bdun bdun gyi rjes la mchod bstod byas la /
NK058(si)001:9117: yam shing la sogs pa'i sreg rdzas so so'i rtsa sngags kyis phul ba'i rjes la /
NK058(si)001:9120: w+aa sham ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK058(si)001:9121: m+aa ra ya phata btags la bargya'am stong pa la
NK058(si)001:9122: sogs pa phul nas 'dod don la gsol ba btab
NK058(si)001:9124: rigs mthun pa'i lha gzhan dang /
NK058(si)001:9126: me lha nyid gsal btab la ci 'byor ba phul te /
NK058(si)001:9128: bzod par gsol te gshegs nas bkra shis kyi bar du bya'o //
NK058(si)001:9129: des ni las rnams 'grub cing bar chad zhi bar byed pa'o //
NK058(si)001:9130: gnyis pa slob ma gzhug cing dbang bskur ba la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:9131: slo ma gzhug pa sta gon gyi cho ga /
NK058(si)001:9132: dbang bskur ba dngos gzhi'i rim pa /
NK058(si)001:9133: phan yon bsgrags shing dga' ston bya ba mjug gi las so //
NK058(si)001:9136: dbang phyug 'jug dang bzod par gsol //
NK058(si)001:9137: khrus dgab dri dang lus dbul dang //
NK058(si)001:9138: bgegs bskrad lhar rlob dam tshig sbyin //
NK058(si)001:9139: de nyid dpag dang chu nan dang //
NK058(si)001:9140: bsgrag dang rin cen dor ba dang //
NK058(si)001:9141: lha dbab pa dang nan tan dang //
NK058(si)001:9142: mig dbye dkyil 'khor legs bstan dang //
NK058(si)001:9143: tshogs mchog yon dang rnam bco brgyad //
NK058(si)001:9145: slob dpon 'jug pa'i chos gcig dang /
NK058(si)001:9146: slob ma 'jug pa'i chos bcu bdun no //
NK058(si)001:9148: rdo rje slob dpon chas gos dmar po dang ldan pas dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgor 'dug ste /
NK058(si)001:9149: me tog bzungs nas badz+ra sa ma ya la sogs pa'i sngags brjod pas /
NK058(si)001:9150: dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las dbyer med pas bsams la //
NK058(si)001:9151: ye shes rgyal po zhes pa la sogs pa'i mthar /
NK058(si)001:9152: badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam la sogs pas dngos grub
NK058(si)001:9153: bskul te bdag dang dkyil 'khor tha mi dad par
NK058(si)001:9156: rgyas par 'jug na slob ma 'jug pa bzhin byas la dbang len pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:9157: de nas slob ma rnams dkyil 'khor gyi phyi rol tu dri'i chus khrus byas te /
NK058(si)001:9158: ras la sogs pa'i mig dar dmar pos gdong g.yogs
NK058(si)001:9159: la snyim pa me tog dang bcas te bzhag go
NK058(si)001:9160: // nang du slob dpon gyis thal mo sbyar la /
NK058(si)001:9161: rdo rje ye shes thob byed pa'i //
NK058(si)001:9162: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK058(si)001:9164: bdag gi slob ma gzhug par bgyi //
NK058(si)001:9165: bzod par mdzad de dgongs su gsol //
NK058(si)001:9167: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dgyes nas 'dzum pa
NK058(si)001:9168: dang bcas pas slob ma chug par gnang ba thob
NK058(si)001:9169: par bsam mo // de nas bu rnams mig dar
NK058(si)001:9170: bkab pa de las kyi slob dpon gyis dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:9171: gyi drung ma yin pa'i sgo nang gi bla ma'i
NK058(si)001:9173: rdo rje sems gtso khyod la 'dud //
NK058(si)001:9174: thar lam chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK058(si)001:9175: de nyid dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK058(si)001:9176: mgon po dpa' bor skyabs gsol cing //
NK058(si)001:9177: theg chen khang par gzhug pa dang //
NK058(si)001:9178: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la rtsol //
NK058(si)001:9180: bla mas bu khyod ci la dga' ba smros zhes dris pas lan du /
NK058(si)001:9181: skal ba bzang la bdag dga' zhes so //
NK058(si)001:9183: bu khyod shog cig ci bde ba'i //
NK058(si)001:9184: las spyod rim par 'gro ba dang //
NK058(si)001:9185: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje bzung //
NK058(si)001:9186: rdzogs pa'i ye shes bde chen la //
NK058(si)001:9187: dmigs pa med par gnas phyir du //
NK058(si)001:9188: ser sna spangs pa'i dang yid kyis //
NK058(si)001:9189: gtong zhing rang sems brtan par gzung //
NK058(si)001:9190: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dbang rdzogs sbyin //
NK058(si)001:9192: de nas las kyi slob dpon des rdo rje phyed
NK058(si)001:9193: lag tu gtad pa la slob mas bzung ba dkyil
NK058(si)001:9194: 'khor gyi drung du khrid la phyag 'tshal te /
NK058(si)001:9195: sarba bud+d+ha p+au tsa pa ta n+aa ma +aa sma nan nir+ya ta y+aa mi /
NK058(si)001:9197: bla mas bi shwa badz+ra la sogs pas bgegs bskrad de /
NK058(si)001:9198: lag sor lnga rigs lnga yab yum bskyed la bden pa bdar te /
NK058(si)001:9199: sor mo bsnol bas sbyor mtshams nas byang chub kyi
NK058(si)001:9200: sems kyi 'od zer 'phros nas bu'i sgrib pa bral
NK058(si)001:9202: dngul chu ltar gnas pa la cho ga gsum gyis
NK058(si)001:9203: slob bu rnam snang du bskyed la go bgo zhing
NK058(si)001:9204: bsrung ba byas te bzhag go //
NK058(si)001:9206: byang chub rdo rjes sangs rgyas la //
NK058(si)001:9207: ji ltar mchod pa mdzad pa ltar //
NK058(si)001:9209: dpal ldan rdo rje sku 'chang ba //
NK058(si)001:9210: zhes pa la sogs pa zhus pa'i rjes la /
NK058(si)001:9212: k+aa ya sid+d+hi la sogs pa gnas gsum du 'bru gsum bzhag la 'phro 'du byas te /
NK058(si)001:9213: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya sid+hi la sogs
NK058(si)001:9214: pa brjod nas sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig sbyin
NK058(si)001:9216: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba 'di //
NK058(si)001:9217: dam nyams ma 'dres med pa la //
NK058(si)001:9218: nam yang smra bar ma byed cig /
NK058(si)001:9219: theg pa chen po ston byed pa //
NK058(si)001:9220: nga la brnyas dang smad mi rung //
NK058(si)001:9221: sku gsung thugs la rtag gnas shing //
NK058(si)001:9222: ma lus sems can don gyis shig /
NK058(si)001:9223: ces bu'i snying gar rdo rje gtad la dam tshig dbog /
NK058(si)001:9225: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK058(si)001:9226: dam tshig 'das na sreg par byed //
NK058(si)001:9227: rdo rje khro bo chen por 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:9228: rdo rje'i chu 'di btung bar gyis //
NK058(si)001:9230: zhes dam tshig gi chu blud nas /
NK058(si)001:9232: de lta bas na bu khyod kyis //
NK058(si)001:9233: dam tshig 'di dag bsrung bar gyis //
NK058(si)001:9234: dam tshig bsrungs na dngos grub pas //
NK058(si)001:9235: rdo rje bdud rtsi'i chu 'thung zhig /
NK058(si)001:9236: badz+ra u ka ta ya h'u tha /
NK058(si)001:9237: zhes yon gyi chu nan bya'o //
NK058(si)001:9239: thabs dang shes rab sems nyid kyis //
NK058(si)001:9240: rtag tu dogs pa med gyis la //
NK058(si)001:9241: 'dod pa lnga yi yon tan spyod //
NK058(si)001:9242: ces thob pa'i dam tshig go bar bsgrag go //
NK058(si)001:9244: me tog la sogs rin cen phreng //
NK058(si)001:9245: sngon tshe ye shes bsnyen pa'i lha //
NK058(si)001:9246: thugs rjes gzung bar dgongs nas kyang //
NK058(si)001:9247: gang yin de la bab gyur cig /
NK058(si)001:9248: pra t+ai dza badz+ra hohs me tog gi cod pan
NK058(si)001:9249: dor la lha gang la las 'brel yod pa brtag
NK058(si)001:9250: go // de nas me tog blangs la spyi bor bzhag la /
NK058(si)001:9251: me tog phog pa'i lha de nyid e h+ye his
NK058(si)001:9252: bu'i spyi bor spyan drangs dzahmh'u bam hohs bstims la
NK058(si)001:9253: / bden pa'i tshig gi rjes su /
NK058(si)001:9254: lha de'i mtshan nas brjod nas slob ma 'di'i snying
NK058(si)001:9255: la zhugs te 'di phyir dngos grub phun sum tshogs
NK058(si)001:9256: pa 'grub par gyur cig ces brjod nas /
NK058(si)001:9257: pra be shas bu'i khog pa kha phye bar bsams la /
NK058(si)001:9258: +aa be shas lha dang de nyid gnyis su med par bsam mo //
NK058(si)001:9259: de nas me tog phog pa'i lha'i rigs dang bstun la /
NK058(si)001:9260: rdo rje rgyal po la sogs pa'i gsang mtshan gdags shing /
NK058(si)001:9261: lha de'i sgom bzlas dbog go //
NK058(si)001:9263: de ring dad pa'i shugs kyis ni //
NK058(si)001:9264: dkyil 'khor dam la blta bar bya //
NK058(si)001:9265: sangs rgyas gsung gi rigs su 'khrungs //
NK058(si)001:9266: dngos grub mchog tu gyur par byed //
NK058(si)001:9267: badz+ra tsak+shuhpra be sha phatah ces pas gdong g.yogs dkrol
NK058(si)001:9268: nas mig phye bas ma rig pa'i mun pa bsal
NK058(si)001:9269: / ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor mthong bar mos par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:9270: de nas chos rnams thams cad gnyis med pa'i //
NK058(si)001:9271: dbyings su thim pa'i 'od zer gsal //
NK058(si)001:9272: gcig dang spros pa thams cad med //
NK058(si)001:9273: dkyil 'khor spros med zlum po'i tshul //
NK058(si)001:9274: zhes pa la sogs pas dkyil 'khor gyi don rtags rnams dang /
NK058(si)001:9275: thams cad rang bzhin rnam dag phyir //
NK058(si)001:9276: sgyu 'phrul bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyis //
NK058(si)001:9277: thams cad lha nyid rtag tu sbyor //
NK058(si)001:9278: thams cad ma lus dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK058(si)001:9279: mtshan nyid legs par shes par bya //
NK058(si)001:9280: zhes pas lha'i de kho na nyid rnams bstan to //
NK058(si)001:9281: de nas yon ci 'byor pa dngos sam med kyang khas blang ba dang yid kyis kyang dbul te /
NK058(si)001:9282: hoh mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen po'i bdag nyid
NK058(si)001:9283: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor dang bcas pa dgongs su gsol
NK058(si)001:9284: / rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen po bla ma
NK058(si)001:9285: rdo rje 'dzin pa che ge mo'i zhal snga nas
NK058(si)001:9286: / / bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed nas shin tu phra ba'i chos nyid la thugs sbyangs pas /
NK058(si)001:9287: da lta gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po'i mnga' bdag tu bzhugs pa hohzhing mchis lags /
NK058(si)001:9288: de dag kun gyi thun mong ma yin pa'i bka'
NK058(si)001:9289: zab mo sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dbang 'di lta bu
NK058(si)001:9290: zhig zhus na / snod dang mi ldan pa zhig
NK058(si)001:9291: mchis na'ang sems can rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor can
NK058(si)001:9292: zhig zhus na / la dgongs nas / gnang ba hohzhing mchis lags /
NK058(si)001:9293: bka' drin gyi lan zho sha ma skyud pa'i mtshan ma tsam 'di dag 'bul lags /
NK058(si)001:9296: gnyis pa dbang bskur ba dngos gzhi'i rim pa la gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:9297: dang por phan pa'i dbang bcu bskur ba ni /
NK058(si)001:9298: dbu rgyan cod pan phreng ba dang //
NK058(si)001:9299: go cha rgyal mtshan phyag rgya dang //
NK058(si)001:9300: gdugs dang bum pa bza' btung dang //
NK058(si)001:9301: snying po lnga yi dbang bskur na //
NK058(si)001:9302: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK058(si)001:9303: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK058(si)001:9304: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK058(si)001:9305: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:9307: slob ma lhar gsal pa la /
NK058(si)001:9308: rin po che'i dbu rgyan bcings pas khams gsum chos
NK058(si)001:9309: kyi rgyal por dbang bskur te phyir mi ldog pa'i
NK058(si)001:9310: mtshon byed du rigs lngas dbu brgyan pa'o //
NK058(si)001:9311: de'ang rnam par shes pa'i tshogs ye shes lngar gsal ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK058(si)001:9312: cod pan bcings pas thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK058(si)001:9313: phreng bas byang chub kyi yan lag thob cing gzugs
NK058(si)001:9314: dang ting nge 'dzin thob pa'i dgos pa yod do
NK058(si)001:9315: // de bzhin du go chas nyon mongs pa'i mtshon
NK058(si)001:9316: gyis mi tshugs shing rtsa gnas d+r+wa ba'i tshul du
NK058(si)001:9317: gnas pa sa ya phrag bcu gsum dag par byed
NK058(si)001:9318: // pa'o // rgyal mtshan gyis mi mthun pa'i phyogs
NK058(si)001:9319: las rnam par rgyal ba ste 'khor ba'i g.yul las
NK058(si)001:9321: phyag rgyas ni rtog tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis yi ge 'khor lo'i sa thob par byed do //
NK058(si)001:9322: gdugs kyis nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba las skyob cing
NK058(si)001:9323: thugs rje'i char 'bebs pa ste dung khang na rtsa
NK058(si)001:9324: 'dab sum cu rtsa gnyis dag par byed pa'o //
NK058(si)001:9325: bum pas nyon mongs pa'i dri ma sbyong zhing zag
NK058(si)001:9326: pa med pa'i chu rgyun gyis rgyud brlan par byed
NK058(si)001:9327: pa'o // bza' btung ni 'dod yon rgyan du shar
NK058(si)001:9328: bas rgud pa sel zhing bsam gtan gyi bde bas
NK058(si)001:9330: snying po lnga ni nyon mongs pa lnga dang phung po lnga /
NK058(si)001:9331: ye shes lnga dang rigs lngar dag par byed pa'o //
NK058(si)001:9332: de ltar dbang bcu ni so so'i dbang rdzas kyis
NK058(si)001:9333: bskur bas sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK058(si)001:9334: yon tan phrin las phun sum tshogs pa'i nus pa
NK058(si)001:9336: de dag gi ngo bo ni thal ba las /
NK058(si)001:9337: khams bcu bde ba'i lam gnyis dang //
NK058(si)001:9338: dbu ma bcud mdud tshad ldan par //
NK058(si)001:9339: d+r+wa ba'i rtsa dang dbang po dang //
NK058(si)001:9340: phung sogs ye shes bde 'khor lo //
NK058(si)001:9341: h'u gis bde ba'i ye shes bcas //
NK058(si)001:9342: tshogs brgyad rang bzhin ye shes lnga //
NK058(si)001:9343: sngags rdzas dgongs pas gang blangs pa //
NK058(si)001:9344: kun nas ldang zhing skyob pa yis //
NK058(si)001:9345: sdug bsngal las grol rigs su nges //
NK058(si)001:9347: gnyis pa nus pa'i dbang lnga las /
NK058(si)001:9349: bla ma yab yum gtso bo yab yum du gsal
NK058(si)001:9350: ba'i sbyor mtshams nas yi ge b+h+r+aum dmar ser gcig
NK058(si)001:9351: 'phros pa slob bu'i rna ba'i nang du phog par
NK058(si)001:9352: bsam zhing / las kyi rdo rjes der bdud rtsi'i thig le re byas la /
NK058(si)001:9353: b+h+r+aum zhu ba las rna ba gnyis su 'khor lo
NK058(si)001:9354: rtsibs bzhi gru chad bzhi la sgo bzhi gtod par
NK058(si)001:9355: / yi ge t+r+aam zung lnga ya bcu dzahmh'u bam hohdang bcas pa 'od du zhu ba las /
NK058(si)001:9356: rin cen 'byung ldan yab yum gyi phyogs bzhir /
NK058(si)001:9364: rdo rje bde ma ste pho brang gi lha bcu /
NK058(si)001:9365: sgo ba yab yum dang bcas te bco brgyad gsal btab la /
NK058(si)001:9366: bla ma'i thugs ka nas phyag rgya'i lha mo bzhi
NK058(si)001:9367: spros la 'og min nas ye shes pa de 'dra
NK058(si)001:9368: ba spyan drangs te bstims pas /
NK058(si)001:9369: spyir sgrib pa mtha' dag dag cing sgos su chos nyan pa la sgrib pa thams cad dag ste /
NK058(si)001:9370: slob ma lha dang bcas pa 'od du zhu ba
NK058(si)001:9371: rin cen 'byung ldan du bskyed pa la gsang ba'i
NK058(si)001:9372: snying po'i po ti gtad de /
NK058(si)001:9374: gsang ba gsang chen gsang mchog gang //
NK058(si)001:9375: gsang ba kun las mnyan par bya //
NK058(si)001:9376: gsang ba'i don nyid brtag pa las //
NK058(si)001:9377: gzhan du smra bar bya ba min //
NK058(si)001:9379: de bzhin du 'og ma la'ang 'gres la /
NK058(si)001:9380: gnyis pa sgom pa'i dbang ni me tog phog pa'i
NK058(si)001:9381: lha gang yin gyi rigs lnga'i sa bon las de'i
NK058(si)001:9382: dkyil 'khor bskyed de zhu ba las /
NK058(si)001:9383: yang lha de nyid du bskyed la /
NK058(si)001:9384: dbang rdzas phreng ba gtad de //
NK058(si)001:9385: dus gsum rgyal ba'i sras chen po //
NK058(si)001:9386: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje bzung //
NK058(si)001:9387: rgyal ba thams cad mnyes mchod la //
NK058(si)001:9388: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK058(si)001:9390: sangs rgyas gsang bas snying nang du h'u las rdo rjer gyur pa mi bskyod par bsams pa las /
NK058(si)001:9391: dbang rdzas rdo rje nyid du sbyor bas mdzad do //
NK058(si)001:9392: gsum pa 'chad pa'i dbang ni lce la b+h+r+aum 'phros
NK058(si)001:9393: gzhal yas khang gi rnam par gyur pa'i nang du
NK058(si)001:9394: h+r+aihdang dzahmh'u bam hohr gyur pa las /
NK058(si)001:9395: snang ba mtha' yas yab yum la /
NK058(si)001:9403: gsal bkra ma dang bcas pa sngar bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:9404: dbang rdzas tshar rnon 'khor lo bris pa lag tu gtad de //
NK058(si)001:9405: chos kyi bdud rtsi bla med kyis //
NK058(si)001:9406: dad ldan skyes bu ngom par byos //
NK058(si)001:9407: rab 'bring tha ma'i blo can la //
NK058(si)001:9408: mthun par gsang bsgrag gzhan du min //
NK058(si)001:9410: bzhi pa phrin las kyi dbang ni lag pa gnyis
NK058(si)001:9411: la sngar bzhin gzhal yas khang du h'u la sogs
NK058(si)001:9412: pa gyur pas / don yod grub pa yab yum la /
NK058(si)001:9420: 'bebs ma dang bcas pa'i dmigs pa sngar bzhin 'gres la /
NK058(si)001:9421: dbang rdzas rdo rje rgya gram lag tu gtad de //
NK058(si)001:9422: khyod ni rdo rje las yin gyi //
NK058(si)001:9423: las rnams ma lus kun gyis shig /
NK058(si)001:9425: khyod kyi dgos pa byed pa yin //
NK058(si)001:9427: lnga pa rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang ni mgo dang
NK058(si)001:9428: yan lag la dkyil 'khor lnga dang phyi rol tu
NK058(si)001:9430: de'ang dpung mgo g.yas su mi bskyod pa yab yum gyi phyogs bzhir sems dpa' rdo rje /
NK058(si)001:9438: mgo la rnam snang yab yum /
NK058(si)001:9447: g.yon gyi dpung mgor rin cen 'byung ldan gyi dkyil 'khor sngar smos pa bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:9448: rkang pa g.yas g.yon la don grub dang /
NK058(si)001:9449: 'od dpag med kyi dkyil 'khor sngar bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:9450: phyi rol gyi phyogs mtshams steng 'og bcur khro bo
NK058(si)001:9451: bcu'i dkyil 'khor bsgoms la ye shes pa bstims te
NK058(si)001:9452: / dgyes nas sbyor ba mdzad pa 'od du zhu bas slob ma kun tu bzang por bskyed la /
NK058(si)001:9453: dbang rdzas rdo rje dang dril bu lag tu gtad de //
NK058(si)001:9454: phyogs bcu dus bzhi thams cad kyi //
NK058(si)001:9455: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje che //
NK058(si)001:9456: dkyil 'khor kun gyi byed pa po //
NK058(si)001:9457: dkyil 'khor kun gyi sbyin pa spyod //
NK058(si)001:9458: ces rjes su gnang ba sbyin no //
NK058(si)001:9459: de nas zab dbang gi don du man+dala phul la gsol ba btab pas /
NK058(si)001:9460: bla ma yab yum gtso bo yab yum du bskyed pa'i mkha' gsang byin gyis brlabs te /
NK058(si)001:9461: sbyor ba mdzad pa'i byang chub kyi sems h'u gi
NK058(si)001:9462: rnam pa'i rgyun yab kyi rdo rje nas byung ba
NK058(si)001:9463: / yum gyi pad+ma'i rtser bskyil ba rdo rje sems
NK058(si)001:9464: dpa'i skur gsal ba slob ma'i lce thog tu bzhag
NK058(si)001:9466: de ma nus na yum gyi pad+ma'i sna rtse nas bus len pa ni shes rab kyi gsang dbang /
NK058(si)001:9467: de yang ma nus na yab yum gyi mkha' nas
NK058(si)001:9468: yab kyi lce yis blangs te bu'i lce thog tu
NK058(si)001:9469: ster ba thabs shes rab gnyis su med pa'i gsang
NK058(si)001:9470: dbang bskur ba'o // de ltar lce thog tu bzhag pas bdud rtsi'i rgyun snying gar babs te /
NK058(si)001:9471: 'gro drug gi las dang gnyid kyi bag chags sbyangs
NK058(si)001:9472: bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ngang la blo gnas par
NK058(si)001:9473: bya'o // de nas shes rab ma nyid bu dang
NK058(si)001:9474: bcas pa gsang dbang bzhin byin gyis brlabs pa byas
NK058(si)001:9475: bya'o // te / snyoms par 'jug pa'i byang chub
NK058(si)001:9476: kyi sems pad+ma'i rtser babs pa las nus pas bzlog
NK058(si)001:9477: cing bde ba'i ngang der bla mas gsal gdab pa
NK058(si)001:9478: ni shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ngo //
NK058(si)001:9479: de nas bde ba'i ngang de nyid gang du'ang ma
NK058(si)001:9480: grub pa'i rang bzhin spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang
NK058(si)001:9481: bral ba rdzogs pa chen po'i ngo bor ngo sprad
NK058(si)001:9482: pa ni bde ba chen po'i dbang ste mthar thug
NK058(si)001:9483: gi lam mo // 'dir bla mas shes rab ye
NK058(si)001:9484: shes kyi dbang ma blangs par gzhan la gsang dbang
NK058(si)001:9486: slob mas kyang dbang yongs su rdzogs par ma byas
NK058(si)001:9487: par lam mi bgrod par de ltar bskur zhing len
NK058(si)001:9489: de ni slob ma blo stobs can chags pa dang ma bral ba'i dbang du byas pa'o //
NK058(si)001:9490: blo'i stobs chung ba grol lam pa la ni ting
NK058(si)001:9491: nge 'dzin dang byang chub bdud rtsi'i ril bu tsam
NK058(si)001:9492: gyis byed pa'o // kha cig 'dir gsang dbang tsam
NK058(si)001:9493: du 'dod pas ni dngos dang shugs kyi don ma
NK058(si)001:9497: dang pos sa bon 'jog pa ste //
NK058(si)001:9498: gnyis pas nus pa bskyed pa yin //
NK058(si)001:9499: gsum pas nyams myong bskyed pa'o //
NK058(si)001:9500: bzhi bas de nyid brtan par byed //
NK058(si)001:9501: lnga pa brtan pas nyams blangs pas //
NK058(si)001:9504: de'ang slob dpon snga ma kha cig phan dbang bcu /
NK058(si)001:9506: zab dbang gsum ste bco brgyad du 'dod cing /
NK058(si)001:9507: kha cig zab dbang gsum gcig tu bsdus nas bcu drug tu 'dod kyang /
NK058(si)001:9508: 'dir phan pa'i dbang dang nus pa'i dbang zhes gnyis su bsdus pas /
NK058(si)001:9509: zab dbang ni nus dbang gi khongs su 'du bas bco lnga kho na'o //
NK058(si)001:9510: gsum pa phan yon bsgrags shing dga' ston bya ba mjug gi las la lnga las /
NK058(si)001:9511: dang po dbang bskur ba'i phan yon la rgyal ba'i sras su chud pa /
NK058(si)001:9512: theg pa dman par mi ldog pa /
NK058(si)001:9514: lung bstan thob pa bzhi las /
NK058(si)001:9515: rgyal ba'i sras su chud pa ni dbang thob pa
NK058(si)001:9516: de nas bzung ste sangs rgyas kyi sras su dgongs
NK058(si)001:9517: shing / tshe 'di nyid la 'dod pa 'grub cing /
NK058(si)001:9518: phyi mar mtho ris dang thar pa 'grub la /
NK058(si)001:9519: ngan song thams cad rgyun chad pa ste /
NK058(si)001:9521: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK058(si)001:9522: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK058(si)001:9523: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK058(si)001:9524: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:9526: theg pa dman par mi ldog pa ni rdo rje rtse mo las /
NK058(si)001:9527: ji srid sa brgyad ma thob par //
NK058(si)001:9528: de srid theg pa dman pas 'jig /
NK058(si)001:9529: gsang chen theg pa 'di ru ni //
NK058(si)001:9530: zhugs pa gang dang gang yin pa //
NK058(si)001:9531: de ni rgyal sras sa pa yin //
NK058(si)001:9533: dus nye ba ni de nyid las /
NK058(si)001:9534: gzhan tshe bcu drug gis thob pa //
NK058(si)001:9536: rgyal ba'i sras kyi sa thob kyang //
NK058(si)001:9537: dkyil 'khor gsang bar ma gyur na //
NK058(si)001:9538: ji ltar khyod kyi de byung ba //
NK058(si)001:9539: de bzhin theg pa yid ches gyis //
NK058(si)001:9540: skyes dang skye ba thams cad du //
NK058(si)001:9541: rdo rje can ni dngos brtson 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:9542: skye ba bcu drug mthar thug pas //
NK058(si)001:9543: zhi ba'i sangs rgyas nyid thob 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:9544: rgyal ba'i sras kyi sa thob kyang //
NK058(si)001:9545: bskal pa grangs med gnyis ka spyod //
NK058(si)001:9546: gsang ba'i theg par ma zhugs pas //
NK058(si)001:9547: bcu drug gis ni 'gyur ma yin //
NK058(si)001:9550: dbang bskur yang dag sbyin ldan na //
NK058(si)001:9551: skye zhing skye bar dbang bskur 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:9552: de yi skye ba bdun na ni //
NK058(si)001:9553: ma bsgrubs pa yang dngos grub 'thob //
NK058(si)001:9556: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gyi rgyud las /
NK058(si)001:9557: slob ma dkyil 'khor btsud nas kyang //
NK058(si)001:9558: yon gyi mchog dag blangs nas ni //
NK058(si)001:9559: rdo rje'i ming gi dbang bsgyur bas //
NK058(si)001:9560: de bzhin gshegs par de lung bstan //
NK058(si)001:9561: phyag rgya'i sbyor ba 'di dag gis //
NK058(si)001:9562: byang chub snying po'i bar du ni //
NK058(si)001:9563: rdo rje'i ming du rab tu grags //
NK058(si)001:9564: de nas sangs rgyas su yang 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:9566: de'ang sa thob pa'i yon tan dang dbang thob pa gnyis rdzu 'phrul la sogs pa mi 'dra yang /
NK058(si)001:9567: sangs rgyas thob pa la 'di nyid nye bas lam zab pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:9568: gnyis pa dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK058(si)001:9570: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK058(si)001:9571: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK058(si)001:9572: nyan pa la sogs brtson pa rnams //
NK058(si)001:9576: gang zhig byang chub sems ni ma bskyed dang //
NK058(si)001:9577: gang zhig dkyil 'khor du ni ma zhugs pas //
NK058(si)001:9578: nga yi gsang sngags bzlas na phung bar 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:9580: gsum pa bla ma mnyes par bya ba ni dgongs 'dus las /
NK058(si)001:9581: dam pa bla ma bshes gnyen zhes //
NK058(si)001:9582: brjod pa'i thog mar zhe sa gzhug /
NK058(si)001:9583: khyad par cis kyang mnyes par bya //
NK058(si)001:9585: ji ltar mnyes par bya ba yang de las /
NK058(si)001:9586: mnyes par bya ba'i yo byad brgyad //
NK058(si)001:9587: dam pa de la rdzogs par dbul //
NK058(si)001:9588: skyo dub med pa'i dad pa dang //
NK058(si)001:9589: gyong khengs med pa'i mnyen lcug dang //
NK058(si)001:9590: ser sna med pa'i zang zing dang //
NK058(si)001:9591: som nyi med pa'i sri zhu dang //
NK058(si)001:9592: g.yo rgyu med pa'i drang thad dang //
NK058(si)001:9593: kha gsags med pa'i rang rgyud dang //
NK058(si)001:9594: rmongs pa med pa'i shes rab dang //
NK058(si)001:9595: dri ma med pa'i lhag sems brgyad //
NK058(si)001:9596: dam pa de la rdzogs par dbul //
NK058(si)001:9598: de'ang bla ma'i bka' mi bcag cing ci byed kyang zhus te bya ba yang /
NK058(si)001:9600: dkyil 'khor la sogs sbyin sreg dang //
NK058(si)001:9601: slob ma gzung dang chos smra ba //
NK058(si)001:9602: lung ma byung bar mi brtsam ste //
NK058(si)001:9603: dam pa'i yul nas de mi rigs //
NK058(si)001:9604: gang des gzhan gyi don byas na //
NK058(si)001:9605: de yis yo byad mi spyad de //
NK058(si)001:9606: de kun dam pa de la dbul //
NK058(si)001:9607: dam pa'i slob ma slob mar yang //
NK058(si)001:9608: dam pa'i mdun du mi rigs so //
NK058(si)001:9610: bla ma'i yo byad rang dgar spyod na'ang skyon du 'gyur te de las /
NK058(si)001:9611: dam pa'i yo byad mnga' dbul ba'i //
NK058(si)001:9612: phongs pa de yis gzhan bsgral na //
NK058(si)001:9613: de yang dbul po nyid du 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:9614: 'tsho ba dam pa dang bral bas //
NK058(si)001:9615: longs spyod chen pos phongs pa ni //
NK058(si)001:9616: mu ge'i dgon pa nyid du lhung //
NK058(si)001:9618: de'ang bla mar bzung nas gus par bya ste /
NK058(si)001:9619: dam par bzung bar gyur phan chad //
NK058(si)001:9620: dam par nges dang ma nges kyang //
NK058(si)001:9621: bka' bcag lung por ga la srid //
NK058(si)001:9622: gal te de yis rgya nyams na //
NK058(si)001:9623: rdo rje'i dmyal bar de 'gro ste //
NK058(si)001:9624: mi bzad sdug bsngal chen por 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:9627: gal te yon tan mi ldan yang //
NK058(si)001:9628: bla mar bzung nas spangs byas na //
NK058(si)001:9629: kun gyi slob dpon brnyas pa yin //
NK058(si)001:9630: dus gsum sangs rgyas skur ba yin //
NK058(si)001:9631: de yis nyes pa brjod mi long //
NK058(si)001:9633: mdor na nyes pa tshad med de /
NK058(si)001:9635: dngos grub zhing gyur dbang phyug ni //
NK058(si)001:9636: sangs rgyas kun gyi mtshan nyid de //
NK058(si)001:9637: 'bad pas mnyes par mi byed pa //
NK058(si)001:9638: bskal par bsgribs nas mun nag sogs //
NK058(si)001:9639: bde bas rab tu brel gyur cing //
NK058(si)001:9640: thabs dang shes rab la sogs lam //
NK058(si)001:9641: shin tu ring bar 'gyur ba yin //
NK058(si)001:9642: nus mthu byin ldan bde gshegs lung //
NK058(si)001:9643: nor bu rgya mtsho mkha' lta bu //
NK058(si)001:9644: sa bcu'i sems dpa' chen pos kyang //
NK058(si)001:9645: nus mthu gzu lum ma yin phyir //
NK058(si)001:9646: gus pa'i rim pas blang bar bya //
NK058(si)001:9648: bzhi pa dam tshig bsrung ba ni /
NK058(si)001:9650: dbang rnams legs par rdzogs gyur bas //
NK058(si)001:9651: rtsa ba yan lag dam tshig kun //
NK058(si)001:9652: ma nyams rab tu bsrung bar bya //
NK058(si)001:9653: des ni dngos grub mchog thob 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:9655: lnga pa dga' ston bya ba ni //
NK058(si)001:9657: de nas rigs kyi bu mchog des //
NK058(si)001:9658: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK058(si)001:9659: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK058(si)001:9660: rab tu gces dang yid 'thad dbul //
NK058(si)001:9662: gsum pa bskyed rdzogs bsgoms pa'i 'bras bu bstan pa la gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:9663: gnas skabs su dbang thob pa des dam tshig la
NK058(si)001:9664: gnas shing bskyed pa dang rdzogs pa'i rim pa bsgoms
NK058(si)001:9665: pas / rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin las tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin 'thob ste /
NK058(si)001:9666: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK058(si)001:9667: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK058(si)001:9668: dbang sgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK058(si)001:9670: de'i rten la phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin yang grub nas /
NK058(si)001:9671: gnyis pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin thob ste /
NK058(si)001:9672: de tshe bcu drug tshun chad kyis //
NK058(si)001:9673: sku lnga lhun gyi rdzogs pa ni //
NK058(si)001:9674: zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK058(si)001:9675: tshe lo brgya ba'i tshe lo bcu drug tsam na mchog 'grub par grags kyang /
NK058(si)001:9676: rang rang gi rig 'dzin de dus kyi mi tshe
NK058(si)001:9677: gang yod la brtsis pa'i tshe bcu drug gi lo
NK058(si)001:9681: skye ba bcu drug mthar thug pas //
NK058(si)001:9685: gnyis pa gzhung gi don la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:9686: dkyil 'khor gsungs tshul mdor bstan pa dang /
NK058(si)001:9687: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:9689: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas
NK058(si)001:9690: de bzhin gshegs pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye
NK058(si)001:9691: shes kyis 'gro ba'i don la dgyes pa chen pos
NK058(si)001:9692: kun tu bzang po nyid rdo rjee gsang ba'i dam
NK058(si)001:9693: tshig gi dkyil 'khor bkod de dbang bskur ba'i rim
NK058(si)001:9694: pa la snyoms par zhugs pa ste yum dang lhan
NK058(si)001:9695: cig phyogs nas ched du brjod pa 'di skad ces
NK058(si)001:9696: brjod do // gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:9697: dbang po rab mchog gi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba /
NK058(si)001:9698: dman pa rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba /
NK058(si)001:9699: gang du dbang bskur ba'i don bsdu ba'o //
NK058(si)001:9701: yum gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba dang /
NK058(si)001:9702: yab kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba'o //
NK058(si)001:9704: dkyil 'khor dgod cing sbyin sreg bya ba /
NK058(si)001:9705: snang la rang bzhin med pa'i mchod pa dbul ba /
NK058(si)001:9714: dang po gnas gang du dkyil 'khor dgod pa ni
NK058(si)001:9715: mchog tu gsang ba'i bde ba chen po ni shes
NK058(si)001:9716: shing rig par dkar bas shin tu phra ba'i don
NK058(si)001:9717: yin la / de nyid tshe 'dir mchog bsgrub pa'i
NK058(si)001:9718: med du mi rung ba'i dam tshig gi mchog yin
NK058(si)001:9719: yin la / pas na / de gang las skyes
NK058(si)001:9720: shing 'dzin pa phyag rgya mtshan ldan bde ba chen
NK058(si)001:9721: pos lus rgyas pa'i phyag mthil yum mkha' rnam par
NK058(si)001:9722: dag pa nyid du dbang bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor gnas
NK058(si)001:9723: yin la / pas na / so // gnyis pa
NK058(si)001:9724: dkyil 'khor gyi tshad ni bde ba chen po gnyis
NK058(si)001:9725: su med pa'i ye shes sangs rgyas thams cad kyi
NK058(si)001:9726: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dam pa de nyid sor gyi
NK058(si)001:9729: dga' bral gyi dga' ba dang /
NK058(si)001:9730: lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba bzhi yi tshad du bya ba'o //
NK058(si)001:9731: de skad du'ang klong gsal las /
NK058(si)001:9732: yum mkha' sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK058(si)001:9733: gsang ba zab mo'i dkyil 'khor te //
NK058(si)001:9734: ye shes bzhi yi rang bzhin du //
NK058(si)001:9735: gnyis su med par dbang nyid bskur //
NK058(si)001:9737: gsum pa thig gdab pa ni /
NK058(si)001:9738: gnas de'i rgyud sbyong ba ste /
NK058(si)001:9739: de'ang 'bru lnga ni skye ba'i sa bon te dug lnga ye shes su gnas pa'o //
NK058(si)001:9740: spos lnga ni de nyid gnas su dag pa'i ye shes lnga'o //
NK058(si)001:9741: rin cen lnga ni phung po lnga'o //
NK058(si)001:9742: snying po lnga ni sku lnga'o //
NK058(si)001:9743: sman lnga dang ni rigs lnga'o //
NK058(si)001:9744: bdud rtsi lnga ni sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK058(si)001:9745: las lnga dbyer mi phyed pa'i sems nyid rnam par
NK058(si)001:9747: rab mnyam la zhes pa ni de ltar yin pa
NK058(si)001:9748: la yin par shes par byed pas chos thams cad
NK058(si)001:9749: sangs rgyas par mnyam pa nyid du ston pa'o //
NK058(si)001:9750: de ltar rig pas yum gyi rgyud ye shes chen
NK058(si)001:9751: por gsal ba'i tshangs thig gi mchog rnam par dag
NK058(si)001:9752: pa ni gsal gdab bar bya'o //
NK058(si)001:9753: de'ang sngar gsang sngags la rgyud ma sbyangs pa'i phyag
NK058(si)001:9754: rgya yin na slob dpon des dge bsnyen nas rim
NK058(si)001:9755: gyis rgyud dag par gsal bar byed pa'i thig rnams
NK058(si)001:9756: gdab par bya'o // rgyud sbyang zin la ni bskyed rdzogs la sogs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:9757: rtsa btsal ba la sogs pa'i cho ga byed pa la thig tu barjooda pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:9758: 'dir kha cig ba so la sogs pa la dkyil 'khor sor bzhi bri ba ste /
NK058(si)001:9759: de la thig gdab pa yang /
NK058(si)001:9760: phung po lnga dag pa sku lnga'i rang bzhin nas /
NK058(si)001:9765: dbang po lnga dag pa phrin las lnga'i rang bzhin ga bur /
NK058(si)001:9768: a ka ru ste spos lnga /
NK058(si)001:9769: yul lnga dag pa yon tan lnga'i rang bzhin gser /
NK058(si)001:9773: nor bu ste rin cen lnga /
NK058(si)001:9774: rnam shes lnga dag pa ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin lan tsh+wa /
NK058(si)001:9779: 'dod yon lnga dag pa gsung lnga'i rang bzhin shu dag dkar po /
NK058(si)001:9783: a mra'i 'bras bu ste sman lnga /
NK058(si)001:9784: khams lnga dag pa rigs lnga'i rang bzhin nyi ma /
NK058(si)001:9788: sha chen gyi dwas ma ste bdud rtsi lnga rnams
NK058(si)001:9789: cha mnyam pa'i chus srad bu sbangs nas thig 'debs
NK058(si)001:9790: par 'dod cing / tshon bkye ba'i dkyil 'khor de slob dpon gyi phyag mthil du bzhag nas /
NK058(si)001:9791: de'i phyogs mtshams su mchod pas bskor nas dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:9792: bsgrub pa'i bar du byas te dbang bskur bar bzhed
NK058(si)001:9793: pa ni / gzhung 'di'i dgongs pa ma yin te /
NK058(si)001:9794: de lta bu'i dkyil 'khor bri bar yang mi nus shing /
NK058(si)001:9795: gal te nus na'ang der dbang bskur ba la yon tan lhag po med de /
NK058(si)001:9796: chung bas yod na sku gzugs la sogs pa yang
NK058(si)001:9797: shin tu chung ba bsod nams che bar thal ba'i
NK058(si)001:9798: phyir dang / bcos ma ni dbang po rtul po'i rim pa ste /
NK058(si)001:9800: ri mor gnas pa'i las dang ni //
NK058(si)001:9801: thig la tshon dgye'i rim pa dang //
NK058(si)001:9803: grub pa'i dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'o //
NK058(si)001:9804: bcos ma gnyis kyi ngo bo gang //
NK058(si)001:9805: de ni bsgrub bya'i dkyil 'khor te //
NK058(si)001:9806: mkhas pa'i bsgrub byar de mi 'dod //
NK058(si)001:9809: rang bzhin lus kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba yin no //
NK058(si)001:9810: bzhi pa ji ltar bri ba ni yum mkha'i rang
NK058(si)001:9811: bzhin gzhal yas khang gi rnam par gnas pa de
NK058(si)001:9812: nyid gsal bar byed pa ste /
NK058(si)001:9813: dbus su lte ba rtsibs dang ldan pa yi ngo bo b+ha ga'i nang gi rtsa 'dab bzhi'o //
NK058(si)001:9814: de'i rtsibs bzhi pa'i 'khor lo mu khyud dang bcas
NK058(si)001:9815: pa de'i phyi rol gyi dbyibs gru chad bzhi dang
NK058(si)001:9816: gru bzhi pa yi rnam pa can gyi bar khyams
NK058(si)001:9817: pad+ma'i sgo khyud ldan pa la de ltar gsal bar
NK058(si)001:9818: bya'o // lnga pa mtshan ma dgod pa ni lha'i
NK058(si)001:9819: gnas der snyigs ma dkar dmar gyi ngo bo mtshon
NK058(si)001:9820: pa sen zlum tsam gyi nyi zla'i gdan la sran
NK058(si)001:9821: ma'i ga'u phyed pa tsa na'i 'bru tsam gyi pad+ma'i
NK058(si)001:9822: gdan gyi steng du shin tu dwangs ma yungs 'bru
NK058(si)001:9823: tsam gyi ngo bo yi ge'i rnam pa h'u du
NK058(si)001:9824: gsal ba las rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i phyag
NK058(si)001:9825: rgya rdo rje til 'bru tsam du bris pa ste
NK058(si)001:9826: bya'o // gsal gdab bo // gnyis pa mchod pa ni /
NK058(si)001:9827: phyag rgya'i g.yon phyogs su dmigs pa'i rten yod dam
NK058(si)001:9828: med kyang rung ste tshogs dang mchod pas brgyan par
NK058(si)001:9829: bya ba yang / kha dog bsgyur ba'i gos bcos
NK058(si)001:9830: bu'i rnam pa dar dang ras ni sna tshogs pa
NK058(si)001:9831: bya ba yang / dang / dbu rgyan mgul rgyan la sogs pa'i rgyan sna tshogs dang /
NK058(si)001:9832: do shal dang d+r+wa phyed la sogs pa'i phreng ba sna tshogs dang /
NK058(si)001:9833: ja dang chang la sogs pa'i btung ba sna tshogs dang /
NK058(si)001:9834: sha dang thud dang zla phrum la sogs pa'i bro bas bskor cing /
NK058(si)001:9835: shin tu snyan pa'i glu dang bstod pa'i tshig mdzes
NK058(si)001:9836: par byed pa'i skye bos rkang pa'i bro dang lag
NK058(si)001:9838: dung dang cha lang dang pi wang dang gling bu
NK058(si)001:9839: dang gdugs dang rgyal mtshan la sogs pa'i rol mo'i
NK058(si)001:9840: sprin phung bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i tshogs kyis rab
NK058(si)001:9841: tu mchod cing / gzhan yang mchod pa'i rkyen du
NK058(si)001:9842: gyur pa'i yum dang yid 'jo bar byed pa'i dga'
NK058(si)001:9843: ma dang na tshod gzhon nur gyur pa'i sems ma
NK058(si)001:9844: yis rol pa'i dga' ba bskyed pa dang /
NK058(si)001:9845: reg bya'i dga' ba bskyed pa dang /
NK058(si)001:9846: mig gi dga' ba bskyed pa ste rnam pa gsum
NK058(si)001:9847: po ji ltar 'dod pa'i las bzhin mchod pas brgyan
NK058(si)001:9848: par bya'o // skabs 'di'i mchod pa'i gtso bo ni
NK058(si)001:9849: bde ba ster bar byed pa'i yum phyi nang gsang
NK058(si)001:9850: ba gsum gyi yul rnams yin par bzhed do //
NK058(si)001:9851: gnyis pa sbyin sreg gi las la gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:9852: dang po las bzhi'i sbyin sreg spyir bstan pa ni /
NK058(si)001:9853: las bzhi'i rim pas thab khung gi dbyibs kyang zlum po la sogs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:9854: kha dog kyang dkar po la sogs pa so so'i
NK058(si)001:9855: mtshan nyid tshang ba dang ldan par me lha'i rang
NK058(si)001:9856: bzhin mchod sbyin gsol ba'i zhal du gyur pa'i lto
NK058(si)001:9857: bar 'jig rten las 'das pa'i me lha bos te
NK058(si)001:9858: spyan drangs la zho zan dang mar khu la sogs
NK058(si)001:9859: pa bza' btung bro ba'i tshogs rnams kyis mchod cing
NK058(si)001:9861: rgyas pa la rin po che la sogs pa las
NK058(si)001:9862: bzhi'i mchod pa so so'i sngags dang ting nge 'dzin
NK058(si)001:9863: gyis rab tu sbyin par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:9864: gnyis pa khro bo'i sbyin sreg bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK058(si)001:9865: zhi ba'i sbyin sreg ji lta bar khro bo'i dkyil
NK058(si)001:9866: 'khor du yang thab dang lha'i mtshan nyid la sogs
NK058(si)001:9867: pa de bzhin du bya ste /
NK058(si)001:9868: ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa'i gnad shin tu phra
NK058(si)001:9869: zhing zab mo rnams la rab tu sbyangs pa yis
NK058(si)001:9870: rnal 'byor pas / lha'i dkyil 'khor bsam yas dag
NK058(si)001:9871: la'ang cho ga'i rim pa de kho na bzhin du
NK058(si)001:9872: sbyin sreg gis mnyes par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:9873: de'ang lha gang gi dkyil 'khor la las gang gis
NK058(si)001:9874: sbyin sreg ji ltar byed pa'i tshul rnams ni gnas
NK058(si)001:9875: skabs dang sbyar ba'i rang gi rig pas legs par
NK058(si)001:9876: dpags pa de tsam du bya'o //
NK058(si)001:9877: gnyis pa snang la rang bzhin med pa mchod pa 'bul ba la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:9878: ting nge 'dzin yid kyi mchod pa dang /
NK058(si)001:9879: gsang ba bde ba chen po'i mchod pa'o //
NK058(si)001:9881: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mchod pa dang /
NK058(si)001:9882: de'i rdzogs rim don dam pa ye shes kyi mchod pa'o //
NK058(si)001:9884: ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod sprin bkod pa ni dkyil
NK058(si)001:9885: 'khor la yid sprul gyis ji ltar mchod pa'i phyag
NK058(si)001:9886: rgya chen po ni rang gi sems kyi bkod pa'i
NK058(si)001:9887: yid bzhin gyi nor bu'i sprin phung 'khrigs pa'i tshogs
NK058(si)001:9888: kyis phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad sangs
NK058(si)001:9889: rgyas kyi zhing khams rnam par dag pa rin po
NK058(si)001:9890: che sna tshogs kyi rang bzhin rgyan stug po bkod
NK058(si)001:9891: pa'i zhing khams lta bur b+h+r+aum gyis gsal gdab bo
NK058(si)001:9892: // de'ang rgyan dang bkod pa'i bye brag bsam gyis
NK058(si)001:9893: mi khyab cing yid du 'ong bas mdzes par spras
NK058(si)001:9894: // shing / mnyen la 'jam zhing reg na bde
NK058(si)001:9895: ba'i rang bzhin rgyu sna tshogs rin po che yi
NK058(si)001:9896: sa gzhi khod snyoms pa la /
NK058(si)001:9897: rin po che sna tshogs kyis mig mang ris su
NK058(si)001:9898: mdzes par bris shing lha'i nor bu sna tshogs kyis
NK058(si)001:9899: tshom bu rab tu brgyan pas phyogs bcu kun tu
NK058(si)001:9900: 'khyil bar spras pa dang t+r+aam las 'dod dgu kun
NK058(si)001:9901: 'byung ba'i rin cen sna bdun gyi phung po 'od
NK058(si)001:9902: zer gyi d+r+wa ba 'bar ba'i ri bo lhun stug
NK058(si)001:9903: pa dang / kham las mtsho dang lteng ka la
NK058(si)001:9904: sogs kha dog mdzes shing dbyibs legs pa'i pad+ma'i rdzing
NK058(si)001:9905: bu ro bro ba'i mchog bsil ba la sogs pa
NK058(si)001:9906: yan lag brgyad ldan gyi chus yongs su gang ba
NK058(si)001:9907: me tog gis khebs shing bya skad snyan par sgrogs
NK058(si)001:9908: pa dang / pa'o // brgyad ldan ni 'dul ba lung las /
NK058(si)001:9909: yang dang dro dang 'jam pa dang //
NK058(si)001:9910: dwangs dang bsil dang rnyog pa med //
NK058(si)001:9911: 'thung na lto la mi gnod dang //
NK058(si)001:9912: mgrin pa la'ang mi gnod pa //
NK058(si)001:9913: 'di dag yan lag brgyad ldan chu //
NK058(si)001:9915: b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i khang pa dbyibs dang kha
NK058(si)001:9916: dog dang bkod pa'i bye brag sna tshogs pas brgyan
NK058(si)001:9917: pa rab tu mang po dang /
NK058(si)001:9918: las skyed mos tshal gyi gzhir rin po che'i rgyan
NK058(si)001:9919: phreng dang lha'i dpag bsam gyi shing ljon pa'i tshal
NK058(si)001:9920: gos dang nor bu sna tshogs kyi d+r+wa bas dpyangs
NK058(si)001:9921: pa dang / h+r+aihls sgra skad thams cad glu dbyangs snyan pa dang /
NK058(si)001:9922: bstod pa dang shis pa brjod pa la sogs pa'i tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra rang 'byung ba dang /
NK058(si)001:9923: las gos kyi rnam pa dang mchod pa'i yo byad
NK058(si)001:9924: bla re dang rgyal mtshan dang gdugs dang stod g.yogs
NK058(si)001:9925: smad g.yogs la sogs pa'i na bza' sna tshogs dang
NK058(si)001:9926: / t+r+aam las dbu rgyan dang mgul rgyan dang do
NK058(si)001:9927: shal dang dpung rgyan dang se mo do la sogs
NK058(si)001:9928: pa rgyan gyi bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK058(si)001:9929: / dang / las ro mchog brgya dang ldan pa'i bza' ba sna tshogs dang /
NK058(si)001:9930: bdud rtsi'i btung ba zhim po dang /
NK058(si)001:9931: gos zung rin po che sna tshogs kyis spras pa'i bgo ba sna tshogs pa rnams dang /
NK058(si)001:9932: h'u las sems can thams cad kyi lus dang rang
NK058(si)001:9933: rang la ji ltar 'os pa'i gos dang rgyan la
NK058(si)001:9934: sogs pas mdzes par brgyan pa yi lha dang lha
NK058(si)001:9935: mo'i rang bzhin rdul phra ba snyed kyi grangs dang
NK058(si)001:9936: mnyam par gyur pa thams cad kyis rkang pa'i bro
NK058(si)001:9937: dang lag pa'i gar dang rol mo'i glu dbyangs la
NK058(si)001:9938: sogs pa bsam yas kyis mnyes par byed pa'o //
NK058(si)001:9939: de lta bu'i mchod pa'i sprin gyis phyogs bcu'i nam
NK058(si)001:9940: mkha'i khams ji snyed pa thams cad yongs su bkang
NK058(si)001:9941: nas 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i dbyings
NK058(si)001:9942: kyis bsdus pa'i gzhi lam 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor du
NK058(si)001:9943: gyur to cog kun la mchod sprin de dag gis
NK058(si)001:9944: re re zhing rgyas par dbul ba'o //
NK058(si)001:9945: gnyis pa tshul ji ltar dbul ba ni skal ldan
NK058(si)001:9946: rnal 'byor pa'i ting nge 'dzin mi gsal ba dang
NK058(si)001:9947: gsal ba'i khyad par gyis rim gyis sam /
NK058(si)001:9948: yang na cig car du gsal lam gyis rgya che
NK058(si)001:9949: ba chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam par sbyor zhing 'bul
NK058(si)001:9950: lo // gnyis pa de'i rdzogs rim don dam ye shes kyi mchod pa ni /
NK058(si)001:9951: ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa la dngos zhen spong
NK058(si)001:9952: ba'i phyir mchod sprin de dag kyang rang gi sems
NK058(si)001:9953: tsam las gang du'ang grub pa med la sems de
NK058(si)001:9954: yang nam mkha' lta bu'i rang bzhin gang na'ang mi
NK058(si)001:9955: gnas shing spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba'i
NK058(si)001:9956: ngang la mchod bya dang mchod byed dang mchod pa
NK058(si)001:9957: gsum ga'i ngo bo ma grub pa'i tshul gyis mchod
NK058(si)001:9958: pa'i phyag rgya chen por bsgom par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:9959: de'ang blo rab kyis mchod dus nyid nas de ltar bsgom zhing 'dzin zhen med par byas la /
NK058(si)001:9960: dman pas rjes la mi dmigs pa'i ngang la bzhag go //
NK058(si)001:9962: dkon cog ta la la'i mdo las /
NK058(si)001:9963: gang la mchod pa nam mkha' 'drar shes shing //
NK058(si)001:9964: gang gis mi dmigs gang du'ang 'dzin pa med //
NK058(si)001:9965: de ni mchod pa kun gyi dam pa ste //
NK058(si)001:9966: ye shes gzhal med bsam yas rab 'thob 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:9968: gnyis pa gsang ba bde ba chen po'i mchod pa la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:9969: thabs bde ba chen po'i mchod pa dang /
NK058(si)001:9970: shes rab mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa'i mchod pa'o //
NK058(si)001:9975: las kyi phyag rgya shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin
NK058(si)001:9976: gsal bar ldan ma'am de dang mi ldan na rnal
NK058(si)001:9977: 'byor pas lhar bskyed cing mkha' gsang byin gyis brlab
NK058(si)001:9978: pa la sogs pa'i cho gas byin gyis brlabs la
NK058(si)001:9979: / pad+ma'i rtser yungs 'bru tsam gyi dwangs ma dkar dmar dkyil 'khor du bskyed de /
NK058(si)001:9980: stong gsum gyi 'jig rten thams cad 'phags pa'i rdzu
NK058(si)001:9981: 'phrul gyis yungs 'brur gzhug cing tshud par byin gyis
NK058(si)001:9982: brlabs pas stong gsum chung ngu mi 'gro yungs 'bru
NK058(si)001:9983: cher mi 'gro ba'i tshul du pad+ma'i khyams rten gyi
NK058(si)001:9984: dkyil 'khor cher mi 'gro ye shes pa chung ngu
NK058(si)001:9985: mi 'gro ba'i chos kyi dbyings nas rgyal ba'i dkyil
NK058(si)001:9986: 'khor dpag tu med pa pad+ma'i khyams su spyan drangs
NK058(si)001:9987: shing bstim la / sbyor ba'i brdas bskul te rol pa'i bde bas mchod par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:9988: des dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams mnyes nas dngos grub
NK058(si)001:9989: chen po bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dam tshig mchog
NK058(si)001:9990: gi go 'phang thob par bsam mo //
NK058(si)001:9991: de ni sngar dkyil 'khor bkod pa sor bzhi la
NK058(si)001:9992: ye shes pa gzhug cing dbang bskur ba'i sngon du
NK058(si)001:9993: bsnyen sgrub bya ba'i rim pa'ang gsal bar bstan to
NK058(si)001:9994: // gnyis pa de'i phan yon la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:9997: dang po la gnyis las sangs rgyas thams cad mnyes pa ni /
NK058(si)001:9998: bde ba'i bdag nyid chen pos yum mkha'i dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:9999: la mchod pa yis phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas
NK058(si)001:10000: kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad mnyes par
NK058(si)001:10001: 'gyur ro // yang bdag nyid chen po rang rig
NK058(si)001:10002: pa'i ye shes la rol pa'i bde bas mchod pa
NK058(si)001:10003: yis khams dang skye mched ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i
NK058(si)001:10004: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la sogs pa'i lha
NK058(si)001:10006: yang yab kyis yum yum gyis yab la bdag nyid
NK058(si)001:10007: chen po'i mchod rdzas des mchod pas thabs dang shes
NK058(si)001:10008: rab kyi lha rnams mnyes par 'gyur pa ste phyi
NK058(si)001:10009: nang gsang ba gsum du shes par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:10010: 'gro ba thams cad tshims pa ni /
NK058(si)001:10011: de ltar bde ba'i rol pas lus snang ba'i grong
NK058(si)001:10012: khyer 'dod pa'i srid pa dag phyed snang gi grong
NK058(si)001:10013: khyer gzugs kyi srid pa yid mi snang ba'i grong
NK058(si)001:10014: khyer gzugs med pa'i srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i
NK058(si)001:10015: tshor ba dang rtog tshogs kyi 'gro ba thams cad
NK058(si)001:10016: la ye shes chen po'i dga' ba bzhi dang gnyis
NK058(si)001:10017: su med pa'i chos nyid bzhi dang spros pa dang
NK058(si)001:10018: bral ba'i 'od gsal chen pos khyab par 'gyur ro
NK058(si)001:10019: // chos nyid bzhi ni lus gnyis su med pa'i
NK058(si)001:10020: chos nyid yab dang yum du 'dzin pa med pas
NK058(si)001:10021: gzung 'dzin mtha' dag las grol ba dang /
NK058(si)001:10022: ngag gnyis su med pa'i chos nyid brjod du med
NK058(si)001:10023: pas spros pa dang zhen pa kun las grol ba
NK058(si)001:10024: dang / yid gnyis su med pa'i chos nyid rtog
NK058(si)001:10025: tshogs bde ba chen por grol bas rang bzhin chos
NK058(si)001:10026: sku'i ngo bo mthong ba dang /
NK058(si)001:10027: ye shes gnyis su med pa'i chos nyid bde ba'i
NK058(si)001:10028: bar la 'dzin med chen por gnas pas 'od gsal
NK058(si)001:10030: 'od gsal bzhi ni de'i tshe bde ba'i 'od gsal
NK058(si)001:10031: sgo gsum dga' bas khyad pas snang srid dga' bder
NK058(si)001:10032: shar ba dang / gsal ba'i 'od gsal bde ba'i
NK058(si)001:10033: ngang las sems kyi ngo bo rang gsal thabs shes
NK058(si)001:10034: su snang ba ma 'gags pa dang /
NK058(si)001:10035: mi rtog pa'i 'od gsal phra rags su zhen pa'i
NK058(si)001:10036: byung tshor nub pas gang la'ang mi 'phro bar rtog
NK058(si)001:10038: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i 'od gsal chos nyid kyi ngang las rtags bcu'i snang ba shar ba'o //
NK058(si)001:10039: rtags bcu ni rlung sems dbu mar tshud pas dbyings
NK058(si)001:10040: dang ye shes ro gcig tu gyur ba'i rtags su
NK058(si)001:10050: 'od zer gyi snang ba lta bu 'byung ba'o //
NK058(si)001:10051: rgyud sde gzhan las kyang de dang cung zad mi 'dra ba'i rtags bcu bshad do //
NK058(si)001:10052: gnyis pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob
NK058(si)001:10053: pa ni sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba thabs dang shes rab
NK058(si)001:10054: kyi ting nge 'dzin rtags bcus mtshon pa de nyid
NK058(si)001:10055: goms pa rab tu brtan pa las byung ba de
NK058(si)001:10056: yis 'bras bu phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi
NK058(si)001:10057: sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa'i rang bzhin
NK058(si)001:10058: dang / khams gsum gyi 'gro ba rnams la thugs
NK058(si)001:10059: rjes gzigs pa'i ye shes dam pa mngon du 'gyur
NK058(si)001:10060: dang / ro // yang na sangs rgyas thams cad
NK058(si)001:10061: kyi dkyil 'khor phung po khams dang skye mched lhar
NK058(si)001:10062: gsal ba mthar thug pa dang /
NK058(si)001:10063: sgo gsum sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bor 'khor lo mngon du 'gyur ba zhes bya'o //
NK058(si)001:10064: gnyis pa shes rab mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa'i mchod pa ni /
NK058(si)001:10065: de ltar yab yum gnyis su med par snyoms par
NK058(si)001:10066: zhugs pa'i nyon mongs pa'i 'dzin zhen dang tha mal
NK058(si)001:10067: gyi rnam rtog rang sar dag par bya ba'i phyir
NK058(si)001:10068: / rang dang yum gyi lus dang ngag dang sems
NK058(si)001:10069: dang bde bas mtshon pa'i phyi nang gi chos thams
NK058(si)001:10070: cad kyi rang bzhin gzung ba'i yul gang na'ang mi
NK058(si)001:10071: gnas shing 'dzin pa'i sems gang du'ang mi dmigs pa'i
NK058(si)001:10072: / ngang las / med bzhin du snang ba mig
NK058(si)001:10073: yor lta bu'i tshul du yab yum gnyis su med
NK058(si)001:10074: par sbyor ba yis thabs dang shes rab gnyis su
NK058(si)001:10075: med pa'i dbyings skye ba med pa'i nam mkha' la
NK058(si)001:10076: ni sems nyid 'gags pa med pa'i ye shes nam
NK058(si)001:10077: mkha' bsgom zhing dbyer med pa'i chos nyid don gyi
NK058(si)001:10078: ngo bor mnyam par bzhag cing rol par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:10079: gsum pa 'jug cing dbang bskur ba'i tshul la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:10083: slob dpon bdag nyid 'jug pa ni /
NK058(si)001:10084: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa nas
NK058(si)001:10085: bzung ste cho ga'i sngon du bya dgos pa kun
NK058(si)001:10086: byas nas tshogs dang rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug rdo
NK058(si)001:10087: rje slob dpon nyid ting nge 'dzin gyi rig pas
NK058(si)001:10088: dkyil 'khor du sngon la 'jug par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:10090: slob dpon zhugs pa de nas slob ma rnams 'jug
NK058(si)001:10091: pa'i chos bcu bdun gyis dkyil 'khor du gzhug par
NK058(si)001:10092: bya'o // gnyis pa dbang bskur pa la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:10094: blo'i rim pa dang sbyar nas dbang bskur ba dngos so //
NK058(si)001:10096: yon dbul ba dngos ni 'jug pa'i chos rnams tshar
NK058(si)001:10097: ba'i rjes de nas rigs kyi bu skal pa mchog
NK058(si)001:10098: dang ldan pa des bla ma la /
NK058(si)001:10099: rang gi 'byor ba thams cad kyis mchod par bya ste /
NK058(si)001:10100: rgyal srid yul 'khor dang bcas pa dang ni /
NK058(si)001:10101: rang gi lus dang bu dang chung ma dang nor
NK058(si)001:10102: gyi dbyig gser dngul la sogs pa'i rin po che
NK058(si)001:10103: sna tshogs te / de rnams kyang gnyis gnyis yod
NK058(si)001:10104: na rab tu gces shos de dang mdor na rang
NK058(si)001:10105: gi yid du 'ong zhing 'thad pa'i dngos po rnams
NK058(si)001:10106: sna tshogs te / dbul lo // gnyis pa phan
NK058(si)001:10107: yon ni rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug rdo rje slob
NK058(si)001:10108: dpon la 'dod pa'i longs spyod rnam pa lngas mchod
NK058(si)001:10109: na phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:10110: thams cad mchod pa yin na /
NK058(si)001:10111: nye ba'i dkyil 'khor yi dam gyi lha mchod pa lta smos kyang ci dgos te /
NK058(si)001:10112: dam tshig rnam par bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK058(si)001:10113: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin mchod na //
NK058(si)001:10114: dkyil 'khor thams cad mchod pa ste //
NK058(si)001:10115: nye ba'i dkyil 'khor smos ci dgos //
NK058(si)001:10116: nyes zad dngos grub mchog thob 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:10118: des dam tshig dang sdom pa'i nyes pa thams cad dag par 'gyur ba kho na'o //
NK058(si)001:10119: gnyis pa blo'i rim pa dang sbyar nas dbang bskur ba dngos ni /
NK058(si)001:10120: dad pa dang brtson pa'i brtul zhugs rab tu rtogs
NK058(si)001:10121: pa'i skal ba yod par shes na de la phan
NK058(si)001:10122: pa'i dbang bcu dang nus pa'i dbang lnga po slob
NK058(si)001:10123: dpon gyis lhag pa'i snying rjes slob ma'i rgyud chud
NK058(si)001:10124: ma zos par gzung zhing sbyin no //
NK058(si)001:10125: gal te skal pa med na mi sbyin pa'am phan dbang tsam bskur gyi nus dbang mi sbyin te /
NK058(si)001:10126: nyes pa chen por 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:10127: de'ang ye shes bkod pa chen po dam tshig mchog gi rgyud las /
NK058(si)001:10128: snod dang mi ldan slob ma la //
NK058(si)001:10129: dbang bskur byas na gnyis ka phung //
NK058(si)001:10131: 'dir phyin ci log gi nags thibs po che log
NK058(si)001:10132: par lta ba'i mun pa mi bzad pas 'thibs shing
NK058(si)001:10133: / nyon mongs pa'i chom rkun rab tu rtsen pas dkrugs shing /
NK058(si)001:10134: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje nyi ma'i 'od zer gyis
NK058(si)001:10135: phrin las 'jug pa'i go skabs med pa kha cig
NK058(si)001:10136: na re / rgyud gzhan las dbang bzhi dang /
NK058(si)001:10137: de las phye bas bcu bzhir gsungs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:10138: khyed kyi 'dir phan pa dang nus pa'i dbang gnyis
NK058(si)001:10139: las phye ba'i bco lnga po grangs mi mthun pas
NK058(si)001:10140: rgyud 'di yang dag pa ma yin no //
NK058(si)001:10143: ma la skal pa ngan pa khyed cag lta bus
NK058(si)001:10144: dbye bsdu dang don gyi rim pa'ang khong du ma
NK058(si)001:10145: chud cing rgyud sde tha dad kyi dgongs pa zab
NK058(si)001:10146: mo la blo kha ma phyogs par zad do //
NK058(si)001:10147: de lta bas na rnal 'byoor gyi rgyud las bum pa dang /
NK058(si)001:10149: rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang dang gsum du gsungs la /
NK058(si)001:10150: ngan song sbyong ba nas dbang bcu gcig gam dbye na bcu dgur gsungs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:10151: de nyid 'dus pa dang zla gsang thig le'i rgyud
NK058(si)001:10152: las bum pa gsang ba shes rab ye shes gsum
NK058(si)001:10155: slob dpon dang slob ma'i dbang gnyis su bsdus pa
NK058(si)001:10156: yod pas rgyud yang dag pa ma yin par 'gyur
NK058(si)001:10157: ro // de dag don la mtshungs pas skyon med
NK058(si)001:10158: do snyam na 'di yang don la mtshungs pas nyes
NK058(si)001:10160: 'di ni rgyud thams cad kyi rtsa ba yin pas
NK058(si)001:10161: rgyud gzhan gyi dbang bskur tshul thams cad 'dir 'dus
NK058(si)001:10162: pa yin no // de'ang bum pa'i dbang dngos su gsungs la /
NK058(si)001:10163: de nyid mi bskyod pa chu'i dbang bskur ba yin no //
NK058(si)001:10164: dbu rgyan dang cod pan dang me tog ni rin cen 'byung ldan gyi dbang ngo //
NK058(si)001:10165: phyag rgya ni rdo rje dang dril bu la sogs
NK058(si)001:10166: pa ste 'od dpag med dang don yod grub pa'o
NK058(si)001:10167: // nus dbang gi skabs su khyod ni rdo rje
NK058(si)001:10168: las yin gyis zhes pa la sogs pas rnam par
NK058(si)001:10169: snang mdzad kyi dbang bskur ba yin la /
NK058(si)001:10170: brtul zhugs dang lung bstan dbugs dbyung la sogs pa
NK058(si)001:10171: thams cad rdo rje rgyal po la sogs pa nus
NK058(si)001:10172: pa'i dbang gis bstan pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:10173: gsang ba'i dbang ni dngos su bstan pas shes rab ye shes dang /
NK058(si)001:10174: tshig dbang rin po che ni de'i nang gses su zhar la bstan pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:10175: de bas na rgyud sde don mthun pa'i phyir na 'di la nyes pa ga la srid /
NK058(si)001:10176: tshul 'di lta bu la smad pas mthong ba'i chos
NK058(si)001:10177: la lce lkog ma'i 'og la don pa dang 'chi
NK058(si)001:10178: gar me yi snang ba chen po 'bar bas dmyal
NK058(si)001:10179: bar 'gro ba'i rtags khyad par can rnams khyed las
NK058(si)001:10180: gzhan pa su la 'byung ba srid de bskal pa
NK058(si)001:10181: du mar snying rje'i 'os su gyur pa nyid do
NK058(si)001:10182: // gnyis pa yab kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba ni /
NK058(si)001:10183: yum gyi dkyil 'khor du gsang ba dang shes rab
NK058(si)001:10184: ye shes kyi dbang bskur ba de las gzhan pa'i
NK058(si)001:10185: tshul yab kyi rdo rje'i rtse las dbang blang bar
NK058(si)001:10186: bstan pa ni / yang na yab kyi thal mo
NK058(si)001:10187: mnyam bzhag gi tshul gyis rab tu bsnol nas lha'i
NK058(si)001:10188: sku phyag rgya chen por gsal ba'i dbang mdzub mo'i
NK058(si)001:10189: bar du ni gu h+ya badz+ra gyi dkyil 'khor ring
NK058(si)001:10190: thung mdzub gang ba'i tshad du yang bde ba'i thabs
NK058(si)001:10191: la mkhas pas dbang bskur ba'i cho ga bzhin du
NK058(si)001:10192: dwangs mas bu la dbang bskur bar bya'o //
NK058(si)001:10193: de nas dbang rnams rdzogs par sbyin no //
NK058(si)001:10194: 'dir kha cig nus dbang sngon la bskur zhing phan
NK058(si)001:10195: dbang rjes gnang gi tshul du phyi la bskur te
NK058(si)001:10196: thams cad gsang dbang kho nas bskur ba ni dbang
NK058(si)001:10197: po rnon po'i dbang du byas la /
NK058(si)001:10198: rdo rje las rim nas gzhan bzhin rtul po'i dbang
NK058(si)001:10199: du byas so zhes pa'ang rigs par ma mthong ste
NK058(si)001:10201: phan pa'i dbang dang nus pa'i dbang //
NK058(si)001:10202: snying rjes chud ma zos par bzung //
NK058(si)001:10203: zhes phan dbang sngon la gsungs shing /
NK058(si)001:10204: go rim kyang thog mar bum dbang dang de nas
NK058(si)001:10205: gsang dbang dang shes rab ye shes bzhi pa rnams
NK058(si)001:10207: gnyis pa dman pa rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba'i tshul la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:10214: chen po bri ba'i cho ga'o //
NK058(si)001:10216: sa'i cho ga ni rab mchog gi dkyil 'khor du
NK058(si)001:10217: dbang bskur ba las tshul gzhan yang na sa gzhi
NK058(si)001:10218: sa'i cho gas rab tu mnyam pa la bri'o //
NK058(si)001:10219: de'ang sngar ma dag pa'i sa gzhi phyis dag par byed pa ma yin te /
NK058(si)001:10220: sa chu spyan dang m+aa ma k+ai //
NK058(si)001:10221: zhes pa la sogs pas shes la /
NK058(si)001:10222: ye nas sa sbyangs zin pa'i phyis gsal 'debs pa'i tshul gyis sbyong ba yin no //
NK058(si)001:10223: gnyis pa 'bri ba dngos ni gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil
NK058(si)001:10224: 'khor chung ngu'i chung ngu khru gang gi tshad du
NK058(si)001:10225: bya'o // chung ngu'i 'bring yang na lus gang gi tshad du ste 'dom gang ngo //
NK058(si)001:10226: chung ngu'i chen po yang na lus ni gsum gyi tshad tsam la /
NK058(si)001:10227: mi rus la sogs pa'i phur bu ni dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:10228: gyi dbus su 'gying phur sor bzhi la sogs pa
NK058(si)001:10229: dang bgegs bsrung ba'i don du sor bco brgyad pa
NK058(si)001:10230: la sogs pa'o // cha dbye ba'i don du ras
NK058(si)001:10231: bal lam pad+ma'i rgyus pa'am dur khrod kyi skra la
NK058(si)001:10232: sogs pa'i srad bu khrun du dkyil 'khor nyis 'gyur
NK058(si)001:10233: la sogs pa'o // yod pa dang / rigs tha
NK058(si)001:10234: dad mtshon pa'i don du kha dog ma 'dres pa'i
NK058(si)001:10235: tshon gyi phye ma lnga la sogs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:10236: las bsgrub pa'i don du gos dang rgyan bzang pos
NK058(si)001:10237: mdzes pa yid du 'ong ba'i grogs las kyi phyag
NK058(si)001:10238: rgya lo bcu drug lon pa'o //
NK058(si)001:10239: de nas srad bu'i sna nas grogs des bzung la /
NK058(si)001:10240: ye shes kyi thig dang las kyi thig gnyis gdab
NK058(si)001:10241: pa'i cho ga phun sum tshogs pa dkyil 'khor gyi
NK058(si)001:10242: las la mkhas par ldan pa chen po rdo rje
NK058(si)001:10243: slob dpon gyis lus sems ma g.yengs par rab tu
NK058(si)001:10244: bsgrims te bya'o // gnyis pa 'bring la gsum las /
NK058(si)001:10246: yang na khru ni bcu drug pa dang /
NK058(si)001:10247: 'bring gi 'bring khru nyi shu ba yod pa'am /
NK058(si)001:10248: 'bring gi chen po khru nyi shu rtsa lngar bya'o //
NK058(si)001:10249: de la snga ma bzhin du thig gdab par bya ste /
NK058(si)001:10250: thig tshon la rigs kyi dkyil 'khor rnam pa lnga
NK058(si)001:10251: bo rnams bsgom zhing zhu ba las byung ba'i ye
NK058(si)001:10252: shes lnga'i thig tshon du bsams te /
NK058(si)001:10253: thig gdab cing tshon bkye nas lha'i gnas so sor sku tsaka li'am 'bur sku'am bar du gdab cing /
NK058(si)001:10255: thugs phyag mtshan gyi mtshan mas lha'i rang bzhin mtshon
NK058(si)001:10256: par ldan pa rdo rje dang 'khor lo la sogs
NK058(si)001:10257: pa'i sku gsung thugs mtshon pa'i gzugs gang rung rnams
NK058(si)001:10258: kyang lha so so'i gnas su dgod par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:10259: gsum pa chen po la'ang gsum las /
NK058(si)001:10260: chen po'i chung ngu ni yang na rgyang grags gcig go //
NK058(si)001:10262: sor mo nyi shu bzhi la khru //
NK058(si)001:10263: khru bzhi la ni gzhu gang ngo //
NK058(si)001:10264: de dag lnga brgya dag la ni //
NK058(si)001:10265: rgyang grags de la dgon par 'dod //
NK058(si)001:10266: de brgyad dpag tshad ces bya'o //
NK058(si)001:10269: chen po'i chen po nam mkha' dbyings kyi bsam yas par /
NK058(si)001:10270: rig 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dngos su sprul pa'am /
NK058(si)001:10271: sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor rigs sna tshogs pa bsgom ste dbang bskur ba yin no //
NK058(si)001:10272: de'i don yang nam mkha'i dbyings thams cad khyab pa'i
NK058(si)001:10273: dkyil 'khor dngos su sprul te slob ma la dbang
NK058(si)001:10274: bskur ba ni / sngon mtsho ma pham gyi 'gram
NK058(si)001:10275: du mtsho la thig btab nas 'jam dpal grags pa
NK058(si)001:10276: la slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas rdo rje dbyings
NK058(si)001:10277: kyi dkyil 'khor dngos su bstan nas dbang bskur ba
NK058(si)001:10278: bskur ba ni / dang / slob dpon chen po
NK058(si)001:10279: pad+mas stag tshang seng ge phug tu rdo rjee gzhon
NK058(si)001:10280: nu'i dkyil 'khor nam mkha' dang mnyam pa bstan nas
NK058(si)001:10281: mtsho rgyal la dbang bskur ba lta bu'o //
NK058(si)001:10282: de'ang sems can gyi rgyud la sku lnga ye shes
NK058(si)001:10283: lnga'i rang bzhin ye gdod ma nas gnas kyang ma
NK058(si)001:10284: rig pas bsgribs nas ma mthong ba'i rmongs pa rnams
NK058(si)001:10285: la bstan pa'i phyir sa tshon gyi kha dog kyang
NK058(si)001:10286: dkar po lta bu re re la dkar ser dkar
NK058(si)001:10287: dmar dkar ljang dkar sngo dkar po nyid dang lngar
NK058(si)001:10288: phye ba bzhin du gzhan bzhi la'ang phye bas nyi
NK058(si)001:10289: shu rtsa lnga'am ni ye shes nyi shu rtsa lnga
NK058(si)001:10290: dang mtshams sems la sogs pa mtshon pa'o //
NK058(si)001:10291: de tsam med na'ang dkar ser dmar ljang mthing ga lnga yi tshon gyis bri bar bya'o //
NK058(si)001:10292: de skad du'ang rgyas pa'i rgyud las /
NK058(si)001:10293: sems can ma lus thams cad la //
NK058(si)001:10294: ye shes lnga yis kun khyab kyang //
NK058(si)001:10295: rang gi rnam rtog bsgribs byas nas //
NK058(si)001:10296: ye shes lnga yi don ma mthong //
NK058(si)001:10297: de ltar rmongs pa thams cad la //
NK058(si)001:10298: ye shes mtshan nyid bstan pa'i phyir //
NK058(si)001:10299: dkar dang dmar dang ser po dang //
NK058(si)001:10300: ljang gu la sogs nag por bstan //
NK058(si)001:10302: ji ltar bri ba ni mthong ba brgyud pa'i lag
NK058(si)001:10303: len rnam par dag par rgyas 'bring bsdus pa la
NK058(si)001:10304: sogs pa'i rnam par bzhag pa ni skabs 'dir 'dul
NK058(si)001:10305: ba'i cho ga ste de'i lugs bzhin du bri'o //
NK058(si)001:10306: de skad du'ang rngam glog las /
NK058(si)001:10308: gzugs brnyan yang ni de ltar bri //
NK058(si)001:10310: 'di la kha cig bya spyod kyi lugs su bzhed cing /
NK058(si)001:10311: la la gdul bya 'dul ba zhes sbyor ba'ang ma go bar snang ngo //
NK058(si)001:10312: de'ang gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus pa
NK058(si)001:10313: gsum ni gang zag gi blo dang 'byor bas phye
NK058(si)001:10314: ba ste / 'khor los sgyur ba la sogs pa la ni dpag tshad la sogs pa yin zhing /
NK058(si)001:10315: phal ba'i 'byor ba mchog la 'bring po dang /
NK058(si)001:10316: chung ba la chung tshad du gsungs shing /
NK058(si)001:10317: chen po'i chen po ni slob ma mchog la 'phags
NK058(si)001:10318: pa'i bla mas dbang bskur ba'i blo yis rim pas
NK058(si)001:10320: gzhung gsum po'ang ma 'khrugs par bshad de /
NK058(si)001:10321: chung ba'i skabs su thig gi rim pa gsungs shing /
NK058(si)001:10322: 'bring gi skabs su thig tshon byin gyis brlabs te bris pa la mtshan ma dgod thabs gsungs la /
NK058(si)001:10323: rgyas pa'i skabs su tshon dgye ba'i rim pas bri thabs rdzogs par gsungs pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:10324: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:10327: gnyis su med par bstim pa'o //
NK058(si)001:10329: sems bskyed pa dang de bzhin nyid la sogs pa'i
NK058(si)001:10330: ting nge 'dzin gyi rol mo mtha' yas pa'i mchog
NK058(si)001:10331: nam mkha'i dbyings kyi mthas gtugs par dkyil 'khor bskyed
NK058(si)001:10332: pa'i nang du / lha so so'i gnas su rang
NK058(si)001:10333: rang gi yi ge tha la sogs pa'am lha mtshon
NK058(si)001:10334: pa'i brda tshon spungs kyi thig le sku mdog dang
NK058(si)001:10335: pa'i nang du / mthun pa'am / snying po h'u dang m+aum la sogs pa'am /
NK058(si)001:10336: phyag rgya rdo rje dang 'khor lo la sogs pa'am
NK058(si)001:10337: gang yang rung ba las lha so so'i sku gsung
NK058(si)001:10338: thugs yongs su rdzogs pa dang ldan par bskyed pa
NK058(si)001:10339: ni rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor ting nge 'dzin ye
NK058(si)001:10340: shes kyi dkyil 'khor du byin gyis brlabs pa zhes
NK058(si)001:10341: bya ste / des grub don ya mtshan pa gnas skabs thun mong gi las bzhi dang /
NK058(si)001:10342: rmad po che mthar thug lha'i dkyil 'khor 'grub par
NK058(si)001:10343: 'gyur ba ni sangs rgyas kun gyis dam bcas pa'i
NK058(si)001:10345: 'di ltar sa dang shing dang rdo la sogs pa'i
NK058(si)001:10346: rgyu'i dngos po ngan pa phyi rol tu gyur pa
NK058(si)001:10347: de dag las sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya'i gzugs
NK058(si)001:10348: bcas pa yang gdul bya'i skal ba dang mthun par
NK058(si)001:10349: rnam par grol ba'i rim pa byang chub gsum so
NK058(si)001:10351: rnam par dag pa'i ye shes ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK058(si)001:10352: sbyangs pa'i sems kyi dngos po ye nas 'od gsal
NK058(si)001:10353: ba las sangs rgyas 'grub pa lta smos kyang ci
NK058(si)001:10354: dgos te / sems de nyid gdod ma nas sangs
NK058(si)001:10355: rgyas yin pa la gsal btab pa tsam gyis 'grub
NK058(si)001:10356: dgos te / pa'i phyir ro // de skad du'ang 'da' ka ye shes las /
NK058(si)001:10357: sems rtogs na sangs rgyas yin pas /
NK058(si)001:10358: sangs rgyas gzhan nas mi btsal ba'i 'du shes rab tu bsgom par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:10361: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas te //
NK058(si)001:10363: gnyis pa spyan drang ba ni /
NK058(si)001:10364: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i dkyil 'khor kun gyi bdag nyid
