NK058(si)001:10365: chen po gshis kyi gnas lugs gang du'ang mi dmigs
NK058(si)001:10366: shing spros pa dang bral ba ni thugs kyi dkyil
NK058(si)001:10367: 'khor chos sku'i ngang las ye shes pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:10368: ji ltar 'dod pa thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK058(si)001:10369: de'ang blos byon par mos pa byed pa tsam la spyan drangs par brjod cing /
NK058(si)001:10370: thams cad mkhyen pa'i thugs rjes kyang byin gyis rlob pa yin la /
NK058(si)001:10371: gtso bor rang gi sems kyi rnam 'phrul tsam goms par byed pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:10372: de'ang sems sangs rgyas yin pas de goms shing gsal bas dkyil 'khor 'grub pa ni 'thad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:10373: gsum pa gnyis su med par bstim pa ni /
NK058(si)001:10374: bskyed pa ting 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK058(si)001:10375: gzhi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor gnyis
NK058(si)001:10376: po de rang snang gi ngo bor dbyer med du
NK058(si)001:10377: gnas te / rang bzhin dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:10378: la bskyed pa ye shes sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor spyan
NK058(si)001:10379: drangs pa de nyid 'jug cing bstim pa'i mtshan nyid
NK058(si)001:10380: kyis dkyil 'khor de gnyis chu la chu bzhag pa
NK058(si)001:10381: bzhin du mnyam par sbyor ba'i tshul gyis bstim pas
NK058(si)001:10382: gnas te / / phyogs bcu dus bzhi kun nas 'gro ba'i don la gshegs pa yi /
NK058(si)001:10383: sangs rgyas thams cad kyis sngon spyad pa spyod pa
NK058(si)001:10384: na gang la las de bzhin gshegs pa yid la
NK058(si)001:10385: byed pa de'i mdun du de bzhin gshegs pa nyid
NK058(si)001:10386: bzhugs par gyur cig ces smos lam gyi bsnyen pa
NK058(si)001:10387: mdzad pa'i 'bras bu grub nas de kho na bzhin
NK058(si)001:10388: don mdzad pa'i phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor de nyid
NK058(si)001:10389: thugs rjes byon nas dam tshig pa'i dkyil 'khor la
NK058(si)001:10390: rab tu rdzogs par 'jug cing nye ba'i sras su
NK058(si)001:10391: dgongs par gyur bas na spyan drangs te bstim pa
NK058(si)001:10392: ni dam tshig gi mchog yin no //
NK058(si)001:10393: gsum pa dkyil 'khor bsgrubs pa'i 'bras bu la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:10394: dngos grub sems las 'byung ba'i 'thad pa dgod pa /
NK058(si)001:10395: de nyid ji ltar bsgrub pa'i thabs bstan pa /
NK058(si)001:10396: thabs des grub pa'i 'bras bu brjod pa'o //
NK058(si)001:10398: dang po dpe ni lha'i dpag bsam gyi shing dang
NK058(si)001:10399: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che dang gzhan
NK058(si)001:10400: yang phyi rol gyi dngos por snang ba las 'dod
NK058(si)001:10401: dgu 'byung ba kun la ya mtshan dang yon tan
NK058(si)001:10403: de dag la phyi rol bden par grub pa'i rdzas
NK058(si)001:10404: kyi dngos po 'ga' zhig yod pa ma yin te
NK058(si)001:10405: gzhon nu me skyes kyi rin po che'i khang bzang
NK058(si)001:10406: ma skyes dgra'i khang pa dang barjesa kyang kho rang
NK058(si)001:10408: khron pa skyes kyi khron pa las kho rang gis
NK058(si)001:10409: lag pa brkyangs na zas gos la sogs pa 'byung
NK058(si)001:10410: gis gzhan gyis ma yin pa dang /
NK058(si)001:10411: nor bu dang dpag bsam gyi shing la'ang lha dang
NK058(si)001:10412: sgra mi snyan pas blangs na 'dod dgu 'byung gis
NK058(si)001:10414: 'o na de dag rgyu ci las de ltar gyur ce na /
NK058(si)001:10415: sngon sbyin pa btang ba'i bag chags kyi sa bon
NK058(si)001:10416: rang gi sems kun gzhi la gnas pa'i bsod nams
NK058(si)001:10417: kyi rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu brtan pa nyid
NK058(si)001:10418: kyi snang ba der smin cing /
NK058(si)001:10419: rkyen de dag dang 'phrad nas dgos 'dod 'byung bar snang ba yin no //
NK058(si)001:10420: de bzhin du thog ma med pa nas kun gzhi
NK058(si)001:10421: la yul du snang ba'i bag chags kyis 'jig rten
NK058(si)001:10422: 'byung ba so so'i gzugs can dang /
NK058(si)001:10423: lus su snang ba'i bag chags kyis rang gi phung po dang /
NK058(si)001:10424: don du snang ba'i bag chags kyis phyi nang gi
NK058(si)001:10425: chos sems can gyi khams rang gi shes pa'i tshogs
NK058(si)001:10426: dang bcas pa du mar snang yang /
NK058(si)001:10427: don tha dad par grub pa med de rmi lam bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:10428: gnyis pa don ni de bzhin du sems nyid don
NK058(si)001:10429: gyi gnas lugs la sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK058(si)001:10430: las kyi dkyil 'khor ngo mtshar ba'i cho 'phrul ya
NK058(si)001:10431: mtshan rmad kyi chos dang gnas skabs kyi dngos grub
NK058(si)001:10432: phrin las bzhi la sogs pa thob pa rnams kyang
NK058(si)001:10433: / bdag gis phar bgrod nas de'i steng du phyin pa'am /
NK058(si)001:10434: phyogs gzhan zhig na yod pa de tshur bkug nas 'ong ba ma yin te /
NK058(si)001:10435: 'di ltar phyi snod gzhal yas khang nang bcud lha
NK058(si)001:10436: dang lha mo rang nyid rgyal ba'i skur gsal ba
NK058(si)001:10437: la sogs pa'i thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa snying rje
NK058(si)001:10438: chen po la sems kyi goms pa rab tu brtan
NK058(si)001:10439: pa'i ngang nas / shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa
NK058(si)001:10440: spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba la goms
NK058(si)001:10441: pa'i dbang gis zung 'jug gnyis su med pa nyid
NK058(si)001:10442: pa'i ngang nas / la sbyangs pas / bskyed rdzogs
NK058(si)001:10443: de lta bu yi ngang du sku dang ye shes
NK058(si)001:10444: kyi dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub par rang byung zhing
NK058(si)001:10446: de'ang rang bzhin spros pa dang bral ba'i shes rab
NK058(si)001:10447: chos kyi dbyings kyi de bzhin nyid chos sku'i ngang
NK058(si)001:10448: las / thabs kyi phyag rgya lhun stug po bkod
NK058(si)001:10449: par gzugs sku'i dkyil 'khor rang snang du bkod pa
NK058(si)001:10450: ni lhun gyis grub pa'i ye shes kyi rol par
NK058(si)001:10451: las / gyur pa'i phyir / chos sku'i ye shes
NK058(si)001:10452: la ni gzugs sku'i ye shes rol pa'i ngang las
NK058(si)001:10453: las / gyur pa'i phyir / / gdul bya'i 'jig
NK058(si)001:10454: rten du snang ba dang mthun par sprul pa'i sku'i
NK058(si)001:10455: ye shes rol pa nyid kyang de las ma 'phos
NK058(si)001:10456: bzhin du snang ba chu zla dang 'dra bas gsog
NK058(si)001:10457: las / gyur pa'i phyir / / ces bya ste / yum bar ma las /
NK058(si)001:10458: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyang rmi lam
NK058(si)001:10459: lta bu sgyu ma lta bu chu zla lta bu
NK058(si)001:10461: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyang rmi
NK058(si)001:10462: lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu chu zla dang
NK058(si)001:10465: kha cig sangs rgyas dang de'i ye shes gnyis la
NK058(si)001:10466: gsog ces rim pas sbyor ba ni longs sku'i de
NK058(si)001:10468: gsum pa des gzhan don 'byung ba'i tshul ni /
NK058(si)001:10469: ye shes kyi rol ba gsog yin na des gzhan don byed pa mi 'thad do snyam na /
NK058(si)001:10470: gsog nyid du snang bas don mdzad pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:10472: sems can gyi mos pa dang mthun par rgyal ba
NK058(si)001:10473: thub pa drug la sogs pa mngon sum du 'byung
NK058(si)001:10474: zhing 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal las skyob pa mdzad pa
NK058(si)001:10475: bcu gnyis pa sogs pas don mdzad pa dang /
NK058(si)001:10476: chos sku'i ngang las lhun stug po bkod pa'i rang snang longs skur snang ba'i byin rlabs las /
NK058(si)001:10477: sa bcu'i sems dpa' la rang bzhin sprul sku rigs
NK058(si)001:10478: lnga'i sangs rgyas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur ston pa'ang
NK058(si)001:10479: ston pa'i thugs rje dang 'gro ba'i rang sems bsod
NK058(si)001:10480: nams goms pa'i mthu las nor bu dpag bsam shing
NK058(si)001:10481: gi dpe de bzhin du snang ba yin te /
NK058(si)001:10483: zhi sku dpag bsam shing ltar gsal gyur cing //
NK058(si)001:10484: yid bzhin nor bu ji bzhin rnam mi rtog /
NK058(si)001:10485: 'gro grol bar du 'jig rten 'byor slad rtag /
NK058(si)001:10486: 'di ni spros dang bral la snang ba 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:10488: des na rang bzhin bden par ma grub bzhin du
NK058(si)001:10489: sprul pa'i skus 'gro don gyi bya ba byed nus
NK058(si)001:10490: pa'i tshul ni lhun gyis grub pa'i thugs rje'i gzi
NK058(si)001:10491: byin mnga' ba'i phrin las kyi rol par rang byung
NK058(si)001:10493: nyi zla'i gzi 'od kyis gling bzhi snang zhing pad+ma'i
NK058(si)001:10494: kha 'byed pa rdzing bur gzugs brnyan ston pa bzhin
NK058(si)001:10495: no // de nyid ye shes kyi sgyu ma ste
NK058(si)001:10496: sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i rang bzhin can chos thams
NK058(si)001:10497: cad la mnga' bsgyur bas che btsan dam pa'i mchog
NK058(si)001:10498: no // yin te / rdo rje las /
NK058(si)001:10499: ye shes sgyu ma rang snang ba //
NK058(si)001:10500: rdo rje btsan po dam tshig mchog /
NK058(si)001:10501: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub che //
NK058(si)001:10502: 'gro ba kun la rab snang ba'o //
NK058(si)001:10504: gnyis pa de nyid ji ltar bsgrub pa'i thabs bstan pa ni /
NK058(si)001:10505: lam ma nor bar ston pa bla ma dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyis zin pa /
NK058(si)001:10506: de las zab mo'i dbang thob pa dam tshig dang sdom pa la gnas pa /
NK058(si)001:10507: sgrub pa'i man ngag la mkhas pa /
NK058(si)001:10508: brtson 'grus phun sum tshogs pas bsgrub nus pa ste /
NK058(si)001:10509: dngos grub sgrub pa'i cho ga lnga ni rgyud la rdzogs par byas shing /
NK058(si)001:10510: sgrub pa'i gnas bar chad med cing yid dang mthun pa /
NK058(si)001:10511: grogs mtshan nyid tshang zhing skal pa bzang ba /
NK058(si)001:10512: 'tsho ba'i yo byad mtha' gnyis su ma ltung zhing log 'tsho med pa /
NK058(si)001:10513: dngos grub kyi rdzas tshang zhing nyams pa med pa /
NK058(si)001:10514: dam tshig gi rdzas tshogs shing rten du yod pa
NK058(si)001:10515: ste dngos grub sgrub pa'i mthun rkyen gyi yo byad
NK058(si)001:10516: lnga ni yongs su rdzogs par ldan zhing /
NK058(si)001:10522: gsang sngags kyi sgrub pa'i yan lag lnga rdzogs pas /
NK058(si)001:10523: spyir lta ba dang dam tshig ma nyams shing bye
NK058(si)001:10524: brag tu sgrub pa'i mthun rkyen tshogs pa las ma
NK058(si)001:10525: nyams pa sgrub pa la 'jug pa dang zhugs nas
NK058(si)001:10526: sgrub pa la nyin mtshan gnyid dang snyoms las spangs
NK058(si)001:10527: te rab tu brtson na myur du 'grub cing /
NK058(si)001:10528: mi brtson na mi 'grub ces pa'o //
NK058(si)001:10529: gzhung kha cig las brtson pas zhes kyang 'byung ngo //
NK058(si)001:10530: de lta na spyi'i sgrar bshad kyi mi 'grub pa ma bstan to //
NK058(si)001:10531: de'ang kha cig de bzhin nyid kun tu snang dang /
NK058(si)001:10532: gsung yig 'bru thugs phyag mtshan sku rdzogs pa ste cho ga lnga dang /
NK058(si)001:10537: +aa li k+ai li'i 'byor ba ste yo byad lnga dang /
NK058(si)001:10538: yan lag la lha lnga bcu'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK058(si)001:10539: rtog pa'i yan lag lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su shes pa /
NK058(si)001:10540: lha re re'ang bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su dbye ba /
NK058(si)001:10541: de dag gi sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs pa /
NK058(si)001:10542: rigs lngas dbang bskur ba ste sngags kyi yan lag
NK058(si)001:10543: lngar 'dod pa ni bskyed rim 'ba' zhig gi phyogs
NK058(si)001:10544: su lhung bas rdzogs rim gyi de nyid dang /
NK058(si)001:10545: gnas dang rdzas kyi yo byad ma tshang ba'i phyir 'os pa ma yin no //
NK058(si)001:10546: gsum pa thabs des grub pa'i 'bras bu brjod pa la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:10550: dbang po dang brtson pa rab kyis /
NK058(si)001:10551: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug ste zla ba drug gam /
NK058(si)001:10552: 'bring gis zla ba bcu gnyis sa /
NK058(si)001:10553: ma tha mas zla ba bcu bzhi'am /
NK058(si)001:10554: shin tu rtul pos kyang zla ba bcu drug gis
NK058(si)001:10555: tshe la dbang sgyur ba'i rig 'dzin gyi dam pa
NK058(si)001:10556: 'grub bo // de'ang phyag rgya dang lhun gyis grub
NK058(si)001:10557: pa 'di'i gong la yod pa la dam pa'i sgras
NK058(si)001:10558: 'grub bo // mi smos par / 'di la smos pa ci yin na /
NK058(si)001:10559: rnam smin las 'phags shing lus de nyid kyis sangs rgyas thob pas de skad ces btags te /
NK058(si)001:10561: chos kyi mchog ces btags pa bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:10562: de skad du yang lam rim las /
NK058(si)001:10563: don mthong 'jug pa mthar phyin pa'i //
NK058(si)001:10564: tshogs spyod sgrub pa'i dngos grub kyis //
NK058(si)001:10565: lus khams skye gnas zag pa zad //
NK058(si)001:10566: rdo rje'i lus gyur tshe yi rigs //
NK058(si)001:10567: mthong ba'i chos la mya ngan 'da' //
NK058(si)001:10568: lus ma bor bar rgyal ba'i sa //
NK058(si)001:10570: tshe dbang thob pa de nyid kyi rten la tshe
NK058(si)001:10571: bcu drug mthud pa'i lo grangs sam dus na 'tshang
NK058(si)001:10572: rgya ste / skye ba bcu drug tshun chad kyi
NK058(si)001:10573: sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs par sangs rgyas ni thob
NK058(si)001:10574: rgya ste / par byed do // sngags kyi gzhung
NK058(si)001:10575: 'ga' las tshe gcig lus gcig pu des mkha' spyod
NK058(si)001:10578: bcu drug na ji ltar 'gor yang 'tshang rgya bar 'dod pa yin mod /
NK058(si)001:10579: 'dir tshe dbang thob pa des lo stong drug brgya'i
NK058(si)001:10580: bar du tshe gcig gis thub par byas te lhun
NK058(si)001:10581: gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin thob par byed do //
NK058(si)001:10582: de'ang tshe'i 'du byed zad pa na thabs kyis tshe
NK058(si)001:10583: bsrings te lo brgya brgya phyir snur ba de lta
NK058(si)001:10584: bu lan bcu drug lus gcig gis gnas pa yin
NK058(si)001:10586: tshe ni bcu dang drug pa yis //
NK058(si)001:10587: brgya brgya dag tu snur zhing gnas //
NK058(si)001:10588: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas sa //
NK058(si)001:10589: zag gsum zag pa de la med //
NK058(si)001:10592: skye ba bcu drug mthar thug pa'i //
NK058(si)001:10595: kha cig tshe gcig yin yang lus lan bcu drug
NK058(si)001:10596: snur te grong 'jug gi tshul du byed ces pa'ang
NK058(si)001:10597: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas so zhes pas bkag
NK058(si)001:10598: pa yin no // de'ang 'dir tshe dbang dang lhun grub gnyis kyi zhar la /
NK058(si)001:10600: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin kyang bstan pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:10601: gnyis pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:10602: lhun stug po bkod par rang snang sku dang ye shes su grub tshul /
NK058(si)001:10603: de nyid dbyings chos sku'i zhing nang gsal spros pa dang bral bar bzhugs tshul /
NK058(si)001:10604: slar yang gdul bya'i 'jig rten du sprul sku 'char tshul lo //
NK058(si)001:10606: dang po mngon par byang chub pa'i tshul ni dbyings
NK058(si)001:10607: rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i sems nyid ye nas sangs
NK058(si)001:10608: rgyas pa'i ye shes spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang
NK058(si)001:10609: bral ba thig le nyag gcig grub bsal med pa'i
NK058(si)001:10611: glo bur kun tu btags pa'i dri ma rang sar
NK058(si)001:10612: dag pas zad pa dang skye ba med pa'i ye
NK058(si)001:10613: shes brnyes te / dbyings der gnyis su med par
NK058(si)001:10614: 'dres pa chu la chu bzhag pa lta bu'i ye
NK058(si)001:10615: shes ro gcig tu gyur pa'i thig le nyid snang
NK058(si)001:10616: ba ni mngon par byang chub pa dang mi 'gyur
NK058(si)001:10617: rdo rje dang zhi ba chos sku dang /
NK058(si)001:10618: gsal ba longs sku dang ye shes sprul pa'i sku
NK058(si)001:10619: lngar lhun gyis grub pas bsam gyis mi khyab cing
NK058(si)001:10620: mtha' yas pa'i mchog phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin
NK058(si)001:10621: gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i
NK058(si)001:10622: rang bzhin dang gnyis su med par mngon par rdzogs
NK058(si)001:10623: par byang chub pas mchog gi dngos grub brnyes pa
NK058(si)001:10624: zhes bya'o // gnyis pa zhing khams ji ltar snang ba'i tshul ni /
NK058(si)001:10625: de'i tshe lhun stug po bkod pa'i zhing khams chos
NK058(si)001:10626: kyi dbyings dang nam mkha'i mtha' klas par khyab pas
NK058(si)001:10627: bsam yas pa'i ngang rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag
NK058(si)001:10628: cing dri ma thams cad dang bral ba de na
NK058(si)001:10629: rgya phyogs bcur ma chad cing 'di tsam du nges
NK058(si)001:10630: so zhes blos bsam pa dang bral ba'i gzhal yas
NK058(si)001:10631: khang gzhi tshad med pa ye shes kyi 'khor lo
NK058(si)001:10632: la brten pa'i rgyan gyi rnam pa yang 'khor lo
NK058(si)001:10633: rin po ches mtshan pa dang /
NK058(si)001:10634: 'dod yon phun sum tshogs pa phyogs bcur 'khrigs pa'i
NK058(si)001:10635: rol mo'i tshogs chen po dang rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:10636: nam mkha'i mthas khyab par snang ba 'od gsal lhun
NK058(si)001:10637: gyis grub pa ma lus pa bsam yas kun gyi
NK058(si)001:10638: rang bzhin / ye shes kyi gzigs pa dag pa'i
NK058(si)001:10639: yul du mthong nas longs spyod chen po'i gzhir mngon
NK058(si)001:10640: sum du nye bar mnga' brnyes pa dang /
NK058(si)001:10641: brjod pa med cing ris su ma chad pas rgya
NK058(si)001:10642: chen po'i gsung yi ge tshogs chen las 'gro ba'i
NK058(si)001:10643: don lhun gyis grub par 'byung ba ni /
NK058(si)001:10644: gzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor ye nas sangs rgyas pa la /
NK058(si)001:10645: lam ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor zab mos gsal btab pas /
NK058(si)001:10646: 'bras bu gdod ma'i gnas lugs su byang chub pa
NK058(si)001:10647: gsum dbyer med pa ni de dag rang bzhin mthun
NK058(si)001:10648: pa'i ye shes zhes bya ste /
NK058(si)001:10649: yin pa la yin par shes pas yin thog tu slebs pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:10650: de lta bu'i zhing de yang phyogs gang shed na
NK058(si)001:10651: grub pa'i tshul gyis kun gyis bltar yod pa ma
NK058(si)001:10652: yin te / sangs rgyas nyid kyi ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK058(si)001:10654: de ltar snang ba'i zhing khams kyang gnam gang gi
NK058(si)001:10655: zla ba ltar dbyings chos sku'i zhing du thim pas
NK058(si)001:10656: phyi rol tu snang char med la nang gsal du
NK058(si)001:10657: mkhyen char ma 'gags pa ni rang bzhin gcig dang
NK058(si)001:10658: du ma dang bral ba yi chos sku mtha' dang
NK058(si)001:10659: dbus med pa'i de bzhin nyid spros pa thams cad
NK058(si)001:10661: phyir snang thim par bzhugs pa'i longs sku'i cha de
NK058(si)001:10662: nyid sangs rgyas kyis kyang phan tshun mi gzigs te
NK058(si)001:10663: shin tu phra ba'i rang byung gi ye shes de
NK058(si)001:10664: nyid gang du'ang gnas pa med par zhi ba'i dbyings
NK058(si)001:10665: na snang ba ste gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:10666: de skad du'ang rmad byung rgyal po las /
NK058(si)001:10667: chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang na dus gsum gyi
NK058(si)001:10668: sangs rgyas thams cad gcig gis gcig mi gzigs pa'i
NK058(si)001:10671: de'ang kha cig 'gro drug gis mi mthong la sangs
NK058(si)001:10672: rgyas kyis gzigs par 'dod pa ni gzhung gi dgongs
NK058(si)001:10674: 'dir snang ba bzhi mthar phyin pa'i skabs yin te /
NK058(si)001:10675: tshe dbang des 'od gsal ba'i ye shes du ba
NK058(si)001:10676: la sogs pa dang por mthong dus chos nyid mngon
NK058(si)001:10678: de nyid gong nas gong du mched pa las phyi
NK058(si)001:10679: nang gi rtags mthong ba ni nyams gong du 'phel
NK058(si)001:10680: ba'i snang ba'o // de nas sangs rgyas longs sku'i
NK058(si)001:10681: zhing mthong ba ni rig pa tshad phebs kyi snang
NK058(si)001:10682: ba'i snang ba'o // ba'o // de nas de yang
NK058(si)001:10683: nang du zhi bas 'dzin pa med pa ni chos
NK058(si)001:10685: de nas gdod ma'i ngang du longs sku'i zhing snang
NK058(si)001:10686: rim pa ni gzhi thog tu phyin pa ste lhun
NK058(si)001:10687: grub rin po che'i sbubs na gzigs pa med par
NK058(si)001:10688: bzhugs pa'o // gsum pa slar yang gdul bya'i 'jig
NK058(si)001:10689: rten du sprul sku'i 'char tshul ni de nas gdul
NK058(si)001:10690: bya'i 'jig rten du lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las
NK058(si)001:10691: kyis gang la gang 'dul du rig pa'i ye shes
NK058(si)001:10692: sprul pa'i sku mngon par snang ste /
NK058(si)001:10693: de'ang thugs rje rig pa'i ye shes de nyid phyin
NK058(si)001:10694: ci log gi log par rtog pas kun nas btags
NK058(si)001:10695: pa'i ngo bo sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa
NK058(si)001:10696: ma lus pa thams cad rnam par dag cing ji
NK058(si)001:10697: lta ba dang ji snyed pa'i shes bya ma lus
NK058(si)001:10698: pa kun mkhyen pa'i ye shes phyogs bcur rgyas te
NK058(si)001:10699: / ye shes de nyid kyang dbyings rang bzhin gyis
NK058(si)001:10700: dag pa'i chos sku yon tan gyi gter las mi
NK058(si)001:10701: gzhan pa ste ngo bo gcig yin pa'i phyir rtog
NK058(si)001:10702: pa med bzhin du 'gro don lhun grub tu 'byung
NK058(si)001:10703: / ste / yul gdul bya'i 'jig rten dang yul
NK058(si)001:10704: can thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes gnyis ye nas
NK058(si)001:10705: lhun gyis grub pa'i thugs rje chen pos yul yul
NK058(si)001:10706: can du 'brel bas na ma dag pa 'gro ba
NK058(si)001:10707: rigs drug gi 'jig rten du 'das ma 'ongs da
NK058(si)001:10708: ltar ba'i dus thams cad du ye shes kyi spyan
NK058(si)001:10709: gyis gzigs shing su ni 'dul ba'i dus la babs
NK058(si)001:10711: mtho ris la sogs pa'i gnas ris sems can gyis
NK058(si)001:10712: khyab pa ma lus pa de dag thub pa drug
NK058(si)001:10713: la sogs pa'i sprul pa tshad med pa so so'i
NK058(si)001:10714: snang ba dang mthun par snang zhing don mdzad pa
NK058(si)001:10715: yin no // de skad du'ang 'khor lo bcu pa'i mdo las /
NK058(si)001:10716: bde gshegs thugs rje dus ring 'gro ba la //
NK058(si)001:10717: 'dul ba'i yul du mkhyen nas don mdzad pa //
NK058(si)001:10718: dus las mi yol skad cig so sor snang //
NK058(si)001:10719: ye shes gzigs pa khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK058(si)001:10721: de'ang chos sku las ma g.yos par 'byung ste /
NK058(si)001:10722: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos par //
NK058(si)001:10723: sprul pa'i rang bzhin sna tshogs kyis //
NK058(si)001:10725: de ltar snang ba'i sangs rgyas de yang pha rol
NK058(si)001:10726: tu phyin pa'i lugs kyis grangs med pa gsum rdzogs
NK058(si)001:10727: pas 'grub ste / mdo sde rgyan las /
NK058(si)001:10728: grangs med gsum ni rdzogs pa yis //
NK058(si)001:10729: bsgoms pa yi ni mthar phyin to //
NK058(si)001:10731: de'i 'go yang tshogs kyi lam bsam pa nges pa tshun chad nas 'dzin te /
NK058(si)001:10733: bzang dang smon pa'i stobs can gyis //
NK058(si)001:10735: gsang sngags phyi ba'i tshul las skal pa dang mos
NK058(si)001:10736: pa dang ting nge 'dzin rab tu gyur pas lung
NK058(si)001:10737: mnos te bsnyen pa'i mtshan ma gnas pas tshe 'dir
NK058(si)001:10738: sangs rgyas kyi zhal mthong ste /
NK058(si)001:10739: de nas tshe gcig gam gnyis sam gsum la sogs pa na sangs rgyas thob par grags so //
NK058(si)001:10740: rnal 'byor chen pos lugs las mos pa dang brtson
NK058(si)001:10741: 'grus dang dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi stobs kyis lus
NK058(si)001:10742: des tshe la dbang ba'i sa thob nas grol bar
NK058(si)001:10743: gsungs so // 'dir dbang thob cing dam tshig dang
NK058(si)001:10744: ldan pas zla ba drug la sogs pas tshe dbang
NK058(si)001:10745: gsungs so // bsgrubs nas / rten des byang chub tshe gcig lus gcig la 'grub par bstan to //
NK058(si)001:10746: de dag kyang gang la zhugs pa de'i lugs ltar bden gyi /
NK058(si)001:10747: 'di nyid kho na'i ltar yin no zhes nges bzung mi bya ste /
NK058(si)001:10748: gnyen po dang lam dang brtson 'grus dang rkyen gyi stobs so so ba yin pa'i phyir te /
NK058(si)001:10749: 'dag chal gyi stobs so sos dri ma dag pa
NK058(si)001:10750: mgyogs bul dang yul gcig tu bgrod pa'ang brtson 'grus
NK058(si)001:10751: dang stobs so sos mgyogs bul du snang yang yul
NK058(si)001:10752: la nye ring yod pa ma yin no //
NK058(si)001:10753: des na sems la dbang ma thob kyi bar du ni rkyen dang las kyi rjes su byed la /
NK058(si)001:10754: de phan chad ni dus kyang ci dgar snang ste
NK058(si)001:10755: ring ba thung bar bsgyur cing thung ba ring bar
NK058(si)001:10756: 'phrul ba la sogs pa yod de /
NK058(si)001:10757: dus kyang sems kyi snang ba tsam yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:10758: de skad du'ang dri ma med par grags pas bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK058(si)001:10759: dus thung bar 'dod pa rnams la bskal pa mang
NK058(si)001:10760: po zhag bdun gyis 'da' bar byin gyis rlob bo
NK058(si)001:10761: // zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK058(si)001:10762: de'i phyir 'phags pa'i go 'phang thob pa tshun chad
NK058(si)001:10763: la lam zab mi zab la sogs pa nye ring
NK058(si)001:10764: du snang yang / de phan chad sems la dbang
NK058(si)001:10765: thob pas ji tsam gyis grol bar rang dbang yod
NK058(si)001:10766: du snang yang / de / yum bar ma las /
NK058(si)001:10767: rab 'byor gang gi tshe chos rnams la chos kyi mig dri ma med pa thob pa de'i tshe /
NK058(si)001:10768: 'dod na zhag bdun gyis bla na med pa'i byang chub tu 'tshang rgya la /
NK058(si)001:10769: 'dod na bskal pa bye ba khrag khrig rab tu
NK058(si)001:10770: mang pos kyang bla na med pa'i byang chub tu
NK058(si)001:10771: 'tshang rgya ste / 'di yang byang chub sems dpa'
NK058(si)001:10772: sems dpa' chen po rnams kyi thabs la mkhas pa'i
NK058(si)001:10775: gsum pa gang du dbang bskur ba'i don bsdu ba ni /
NK058(si)001:10776: sngar bstan pa'i mchog dbang bde ba chen po'i dkyil
NK058(si)001:10777: 'khor ni yab yum stangs dpyal gnyis sam yang na
NK058(si)001:10778: rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor kha dog lnga ba byas
NK058(si)001:10779: te slob ma dad ldan rnams rab tu zhugs na
NK058(si)001:10780: ji ltar 'dod pa'i dngos grub yid du 'ong ba
NK058(si)001:10781: sngon gzhan gyis thob pa dang mnyam par 'thob par
NK058(si)001:10782: 'gyur ro // de ltar skal pa mnyam pa'i ye
NK058(si)001:10783: shes chen po de don du gnyer na tshe 'di
NK058(si)001:10784: nyid la dngos grub chen po nye bar 'byung ba
NK058(si)001:10785: yi rang bzhin las bzhi dang tshe dbang thob pa'i
NK058(si)001:10786: rten des mchog gi dngos grub ya mtshan chen po
NK058(si)001:10787: sangs rgyas nyid 'byung zhing thob par nges so //
NK058(si)001:10788: de skad du'ang me long las /
NK058(si)001:10789: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs lha'i //
NK058(si)001:10790: dkyil 'khor mngon du mthong zhugs pa //
NK058(si)001:10791: bsod nams bstan pa gang yin pa //
NK058(si)001:10792: phyi sa byas pa'ang de bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:10794: de las gzhan du chos dang bla ma la dad
NK058(si)001:10795: pa med cing rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam
NK058(si)001:10796: tshig nyams pas bsgrubs na tshe 'dir nad dang gnod
NK058(si)001:10797: pa la sogs pa mi 'dod pa sna tshogs 'byung
NK058(si)001:10798: zhing phyi mar ngan song du skye bar phung bar
NK058(si)001:10800: byang chub sems ni ma bskyed dang //
NK058(si)001:10801: the tshom yod pa nyid dang ni //
NK058(si)001:10802: bka' bzhin rtsol ba mi byed pa //
NK058(si)001:10803: ma dad pas ni mi 'grub cing //
NK058(si)001:10806: tshul de skad ces de bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang bcas pas ched du brjod do //
NK058(si)001:10807: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi gnas
NK058(si)001:10808: lugs gsang ba'i snying po don gyi ye shes de
NK058(si)001:10809: kho na nyid nges pa las ye nas grub pa'i
NK058(si)001:10810: dkyil 'khor gyi ngo bo rdo rje'i mtshon byed gzugs
NK058(si)001:10811: brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du bkod pa mchog tu gsang
NK058(si)001:10812: ba sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dam tshig gi le'u
NK058(si)001:10813: ste dgu pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:10815: // don gnyis pa dbang bskur ba'i thabs bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:10816: dbang bskur ba la 'jug pa'i tshul mdor bstan pa dang /
NK058(si)001:10817: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:10819: dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas bcom ldan 'das zag
NK058(si)001:10820: pa med pa'i bde bas dgyes pa chen pos kun
NK058(si)001:10821: tu bzang po yab yum khams gsum chos kyi rgyal
NK058(si)001:10822: por dbang bskur ba slob ma'i rgyud la sbyin pa
NK058(si)001:10823: zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NK058(si)001:10824: nas dbang bskur ba'i ched du brjod pa 'di skad
NK058(si)001:10825: ces brjod do // de'ang dbang gi don la a b+hi she ka ta zhes zer zhing /
NK058(si)001:10826: de'i don yang nus pa 'jug par byed pa ste /
NK058(si)001:10827: 'jig rten na rgyal sar 'don pa la rig byed
NK058(si)001:10828: kyi bum pas dbang bskur nas yul khams la dbang
NK058(si)001:10829: ba'i nus pa 'jug pa dang 'dra bar /
NK058(si)001:10830: rang gzhan gyi don byed pa'i nus pa 'jug pa ste /
NK058(si)001:10831: rgyal po sbyin pa zhes bya'o //
NK058(si)001:10832: yang a b+hi shiny+tsa'i sgras ye shes kyis bgos shing
NK058(si)001:10833: sgo gsum gyi dri ma 'khrud pas na dbang ngo
NK058(si)001:10839: zab dbang spyir bstan pa ni sngar bstan pa bzhin
NK058(si)001:10840: lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed cing bdag nyid 'jug pa dang
NK058(si)001:10841: slob ma 'jug pa dang phan dbang dang nus dbang
NK058(si)001:10842: bskur la gzungs ma byin gyis brlabs te /
NK058(si)001:10843: yum shes rab kyi phyag rgya la yab thabs kyi
NK058(si)001:10844: phyag rgya snyoms par zhugs pa las yab kyi byang
NK058(si)001:10845: sems bde ba'i rang bzhin yi ge h'u gi 'bru
NK058(si)001:10846: tshogs su gsal ba'i rgyun gsang ba rdo rje'i lam
NK058(si)001:10847: nas phyung ste yum gyi pad+mora 'khyil pa slob ma'i
NK058(si)001:10848: lce rtse nas khong bar bstim zhing gtso bo'i dkyil
NK058(si)001:10849: 'khor gyi 'phro 'dus byin rlabs bsdus te slob ma'i
NK058(si)001:10850: snying gar bsgyur zhing gsang sngags brjod do //
NK058(si)001:10851: gzhung 'di kha cig nus dbang lnga po thams cad
NK058(si)001:10852: cho ga 'dis bskur zhing so so'i dmigs pa dang
NK058(si)001:10853: rjes gnang sbyin par byed de /
NK058(si)001:10854: gsang ba'i rgyun de t+r+aam la sogs pa'i yig 'brur
NK058(si)001:10855: gyur pa slob ma'i khong du thim pas lha so
NK058(si)001:10856: so'i dkyil 'khor lnga po'i spro bsdu byed par bzhed
NK058(si)001:10857: do // de ni go rim log pa'i skyon yod do //
NK058(si)001:10858: gnyis pa nus dbang bye brag tu bshad pa la lnga las /
NK058(si)001:10859: nyan pa'i dbang gi ting nge 'dzin ni slob ma
NK058(si)001:10860: rin cen 'byung ldan du gsal ba'i nyan byed rna
NK058(si)001:10861: ba gnyis kyi nang du b+h+r+aum las 'khor lo rtsibs
NK058(si)001:10862: bzhi t+r+aam las lha'i gzhal yas su gsal ba'i rna
NK058(si)001:10863: ba'i dbang po sgra la nyan nus su 'dzin pa'i
NK058(si)001:10864: thig le shin tu dwangs pa'i ngo bo nyid du
NK058(si)001:10865: gnas pa de yi ge t+r+aam zung lnga ya bcu
NK058(si)001:10866: h'u bzhi dzahh+aum bam hohdang bcas pa gsum chos kyi
NK058(si)001:10867: phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog yi ge rnams 'od du zhu
NK058(si)001:10868: ba las / rin chen 'byung ldan gyi dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:10869: gsal bar bskyed la bla mas ye shes pa de
NK058(si)001:10870: kho na 'dra ba spros te slob ma'i rna bar
NK058(si)001:10871: thim pas nyan pa'i sgrib pa dag nas lha dang
NK058(si)001:10872: bcas pa 'od du zhu ba las rin chen 'byung
NK058(si)001:10873: ldan du bsams la dam tshig bsgrag cing rjes gnang
NK058(si)001:10874: ba las / sbyin pa ni / t+r+aam ni 'go
NK058(si)001:10875: 'dren pa ste gsang ba ma h+aa gsang chen a
NK058(si)001:10876: nu gsang mchog gang yin pa rdzogs pa chen po
NK058(si)001:10877: a ti yo ga ste nang ba dang /
NK058(si)001:10878: kri ya u pa yo ga la sogs pa phyi
NK058(si)001:10879: thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa'i gsang ba kun slob
NK058(si)001:10880: dpon las mnyan par bya zhing /
NK058(si)001:10881: rang gis slob dpon gyi dbang ma thob pa de
NK058(si)001:10882: srid du gsang ba'i don nyid rang gi rgyud la
NK058(si)001:10883: goms 'dris su byed cing brtag par bya ba las
NK058(si)001:10884: gang zag gzhan dang yul dus gzhan du smra bar
NK058(si)001:10885: bya ba min bas ma sgrogs shig ces so //
NK058(si)001:10886: gnyis pa sgom pa'i dbang gi ting nge 'dzin ni
NK058(si)001:10887: gsal ba'i 'khor lo'i snying gzhal yas khang du bskyed
NK058(si)001:10888: pa'i nang du dran gzhi gsal ba'i rten byed pa'i
NK058(si)001:10889: dwangs mi thig le yungs 'bru tsam gyi ngo bo
NK058(si)001:10890: nyid gtso bo'i sa bon yi ge h'u gi phreng
NK058(si)001:10891: ba'i tshogs mchog 'od du zhu ba las /
NK058(si)001:10892: thugs kyi rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du gsal btab ste
NK058(si)001:10893: ye shes pa spro zhing thim pas yid kyi sgrib
NK058(si)001:10894: pa sbyangs te 'od du zhu ba lhar gyur pa
NK058(si)001:10895: la rjes gnang sbyin pa ni //
NK058(si)001:10896: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba'i sras po chen po zhes slob ma la bos nas /
NK058(si)001:10897: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi rdo
NK058(si)001:10898: rje lus lha ngag sngags sems chos nyid zab mo'i
NK058(si)001:10900: de'i ngang las rgyal ba thams cad mnyes pa'i mchod
NK058(si)001:10901: pa bsgrub pa dang phyi nang gsang ba bde ba
NK058(si)001:10902: chen pos mchod la 'bras bu rgyal ba kun dang
NK058(si)001:10903: mnyam par sbyor ba'i go 'phang 'thob par gyis shig
NK058(si)001:10904: ces pa'o // gsum pa phrin las kyi dbang gi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK058(si)001:10905: lag pa'i 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su reg shes gsal
NK058(si)001:10906: ba'i rten byed pa'i thig le dwangs pa'i ngo bo
NK058(si)001:10907: nyid h'u gi phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog yi ge'i rang
NK058(si)001:10909: phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor gsal bar bskyed la ye
NK058(si)001:10910: shes pa spro zhing thim pa zhu ba las don
NK058(si)001:10911: grub yab yum du gyur pa la rjes gnang sbyin
NK058(si)001:10912: pa ni // rigs kyi bu khyod ni de ring
NK058(si)001:10913: nyid nas rdo rje las te don yod grub pa
NK058(si)001:10914: pa ni // yin gyis / sems can gyi don
NK058(si)001:10915: dang sangs rgyas mchod pa rang rang gi bsgrub pa'i
NK058(si)001:10916: las rnams ma lus pa kun gyis shig /
NK058(si)001:10917: des sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i rnam 'phrul
NK058(si)001:10918: gyi pho nya mang po'i tshogs tshur 'du bas dngos
NK058(si)001:10919: grub ster zhing phar 'phro bas phrin las bsgrub pa'i
NK058(si)001:10920: rang bzhin du gyur ba kun gyis khyod kyi dgos
NK058(si)001:10921: pa'i don thams cad sgrub par byed pa yin zhes
NK058(si)001:10922: so // yang na pho nya'i lam bsgoms pas dngos grub 'grub par byed pa'o //
NK058(si)001:10923: bzhi pa 'chad pa'i dbang gi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK058(si)001:10924: tshig smra bar byed pa'i lce'i 'khor lo'i gzhal yas
NK058(si)001:10925: su ro 'dzin lce'i dbang po dwangs shing gsal ba'i
NK058(si)001:10926: thig le'i ngo bo nyid yi ge h+r+aihyi rang bzhin
NK058(si)001:10927: zung lnga'i phyag rgya'i tshogs kyi mchog 'od du zhu
NK058(si)001:10928: ba las / snang ba mtha' yas gsung chos kyi
NK058(si)001:10929: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du gsal ba la ye shes
NK058(si)001:10930: pa spro zhing thim pa zhu ba las 'od dpag
NK058(si)001:10931: med du bskyed la rjes gnang sbyin pa ni //
NK058(si)001:10932: phyi nang gsang ba'i chos kyi bdud rtsi bla na
NK058(si)001:10933: med pa rnams kyis theg pa so so gang dang
NK058(si)001:10934: gang la dad pa dang ldan pa'i skyes bu de
NK058(si)001:10935: dang de chos bstan pas ngoms par byos la /
NK058(si)001:10936: dbang po rab la gsang chen rmad du byung ba'i theg pa /
NK058(si)001:10937: 'bring la rgyu'i theg pa chen po /
NK058(si)001:10938: tha ma'i blo can la nyan rang dang lha mi'i
NK058(si)001:10939: theg pa dbang po'i rim pa dang mthun par chos
NK058(si)001:10940: kyi gsang ba so sor bsgrags kyis /
NK058(si)001:10941: dman pa'i gang zag la chen po'i chos dang chen
NK058(si)001:10942: po la dman pa la sogs pa 'chol bar bsgrag
NK058(si)001:10943: pa'i tshul gzhan du bya ba min te /
NK058(si)001:10944: don du mi 'gyur ba dang chos spong ba'i las gsog pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:10946: dman la mchog gi chos mi bshad //
NK058(si)001:10948: rgyan stug po bkod pa las /
NK058(si)001:10949: rgya cher chos kyi snod gyur pa //
NK058(si)001:10950: snod ma yin la sbyar mi bya //
NK058(si)001:10952: lnga pa rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi
NK058(si)001:10953: dbang gi ting nge 'dzin ni mgo la sogs pa
NK058(si)001:10954: yan lag lnga ni 'gro 'dug dang phyag rgya dang
NK058(si)001:10955: yul la blta zhing sgul skyod byed pas bskyod chen
NK058(si)001:10956: 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su lus kyi dbang po dwangs
NK058(si)001:10957: shing gsal ba'i thig le'i ngo bo nyid dang gnyis
NK058(si)001:10958: su med pa / lag pa g.yas kyi dpung mgor
NK058(si)001:10959: h'u mgo la g.yon la s+w+aa rkang pa g.yon la
NK058(si)001:10960: +aam g.yas la h+aa rnams 'od du zhu ba las
NK058(si)001:10961: su med pa / / rigs lnga so so'i dkyil
NK058(si)001:10962: 'khor lnga dang phyi rol tu bsrung ba'i 'khor lo
NK058(si)001:10963: khro bo bcu'i phreng ba dang bcas pa bsgom zhing
NK058(si)001:10965: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku
NK058(si)001:10966: dang gsung dang thugs kyi rdo rje chen po 'khor
NK058(si)001:10967: 'das thams cad la ye nas khyab pa'i rang bzhin
NK058(si)001:10968: rmad du byung ba'i dkyil 'khor kun gyi byed pa
NK058(si)001:10969: po dpal kun tu bzang po khyod yin pas /
NK058(si)001:10970: rigs kyi bu 'di la mchog gi dkyil 'khor dngos
NK058(si)001:10971: grub kun gyi sbyin pa dam pa spyod pa ste
NK058(si)001:10973: gsum pa dbang dang mi ldan pa'i nyes pa ni
NK058(si)001:10974: sgo gsum yo byad dang bcas pas gsang sngags kyi
NK058(si)001:10975: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing phyi nang gsang
NK058(si)001:10976: ba'i dbang rnams rgyud la thob par ma byas par
NK058(si)001:10978: sgrub pa dang gzhan la 'chad pa la sogs pa rtsom par byed pa rnams la /
NK058(si)001:10979: tshe 'dir bsgrubs pa'i 'bras bu dngos grub med cing
NK058(si)001:10980: phyi ma ngan song du sdug bsngal myong bas brlag
NK058(si)001:10981: par 'gyur te / chos zab mo la dbang zos pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:10983: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK058(si)001:10984: gsang sngags bsgrub pa log par 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:10986: gnyis pa phan pa'i dbang ni slob ma lha'i bdag nyid du gsal ba la /
NK058(si)001:10987: rin po che'i dbu rgyan bcings pa ni khams gsum chos kyi rgyal por mnga' dbang bskur te /
NK058(si)001:10988: rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar gsal zhing phyir mi ldog par mtshon pa'o //
NK058(si)001:10989: cod pan te dar dbyangs kyis sgrib pa gnyis dag
NK058(si)001:10990: cing thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel bar mtshon
NK058(si)001:10991: pa'o // me tog gi phreng bas ni las dang
NK058(si)001:10992: bag chags dag cing byang chub kyi yan lag gi
NK058(si)001:10993: tshogs thob pa'i mtshon byed do //
NK058(si)001:10994: de gsum ga dbu rgyan gyi dbang ste sangs rgyas kyi rgyal tshab tu 'gyur ba'o //
NK058(si)001:10995: go cha ni nyon mongs pa'i mtshon gyis mi tshugs shing bdud kyi sgyu 'dul bar mtshon pa'o //
NK058(si)001:10996: rgyal mtshan ni 'khor ba'i rgyu kun nas ldang ba'i
NK058(si)001:10997: cha dang bcas pa dag cing mi mthun pa'i phyogs
NK058(si)001:10998: las rnam par rgyal ba mtshon pa'o //
NK058(si)001:10999: rdo rje la sogs pa rigs lnga'i phyag rgya ni
NK058(si)001:11000: nyon mongs pa lnga gnas su dag cing ye shes
NK058(si)001:11001: lnga thugs su chud par mtshon pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11002: gdugs ni nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba skyob cing thugs rjes 'gro ba skyob par mtshon pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11003: 'di bzhi ni gzhan don phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang ngo //
NK058(si)001:11004: bum pa ni nyon mongs pa'i dri ma 'khrud cing
NK058(si)001:11005: rigs lnga'i nus pa 'jog pa ste zag pa med
NK058(si)001:11007: bza' ba dang btung ba ni 'khor 'das kyi rgud
NK058(si)001:11008: pa dang bral nas bsam gtan gyi ros rgyas par
NK058(si)001:11009: mtshon pa'o // 'di gnyis ni rang don phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang ngo //
NK058(si)001:11010: nyi ma zla ba chu sa sha chen gyi dwangs
NK058(si)001:11011: ma ste snying po lnga yi dbang bskur ba ni
NK058(si)001:11012: / phung po lnga yab lnga 'byung ba lnga yum
NK058(si)001:11013: lnga nyon mongs pa lnga ye shes lngar dag cing
NK058(si)001:11015: 'di ni 'khor 'das gnyis su med par ston pa'i dbang ngo //
NK058(si)001:11016: gsum pa dbang thob pa'i phan yon ni de ltar
NK058(si)001:11017: nus pa dang phan pa'i dbang rnams rdzogs par thob
NK058(si)001:11018: pa'i dus 'di phyin chad rigs kyi bu khyod rgyal
NK058(si)001:11019: ba kun tu bzang po'i sras su gyur pa yin
NK058(si)001:11021: gsang ba'i dbang ni thob ma thag /
NK058(si)001:11022: kun bzang don gyi sras su 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:11024: de'ang phyi pha rol tu phyin pas kyang sems bskyed
NK058(si)001:11025: thob ma thag tu rgyal ba'i sras su brjod de
NK058(si)001:11027: byang chub sems bskyed gyur nas skad cig la //
NK058(si)001:11028: 'khor ba'i btson rar bsdams pa'i nyam thag rnams //
NK058(si)001:11029: bde gshegs rnams kyi sras zhes brjod bya zhing //
NK058(si)001:11030: 'jig rten lha mir bcas pas phyag byar 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:11032: dbang thob nas skye ba phyi ma ngan song du
NK058(si)001:11033: lhung ba'i las dang bag chags kyis mtshams sbyor ba
NK058(si)001:11034: mngon gyur bsrabs shing zad pas ngan song gsum dang
NK058(si)001:11035: de'i sdug bsngal thams cad med pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11036: tshe dbang gi rgyu mthun yod pas 'dir yang tshe
NK058(si)001:11037: ring zhing nor dang 'byor ba dang dbang phyug dam
NK058(si)001:11038: pa'i bde ba phun sum tshogs pa thams cad dang
NK058(si)001:11039: ldan zhing sdug bsngal med pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11040: phyi ma la yang gnas skabs mtho ris kyi 'jig
NK058(si)001:11041: rten lha dang mi'i nang du skye zhing rtag tu
NK058(si)001:11042: dge ba'i chos la spyod pa dang mthar thug thar
NK058(si)001:11043: pa'i bdag po chos sku dang gzugs sku phun sum
NK058(si)001:11044: tshogs pas 'gro ba'i don gnyis phun sum tshogs pa
NK058(si)001:11047: de skad du'ang kha sbyor thig le'i rgyud las /
NK058(si)001:11048: dbang thob bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK058(si)001:11050: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK058(si)001:11051: phyi mar don gnyis lhun grub 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:11053: thugs kyi ye shes mchog tu gsang ba'i snying po
NK058(si)001:11054: phun sum tshogs pa zab mo de kho na nyid
NK058(si)001:11055: nges pa las sangs rgyas kyi rgyal tshab tu dbang
NK058(si)001:11056: bskur ba'i ye shes sbyin pa'i le'u ste bcu pa'i
NK058(si)001:11059: // spyi don gnyis pa lam bskyed pa dang rdzogs pa'i rim pa bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:11060: tha mal gyi mngon zhen bzlog pa bskyed pa'i rim pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11061: snying po'i don la 'jug pa rdzogs pa'i rim pa'o //
NK058(si)001:11063: thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11064: de'i yan lag bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:11070: gzhi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba de nas lam
NK058(si)001:11071: bskyed pa'i rim pa thabs snang ba'i dngos po lam
NK058(si)001:11073: de bzhin gshegs pa thabs kyis rol pas dgyes pa
NK058(si)001:11074: chen pos kun tu bzang po nyid thabs snang ba'i
NK058(si)001:11075: sgyu 'phrul 'dod yon lnga la sogs pa 'khor ba'i
NK058(si)001:11076: chos nyon mongs pa'i rnam par snang ba rnams shes
NK058(si)001:11077: rab stong pa'i rang bzhin du gnas pas d+r+wa ba'i
NK058(si)001:11078: ngo bo ste ye nas spang blang dang dgag bsgrub
NK058(si)001:11079: gnyis su med pa'i chos nyid zung 'jug chen po
NK058(si)001:11080: ni ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i phyir chos thams cad
NK058(si)001:11081: kyi gnas lugs sam rgyas po zhes bya'o //
NK058(si)001:11082: de nyid shes par bya ba'i phyir 'dod yon dang
NK058(si)001:11083: nyon mongs pa ma spangs par ji ltar snang dus
NK058(si)001:11084: nyid nas ye shes chen por dbang bsgyur ba zhes
NK058(si)001:11085: bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin dam pa la yab yum
NK058(si)001:11086: snyoms par zhugs nas thams cad thar lam du bstan
NK058(si)001:11087: pa'i ched du brjod pa 'di skad ces brjod par
NK058(si)001:11088: mdzad do // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:11089: gzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor shes par bya ba dang /
NK058(si)001:11090: lam thabs dang shes rab kyi dkyil 'khor nyams su blang ba'o //
NK058(si)001:11092: snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK058(si)001:11093: ye nas stong pa'i ngang las byung bar rgyu gcig
NK058(si)001:11094: pa yin te / ting nge 'dzin rgyal po las /
NK058(si)001:11095: ji ltar bar snang cung zad sprin med las //
NK058(si)001:11096: skad cig tu ni sprin gyi dkyil 'khor snang //
NK058(si)001:11097: byung nas zhig ste sprin gyi dkyil 'khor med //
NK058(si)001:11098: thog ma gang las byung ba brtag par bya //
NK058(si)001:11099: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par gyis //
NK058(si)001:11101: de ltar stong pa'i ngang las dang por byung bar ma zad /
NK058(si)001:11102: da lta snang dus nyid nas kyang yig 'bru a'i
NK058(si)001:11103: tshul du rang bzhin gyis ma skyes pa'i ngo bo
NK058(si)001:11104: snang stong gnyis su med par gnas te /
NK058(si)001:11105: lha'i bus zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK058(si)001:11106: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa a'i tshul du gnas so //
NK058(si)001:11109: stong pa ni +aah gnyis su med pa ni h'u
NK058(si)001:11110: gi rang bzhin du gnas pas snang bzhin du stong
NK058(si)001:11111: stong bzhin du snang snang ba dang stong pa gnyis
NK058(si)001:11114: rmi lam ji bzhin sgyu ji bzhin //
NK058(si)001:11115: dri za'i grong khyer ji bzhin du //
NK058(si)001:11116: de bzhin skye dang de bzhin gnas //
NK058(si)001:11117: de bzhin du ni 'jig pa'ang gsungs //
NK058(si)001:11119: gang phyir stong pa ma gtogs pa'i //
NK058(si)001:11120: chos 'ga' yod pa ma yin no //
NK058(si)001:11122: me yi rang bzhin tsha bas byin gyis brlabs pa
NK058(si)001:11123: ltar chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin ye nas dkyil
NK058(si)001:11124: 'khor gyi rang bzhin du sangs rgyas par byin gyis
NK058(si)001:11125: brlabs dang ste ma dag pa med cing dag pa
NK058(si)001:11126: 'ba' zhig gi tshul du gnas te /
NK058(si)001:11128: chos kun ye nas dkyil 'khor du //
NK058(si)001:11129: byin gyis brlabs pa rnam par dag /
NK058(si)001:11131: de'ang stong pa chos sku snang ba longs sku sna
NK058(si)001:11132: tshogs su snang ba sprul pa sku'i rang bzhin ni
NK058(si)001:11134: sgra thams cad gsung gi dkyil 'khor /
NK058(si)001:11135: chos nyid thams cad thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du gnas so //
NK058(si)001:11136: de ltar gnas pa'i rang bzhin rnams kyang dus gzhan
NK058(si)001:11137: nam lkog tu gyur pa la sogs pa ma yin
NK058(si)001:11138: par snang dus 'di nyid nas phyi snang ba yum
NK058(si)001:11139: nang phung po yab rtogs tshogs lha'i rang bzhin du
NK058(si)001:11140: gnas pa'i ngo bo mngon sum par snang zhing snang
NK058(si)001:11141: dus nyid nas mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las mi
NK058(si)001:11142: g.yo ba'i dgongs pa ston pa yin te /
NK058(si)001:11144: kun rgyu byang chub sems las ni //
NK058(si)001:11145: sems kyi ngo bo 'byung chen lnga //
NK058(si)001:11146: ston pa byang chub sems lnga byung //
NK058(si)001:11147: sku ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK058(si)001:11148: chos ni rang gi ngo bos 'chad //
NK058(si)001:11149: ston ni rang gi rang bzhin ston //
NK058(si)001:11150: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs sku ste //
NK058(si)001:11151: dgongs pa nyid la nyid mi rtog /
NK058(si)001:11152: chos rnams gzhan la'ang rtog mi byed //
NK058(si)001:11153: byang chub sems kyi ston pa lngas //
NK058(si)001:11154: kun kyang chos nyid de bzhin ston //
NK058(si)001:11156: de bzhin du ye shes yod par dug lngas ston pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11157: sku lnga sems kyis ston pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11158: yum lnga 'byung lngas ston pa ste /
NK058(si)001:11159: bzhin dang gzugs brnyan las kyang gsal bar chos rnams
NK058(si)001:11160: kyi rang gi mtshan nyid sangs rgyas pa'i chos nyid
NK058(si)001:11161: dang snang la ngos gzung med pa'i chos can du
NK058(si)001:11163: de ltar gnas pa'i don gzhi'i gnas lugs rang gi
NK058(si)001:11164: bsod nams dang bla ma dam pa'i thugs rjes byin
NK058(si)001:11165: gyis brlabs pa la brten nas phyin ci ma log
NK058(si)001:11166: par rab tu rtogs pa rnam pa bzhi yis chos
NK058(si)001:11167: thams cad ye nas mngon par rdzogs par byang chub
NK058(si)001:11168: pa'i rgyal po chen por rtogs pa na /
NK058(si)001:11169: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams la spong len
NK058(si)001:11170: med par phyam gcig ye shes kyi rol bar 'char
NK058(si)001:11171: bas gsang chen don gyi gnas lugs so //
NK058(si)001:11172: de ni dbyings de bzhin nyid du bshad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:11174: rgyu gcig pa ting nge 'dzin gsum dang /
NK058(si)001:11175: yig 'bru lha so so'i snying po bskyed pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11176: byin gyis brlabs pa lha'i dkyil 'khor du bskyed pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11177: mngon sum pa de'i ngang la lhan cig pa'i rdzogs
NK058(si)001:11178: pa bsgom pa rab tu rtogs pa rnam pa bzhi
NK058(si)001:11179: yis chos thams cad shes par byed pa'o //
NK058(si)001:11181: rgyu gcig pa 'khor 'das sems su gcig pa'o //
NK058(si)001:11182: yig 'bru'i tshul skye ba med pa'i ngang du rtogs pa'o //
NK058(si)001:11183: byin gyis brlabs pa de ltar mnyam par 'jog pa
NK058(si)001:11184: thugs rdo rje'i ngo bor gnyis su med par gyur
NK058(si)001:11185: pa'o // mngon sum pa so so rang gi rig
NK058(si)001:11186: pa'i ye shes kyis bsgoms pa las rtogs pa ste
NK058(si)001:11188: rgya mtsho dwangs pa'i gzugs brnyan ltar //
NK058(si)001:11189: sgra rten yid la byed min par //
NK058(si)001:11190: rang rig mngon sum dmigs bral bar //
NK058(si)001:11191: rang gsal gsum bral mi sgul bas //
NK058(si)001:11192: nges par gdeng du gang byas pa //
NK058(si)001:11193: thos bsam brtan pa'i lta mthar phyin //
NK058(si)001:11196: rgyu gcig pa bskyed rdzogs dang bden gnyis su gcig pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11197: de'i ngo bo rtag chad las 'das pa yi ge sprin du gnas pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11198: dbyings rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i ngang las bskyed rdzogs su rang snang bar byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11199: de nyid rig pas thag chod cing mi 'gal bar
NK058(si)001:11200: mngon du rtogs nas nyin mtshan du brtson pa ste
NK058(si)001:11202: rtogs pa yang ni rnam pa bzhir //
NK058(si)001:11203: rnal 'byor nang pa bzhed pa ste //
NK058(si)001:11204: rgyu gcig pa dang yi ge'i tshul //
NK058(si)001:11205: byin gyis brlabs dang mngon sum las //
NK058(si)001:11207: rgyun ni bden gnyis cig car du //
NK058(si)001:11208: gcig pas gcig pa'i mtshan nyid dang //
NK058(si)001:11209: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK058(si)001:11210: chos kun rang bzhin rtogs pa dang //
NK058(si)001:11211: skye med dbyings kyi byin rlabs las //
NK058(si)001:11212: chos kun snang bar shes pa dang //
NK058(si)001:11213: de lta bu yi rang bzhin te //
NK058(si)001:11214: gzhan la ma brten mi 'gal bar //
NK058(si)001:11215: mngon sum rig pas thag chod na //
NK058(si)001:11216: rnal 'byor sa la slebs pa yin //
NK058(si)001:11218: gzhung 'di lta bu ni phyogs gcig bu 'di kho na yin no zhes pa'ang mi rung ste /
NK058(si)001:11219: rdo rje'i tshig barlinga zhing gang du'ang sbyar du yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:11220: gnyis pa lam thabs dang shes rab kyi dkyil 'khor nyams su blang ba la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:11221: cir snang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK058(si)001:11223: gang bsgrub thabs kyi yan lag go //
NK058(si)001:11225: snang sems gnyis med kyi dkyil 'khor spyir bstan pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11226: sbyor sgrol gnyis med kyi dkyil 'khor bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:11230: rol pa gnyis su med pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK058(si)001:11232: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor du shes par bya ba ni
NK058(si)001:11233: lus kyi yan lag lnga dang mig la sogs pa'i
NK058(si)001:11234: dbang po dang de dag gi rnam par shes pa'i
NK058(si)001:11235: tshogs dang bcas pa kun tha mal gyi rnam pa
NK058(si)001:11236: rang mtshan pa min par ste ye shes lnga'i rang
NK058(si)001:11237: bzhin du shes par bya zhing de'i mtshon byed du
NK058(si)001:11238: yab lnga sems dpa' brgyad sgo ba bzhi thub pa
NK058(si)001:11239: drug dang bcas pa'i rang bzhin me long nang gi
NK058(si)001:11240: gzugs brnyan ltar med bzhin snang ba'i rigs lnga longs
NK058(si)001:11241: spyod rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom mo //
NK058(si)001:11242: gnyis pa khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du shes par bya
NK058(si)001:11243: ba ni yang na gdul bya'i dbang ngam rang gi
NK058(si)001:11244: mos pa'i dbang gis phung po dang dbang shes kun
NK058(si)001:11245: ye shes lnga'i ngo bo rab tu khros pa'i dkyil
NK058(si)001:11247: gnyis pa yum gyi dkyil 'khor la'ang gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:11248: dang po zhi ba'i yum du shes par bya ba
NK058(si)001:11249: ni snang srid skye 'gros bsdus pa'i gzugs thams cad
NK058(si)001:11250: dang sgra dang dri dang ro dang reg bya la
NK058(si)001:11251: sogs khongs nas chos dang 'byung ba lngar snang ba
NK058(si)001:11252: thams cad / tha mal ba'i gzugs sgra la sogs
NK058(si)001:11253: pa'i rnam pa de dag tu min par m+aum ste
NK058(si)001:11254: gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo nyid
NK058(si)001:11256: de'i mtshon byed sgo ma bzhi sems ma brgyad yum lnga'i rnam pa ste /
NK058(si)001:11257: snang la ngos gzung med pa yum gyi dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:11258: gnyis pa khro bo'i yum du gsal ba ni yang
NK058(si)001:11259: na gdul bya'am rang gi mos ba'i dbang gis khro
NK058(si)001:11261: gsum pa rol pa gnyis su med pa'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK058(si)001:11262: lus la bgo ba'i gos dang 'dogs pa'i rgyan dang
NK058(si)001:11263: bza' ba dang btung ba ngag gi glu dang brjod
NK058(si)001:11264: pa'i tshig dang lus kyi rnam 'gyur rkang pa'i bro
NK058(si)001:11265: dang lag pa'i gar dang nye bar spyad pa'i yo
NK058(si)001:11266: byad kyi tshogs ci dang ci spyod pa thams cad
NK058(si)001:11267: kyi sprin phung chen po la tha mal gyi snang
NK058(si)001:11269: snang stong ngam yab yum gnyis su med pa'i rang
NK058(si)001:11270: bzhin h'u ste gnyis med bde ba chen po'i chos
NK058(si)001:11271: nyid du shes pas chags zhen med la tshogs kyi
NK058(si)001:11272: yo byad rmi lam ltar bden med kyi ngang nas
NK058(si)001:11273: lha mo drug gi rang bzhin du rab tu longs
NK058(si)001:11274: spyod na 'bras bu mchog dang thun mong gi dngos
NK058(si)001:11275: grub ngo mtshar ba'i rang bzhin 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:11276: phung po khams dang skye mched na bzhugs pa'i sangs
NK058(si)001:11277: rgyas thams cad mnyes pas myur du byang chub 'grub
NK058(si)001:11278: pa'i phan yon rlabs po che thob par byed do
NK058(si)001:11279: // gnyis pa sbyor sgrol gnyis med kyi dkyil 'khor la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:11280: sbyor ba gnas su dag pa bde chen byang chub mchog gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK058(si)001:11281: sgrol ba gnas su dag pa thabs chen gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor /
NK058(si)001:11282: sbyor sgrol gyi nyes pas mi gos pas ye shes sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK058(si)001:11287: rten phyag rgya'i dbye ba dang /
NK058(si)001:11288: brten pa ye shes kyi rang bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:11293: bcu gnyis ma ni mkha' pad 'dab brgyad dang ldan
NK058(si)001:11294: pas yab yum gnyis ka la bde bas khyab par
NK058(si)001:11297: bden don rnam pa bcu gnyis ldan //
NK058(si)001:11299: bcu drug ma ni 'dab ma bzhi dang ldan pas
NK058(si)001:11300: yab la bde ba sbyin pa'i phyir klu mo ste
NK058(si)001:11301: / de nyid rnam pa bcu drug rig /
NK058(si)001:11303: nyi shu ma ni 'dab ma gnyis dang ldan pas
NK058(si)001:11304: yum la bde ba 'byin pa'i phyir rigs ngan mo
NK058(si)001:11305: ste / rnam pa nyi shu'i byang chub pa'o //
NK058(si)001:11307: de'ang bcu gnyis nas bco lnga'i bar lha mo /
NK058(si)001:11308: bcu drug nas bcu dgu'i bar klu mo /
NK058(si)001:11309: nyi shu phan chad rigs ngan mos bsdus pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:11310: de dag kyang gzugs bzang zhing chags pa che ba /
NK058(si)001:11311: gzhan dang mi 'grogs shing gsang thub pa /
NK058(si)001:11312: sbyor thabs la mkhas shing shes rab che ba /
NK058(si)001:11313: sgrub pa po la gus shing snying nye ba /
NK058(si)001:11314: dad brtson dang snying rje che ba /
NK058(si)001:11315: bde ba'i rtsa khyad par can ldan pa ste /
NK058(si)001:11316: de ltar na yum de gsum ni thugs gsung sku'i yum ste dngos grub myur du 'thob bo //
NK058(si)001:11317: 'dir kha cig lha klu'i bu mo dngos su 'gugs par 'dod pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11318: kha cig gzugs mdzes mi mdzes bar ma gsum la 'dod pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11321: phyag rgya chen po gsum la 'dod pa ni gzhung gi dgongs pa ma mthong ba ste /
NK058(si)001:11323: rnal 'byor pa kun gyis bsten cing bdag gir bya ba'i yul du ma gyur pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11324: mi mdzes pa las bde ba'i 'os ma yin pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11325: las kyi las rgya dngos kyi rten la sbyor ba'i rim par gsungs pas gnod do //
NK058(si)001:11326: gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa la drug ste /
NK058(si)001:11334: pad+ma can rab ni lus ha cang ring ba ma yin thung ba ma yin /
NK058(si)001:11335: byad gzur ba ma yin leb pa ma yin /
NK058(si)001:11336: sha rtsi sngo ba ma yin ser ba ma yin /
NK058(si)001:11337: mdzes shing dkar la dmar chags pa ste /
NK058(si)001:11338: skyes pa bas rtsa sna bdun cu rtsa gnyis kyis mang ba /
NK058(si)001:11340: lus la tsan+dana gyi dri bro zhing kha nas ut+pala'i ngad ldang ba /
NK058(si)001:11341: lus rgyas kyang sked pa phra ba /
NK058(si)001:11342: rkang lag bya ltar dmar zhing phra ba /
NK058(si)001:11343: mchu sgor cung zad che zhing mchu la pad+ma ri mo yod pa /
NK058(si)001:11344: so legs shing mchu la bung ba 'dul ba /
NK058(si)001:11345: lte ba zab cing pad+ma'i ri mo yod pa sa la'ang pad+ma'i ri mo 'bri ba /
NK058(si)001:11346: lte ba'i 'og nas ri mo 'greng bu gsum yod pa /
NK058(si)001:11347: smin mtshams su ri mo gsum bsgreng ba /
NK058(si)001:11348: skra mtshams dang mur gong nas dar thod lta bu'i ri mo yod pa /
NK058(si)001:11349: lce la ral gri lta bu'i ri mo dang /
NK058(si)001:11350: phrag gong ngam sogs dbrag na g.yung drung 'khyil ba lta bu'i ri mo yod pa /
NK058(si)001:11352: b+ha ga rub cing spu med sha ldan mthon po
NK058(si)001:11353: rus sbal gyi rgyab dang 'dra ba yod pa ste
NK058(si)001:11354: / byed pa sdug cing bcos dka' ba /
NK058(si)001:11355: mthong ba tsam gyis bde ba bskyed cing /
NK058(si)001:11356: skad thos pa'am reg pas rtog pa mi rtog pa'i
NK058(si)001:11357: ye shes su bsgyur cing bde ba'i ting 'dzin ngang
NK058(si)001:11359: de lta bu yod pa'i yul phyogs tsam du'ang bkra shis shing /
NK058(si)001:11360: rnal 'byor pa'i bde ba rgyas par byed la /
NK058(si)001:11361: de dang rtsa phrad na tshe 'di nyid la mchog gi go 'phang thob par nges so //
NK058(si)001:11362: pad+ma can 'bring ni sha dkar zhing rus khyim che la yan lag rags pa /
NK058(si)001:11363: spyod lam rtsing zhing khong dal ba /
NK058(si)001:11364: 'jig rten gyi bya ba mkhas shing bu tsha khye'u skye ba /
NK058(si)001:11365: gzhan gyis bcos su mi btub cing snying nye ste /
NK058(si)001:11366: de dang rtsa 'phrad na lo dus tshun chad kyi 'bras bu thob bo //
NK058(si)001:11367: pad+ma can tha ma ni mdog dkar zhing byad legs kyang snying du mi sdug pa /
NK058(si)001:11368: gzugs 'chos shing byi dor la brtson pa /
NK058(si)001:11369: kha yangs shing gsang mi thub pa /
NK058(si)001:11370: mig phra zhing ba spu kha na yang ba ste /
NK058(si)001:11371: de ni dkar mo mig sgyu ma zhes bya ba ste mi bsten no //
NK058(si)001:11372: de ltar pad+ma can ni kun tu bzang po ye shes mchog gi yum mo //
NK058(si)001:11373: gnyis pa dung can ma la'ang gsum las /
NK058(si)001:11374: rab ni mdog snum zhing skra rtse 'khyil ba /
NK058(si)001:11375: sha ser la rtsa dmar ba /
NK058(si)001:11376: spyod lam mkhas la 'dug tshugs legs pa /
NK058(si)001:11377: tshig dal la zur mig lta ba /
NK058(si)001:11378: shes rab che zhing zur tsam gyis go ba /
NK058(si)001:11379: zug rngu rno zhing rnam rtog rags pa /
NK058(si)001:11380: sha lus sbom zhing mnyen la 'bol ba /
NK058(si)001:11381: skad gdangs che zhing dung 'bud pa 'dra ba /
NK058(si)001:11382: lte ba na dung g.yas su 'khyil ba lta bu'i ri mo yod pa ste /
NK058(si)001:11383: de dang rtsa 'phrad na tshe 'di nyid la mchog gi go 'phang 'thob bo //
NK058(si)001:11384: 'bring ni rgyab nas bltas na dgye ba snyam pa /
NK058(si)001:11385: mdun nas blta na dgu ba snyam pa /
NK058(si)001:11386: lus mdzes la rngom chung ba /
NK058(si)001:11387: brang dgye zhing ol ko legs pa /
NK058(si)001:11388: byad kyi gzengs thung zhing rgyas pa /
NK058(si)001:11389: khyim du byad bying bying tsug byed pa /
NK058(si)001:11390: lus 'dres nas snying nye zhing brtse gdung che ba ste /
NK058(si)001:11391: de dang 'phrad na lo dang zla bas dngos grub 'grub bo //
NK058(si)001:11392: tha ma ni sha ser la mig 'bor che ba /
NK058(si)001:11393: blo rno la dran pa gsal ba /
NK058(si)001:11394: 'dug mi tshugs shing 'gro la dga' ba /
NK058(si)001:11395: lag 'tshub cing bya byed mang ba /
NK058(si)001:11396: gzhung ngan zhing chad la mi btsan pa /
NK058(si)001:11397: skyes pa mig la 'tsho zhing mig ser che ba ste /
NK058(si)001:11398: bkra mi shes pas mi bsten no //
NK058(si)001:11399: de ltar dung can ma ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi yum mo //
NK058(si)001:11400: gsum pa ri mo can la'ang gsum las /
NK058(si)001:11401: rab ni sngo la byad dkyus dang yan lag ring ba /
NK058(si)001:11402: mchu skor che zhing sha lus sbom pa /
NK058(si)001:11403: ol ko nas pad+ma'i bar du gnyer chung yod pa /
NK058(si)001:11404: mig dkyus ring zhing legs pa /
NK058(si)001:11405: so ring thung med cing mnyam pa /
NK058(si)001:11406: byad dang lus la rme ba chung ngu yod cing skad snyan pa /
NK058(si)001:11407: zhi dal che zhing spyod lam 'jam pa /
NK058(si)001:11408: gzugs bzang zhing zhes mkhas pa /
NK058(si)001:11409: dbyibs phyed cing dpral bar ri mo gsum 'greng ba /
NK058(si)001:11410: lha chos dang mi chos gang la'ang goms 'dres che ba /
NK058(si)001:11411: skra mtshams na thod bcings pa lta bu'i ri mo gcig gam gsum yod pa ste /
NK058(si)001:11412: de dang 'phrad na longs spyod dang ldan zhing dngos grub myur du 'thob bo //
NK058(si)001:11413: 'bring ni rtags de dag gi steng du dad pa dang shes rab che ba /
NK058(si)001:11414: gsang thub cing snying nye ba'o //
NK058(si)001:11415: tha ma ni sha rtsi nag la dpral ba ser ba /
NK058(si)001:11416: mig chung la gting mig tu yod pa /
NK058(si)001:11417: kha yangs shing gtam mang ba /
NK058(si)001:11418: nyon mongs che zhing gsang mi thub pa ste mi bsten no //
NK058(si)001:11419: de ltar ri mo can ni rin cen rigs kyi yum mo //
NK058(si)001:11420: bzhi pa ri dwags can ni /
NK058(si)001:11421: ri dwags kyi lus 'dra ba ste /
NK058(si)001:11422: sha rgyas shing nu ma che ba /
NK058(si)001:11423: smad kyi sha rgyas shing b+ha ga rub pa /
NK058(si)001:11424: dbugs dang skye gnas la gla rtsi bro ba /
NK058(si)001:11425: sked pa phra zhing 'gros dal ba /
NK058(si)001:11426: skyes pa la mig mi 'dzum par lta zhing skad snyan pa ste /
NK058(si)001:11427: de dang 'phrad na'ang dngos grub myur du 'thob bo //
NK058(si)001:11428: 'di yi 'bring ni gzugs mdzes shing skad snyan pa /
NK058(si)001:11430: tha ma ni de las ldog pa ste mi bsten no //
NK058(si)001:11431: de ltar ri dwags can ni rdo rje'i rigs kyi yum mo //
NK058(si)001:11432: lnga pa glang po can ma rab ni mig dkyus ring la smin dbrag yangs pa /
NK058(si)001:11433: lus mi ring zhing khong dal ba /
NK058(si)001:11434: gzhan gyi ngag mi phyogs shing sems chung ba /
NK058(si)001:11435: rna ba che zhing ngo tsha chung ba /
NK058(si)001:11436: spyod pa rigs ma rigs shes shing lhod chags pa /
NK058(si)001:11437: kha dbang che zhing shogs che ba /
NK058(si)001:11438: dri zhim zhing yan lag thung ba ste /
NK058(si)001:11439: de nyid rtsa mang bas dngos grub mur du 'grub bo //
NK058(si)001:11440: 'bring ni byad sngo zhing gzengs mtho ba /
NK058(si)001:11441: lus khyim legs shing shed che ba /
NK058(si)001:11442: don mi 'chor zhing bslur mi btub pa /
NK058(si)001:11443: mdo che la spro ring ba ste dpal gyi mtshan dang ldan pas bsten no //
NK058(si)001:11444: tha ma ni rnam 'gyur dang gtam mang ba /
NK058(si)001:11446: dga' mi dga' gnyis ka sla ba /
NK058(si)001:11447: 'dod che zhing ster mi dga' ba ste /
NK058(si)001:11448: bre mo rta ri ma'i rigs zhes bya ba yin pas mi bsten no //
NK058(si)001:11449: de ltar glang po can ni pad+ma'i rigs kyi yum mo //
NK058(si)001:11450: drug pa sna tshogs can ma rab ni /
NK058(si)001:11451: gzugs mdzes shing sked pa phra ba /
NK058(si)001:11452: skad snyan zhing gsang thub pa /
NK058(si)001:11453: sha mdangs gsal zhing gting 'tsher ba /
NK058(si)001:11454: cung zad thung zhing skra li ba /
NK058(si)001:11456: bya bzhag mkhas shing stobs che ba /
NK058(si)001:11457: dpral ba na gnyer ma rdo rje rgya gram ltar yod pa ste /
NK058(si)001:11458: de dang 'phrad na dngos grub nye ba'o //
NK058(si)001:11459: 'bring ni de'i steng du dad pa dang ngo tsha shes shing spro thung bar mngon pa'o //
NK058(si)001:11460: tha ma ni de dag dang mi ldan zhing gom pa gya tshom du 'dor ba /
NK058(si)001:11461: sha rtsub cing yan lag rags pa /
NK058(si)001:11463: gtam mang zhing dgod ka yangs pa /
NK058(si)001:11464: brtags shing mi mdzes la 'jigs par snang ba /
NK058(si)001:11465: ngo tsha chung zhing 'thab la dga' ba /
NK058(si)001:11466: kun dang mi mthun zhing yid du mi 'ong ba ste /
NK058(si)001:11467: bkra mi shis pas mi bsten no //
NK058(si)001:11468: de ltar sna tshogs can ni las kyi rigs kyi yum mo //
NK058(si)001:11469: mtshan 'di dag ni lo nyi shu man chad du
NK058(si)001:11470: gsal zhing de nas cung zad mi gsal ba yin
NK058(si)001:11471: no // de ltar las su rung ba'i phyag rgya ni /
NK058(si)001:11474: sgyu ma dag ni thams cad las //
NK058(si)001:11475: bud med sgyu ma khyad par 'phags //
NK058(si)001:11477: de lta bu'i phyag rgya mtshan dang ldan pa btsal nas /
NK058(si)001:11479: gsang ba'i dbang gi bar gyis rgyud sbyangs shing dag
NK058(si)001:11480: par byas te gdod sgrub pa'i grogs su rung ba
NK058(si)001:11481: yin no // ji skad du he badz+ra las /
NK058(si)001:11482: dang por gso sbyong sbyin par bya //
NK058(si)001:11483: de rjes bslab pa'i gnas bcu nyid //
NK058(si)001:11484: ces gsungs pa dang mthun no //
NK058(si)001:11485: gnyis pa brten pa ye shes kyi rim pa la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:11486: sngon du bsnyen pa bya ba /
NK058(si)001:11487: sgrub pa dang sgrub pa chen pos las la sbyar ba /
NK058(si)001:11488: dngos gzhi ye shes kyi dbye ba'o //
NK058(si)001:11490: rang nyid rlung sems las su rung bas /
NK058(si)001:11491: nyi ma 'gar dal bar bya ste /
NK058(si)001:11496: dgod pa la sogs pas lus kyi rtsa rnams bde bas rgyas par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:11498: de nas stan bde ba la lha'i dkyil 'khor yab
NK058(si)001:11499: yum du gsal ba'i mkha' gsang rdo rje dang pad+mara
NK058(si)001:11501: de'i rtser sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed cing spyan drangs pa la /
NK058(si)001:11505: nu ma mnyed pa la sogs pas khams byang chub kyi sems g.yo bar byed pa ni bsgrub pa'o //
NK058(si)001:11506: de nas snyoms par zhugs pas yab yum gnyis su med pa'i rol pa ni sgrub pa chen po'o //
NK058(si)001:11508: de'i tshe dwangs ma spyi bo nas mgrin par g.yo ba ni dga' ba'i ye shes /
NK058(si)001:11509: mgrin pa nas snying gar babs pa ni mchog dag'i ye shes /
NK058(si)001:11510: snying ga nas lte bar babs pa ni dga' bral gyis ye shes /
NK058(si)001:11511: lte ba nas gsang bar babs pa ni lhan cig skyes dag'i ye shes te /
NK058(si)001:11512: gzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i spros pa mtha' dag nye
NK058(si)001:11513: bar zhi zhing bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes
NK058(si)001:11514: bde ba chen po ni dgyes mnyam mchog gi mchod
NK058(si)001:11515: sbyin te / mchod pa chen po 'dod chags che //
NK058(si)001:11516: sems can thams cad dga' bar byed //
NK058(si)001:11518: de nas rdo rje'i lam nas thig le dkar dmar drangs te /
NK058(si)001:11519: lte ba nas spyi bo'i bar gyi 'khor lo bzhi
NK058(si)001:11520: dang de'i rtsa 'dab rnams gang bas zag pa med
NK058(si)001:11521: pa'i bde bas rgyas shing spros pa thams cad bral
NK058(si)001:11522: ba'i ye shes kyis khyab par bsam pa ni sgrub
NK058(si)001:11523: pa'i nyi zla'i snying po de /
NK058(si)001:11524: dkyil 'khor rdo rje'i lce yis blang //
NK058(si)001:11526: de nas rtsa rnams su 'khrul 'khor dang /
NK058(si)001:11528: dmigs pa med pa'i gnad gsum gyis dgram zhing /
NK058(si)001:11529: rang bzhin spros pa dang bral ba'i ngang du la
NK058(si)001:11530: bzla ba ni chos nyid don gyi ye shes kun
NK058(si)001:11532: de'ang ye shes dang pos zhe sdang gi rtog pa
NK058(si)001:11533: gnas su dag pas bde bar gsal la rang bzhin
NK058(si)001:11534: med pa me long lta bu'i ye shes so //
NK058(si)001:11535: gnyis pa ni nga rgyal rlom sems dag cing yab
NK058(si)001:11536: yum gnyis su med pas mnyam pa nyid kyi ye
NK058(si)001:11538: 'dod chags rags pa'i 'dzin rtog nub pas bde ba'i
NK058(si)001:11539: rang bzhin stong par shes pa so sor rtog pa'i
NK058(si)001:11540: ye shes so // bzhi pa ni /
NK058(si)001:11541: phrag dog dag cing bde stong gi bya ba mthar thug pas bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK058(si)001:11542: de nas yas brtan gyi dga' ba bzhi mthar phyin te /
NK058(si)001:11543: gang du'ang rtog pa med pa ni chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes te /
NK058(si)001:11544: sbyor ba thams cad ye shes su dag cing /
NK058(si)001:11545: ye shes bzhi chos kyi dbyings su dag pa ni /
NK058(si)001:11547: sa bon n+aa da la thim /
NK058(si)001:11548: n+aa da bin d+hu la thim /
NK058(si)001:11549: bin d+hu chos kyi dbyings su thim pa ni rang bzhin lnga dang sbyar ba ste /
NK058(si)001:11550: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa kun bzang yab yum gyi dgongs pa mthar thug pa'o //
NK058(si)001:11552: snying po thig le mnyam sbyor bas //
NK058(si)001:11553: bde ba'i ye shes rol mo las //
NK058(si)001:11554: ye shes dgyes la mchod par 'bul //
NK058(si)001:11555: zhes pa'i don 'dir bstan pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:11556: gnyis pa gzhung gi don la lnga las /
NK058(si)001:11557: yul gang la sbyar ba ni bcu gnyis ma thugs
NK058(si)001:11558: kyi gsang yum lha mo bcu drug ma gsung gi
NK058(si)001:11559: gsang yum klu mo nyi shu ma sku'i gsang yum
NK058(si)001:11560: rigs ngan mo rnams kyi bzang ngan dang bye brag
NK058(si)001:11561: so sor dbye nas ngan pa dor bzang ba bsten
NK058(si)001:11562: pa'am yang na mi dbye bar gang rung yul du
NK058(si)001:11563: byed pa'o // tshul ji lta bus sbyar na ni
NK058(si)001:11564: lha gcig la'ang bsnyen sgrub bzhis bsten pa ltar 'dir
NK058(si)001:11565: yang phyag rgya'i rgyud sbyong zhing byang chub kyi sems
NK058(si)001:11566: rgyas par byed pas bsnyen pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11567: 'du shes dag pas lta ba dang reg pa la sogs pa ni nye ba'i bsnyen pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11568: lhar gsal bas 'khyud pa la sogs pa ni sgrub pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11569: gnyis su med par rol pas 'khor lo bzhi nas
NK058(si)001:11570: gsang bar 'bebs pa ni sgrub pa chen po'i rim
NK058(si)001:11571: pa bzhis ye shes la sbyor ba'o //
NK058(si)001:11572: ngo bo gang sbyor ba ni de nas yum gyi
NK058(si)001:11573: pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor du gnyis su med pa'i byang chub
NK058(si)001:11574: kyi sems yungs 'bru tsam gyi rten bsam pa la
NK058(si)001:11575: / bde ba chen po'i rang bzhin thugs kyi dkyil
NK058(si)001:11576: 'khor sangs rgyas kyi tshom bus brgyan pa spro zhing
NK058(si)001:11577: bskyed la ye shes pa dbyings nas spyan drangs shing
NK058(si)001:11579: sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad la /
NK058(si)001:11580: rol pa'i mchod pa phul bas /
NK058(si)001:11581: spyan drangs pa'i lha dang bdag gi lus kyi gnas
NK058(si)001:11582: su rang bzhin gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK058(si)001:11583: thams cad dgyes pa mnyam pa'i mchog gi sbyin pa
NK058(si)001:11584: chen pos so sor bstim zhing tshim par phul bas
NK058(si)001:11585: gnyis med bde ba chen po'i dngos grub thob par
NK058(si)001:11586: bsam zhing byang chub kyi sems pad+mora 'khyil ba 'dzin
NK058(si)001:11587: par byed do // dngos grub ji ltar blang ba
NK058(si)001:11588: ni de ltar bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhis bsgrub pa
NK058(si)001:11589: byas pa'i mkha' gsang gi nyi ma dang zla ba'i
NK058(si)001:11590: snying po de rtsa 'khor lo bzhi'i dkyil 'khor du
NK058(si)001:11591: gsang ba rdo rje'i lce yis blangs te /
NK058(si)001:11592: mas rim gyis dgang zhing lus kyi gnas thams cad
NK058(si)001:11593: du khyab par dgram zhing ye shes su la bazla'o
NK058(si)001:11594: // 'di la kha cig lhar gsal ba'i lce rdo
NK058(si)001:11595: rjer bsam pas blangs te khong du 'thung bar 'dod
NK058(si)001:11597: sbyor ba'i don ma go ba yin no //
NK058(si)001:11598: bsgrub pa de'i 'bras bu ni rdzu 'phrul gyis nam
NK058(si)001:11599: mkha' la 'gro ba dang mngon par shes pas chos
NK058(si)001:11600: thams cad mngon sum du gsal bar rtogs pa dang
NK058(si)001:11601: / ting nge 'dzin dang ye shes kyi 'od zer
NK058(si)001:11602: 'bar bas sa dang lam gyi khyad par gong mar
NK058(si)001:11603: / bgrod pa dang / tshe nyi zla dang mnyam
NK058(si)001:11604: pas rang bzhin gyi don sgrub cing rdo rje'i sku
NK058(si)001:11605: / bgrod pa dang / brnyes pa dang / la sogs pa'i khongs nas ral gri dang /
NK058(si)001:11609: rkang mgyogs la sogs pa thun mong gi grub pa brgyad thob par bstan to //
NK058(si)001:11610: mthar thug kun tu bzang po'i sa mchog yid bzhin
NK058(si)001:11611: sprin gyis bdag por 'gyur zhing sku dang ye shes
NK058(si)001:11612: 'du 'bral med pas 'gro ba'i don gnyis lhun gyis
NK058(si)001:11613: grub pa'o // gnyis pa sgrol ba gnas su dag
NK058(si)001:11614: pa thabs chen gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor la gsum las
NK058(si)001:11615: grub pa'o // / gang bsgral ba'i yul ni snying rje'i zhing du gyur pa ste /
NK058(si)001:11617: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK058(si)001:11618: bsad cing mnan pa ma yin te //
NK058(si)001:11619: phung po rdo rje gtams byas nas //
NK058(si)001:11620: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK058(si)001:11622: rang la zhe sdang gi sems rang mtshan pa med cing snying rjes 'drongs pa dgos so //
NK058(si)001:11623: de'ang zhi rgyas kyis mi 'dul zhing mngon spyod kyis 'dul bar bya ba'i sems can de /
NK058(si)001:11624: mchog mtho ris kyis lha mi dang mchog phran ngan
NK058(si)001:11625: song gi 'gro ba ste dbye na zhing rnam pa
NK058(si)001:11626: bcu po rnams sdug bsngal gyi rgyu dang 'bras bu
NK058(si)001:11627: la gnas pas / de dag rang rang gi sdug
NK058(si)001:11628: bsngal de dang bral bar bya ba'i phyir bsgral la
NK058(si)001:11629: la gnas pas / / de'ang dam tshig gsal bkra las /
NK058(si)001:11630: dkon mchog slob dpon sku dgra gnyis //
NK058(si)001:11631: dam las log dang 'khus pa dang //
NK058(si)001:11633: dam dgra ngan pa'i ngang tshul can //
NK058(si)001:11634: ngan song gsum dang bcu po 'di //
NK058(si)001:11635: rnal 'byor kun gyis dang du blang //
NK058(si)001:11639: snying rje chen po gsum yod pa la ni /
NK058(si)001:11640: rgyu'i theg pa la'ang mi dge ba dang po bdun gnang ba'i skabs yod de /
NK058(si)001:11641: sems dpa' che la mi dge bdun po gnang //
NK058(si)001:11643: mi nag mdung thung can la bya ba bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:11644: ji ltar bsgral ba'i thabs ni rnal 'byor pa rab ting nge 'dzin gyis sgrol la /
NK058(si)001:11645: 'bring ting nge 'dzin dang sngags dang phyag rgyas sgrol la /
NK058(si)001:11646: tha mas de dag gi steng du 'brub khung dang
NK058(si)001:11647: ling+ga la sogs pa rdzas dngos su bsags te gzugs
NK058(si)001:11648: brnyan dang bcas pas sgrol ba yin pas /
NK058(si)001:11649: bca' gzhi ni dkyil 'khor gyi lho nub tu 'brub
NK058(si)001:11650: khung ro sol gyis byugs pa e gru gsum 'bar
NK058(si)001:11651: ba'i nang du ma las nyi ma dang a las
NK058(si)001:11652: zla ba'i steng du ling+ga ming rus dang bcas pa
NK058(si)001:11653: sgrol ba'i las la mkhas pa'i rnal 'byor bas bzhag
NK058(si)001:11654: ste / ting nge 'dzin gyis dgug gzhug bya'o //
NK058(si)001:11656: rang bzhin gyis sgrol ba'i lta ba la mkhas pa /
NK058(si)001:11657: ting nge 'dzin gyis sgrol ba'i sgom pa la mkhas pa /
NK058(si)001:11658: dbang po yul dus kyis sgrol ba'i spyod pa la mkhas pa /
NK058(si)001:11659: thabs chen gsang bas sgrol ba'i gdams ngag la mkhas pa /
NK058(si)001:11660: mngon phyung zab mos sgrol ba'i mdzad spyod la mkhas pa'o //
NK058(si)001:11661: de nas bdag nyid dpa' bo chen po yab yum
NK058(si)001:11662: gyi ngo bor bskyed la gdug pa can bsgral bar
NK058(si)001:11663: bya'o snyam pa'i nga rgyal dang ldan pas /
NK058(si)001:11664: lag pa'i sor mo bcu la dpa' bo 'bru lnga'am
NK058(si)001:11665: sgrol ging bcu'i sa bon h'u bcu las ging pho
NK058(si)001:11666: bcur bskyed pa'i bar du zangs gri'am phur pa 'dril
NK058(si)001:11667: zhing lag pa'i 'du byed ling+ga'i snying la gzir bas
NK058(si)001:11668: sha khrag dum bur gtubs te sgrol ging bcus gtso
NK058(si)001:11669: bo la bstabs shing dkyil 'khor la mchod par bsgom
NK058(si)001:11670: mo // yang sgo gsum gyi sgrib pa sbyangs te /
NK058(si)001:11671: rnam par shes pa h'u dkar po gcig tu gyur
NK058(si)001:11672: pas las dang bag chags thams cad rnam par dag
NK058(si)001:11673: nas h'u de nyid rim gyis zla tshes kyi dbyings
NK058(si)001:11674: su thim nas zla tshes me long lta bu'i ye
NK058(si)001:11675: shes yongs su gyur pa las /
NK058(si)001:11676: thugs kyi phyag rgya rdo rje 'od 'bar ba gcig tu gyur /
NK058(si)001:11677: de las rdo rje sems dpa'i skur gyur cing 'od zer rab tu 'phro bas brjid par bsgom mo //
NK058(si)001:11678: de'i spyi gtsug tu 'khor ba las rnam par rgyal
NK058(si)001:11679: ba'i rtags su kun tu bzang po'i sku tshon gang
NK058(si)001:11681: rlung gi dkyil 'khor gyi steng du zla ba'i gdan la bzhag nas /
NK058(si)001:11683: de bzhin gshegs pa'i zhal du zhugs yum gyi mkhar
NK058(si)001:11684: rdo rje sems dpar bskyed de de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK058(si)001:11685: sras su byas nas sems can gyi don byed par
NK058(si)001:11686: bsam mo // de ltar bsgral ba'i phan yon ni
NK058(si)001:11687: sdig pa can de dag phyi ma ngan song mu
NK058(si)001:11688: mtha' med par skye nges mngon spyod kyis bsgral bas
NK058(si)001:11689: mtho ris su thar pa thob pa'i thabs 'di ni
NK058(si)001:11690: bsam mo // / theg pa gzhan las ngo mtshar
NK058(si)001:11691: ba rdo rje theg pa'i gsang chen te sdig can
NK058(si)001:11692: ngan 'gro las thar nas grol ba thob pa'i thabs
NK058(si)001:11694: kha cig gsod pa 'di ni zhe sdang gi las
NK058(si)001:11695: yin pas lam dam pa ma yin no zhe na
NK058(si)001:11696: / de'ang dam pa rnams ni zhe sdang med pa'i
NK058(si)001:11697: phan sems kyis sgrol bas 'gro ba thar pa la
NK058(si)001:11698: dgod pa'i phyir nyes pa med de /
NK058(si)001:11700: gang du gdug pa gdug spyod pa //
NK058(si)001:11701: de la nyes pa ma mthong ngo //
NK058(si)001:11703: rnal 'byor gyi rgyud ngan song sbyong ba las kyang /
NK058(si)001:11704: bla ma dmod brtson ma rungs dang //
NK058(si)001:11705: de sogs byed pa tshar gcod na //
NK058(si)001:11709: bla ma dmod la brtson pa dang //
NK058(si)001:11710: dkon cog gsum la gnod pa dang //
NK058(si)001:11711: sangs rgyas bstan pa 'jig pa ni //
NK058(si)001:11712: sngags mkhan sngags kyis bsgral bar bya //
NK058(si)001:11714: gsum pa sbyor sgrol gyi nyes pas mi gos pa ye shes sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK058(si)001:11715: don dam par chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs ye
NK058(si)001:11716: gdod ma nas skye ba med pa'i de bzhin nyid
NK058(si)001:11717: yin te / dkon cog ta la'i mdo las /
NK058(si)001:11718: chos kun ma skyes rtag tu nam mkha' 'dra //
NK058(si)001:11720: chos thams cad 'byung ba med pa'i mdo las /
NK058(si)001:11721: sangs rgyas yod min sangs rgyas chos med de //
NK058(si)001:11722: nam yang sems can med par sus mthong zhing //
NK058(si)001:11723: nam mkha' 'dra ba'i chos nyid sus shes pa //
NK058(si)001:11724: de ni myur du skyes bu gtso bor 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:11726: kun rdzob snang tsam nyid nas rang bzhin med bzhin
NK058(si)001:11727: du rkyen gyis sna tshogs su snang ba'i shing bu
NK058(si)001:11728: rde'u las rta glang dang skyes ba bud med la
NK058(si)001:11729: sogs pa'i rnam par shar ba'i sgyu ma dang ngos
NK058(si)001:11730: gzung med pa'i mig g.yor gyi tshul te /
NK058(si)001:11731: ye shes snang pa rgyan gyi mdo las /
NK058(si)001:11732: ji ltar sgyu mar gyur pa'i gzugs //
NK058(si)001:11733: skyes pa ma yin 'ong ba min //
NK058(si)001:11734: sna tshogs chos rnams de 'dra ste //
NK058(si)001:11735: skyes pa ma yin 'ong ba min //
NK058(si)001:11737: de ltar chos rnams thams cad ye nas dag cing
NK058(si)001:11738: sgyu ma'i rang bzhin yin pas sbyor sgrol yang ye
NK058(si)001:11739: nas dag cing sgyu ma'i rang bzhin du khong du
NK058(si)001:11741: sbyor ba dang sgrol ba'i bya ba kun byas kyang
NK058(si)001:11742: byed dus nyid nas las gsog byed kyi nyes pas
NK058(si)001:11743: bskyed pa'i sbyor sgrol rang mtshan pa rdul phra rab
NK058(si)001:11744: kyi cha tsam yang don la byas pa med de
NK058(si)001:11746: de skad du'ang ye shes rgyas pa las /
NK058(si)001:11747: ji ltar sgyu ma'i mkhan po dag /
NK058(si)001:11748: rang gis sprul pa'i sgyu ma la //
NK058(si)001:11749: dge dang mi dge'i 'du byed pa //
NK058(si)001:11750: nyes pa gang gis mi gos ltar //
NK058(si)001:11751: thabs la mkhas pas rnam par spyod //
NK058(si)001:11754: skye bo phal cher mgo mang bye ba gcod byed kyang //
NK058(si)001:11755: 'gro kun sprul 'drar rab shes de la 'jigs pa med //
NK058(si)001:11758: sems can thams cad bsad na yang //
NK058(si)001:11759: de la sdig gis gos pa med //
NK058(si)001:11761: de'ang sdig pa rang mtshan pa 'byung ba la bden
NK058(si)001:11762: zhen rang mtshan yod pa dgos shing ngo bo ma
NK058(si)001:11763: grub pa dang / 'du shes gzhan du gyur pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11764: 'dzin zhen med pa smyo ba'i gang zag gi nyes pas kyang ltung ba med par bzhag ste /
NK058(si)001:11766: rmi lam ni med pa dang 'dra'o //
NK058(si)001:11767: de'i 'bras bu ni ma byas pa nyid do //
NK058(si)001:11769: smyo ba dang sems 'khrugs pa la ltung ba med do //
NK058(si)001:11771: shes gtso 'du shes gzhan du gyur pa nyid na'o //
NK058(si)001:11772: zhes pa la sogs pas shes te /
