NK058(si)001:11773: 'dir yang sbyor sgrol rmi lam ltar ngo bo med par rtog pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11775: smyon pa ltar bden zhen med pas nyes pa med pa'o //
NK058(si)001:11776: gnyis pa rol pa tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:11782: ji ltar bya ba'i thabs so //
NK058(si)001:11784: ga na tsakra'i sgra las tshogs kyi 'khor lo ste /
NK058(si)001:11785: de'i mtshan nyid gsang sngags kyi kun tu spyod pa'i
NK058(si)001:11786: skabs gang zhig rten dang gang zag dang yo byad
NK058(si)001:11787: khyad par can tshogs pa ste /
NK058(si)001:11789: rten dang gang zag yo byad tshogs //
NK058(si)001:11790: thabs chen gsang bas tshogs zhes bya //
NK058(si)001:11795: gang gi don du bya ba'o //
NK058(si)001:11798: skye bo mdza' ba kun tshogs pa //
NK058(si)001:11800: 'byor pa'i longs spyod tshang ba ni //
NK058(si)001:11801: bde ba'i longs spyod tshogs su bshad //
NK058(si)001:11802: lha dang dam can kun 'dus pa //
NK058(si)001:11803: 'dus pa chen po'i tshogs su bshad //
NK058(si)001:11804: tshogs gnyis rgyun du rdzogs byed pa //
NK058(si)001:11805: tshogs chen po ru nges par brtag /
NK058(si)001:11811: bsod nams ye shes kyi tshogs so //
NK058(si)001:11813: dam tshig dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pho mo zung
NK058(si)001:11814: du tshogs pa ste thabs dang shes rab kyi rang
NK058(si)001:11815: bzhin mtshon pa'o // de'ang 'dus pa chung ngu'i tshe gtso bo yab yum tsam /
NK058(si)001:11816: sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin zung gsum /
NK058(si)001:11817: rigs lnga'i mtshon byed zung lnga ste /
NK058(si)001:11821: 'dus pa 'bring la dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i grangs te bargya'o //
NK058(si)001:11822: 'dus pa chen po la de yan chad rab tu mang po'o //
NK058(si)001:11823: de skad du'ang gsang rgyud las /
NK058(si)001:11824: 'dus pa chung la gnyis drug bcu //
NK058(si)001:11826: chen po rab tu mang po'o //
NK058(si)001:11828: de'ang rnal 'byor pho mo gang rung mang po tshogs
NK058(si)001:11829: kyang zung du ma 'brel bas dpa' bo'i dga' ston
NK058(si)001:11830: dang / dpa' mo'i ston mo zhes par 'gyur ro //
NK058(si)001:11832: phyi nang gsang ba'i yo byad thams cad yin la /
NK058(si)001:11833: khyad par du sha dang chang ni med du mi
NK058(si)001:11834: rung ba'i thabs dang shes rab kyi rdzas te de
NK058(si)001:11835: las / ma h+aa m+aam sa bdud rtsir bcas //
NK058(si)001:11836: med du mi rung dngos grub rdzas //
NK058(si)001:11838: 'dod pa'i yon tan thams cad do //
NK058(si)001:11840: de'ang glu gar dang rol mo'i sprin phung du mas brgyan pa'o //
NK058(si)001:11842: rten dang brten par bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor dam can
NK058(si)001:11843: rgya mtsho'i tshogs gtso bo la 'khor gyis bskor ba
NK058(si)001:11844: thams cad de dngos kyi sku dang /
NK058(si)001:11845: me tog gi tshom bu lhar bskyed pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11846: ting nge 'dzin gyis bsod nams kyi zhing du spyan drangs pa thams cad do //
NK058(si)001:11848: rgyun gyi tshogs gnyis dang khyad par du tshogs kyi
NK058(si)001:11849: 'khor lo'i tshe thabs bskyed rim dang 'brel ba'i kun
NK058(si)001:11850: tu spyod pa snang bcas thams cad bsod nams kyi
NK058(si)001:11851: tshogs dang / shes rab rdzogs rim gyis bsdus pa'i
NK058(si)001:11852: zab mo skye med du rtogs shing bsgom pa rnams
NK058(si)001:11853: tshogs dang / ye shes so // gnyis pa las rim la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:11857: zhi ba'i tshogs kyi tshe rnal 'byor ba rnams zhi
NK058(si)001:11858: ba'i cha lugs dang phyag mtshan dang me tog phog
NK058(si)001:11859: pa'i lha'i rtags dang ldan pas tshogs khang du zhugs
NK058(si)001:11860: pa na / gshin rje gshed la sogs pa'i sgo ba bzhi tshogs khang gi sgo nas sdod pas /
NK058(si)001:11861: legs par 'ongs sam zhes pa'i brdar mdzub mo gcig bsgrengs pa'i lan du /
NK058(si)001:11862: 'ongs so zhes gnyis bsgrengs te nang du phyin pa
NK058(si)001:11863: las las kyi rdo rjes rigs gang yin zhes pa'i
NK058(si)001:11864: brdar / rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i phyag rgya gdengs pa'i lan du /
NK058(si)001:11865: rigs gang la me tog phog pa'i gtso bo de'i phyag rgya bstan to //
NK058(si)001:11866: de nas rdo rje slob dpon la phyag 'tshal te /
NK058(si)001:11867: dbang gi rim pas bum dbang dge bsnyen /
NK058(si)001:11869: shes rab ye shes dge slong /
NK058(si)001:11870: rdzogs pa chen po gnas brtan te /
NK058(si)001:11871: gtso bo'i phyogs bzhi nas rigs bzhi gral rkyang pa'am /
NK058(si)001:11872: g.yas g.yon dang gung la rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK058(si)001:11873: gral mtshon pa rdo rje dang 'khor lo la sogs
NK058(si)001:11874: pa'i phyag mtshan gral 'gor bzhag pa nas rim gyis
NK058(si)001:11875: 'khod de / cho ga rdzogs par byed pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:11876: gnyis pa khro bo la yang tshul de dang 'dra bar shes par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:11877: zhi khro phyogs gcig pa'i tshogs 'khor la ni zhi
NK058(si)001:11878: ba'i rnal 'byor pho mo rnams rdo rje slob dpon
NK058(si)001:11880: khro bo rnams g.yon gral la 'khod do //
NK058(si)001:11881: rnal 'byor pho mo yang grangs mnyam na shin tu legs so //
NK058(si)001:11882: gsum pa gang gi don du bya ba ni /
NK058(si)001:11883: las bzhi'i bye brag gis shes par bya ste /
NK058(si)001:11884: rnal 'byor pa gang dag dam tshig gso zhing sgrib
NK058(si)001:11885: pa sbyong na zhi ba'i don du tshogs kyis bskangs
NK058(si)001:11886: shing / tshe dang 'byor ba spel na rgyas pa /
NK058(si)001:11887: dbang dang dgug pa'i ched du dbang /
NK058(si)001:11888: bgegs dang gdug pa tshar gcod pa la sogs pa'i
NK058(si)001:11889: don du drag po'i rim pa so so'i 'dod don
NK058(si)001:11890: bsgrub pa la sbyor ba yin no //
NK058(si)001:11891: gsum pa ji ltar bya ba'i thabs la lnga ste /
NK058(si)001:11892: dang po rten dang yo byad bsham pa ni /
NK058(si)001:11893: gnas der mtshan mo la sogs pa'i tshe lha'i dkyil
NK058(si)001:11894: 'khor ras bris sam rdul mtshon tshom bu bkod pa'i
NK058(si)001:11895: drung du phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11896: tshogs kyi yo byad ci 'byor ba dang /
NK058(si)001:11897: nang mchod bdud rtsi ril bus bran pa rnams bsham mo //
NK058(si)001:11898: gnyis pa rnal 'byor la gnas par gsol ba gdab
NK058(si)001:11899: pa ni rnal 'byor pho mo kun gral la 'khod
NK058(si)001:11900: pa la las kyi rdo rjes phyag 'tshal zhing me
NK058(si)001:11901: tog gtor nas phod ka'i phu dung pus mos bsnol
NK058(si)001:11902: zhing 'dud de / hoh dpal kun tu bzang po'i
NK058(si)001:11903: rang bzhin tshad med pa'i thugs rjes 'gro ba'i don
NK058(si)001:11904: la zhugs pa bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa che
NK058(si)001:11905: ge mos gtso mdzad rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen
NK058(si)001:11907: chos thams cad rdzogs pa chen po'i rang bzhin du gdod nas mngon par byang chub kyang /
NK058(si)001:11908: 'gro ba'i khams rnam ma rig pa'i dbang gis 'jig
NK058(si)001:11909: rten drug gi phyogs bcu kun tu khyab pa la
NK058(si)001:11910: dgongs te / thugs rje chen po'i rol pas rang
NK058(si)001:11911: bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du ting nge
NK058(si)001:11912: 'dzin zab mos rnal 'byor la gnas par zhu 'tshal
NK058(si)001:11913: dgongs te / / zhes dal bus brjod nas phyag bya'o //
NK058(si)001:11914: gsum pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK058(si)001:11915: de nas bgegs la gtor ma byin nas rgya mtsho'i mthar bskrad de /
NK058(si)001:11916: me ri me dpung mtshon cha'i ra ba khro bo
NK058(si)001:11917: bcu dang bcas pa'i mtshams bcad de sngar bstan pa
NK058(si)001:11918: bzhin lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal btab la /
NK058(si)001:11919: mchod pas mnyes pa'i bar du mnyes par bya ste /
NK058(si)001:11920: tshogs mchod rnams bsang sbyangs spel bsgyur ji lta ba bzhin bya'o //
NK058(si)001:11921: de'ang thod pa'i snod yangs shing rgya che bar sha
NK058(si)001:11922: lnga bdud rtsi lnga'i rang bzhin las grub par byin
NK058(si)001:11924: bzhi pa longs spyod pa ni lag pa gnyis kyi
NK058(si)001:11925: mthil du nyi ma dang zla ba'i dbus su dpa'
NK058(si)001:11926: bo 'bru lnga dang dpa' mo 'bru lnga las /
NK058(si)001:11927: tshogs kyi lha yab yum bcu 'dod yon lnga'i mchod sprin 'gyed pa gsal bar bskyed nas /
NK058(si)001:11928: bza' btung la reg pas mnyes par bsams la /
NK058(si)001:11929: de nas phung po khams dang skye mched kyi lha mchod par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:11930: de yang las kyi rdo rjes phyag 'tshal zhing thabs
NK058(si)001:11931: dang shes rab kyi rdzas pad+ma'i phyag rgyas brim zhing
NK058(si)001:11933: dpa' bo chen po dgongs su gsol //
NK058(si)001:11934: 'di ni chos rnams bzang po ste //
NK058(si)001:11935: 'dus pa rnams la the tshom med //
NK058(si)001:11936: bram ze khyi dang gdol ba gsum //
NK058(si)001:11937: rang bzhin gcig tu dgongs te rol //
NK058(si)001:11938: zhes pa'i lan du len pa pos kyang pad+ma'i phyag rgyas //
NK058(si)001:11939: bde bar gshegs pa chos kyi sku //
NK058(si)001:11940: gzung dang 'dzin pa rnam par spangs //
NK058(si)001:11941: 'dod chags la sogs dri ma bral //
NK058(si)001:11942: de bzhin nyid la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK058(si)001:11943: a la la hoh zhes pas blangs te longs spyod /
NK058(si)001:11944: de'ang tshogs kyi gral du rtsod pa dang ku co
NK058(si)001:11945: dang tha mal gyi snang bas bden par zhen pa
NK058(si)001:11946: la sogs pa mi bya bar /
NK058(si)001:11952: sems chos nyid kyi dkyil 'khor gsum du shes par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:11953: lnga pa mjug gi bya ba ni /
NK058(si)001:11954: rjes la lhag ma'i gtor ma btang la /
NK058(si)001:11958: bkra shis brjod pa rnams bya'o //
NK058(si)001:11961: bsod nams nang na tshogs 'khor mchog /
NK058(si)001:11963: bgegs dang bar chad zhi ba dang //
NK058(si)001:11964: phyi ma rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing //
NK058(si)001:11965: kun tu bzang po thob par 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:11967: de'ang rnam pa gsum gyis theg pa 'og ma'i mchod sbyin las 'phags te /
NK058(si)001:11968: yul lhar gsal bas sangs rgyas yin pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11969: dngos grub bdud rtsir gyur pas tha mal ma yin pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11970: bsam pa chos nyid du rol pas 'dzin zhen med pa ste /
NK058(si)001:11971: de'i phyir thabs kyi rang bzhin rdo rje'ii theg pa shes rab khyad par can gyis 'phags so //
NK058(si)001:11972: gnyis pa gzhung gi don la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:11973: kun tu bzang po'i tshogs mchod mdor bstan pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11974: dkyil 'khor so so'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:11976: rang bzhin shes par bya ba ni dag pa gsum
NK058(si)001:11977: dang mnyam pa bzhis chos thams cad ye nas sangs
NK058(si)001:11978: rgyas pa kun tu bzang po'i zhing du mtshon pa
NK058(si)001:11979: ste / de'ang phyi snod kyi 'jig rten 'byung ba
NK058(si)001:11980: lnga'i ngo bo yum lnga'i rang bzhin du dag cing
NK058(si)001:11981: ste / / nang bcud kyi sems can phung po lngas bsdus pa yab lngar dag la /
NK058(si)001:11982: rang rang gi rgyud kyi dbang po dang rnam par
NK058(si)001:11983: shes pa dang de dag gi yul rnams sems dpa'
NK058(si)001:11984: dang sems ma dang sgo ba yab yum du dag
NK058(si)001:11985: pa'o // yang snod gzhal yas khang /
NK058(si)001:11987: rang gi rgyud ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:11988: chen por gnas pa rnams ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i
NK058(si)001:11989: rang bzhin du rnam par dag par rtogs shing /
NK058(si)001:11990: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad don dam
NK058(si)001:11991: par ma skyes par mnyam zhing kun rdzob tu sgyu
NK058(si)001:11992: ma lta bur mnyam pa gnyis dang /
NK058(si)001:11993: phung po lnga sangs rgyas su mnyam pa dang /
NK058(si)001:11994: rnam shes brgyad ye shes su mnyam pa ste /
NK058(si)001:11995: lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis kyis chos thams cad la bzang ngan blang dor med pa'i dkyil 'khor te /
NK058(si)001:11996: chos nyid don gyi gnas lugs ji ltar shar zhing
NK058(si)001:11997: snang ba de dag rang bzhin kun tu bzang po'i
NK058(si)001:11998: zhing khams rgya chad phyogs lhung med pas 'khor 'das
NK058(si)001:12002: dkyil ni ma nor don gyi snying po ste //
NK058(si)001:12003: 'khor ni 'khor 'das brdal ba yongs la khyab //
NK058(si)001:12005: gang gis shes par bya ba ni /
NK058(si)001:12006: de ltar rdzogs pa chen po'i rang bzhin du rtogs
NK058(si)001:12007: pas chos nyid don gyi dkyil 'khor la dbang thob
NK058(si)001:12008: pa'i tshad sgo gsum gyi byed spyod ci byas kyang
NK058(si)001:12009: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs chen po nyid
NK058(si)001:12010: ngang ngam shugs kyis rdzogs par gyur nas cir snang
NK058(si)001:12013: chos kun skye med lhun rdzogs shing //
NK058(si)001:12014: ye nas grol bar rtogs pa na //
NK058(si)001:12015: kun spyod bskyed rdzogs lhun gyis grub //
NK058(si)001:12016: ma byas rang bzhin rdzogs par snang //
NK058(si)001:12018: de'ang sngar smos pa bzhin sngags kyi yan lag lnga
NK058(si)001:12019: ma nyams shing yo byad lnga dang ldan pa dang
NK058(si)001:12020: cho ga lnga po rdzogs par shes pa yi rnal
NK058(si)001:12021: 'byor pas dus khyad par can la sogs par dur
NK058(si)001:12022: khrod la sogs pa'i gnas su rten gang zag tshogs
NK058(si)001:12023: kyi yo byad rnams yongs su tshogs pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:12025: bsgrubs na 'bras bu gnas skabs rig 'dzin gsum dang
NK058(si)001:12026: phrin las bzhi mthar thug nges par legs pa'i dgos
NK058(si)001:12028: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor so so'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:12029: rten dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin dang /
NK058(si)001:12030: de ji ltar bsgrub pa'i rim pa'o //
NK058(si)001:12039: rigs lnga dang rigs lnga'i zhing yum lnga dang gnyis
NK058(si)001:12040: su med par sbyor ba las tshom bu lnga yi
NK058(si)001:12041: lha yab yum rtsa ba lnga las yab yum bcu
NK058(si)001:12042: / rigs bzhi po re re'ang bcu bcu ste /
NK058(si)001:12043: lnga bcu bkod la phyi rol tu bsrung ba'i 'khor
NK058(si)001:12044: lo khog pa stong pa phyogs mtshams brgyad steng 'og
NK058(si)001:12045: gnyis te rtsibs bcu la h'u ka ra la sogs
NK058(si)001:12047: rdo rje sgra 'byin ma la sogs pa khro mo
NK058(si)001:12048: bcu bar chad bsrung ba'i 'khor lo'i tshul du rnam
NK058(si)001:12050: de'ang dbus su gtso bo yab yum kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin la /
NK058(si)001:12054: las kyi rdo rje bzhi'i yum /
NK058(si)001:12058: bskyod ma rdo rje ste yab yum bcu'o //
NK058(si)001:12059: shar du mi bskyod pa yab yum la /
NK058(si)001:12063: rdo rje legs pa bzhi'i yum /
NK058(si)001:12068: lhor rin cen 'byung ldan yab yum la /
NK058(si)001:12072: rdo rje bzhad pa bzhi'i yum /
NK058(si)001:12077: nub tu 'od dpag med yab yum la /
NK058(si)001:12081: rdo rje smra ba bzhi'i yum /
NK058(si)001:12086: byang du don yod grub pa yab yum la /
NK058(si)001:12090: rdo rje khu tshur bzhi'i yum /
NK058(si)001:12095: de ltar lnga bcu'i phyi rol tu khro bo bcu
NK058(si)001:12096: yab yum dang bcas pas lha bdun bcu ni tshom
NK058(si)001:12097: bu lnga ba'o // spyir na tshom bu ni sgo
NK058(si)001:12098: dang rta babs la sogs pa gzhal med khang gi
NK058(si)001:12099: rnam par med pa'i lha'i gtso 'khor yin la /
NK058(si)001:12100: dkyil 'khor ni gzhal med khang dang bcas par 'dod kyang /
NK058(si)001:12101: 'dir lha de dag skor tshoms su 'dug pa'i cha nas btags pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:12102: gnyis pa tshom bu gsum pa'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK058(si)001:12103: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang rdo rje'i rigs dang
NK058(si)001:12104: pad+ma'i rigs te re re'ang yab yum bcu bcu'i rang
NK058(si)001:12105: bzhin sku gsung thugs kyi lha sum cu'i dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:12106: gyi mthar khro bo'i tshogs te sgo ba yab yum
NK058(si)001:12107: brgyad dang ldan pa yi tshom bu gsum gyi lha
NK058(si)001:12109: gsum pa tshom bu gcig pa'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK058(si)001:12110: rigs thams cad kyi nang nas de bzhin nyid kun
NK058(si)001:12111: tu bzang po'i rigs te rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK058(si)001:12112: gtso bo rnam par snang mdzad kyi rang bzhin ni
NK058(si)001:12113: / de bzhin gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor rigs lngar phye
NK058(si)001:12114: ba'i thugs kyi thugs te gtso bor rnam snang mthing
NK058(si)001:12115: gas brgyan pa ni thugs kyi mchog /
NK058(si)001:12116: lha bcu'i dkyil 'khor gyi mthar sgo ba yab yum
NK058(si)001:12117: brgyad kyi khro bo'i tshogs dang ldan pa yi tshom
NK058(si)001:12118: bu gcig pa'i lha bco brgyad po rnams bsgom par
NK058(si)001:12119: bya'o // gnyis pa khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK058(si)001:12120: khro bo lnga dang khro mo kro d+h+ai shwa ri lnga'i tshogs chen po ste yab yam bcu dang /
NK058(si)001:12121: de dag gi bya ba bsgrub pa'i pho nya gnas kyi ma mo brgyad dang /
NK058(si)001:12122: phyag brnyan yul gyi phra men brgyad dang /
NK058(si)001:12123: bka' nyan ye shes kyi sgo ma bzhi dang /
NK058(si)001:12124: ci bgyi'i las byed dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa
NK058(si)001:12125: brgyad la sogs pa khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad
NK058(si)001:12126: kyi tshogs rnams kyis 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor du tshogs
NK058(si)001:12127: sgrub na'ang / gnas skabs su gdug pa can tshar
NK058(si)001:12128: gcod pa la sogs pa drag po'i las rnams dang
NK058(si)001:12129: sgrub na'ang / / mthar thug nges par legs pa'i dgongs pa mchog gi dngos grub 'grub bo //
NK058(si)001:12130: gnyis pa de nyid ji ltar bsgrub pa'i rim pa la bzhi ste /
NK058(si)001:12134: rdo rje'i dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor ji ltar bsgrub pa'o //
NK058(si)001:12136: gang zag gang gis bsgrub pa ni sems nyid rnal
NK058(si)001:12137: ma'i don la blo chos nyid du 'byor ba ste
NK058(si)001:12141: 'bras bu lhun grub kyi rnal 'byor gsum las /
NK058(si)001:12144: gzhi dang rang bzhin 'bras bu'i tshul //
NK058(si)001:12145: bskyed dang rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK058(si)001:12148: stong nyid snying rje'i snying po can //
NK058(si)001:12149: byang chub bsgrub pa kha cig la'o //
NK058(si)001:12151: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsang ba zab mo rmad du
NK058(si)001:12152: byung ba'i sngags kyi tshig don 'chang bar byed pa'o
NK058(si)001:12153: // de'ang man+t+ra'i sgra las sngags te /
NK058(si)001:12156: gzungs sngags gsum gyi rang bzhin 'chang ba'o //
NK058(si)001:12158: phyi nang gi lta sgom spyod 'bras gsang ba rmad
NK058(si)001:12159: du byung bas 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las skyob par
NK058(si)001:12161: drang srong la sogs pa ting nge 'dzin la dbang
NK058(si)001:12162: thob pa'i rig pa'i mthus sdug bsngal las skyob pa'o
NK058(si)001:12164: bden tshig bgos pa'i tshig 'bras bu phan gnod byed pa'o //
NK058(si)001:12165: de lta bu'i don gyis bsgrub par bya ba'i dngos
NK058(si)001:12166: grub ni mchog dang thun mong gi yon tan phun
NK058(si)001:12168: de nyid chos thams cad ye nas mnyam pa nyid
NK058(si)001:12169: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang du lhun gyis
NK058(si)001:12170: grub cing dbyer med pa phyogs bral 'dzin zhen med
NK058(si)001:12172: blang dor med par spyod pas chos la'ang thogs chags
NK058(si)001:12173: dang zhen pa med pa'i rang bzhin chos thams cad
NK058(si)001:12174: ye nas ngo bo gcig cing dbyer med par rtogs
NK058(si)001:12176: dkyil 'khor gang bsgrub pa'i thugs rdo rje'i rigs su rigs thams cad kyi dkyil 'khor 'dus pas /
NK058(si)001:12177: lha dang gzhal yas khang pa thams cad ye shes
NK058(si)001:12178: kyi 'od zer 'phro zhing gzi brjid 'bar bar rab
NK058(si)001:12179: tu bsgom zhing / 'dod yon thams cad la zhen
NK058(si)001:12180: chags med pa lha la lha mchod tshul gyis rol
NK058(si)001:12182: de'i 'bras bu sems nyid gnyis su med pa'i chos
NK058(si)001:12183: skur gyur nas lhun gyis grub pa'i phyag rgya chen
NK058(si)001:12185: gnyis pa tshom bu gsum pa ni /
NK058(si)001:12186: snga ma las gzhan yang na sku mi bskyod pa
NK058(si)001:12187: gsung 'od dpag med thugs rnam par snang mdzad kyi
NK058(si)001:12188: dkyil 'khor nyid bsgrub par bya ste /
NK058(si)001:12189: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa
NK058(si)001:12190: bsdu na sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du 'dus
NK058(si)001:12191: pa'i phyir ro // de bsgrub pa'i bskyed rdzogs kyi
NK058(si)001:12192: ting nge 'dzin yang lha'i rnam par gsal zhing mtshan
NK058(si)001:12193: dang dpe byad du 'bar ba'i 'od zer 'phro bas
NK058(si)001:12194: sems can gyi don byed par bsgom pa'o //
NK058(si)001:12195: 'dod yon thams cad yum du bsam pa yab kyis
NK058(si)001:12196: rol pas gnyis su med pa'i chos dbyings spros pa
NK058(si)001:12197: dang bral ba'i rang bzhin gyi ngang du thim par
NK058(si)001:12198: bsam mo // 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin gyi dngos grub mchog thob par 'gyur ro //
NK058(si)001:12199: de las gdul bya'i don du lha'i dkyil 'khor ma
NK058(si)001:12200: lus pa yon tan gyi dpal 'bar ba 'grub cing
NK058(si)001:12201: / sems can nyon mongs pa'i sdug bsngal ma lus pa sel bar mdzad nas /
NK058(si)001:12202: sems can de dag rdo rje'i rigs su skye ba'i gnas la 'god pa'i phrin las byed do //
NK058(si)001:12203: gsum pa tshom bu lnga pa la yang gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:12204: gang zag gang gis tshul ji lta bus bsgrub pa'i tshul ni /
NK058(si)001:12205: sngags 'chang ba'i rnal 'byor pas dngos grub yang dag pa ni rgyud la thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK058(si)001:12206: yab yum thabs dang shes rab tu gsal zhing ting
NK058(si)001:12207: nge 'dzin gsum la sogs pa'i cho ga thams cad
NK058(si)001:12208: kyi tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor lnga dang phyi rol tu
NK058(si)001:12210: 'dod yon la chags pa med pa'i tshul gyis ni
NK058(si)001:12211: lha la lha thim pa'i tshul gyis mchod bya mchod
NK058(si)001:12212: byed gnyis su 'dzin zhen med par bstim par bya'o
NK058(si)001:12213: // 'bras bu dngos grub mchog gi snying po lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin 'grub bo //
NK058(si)001:12214: de'ang kha cig tshom bu gcig pas phyag rgya dang /
NK058(si)001:12216: lnga pas lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin so sor 'grub par 'dod pa ni ma 'brel te /
NK058(si)001:12217: tshom bu re res kyang gnas skabs su rig 'dzin
NK058(si)001:12218: gsum dang mthar thug lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin
NK058(si)001:12220: bzhi pa rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa la'ang gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:12221: gang zag gang gis ji ltar bsgrub pa ni /
NK058(si)001:12222: rnal 'byor pa yab thabs dang yum shes rab kyi rang bzhin gyis /
NK058(si)001:12223: de bzhin gshegs pa lnga dang lnga'i yum du bsgom
NK058(si)001:12224: zhing dbang po dang rtog tshogs sems dpa' dang sems
NK058(si)001:12225: ma sgo ba yab yum dang bcas pa nyid du
NK058(si)001:12226: bsgom par bya'o // lha de dag kyang 'od zer
NK058(si)001:12227: gyi tshogs rnam pa mang po phyogs bcur 'phro ba'o
NK058(si)001:12228: bsgom par bya'o // // 'grel ba spar khab las
NK058(si)001:12229: 'di sgyur 'phrul bsdus pa lha bco brgyad kyi dkyil
NK058(si)001:12230: 'khor yin no zer ba'ang mi 'gal mod kyi /
NK058(si)001:12231: gzhung du rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor du gsal lo //
NK058(si)001:12232: gsum pa gang sgrub thabs kyi yan lag la gsum las /
NK058(si)001:12233: gang sgrub pa ting nge 'dzin gyi yan lag ni /
NK058(si)001:12234: chos thams cad dkyil 'khor du sgrub pa'i tshe phyi
NK058(si)001:12235: nang gi lus dang longs spyod la sogs pa spyad
NK058(si)001:12237: spyod byed bdag nyid dkyil 'khor gyis rol pas /
NK058(si)001:12238: so so'i sngags dang phyag rgya dang ting nge 'dzin
NK058(si)001:12239: gyi rnam pa skabs su gang bab rnams phyin ci
NK058(si)001:12240: ma log pa yang dag par so sor gsal zhing
NK058(si)001:12242: ji ltar bsgrub pa mthun pa'i yan lag ni sgrub
NK058(si)001:12243: pa'i gnas mtshan nyid tshang zhing bar chad med pa
NK058(si)001:12244: dang nye bar mkho ba'i longs spyod mtha' gnyis su
NK058(si)001:12245: ma lhung zhing ci bde bar yod pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12246: des mtshon nas sgrub pa'i grogs su 'gyur ba'i yo
NK058(si)001:12247: byad dang rten dang dam rdzas la sogs pa mthun
NK058(si)001:12248: pa'i rkyen rnams ma nyams par tshang zhing 'gal rkyen
NK058(si)001:12249: med la / sgrub pa'i blo ni /
NK058(si)001:12250: rkyen gzhan gyis mi 'phrog cing mtha' gcig tu tshugs
NK058(si)001:12251: pas zhe bcad rab dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas
NK058(si)001:12252: / sgrub pa la 'jug pa'i dang po ngas ma
NK058(si)001:12253: grub kyi bar du stan 'di las ldang ba dang
NK058(si)001:12254: gnas 'di nas 'gro bar mi bya'o snyam pa la
NK058(si)001:12255: sogs pa'i dam bca' ji ltar nos pa bzhin du
NK058(si)001:12257: sgrub dus su de las gzhan pa'i bya ba la brtson pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12258: rtags dang mtshan ma ngan pa'am /
NK058(si)001:12259: ma byung bas sgyid lug pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12260: ngas mi 'grub snyam du bdag nyid brnyas pas le lo rnams dang /
NK058(si)001:12261: sos dal dang dus su mi sgrub cing lus ngag
NK058(si)001:12262: cha babs su byed pa'i sgyid snyoms la lus pa
NK058(si)001:12263: rnams med pa yi sgo nas brtson 'grus bskyed cing
NK058(si)001:12264: / sngags dang ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa yin
NK058(si)001:12265: nam ma yin nam 'bras bu 'byung ngam mi 'byung
NK058(si)001:12266: ngam snyam pa la sogs pa'i the tshom dang yid
NK058(si)001:12267: gnyis med par yin nges snyam pa mtha' gcig tu
NK058(si)001:12268: gting tshugs pa'i blos sgrub par byas na gang sgrub
NK058(si)001:12269: kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad 'grub par 'gyur te /
NK058(si)001:12270: rdo rje gsang ba'i mchog sku dang ye shes 'du
NK058(si)001:12271: 'bral med pa'i chos sku dam pa 'thob par 'gyur
NK058(si)001:12272: ro // nam gyi tshe sgrub pa dus kyi yan lag ni /
NK058(si)001:12275: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK058(si)001:12276: zhes pa la sogs pa dang sgrub pa la 'jug
NK058(si)001:12277: pa'i tshes grangs dang gza' skar la sogs pa ni
NK058(si)001:12279: dus ni yar ngo'i brgyad la brtsam //
NK058(si)001:12280: shin tu skar ma rgyal rnams la //
NK058(si)001:12281: byang chub spyod pa cher spyod pas //
NK058(si)001:12282: gsang mchog dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK058(si)001:12283: gza' skar shis pa'ang blang bar bya //
NK058(si)001:12284: zhes smos pa bzhin du bshad par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:12285: de'ang spang blang med pas nges bzung mi 'thad do zhe na /
NK058(si)001:12286: ngo bo la de ltar yin yang kun rdzob rgyu
NK058(si)001:12287: 'bras mi bslu ba'i rten 'brel gyis mthun pa'i tshe
NK058(si)001:12288: 'jug gi mi mthun pa'i tshe mi 'jug ste /
NK058(si)001:12289: drod gsher 'dzom dus sa bon gdab kyi de las
NK058(si)001:12290: gzhan gyi dus su mi gdab pa dang 'dra bar
NK058(si)001:12293: rig byed dag gi yan lag las //
NK058(si)001:12294: dus rnams shes par bya ba ni //
NK058(si)001:12295: bkra shis lha yi nyi ma dang //
NK058(si)001:12296: 'byor dang dus tshod bzang ba ni //
NK058(si)001:12297: mtshan ma'i rtog pa yin mod kyang //
NK058(si)001:12298: brtags dang dngos grub mtshan ma 'byung //
NK058(si)001:12300: 'dir phyin ci log gi grong khyer lhun mtho zhing
NK058(si)001:12301: the tshom gyi rtsig pa brgal bar dka' ba'i ra
NK058(si)001:12302: bas bskor nas / mthong ba dang shes pa rgya chung ngur gyur pa dag na re /
NK058(si)001:12303: khyod kyi gsang ba snying po 'di rgyud ma yin te /
NK058(si)001:12304: rgyud la kha 'phangs pas so zhe na /
NK058(si)001:12305: de lta na khyed rang rgyud du 'dod pa'i nges brjod bla ma dang /
NK058(si)001:12306: brtag gnyis la sogs pa'ang rgyud ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK058(si)001:12307: rgyud gzhan la kha 'phangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:12309: ji skad mang du brjod pas ci //
NK058(si)001:12310: ji ltar de nyid bsdus pa yi //
NK058(si)001:12311: dkyil 'khor cho ga bzhin du bya //
NK058(si)001:12312: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12314: rgyud chen sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las //
NK058(si)001:12316: des na ston pas rgyud mtshungs par gsungs pa'i rang bzhin gong 'og gi bzlos pa spang pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12317: rtsa rgyud 'di las 'phros pa'i yan lag gi rgyud
NK058(si)001:12318: dang 'grel ba bsgrub pa'i don du kha 'phangs te
NK058(si)001:12320: gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK058(si)001:12321: chos thams cad kun tu bzang po'i rol par ye
NK058(si)001:12322: nas dag pas thams cad spang blang med par spyod
NK058(si)001:12323: par bya'o // rdo rje gsang ba'i ngo bo rgyud 'di ni /
NK058(si)001:12325: zhes gsungs dus lhun stug po bkod pa'i rang snang
NK058(si)001:12326: thams cad sangs rgyas kyi rol pa las gzhan ma
NK058(si)001:12327: yin pas de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la de bzhin
NK058(si)001:12328: gshegs pa nyid ched du gleng ngo zhes bya ba
NK058(si)001:12329: ste / yul yul can gnyis su med par mtshon pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:12330: tshul 'dis chos thams cad rang snang du bstan te /
NK058(si)001:12331: rang snang la rang gi sems nyid gnyis su med
NK058(si)001:12332: pa rmi lam dang 'dra bar ngo bo nyid kyis
NK058(si)001:12334: chos nyid gsang ba'i snying po gang snang ye shes
NK058(si)001:12335: kyi rol pa de kho na nyid nges pa las
NK058(si)001:12336: / rnal 'byor pa lta spyod mthun pa kun 'dus pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12337: de rnams kyis 'byor ba'i yo byad bde bar spyod pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12338: de'i dus su yi dam gyi lha dang mkha' 'gro dam can 'du bar byed pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12339: zhen 'dzin med pa'i sgo nas rgyud la tshogs gnyis
NK058(si)001:12340: rdzogs par byed pas tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi don
NK058(si)001:12341: te / gang snang gi chos thams cad thabs shes
NK058(si)001:12342: kyi lam du byed pa'i le'u ste bcu gcig pa'i
NK058(si)001:12345: // don gnyis pa de'i yan lag bye brag tu bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:12350: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bshad pa de nas de bzhin
NK058(si)001:12351: gshegs pa chos thams cad gnyis su med par rol
NK058(si)001:12352: pa'i dgyes pa chen po kun tu bzang pos snang
NK058(si)001:12353: srid kyi chos thams cad ye shes kyi rol mo'i
NK058(si)001:12354: sprin 'dod dgu lhun rdzogs su 'byung ba'i rang bzhin
NK058(si)001:12355: nam mkha'i mthas klas pa kun tu rnam par spros
NK058(si)001:12356: te / sangs rgyas kyi zhing dang 'gro ba drug
NK058(si)001:12357: gi spyod yul thams cad du longs spyod chen pos
NK058(si)001:12358: 'byor ba'i rgyan rang rang gi snang ba dang mthun
NK058(si)001:12359: par bkod pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NK058(si)001:12360: nas ston pa nyid kyi rang snang dag pa'i 'khor
NK058(si)001:12361: te / bkod pa na / bskul zhing zhu ba
NK058(si)001:12362: po'i rnam pa med par ched du brjod pa 'di
NK058(si)001:12363: dag rang byung du brjod do //
NK058(si)001:12366: tshogs kyi ting nge 'dzin phan yon dang bcas pa spyir bstan pa /
NK058(si)001:12367: tshogs bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu bye brag tu bshad /
NK058(si)001:12368: tshogs kyi rten dkyil 'khor kun 'dus pa chen pos don bsdu ba'o //
NK058(si)001:12373: chos thams cad ye shes kyi rol pa sgyu 'phrul
NK058(si)001:12374: d+r+wa ba'i ngo bor yul yul can yab yum zung
NK058(si)001:12375: 'brel chen por mngon par rdzogs pa lha dang lha
NK058(si)001:12376: mo'i dkyil 'khor du gnas pa nyid /
NK058(si)001:12377: blo gsal gdab cing goms par byas pa'i don brtan
NK058(si)001:12378: pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi 'phro 'dus mchog dang thun
NK058(si)001:12381: bro gar gyi ting nge 'dzin phan yon dang bcas pa gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:12382: ting nge 'dzin ni lus kyi mgo la sogs pa
NK058(si)001:12383: yan lag lnga rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor du bskyed cing
NK058(si)001:12384: / sa gzhi rdo rje'i rang bzhin la gnas khang
NK058(si)001:12385: lha'i gzhal med khang mdzes pa sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK058(si)001:12386: khams rnam par dag par mos par byas te /
NK058(si)001:12387: rkang pa'i bro dang lag pa'i gar gyi phyag rgya rnam pa sna tshogs pa'i 'du 'phro dang /
NK058(si)001:12388: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba gnyis su med pa lha'i rnam
NK058(si)001:12389: pa dang bden med du shes pa'i ngang nas 'gro
NK058(si)001:12390: 'dug dang lag pa'i 'du byed thams cad lha'i rang
NK058(si)001:12391: bzhin las mi 'da' ba'i phyir na /
NK058(si)001:12392: bro gar la sogs pa'i bya ba ci byed thams
NK058(si)001:12393: cad phyag rgya'i sgrar brjod de mdzub mo brkyangs bskums
NK058(si)001:12394: la sogs pa phyag rgyar 'dod pa ma yin no
NK058(si)001:12396: de ltar byas pa yis sa la 'dzul zhing ri
NK058(si)001:12397: brag rnams la thogs pa med pas 'og gi phyag
NK058(si)001:12398: rgya klu mo rnams dbang du byed pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12399: steng gi lam nam mkha' la bya bzhin thogs pa
NK058(si)001:12400: med par 'gro bas lha dang lha ma yin la
NK058(si)001:12401: sogs pa dbang du byed par 'gyur ro //
NK058(si)001:12402: gnyis pa glu'i phyag rgya la'ang gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:12403: ting nge 'dzin ni rang gi lkog mar h+r+aihbakoda la
NK058(si)001:12404: ngag gi gdangs glu snyan po dang de'i tshig bstod
NK058(si)001:12405: pa dang shis pa brjod pa la sogs pa sgra
NK058(si)001:12406: yi phyag rgya yis dkyil 'khor gyi lha mchod pa'o
NK058(si)001:12408: gsung mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo gcig gis go
NK058(si)001:12409: bar nus pa chos kyi gsung dung gi dngos grub
NK058(si)001:12411: de'ang 'od zer kun tu bkye ba'i mdo las /
NK058(si)001:12412: nga la 'od zer yang yod de //
NK058(si)001:12413: de ming chos kyi dung zhes bya //
NK058(si)001:12414: dbyangs gcig thams cad go ba yis //
NK058(si)001:12415: 'jig rten kun tu khyab par byed //
NK058(si)001:12416: 'od zer de yi dge ba'i rtsa //
NK058(si)001:12417: dpag med de las skyes pa yin //
NK058(si)001:12419: de'ang sangs rgyas kyi gsung ni gdul bya gang yod
NK058(si)001:12420: du nye ring med par mos pa dang mthun par
NK058(si)001:12421: thos pa ste / 'khor gyi khyams dang gad+g+aa'i klung
NK058(si)001:12422: gi bye ma snyed 'das pa'i pha rol la khyad
NK058(si)001:12423: med pa ste nub phyogs 'od zer can gyi 'jig
NK058(si)001:12424: rten du moo gal gyi bus phyin nas sh+aakya thub
NK058(si)001:12425: pa'i chos sngon bzhin thos pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12426: skal pa med na 'khor gyi nang na 'khod kyang
NK058(si)001:12427: mi thos te za ma tog gsungs pa na dze
NK058(si)001:12428: t+aa'i tshal du nyan thos kun gyis ma thos pa
NK058(si)001:12429: byang chub sems dpas thos pa bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:12430: gsum pa rgyan dang gos kyi phyag rgya la'ang gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:12431: ting nge 'dzin ni t+r+aam las dbu rgyan la sogs pa'i rgyan rnams rin po cher gsal zhing /
NK058(si)001:12432: a las gos rnams lha'i gos dang zhi khro'i cha lugs su byin gyis brlabs te /
NK058(si)001:12433: rin po che dang rus pa la sogs pa'i rgyan
NK058(si)001:12434: dang stod g.yogs smad dkris la sogs pa'i bgo ba
NK058(si)001:12435: rnams gyon nas lha la mchod pa'i phyag rgya yis
NK058(si)001:12436: longs spyod do // phan yon ni gnas skabs su
NK058(si)001:12437: 'od dang gzi brjid sred med kyi bus kyang mi
NK058(si)001:12438: shigs pa'i go cha sra ba'i gos su 'gyur zhing
NK058(si)001:12439: mthar thug mtshan dang dpe byad kyis 'bar ba 'khor
NK058(si)001:12440: los sgyur ba dang byang chub sems dpa' yin la
NK058(si)001:12441: longs spyod do // / de'i rgyal po sangs rgyas
NK058(si)001:12442: kyi sku ste bdud dang phyir rgol ba gang gis
NK058(si)001:12443: kyang thub pa med pa'i stobs bcus gnon pa 'grub
NK058(si)001:12444: longs spyod do // / bo // de'ang 'dzam bu'i gling ba'i mi bdun las gyad gcig stobs che'o //
NK058(si)001:12445: de bzhin du gyad 'dun las sh+aakya'i gzhon nu gcig go //
NK058(si)001:12446: de bdun las lha ma yin dang /
NK058(si)001:12452: sa thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa' stobs dang sgyu rtsal bdun 'gyur gyi bar du 'phags shing /
NK058(si)001:12453: de thams cad kyis nam mkha'i dbyings bkang ba'i stobs
NK058(si)001:12454: las sangs rgyas 'phags par dkon cog brtsegs pa las
NK058(si)001:12455: gsungs pa'i tshul gyis stobs bcu'i rtsal mnga' ba yin
NK058(si)001:12456: no // bzhi pa bza' btung gi phyag rgya la'ang gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:12458: kham las bza' btung bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs te /
NK058(si)001:12459: nya dang sha la sogs pa'i bza' ba dang ja
NK058(si)001:12460: dang chang la sogs pa'i btung ba'i phyag rgya yis
NK058(si)001:12461: phyi nang gi lha mchod do //
NK058(si)001:12463: rang gi lus 'dod dgur bsgyur ba yid bzhin gyi
NK058(si)001:12464: nor bu lta bu'i sku dang gsung ro bro ba'i
NK058(si)001:12465: mchog gang la longs spyad pa de dag ro brgya
NK058(si)001:12466: dang ldan pa'i bdud rtsir 'grub bo //
NK058(si)001:12467: lnga pa sbyor sgrol gyi phyag rgya'i ting nge 'dzin
NK058(si)001:12468: ni yab yum lhar gsal ba'i mkha' gsang du dkyil
NK058(si)001:12470: +aahli bde ba chen pos mchod pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12471: zhing dang zhing phran gyi sha khrag bdud rtsir gyur
NK058(si)001:12472: pas mchod pa k+aa li sgrol ba'i phyag rgya yis
NK058(si)001:12473: mnyes par bya'o // phan yon ni /
NK058(si)001:12474: sbyor bas zag pa med pa'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK058(si)001:12475: sogs pa mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub thams
NK058(si)001:12476: cad dang sgrol bas gdug pa can tshar bcad de
NK058(si)001:12477: / rang gzhan gyi gnod pa zhi ba dang pha
NK058(si)001:12478: rol thar pa la sogs pa'i phrin las rlabs po
NK058(si)001:12480: gnyis pa tshogs sgrub pa'i 'bras bu bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:12488: bid+y+aa ni rig pa ste shes rab dang ye shes dang sangs rgyas kyi gdung ngo //
NK058(si)001:12489: d+h+aa ra ni 'dzin cing 'chang ba ste don la slob pa'am ldan pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:12491: dbye ba spyir bstan pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12492: rang bzhin bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:12495: rnam smin tshe dbang phyag rgya lhun gyis grub //
NK058(si)001:12500: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin no //
NK058(si)001:12503: yi dam lha'i rnal 'byor du smin pa /
NK058(si)001:12504: lus rnam smin gyi gzugs las gnas ma gyur pa /
NK058(si)001:12505: lus rgya dang bral nas phyag rgya chen po'i sku 'thob pa ste /
NK058(si)001:12507: yid kyi lha yi gzugs bzung zhing //
NK058(si)001:12508: lus kyi rgya mdud grol gyur nas //
NK058(si)001:12509: phyag rgya'i sku nyid gsal gyur pa //
NK058(si)001:12510: rnam par smin zhes de la brjod //
NK058(si)001:12513: rnam smin gyi lus rdo rje'i lus su gnas 'gyur
NK058(si)001:12514: zhing de nyid ma spangs bar sangs rgyas kyi sa
NK058(si)001:12515: la sbyor bas phung po'i zag pa med cing ye
NK058(si)001:12516: shes kyi blo skyes pa ste /
NK058(si)001:12517: lus dang phung po'i bcas pa yis //
NK058(si)001:12518: gnas par dbang ba'i rigs grub cing //
NK058(si)001:12520: zag kun zad pa'i rigs chen de //
NK058(si)001:12521: ji ltar spyod kyang bzlog pa med //
NK058(si)001:12522: rang dbang thob pas dbugs dbyung phyir //
NK058(si)001:12523: skabs 'dir bden pa bar ma mthong //
NK058(si)001:12526: rang gi lus gang bsgoms pa'i cha byad du gnas gyur pa ste /
NK058(si)001:12528: rang lus rgyal ba'i phyag rgya che //
NK058(si)001:12529: bsgoms pas mngon du gyur pa'i lha //
NK058(si)001:12530: mtshan dang dpe byad mngon shes ldan //
NK058(si)001:12531: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin grags //
NK058(si)001:12533: 'o na sangs rgyas dngos su 'gyur mod snyam na /
NK058(si)001:12534: da dung sgrib pa mtha' dag ma bral bas bsgrub dgos te /
NK058(si)001:12536: sangs rgyas nyid ni thob pa dang //
NK058(si)001:12537: zhes sa dang por sangs rgyas thob par bshad kyang /
NK058(si)001:12538: sa lhag ma'i dri ma sbyong dgos par gsungs pa bzhin du 'dir yang shes par bya ste /
NK058(si)001:12540: byang chub phyag rgya'i cha lugs sku //
NK058(si)001:12541: mtshan dang dpe byad la sogs pas //
NK058(si)001:12542: cha lugs mngon du byung na yang //
NK058(si)001:12543: zhi ba de nyid mthong ba min //
NK058(si)001:12546: spangs pa dang rtogs pa mthar phyin pa'i sangs rgyas te /
NK058(si)001:12548: snga ma'i rigs las mthu rdzogs pas //
NK058(si)001:12549: bshad pa bzhin du dri ma sbyongs //
NK058(si)001:12550: sangs rgyas sa yi shes rab gsum //
NK058(si)001:12551: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin no //
NK058(si)001:12553: gnyis pa rang bzhin bye brag tu bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK058(si)001:12555: zag pa med pa'i bsdus tshul /
NK058(si)001:12556: pha rol phyin pa'i rdzogs tshul /
NK058(si)001:12557: mthar thug pa'i thob tshul lo //
NK058(si)001:12559: rig 'dzin de dag gis 'gro ba'i don du mi'i gtso bo 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po dang /
NK058(si)001:12560: lha'i gtso bo tshangs pa dang brgya byin la sogs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12561: tshangs pa chen po'i skye bar sprul nas gang la gang 'dul gyis don byed do //
NK058(si)001:12562: kha cig rnam smin gyis mi /
NK058(si)001:12564: phyag rgya chen pos tshangs pa /
NK058(si)001:12565: lhun grub gyis kun gyi rol par bzhed de 'gal ba med do //
NK058(si)001:12567: rnam smin tshogs sbyor mthar thug gi sa dang /
NK058(si)001:12568: tshe dbang mthong lam yan chad slob pa'i sa dang /
NK058(si)001:12569: phyag rgya chen po 'phags pa'i ye shes mthong sgom gyi rtogs pa khyad par can gyi sa dang /
NK058(si)001:12570: lhun grub sangs rgyas kyi sas bsdus kyang de thams
NK058(si)001:12571: cad phyogs gcig tu khyad par gyi sa bcu gsum
NK058(si)001:12572: pas bsdus te / der nges par mngon du byed pa ste /
NK058(si)001:12573: dper na lcags kyus zin pa'i nya chu nang na yod kyang skam sar bton pa dang 'dra'o //
NK058(si)001:12574: de'ang 'phags pa'i ye shes kyi cha nas phyag rgya chen po dang /
NK058(si)001:12575: skye shi med pa'i cha nas tshe dbang du btags pa'o //
NK058(si)001:12578: sar smin pa ste gsum du'ang bshad do //
NK058(si)001:12579: kha cig tshe dbang sa dang po /
NK058(si)001:12581: lhun grub bcu bar 'dod pa ni sgyu 'phrul gyi dgongs pa ma dgongs te /
NK058(si)001:12582: de tshe bcu drug tshun chad kyi //
NK058(si)001:12583: sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa ni //
NK058(si)001:12585: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas su /
NK058(si)001:12586: zhes lhun grub sangs rgyas su bshad pa dang yang 'gal zhing /
NK058(si)001:12587: tshe dbang dang phyag rgya'i mtshan nyid ma phyed par snang ngo //
NK058(si)001:12589: rim gyis pas pha rol tu phyin pa bcu rim gyis sbyong zhing sa bcu 'phar bar ston la /
NK058(si)001:12590: cig car bas myur du rdzogs pa ste /
NK058(si)001:12591: de'ang chos thams cad la yongs su 'dzin pa med pas /
NK058(si)001:12592: sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa 'bras bu dang
NK058(si)001:12593: bcas pa btsal ba med par lhun gyis rdzogs par
NK058(si)001:12594: bstan to // de bzhin du mnyam pa nyid du
NK058(si)001:12595: rig pas gos pa med pa dang blang dor med
NK058(si)001:12597: 'khrugs pa med pa dang ye shes kyi mtshan nyid yongs su rdzogs pa ni bzod pa'o //
NK058(si)001:12598: nyams pa med pa dang byed spyod tshogs su gyur pa ni brtson 'grus so //
NK058(si)001:12599: dbang po yul la 'jug kyang mnyam pa nyid las
NK058(si)001:12600: mi g.yo zhing chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin la
NK058(si)001:12601: gnas pa ni bsam gtan no //
NK058(si)001:12602: rang bzhin phyi ci ma log par rtogs pas dngos
NK058(si)001:12603: po dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa las 'das pa ni
NK058(si)001:12604: shes rab bo // bdag kyang gzhan gyi don du 'gyur pa ni thabs so //
NK058(si)001:12605: zhing dang spyod yul yongs su dag par 'gyur ba ni smon lam mo //
NK058(si)001:12606: mi mthun pa'i phyogs kyis yongs su mi bardzi ba ni stobs so //
NK058(si)001:12607: don ji lta ba bzhin rtogs pa ni ye shes te /
NK058(si)001:12608: pha rol tu phyin pa bcu lhun gyis rdzogs pas
NK058(si)001:12609: sa bcu'ang dus yun ring mo zhig tu sbyangs mi
NK058(si)001:12610: dgos par myur du rdzogs par 'gyur ro //
NK058(si)001:12611: sa rnams kyi nges tshig dang yon tan yang /
NK058(si)001:12613: byang chub la yang nye ba dang //
NK058(si)001:12614: sems can don grub mthong ba la //
NK058(si)001:12615: rab tu dga' ba skye 'gyur te //
NK058(si)001:12616: de phyir rab dga' zhes brjod do //
NK058(si)001:12617: 'chal tshul rtsol ba'i dri bral phyir //
NK058(si)001:12618: dri ma med pa'i sa zhes bya //
NK058(si)001:12619: chos kyi snang ba chen po ni //
NK058(si)001:12620: byed pa'i phyir na 'od byed dang //
NK058(si)001:12621: 'di ltar byang chub mi mthun phyogs //
NK058(si)001:12623: sems can rnams yongs smin byed cing //
NK058(si)001:12624: rang gi sems kyang bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK058(si)001:12625: blo ldan rnams kyis sbyang dka' ba //
NK058(si)001:12626: de phyir sbyang dka' zhes brjod do //
NK058(si)001:12627: shes rab pha rol phyin brten nas //
NK058(si)001:12629: gnyis 'dir mngon du gyur pas na //
NK058(si)001:12630: mngon du gyur pa'i sa zhes bya //
NK058(si)001:12631: bgrod gcig lam dang 'brel ba'i phyir //
NK058(si)001:12632: ring du gyur pa'i sa zhes bya //
NK058(si)001:12633: 'du shes gnyis kyis mi g.yo'i phyir //
NK058(si)001:12634: mi g.yo ba yi sar 'dod do //
NK058(si)001:12635: so so yang dag rig blo bzang //
NK058(si)001:12636: sa de legs pa'i blo gros yin //
NK058(si)001:12637: sprin bzhin gnyis kyis nam mkha'i chos //
NK058(si)001:12638: khyab pa'i phyir na chos kyi sprin //
NK058(si)001:12640: yon tan ni sa dang por skad cig snga phyi
NK058(si)001:12641: med bzhin du sangs rgyas brgya'i zhal blta ba la
NK058(si)001:12642: sogs pa brgya phrag bcu gnyis mngon du byed de
NK058(si)001:12644: ting 'dzin brgya dang sangs rgyas brgya rnams mthong byed cing //
NK058(si)001:12645: zhing brgya bskyod cing rab tu snang byed kun tu 'gro //
NK058(si)001:12646: sems can brgya sbyong chos kyi sgo la 'god par byed //
NK058(si)001:12647: bskal pa brgyar 'jug lus brgya rab tu ston par byed //
NK058(si)001:12648: rgyal ba'i sras kyang brgya yi grangs tshad rab tu ston //
NK058(si)001:12649: de yi gong na smon mchog stobs ldan tshad kyang med //
NK058(si)001:12651: de bzhin du sa gnyis par stong phrag bcu gnyis /
NK058(si)001:12653: bzhi par bye ba brgya phrag bcu gnyis /
NK058(si)001:12654: lnga par bye ba stong phrag bcu gnyis /
NK058(si)001:12655: drug par bye ba khrag khrig phrag bcu gnyis /
NK058(si)001:12656: bdun par bye ba khrag khrig 'bum phrag bcu gnyis /
NK058(si)001:12657: brgyad par stong chen 'bum phrag gcig gi rdul gyi grangs dang mnyam pa /
NK058(si)001:12658: dgu par 'bum phrag bcu'i rdul dang mnyam pa /
NK058(si)001:12659: bcu par brjod du med pa'i grangs dang mnyam pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhal blta ba dang /
NK058(si)001:12661: zhing g.yo bar byed pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12662: 'od kyis gsal bar byed pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12663: zhing de dag tu 'gro ba dang /
NK058(si)001:12664: sems can smin par byed pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12666: ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par 'jog pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12667: dus skad cig ma gcig bskal pa du mar ston zhing /
NK058(si)001:12668: bskal pa du ma skad cig ma gcig tu ston pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12669: sngon dang phyi ma'i mthar de snyed la gzigs pa 'jug pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12670: rang gi lus sangs rgyas kyi sku du mar sprul pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12671: de re re'ang 'khor du mas bskor bar ston pa rnams skad cig snga phyi med par 'byung ba'o //
NK058(si)001:12672: bzhi pa mthar thug sa'i thob tshul ni /
NK058(si)001:12673: de ltar sa bcu rdzogs nas 'od zer mang po
NK058(si)001:12674: bkye nas sems can gyi don mdzad pa bcu gcig
NK058(si)001:12676: ye shes kyi snang ba dang thugs rje chen pos
NK058(si)001:12677: chags pa med pas bcu gnyis ma chags pad+ma can
NK058(si)001:12678: gyi sa dang / chos thams cad kyi dbang mthar
NK058(si)001:12679: thug pa lhun gyis rdzogs pa sa bcu gsum rdo
NK058(si)001:12680: gyi sa dang / rje 'dzin pa'am / yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen nam /
NK058(si)001:12682: rig pa 'dzin pa'i sa zhes bya ba lhun grub tu rdzogs pa'o //
NK058(si)001:12683: de'ang sa bcu gsum pa nyid chos sku spros dang bral ba'i cha nas khyad par chen po'o //
NK058(si)001:12684: de'i ngang las longs sku'i 'char gzhi byed pas yi ge tshogs chen /
NK058(si)001:12685: de nyid kun gyi bla ma yin pas rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK058(si)001:12686: ye shes mthar thug gi ngo bo yin pas rig
NK058(si)001:12687: pa 'dzin pa zhes yon tan gyi cha nas de
NK058(si)001:12689: sa 'di dag la skas kyi gdang bu ltar mtho dman yod pa ma yin te /
NK058(si)001:12690: sangs rgyas gcig gi ngo bo la sku gsum gyi cha nas de skad brjod do //
NK058(si)001:12691: yon tan gyis phye bas de dang de las mang bar yang gsungs te /
NK058(si)001:12692: bde ba tshad med pas bcu bzhi pa bde ba chen po /
NK058(si)001:12694: bcu drug pa ye shes bla ma zhes grags shing /
NK058(si)001:12695: don gyi ngo bo la grub bsal med pas sa gcig tu'ang bshad de /
NK058(si)001:12696: kun tu bzang po dbye ba med pa rdzogs pa chen por gcig pa ste /
NK058(si)001:12698: gcig ni kun byed byang chub sems kyi sa //
NK058(si)001:12701: gnyis pa gzhung gi don la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:12703: des grub pa gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu /
NK058(si)001:12704: de mthar phyin pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu'o //
NK058(si)001:12706: rgyu dngos ni chos thams cad rtogs pa bzhi'i tshul
NK058(si)001:12707: gyis ye nas sangs rgyas par shes pa'i mtshan nyid
NK058(si)001:12708: kyi lta ba phun sum tshogs pa'i gnas lugs rgyud
NK058(si)001:12709: la 'byor ba'i gzungs ni 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhir
NK058(si)001:12710: smin par byed pa'i rgyu yin zhing /
NK058(si)001:12711: shes nas sgrub pa la 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid bskyed rdzogs zung 'brel du 'byor pa'i gzungs ni /
NK058(si)001:12712: 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhir smin par byed pa'i rkyen yin te /
NK058(si)001:12713: mtshan nyid shes nas bsgrubs pas chos kyi 'bras bu thob pa'o //
NK058(si)001:12714: de lta bu'i rgyu rkyen la goms shing 'dres par
NK058(si)001:12715: byas pas nus mthu khyad par can du gang gyur
NK058(si)001:12716: pa de ni / rgyu sa bon grung po /
NK058(si)001:12717: rkyen chu lud kyis bran pas /
NK058(si)001:12718: 'bras bu myu gu nas ston thog gi bar du 'byung ba bzhin du /
NK058(si)001:12719: rnam par smin pa nas lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin gyi bar du 'byung ngo //
NK058(si)001:12720: gnyis pa des grub pa'i tshul ni de lta bu'i
NK058(si)001:12721: rig 'dzin rnams ni rgyal ba skyed par byed pa'i
NK058(si)001:12723: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing du grags shing lung bstan pa thob ste /
NK058(si)001:12724: 'di ltar 'jig rten gyi khams che ge mo zhig na /
NK058(si)001:12725: rig 'dzin ga ge mo zhig gnas te /
NK058(si)001:12726: dus 'di zhes bya ba la sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrub bo zhes pa'o //
NK058(si)001:12727: gnyis pa des grub pa gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu la gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:12728: 'gro ba gang gis bsgrub pa ni /
NK058(si)001:12729: rig 'dzin de dag las kha cig gling bzhi'i mi
NK058(si)001:12730: dang 'dod pa'i lha dang gzugs kyi tshangs pa la
NK058(si)001:12732: de dag gi rnam par skye ba rnam par dag
NK058(si)001:12733: pa skyon med cing yon tan phun sum tshogs pa
NK058(si)001:12734: nyid 'dzin med kyi gnas rigs de dag gi 'gro
NK058(si)001:12735: ba rnams dang yon tan gyi chos mtshungs pa'am skal
NK058(si)001:12736: pa mnyam pa ma yin no //
NK058(si)001:12737: dper na sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams
NK058(si)001:12738: 'gro ba'i gnas rigs so so'i lus su snang yang
NK058(si)001:12739: skal pa dang yon tan mi mtshungs pa bzhin no
NK058(si)001:12740: // de'ang skye ba 'dzin tshul bzhi ste /
NK058(si)001:12742: blo ldan rnams kyi las dang ni //
NK058(si)001:12743: gzhan don smin lam dbang dag dang //
NK058(si)001:12745: dbang gi skye bar 'dod pa yin //
NK058(si)001:12747: de las so so skye bo'i sar las bzang ngan gyis mtho ris dang ngan song du skye'o //
NK058(si)001:12748: sa dang po nas bdun pa'i bar du smon lam
NK058(si)001:12749: dang thabs la mkhas pa'i sprul pas skye bar 'dod
NK058(si)001:12750: do // dag pa sa gsum du ting nge 'dzin
NK058(si)001:12751: dang dbang 'byor bas gang la gang 'dul du skye
NK058(si)001:12752: do // bar snang ngo // sangs rgyas kyi sar
NK058(si)001:12753: lhun gyis grub pa'i sprul pas dbang 'byor pa chen
NK058(si)001:12754: po'i rol pa mdzad pa bcu gnyis la sogs par
NK058(si)001:12755: do // bar snang ngo // snang ngo // 'phags
NK058(si)001:12756: pa rnams la skye ba mtshan nyid pa med de
NK058(si)001:12757: do // bar snang ngo // snang ngo // /
NK058(si)001:12758: skye rga na 'chi'i chu bo las brgal ba'i phyir
NK058(si)001:12759: do // bar snang ngo // snang ngo // / / 'on kyang thugs rjes sprul pa ste /
NK058(si)001:12762: rga ba'i sdug bsngal rtsad nas spangs //
NK058(si)001:12763: las dang nyon mongs dbang gis skye //
NK058(si)001:12764: de la de med phyir de med //
NK058(si)001:12765: ji bzhin yang dag mthong ba'i phyir //
NK058(si)001:12766: skye sogs rnams las 'das gyur kyang //
NK058(si)001:12767: snying rje'i bdag nyid skye ba dang //
NK058(si)001:12768: 'chi dang rga dang na bar ston //
NK058(si)001:12771: rga dang na dang 'chi ba med kyang 'chi 'pho ston //
NK058(si)001:12773: de la rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin ni las
NK058(si)001:12774: kyi skye ba zad de lus bor ma thag tu
NK058(si)001:12775: 'phags pa'i sa thob pas sbyor lam mthar thug dang
NK058(si)001:12777: de'ang sbyor lam drod nas kyang ngan 'gro med par mngon rtogs rgyan gyi drod kyi skabs su /
NK058(si)001:12778: the tshom mi dal zad pa dang //
NK058(si)001:12780: des na smon lam gyis dag pa'i zhing la sogs par 'gro ba'i don du skye'o //
NK058(si)001:12781: tshe dbang dang phyag rgya ni ting nge 'dzin gyi skye bas don byed kyi /
NK058(si)001:12782: skye ba rang mtshan pa med de /
NK058(si)001:12783: lus de nyid rdo rje'i skur gnas gyur pas 'jig 'bral med pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:12784: lhun grub ni dbang 'byor ba'i skye ba gang la
NK058(si)001:12785: gang 'dul der snang bas sprul pa 'gyed pa yin
NK058(si)001:12786: no // gnyis pa sa gang gis bsdus pa ni /
NK058(si)001:12787: rig 'dzin dang po gsum rgyu'i sas bsdus shing /
NK058(si)001:12788: phyi ma 'bras bu'i sas bsdus la /
NK058(si)001:12789: de thams cad phyir mi ldog pas khyad par gyi sas bsdus pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK058(si)001:12790: khyad par sa la gnas 'gyur yin //
NK058(si)001:12791: pha rol phyin pa kun tu rdzogs //
NK058(si)001:12793: rgyu'i sas bsdus tshul du bshad na /
NK058(si)001:12794: rig 'dzin dang po gsum po de mi dang lha dang tshangs pa yi skye ba 'dzin mod kyi /
NK058(si)001:12795: khyad par du sa bcu la gnas par 'gyur ba yin te /
NK058(si)001:12796: sa bcu'i ngo bo pha rol tu phyin pa bcu
NK058(si)001:12797: po kun tu rdzogs par rgyud la thob pa'i phyir
NK058(si)001:12798: zhes pa'o // 'bras bu'i sas bsdus tshul du bshad na /
NK058(si)001:12799: lhub grub de khyad par gyi sa bcu gsum rdo
NK058(si)001:12800: rje 'dzin pa la gnas par 'gyur ba yin te
NK058(si)001:12801: / 'bras bu mthar thug gi sgrub byed rgyu'i pha
NK058(si)001:12802: rol tu phyin pa bcu po kun tu rdzogs pa'i
NK058(si)001:12803: / phyir zhes so // phyir mi ldog par khyad
NK058(si)001:12804: par gyi sas bsdus tshul du bshad na rig 'dzin
NK058(si)001:12805: bzhi po thams cad 'bras bu'i rig 'dzin la gnas
NK058(si)001:12806: par nges pas khyad par gyi sa la gnas par
NK058(si)001:12808: sa de nyid grub pa'i ngo bo rgyu dang 'bras
NK058(si)001:12809: bu'i pha rol tu phyin pa kun tu rdzogs par
NK058(si)001:12810: bsgrub pa'i rim pa dper na lcags kyus zin pa'i
NK058(si)001:12811: nya skam sar bton pa bzhin zhes pa'o //
NK058(si)001:12812: gsum pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu ni bcu gcig
NK058(si)001:12813: kun tu 'od kyi sa ni thabs mthar phyin pa
NK058(si)001:12814: rnam par 'phrul pa'i sprul pa dang phrin las kyi
NK058(si)001:12817: 'od zer bkye bas gdul bya snod du rung bar byed pa'i phyir kun tu 'od kyi sa'o //
NK058(si)001:12819: shes rab dang thabs kyi mchog zung du 'brel ba
NK058(si)001:12820: mthar thug pa bcu gnyis ma chags pad+ma can lhun
NK058(si)001:12821: stug po bkod pa'i zhing khams rtsol med du rang
NK058(si)001:12822: snang ba'i ste / kun gsal las /
NK058(si)001:12823: pad+ma can la longs spyod rdzogs //
NK058(si)001:12824: lhun grub ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK058(si)001:12826: shes rab mchog gi longs sprul gnyis chos sku'i gzhi
NK058(si)001:12827: la mya ngan las 'da' ba de'i dbyings su thim
NK058(si)001:12828: pa'i gzhir gyur pas mchog tu gyur pa lhun grub
NK058(si)001:12829: rin po che'i sbubs chos kyi sku spros pa thams
NK058(si)001:12830: cad dang bral ba'i zhing khams gdod ma'i kun tu
NK058(si)001:12831: bzang po ste / gcig dang du ma bral ba yi //
NK058(si)001:12832: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK058(si)001:12833: sangs rgyas nyid kyang mi gzigs te //
NK058(si)001:12834: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK058(si)001:12836: de ltar gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi sa yi
NK058(si)001:12837: khyad par rab tu dga' ba la sogs pa bcu
NK058(si)001:12838: dang kun tu 'od la sogs pa gsum ni rgyu
NK058(si)001:12839: dang 'bras bu'i khyad par gyis phye ba ste /
NK058(si)001:12840: btsal ba med par rang bzhin lhun gyis rdzogs pa ni mthar thug gi thob bya'o //
NK058(si)001:12841: gsum pa tshogs kyi rten dkyil 'khor kun 'dus pa chen pos don bsdu ba la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:12842: kun tu bzang po'i bskyed rdzogs bstan pa /
NK058(si)001:12844: phra mo'i nyes pas mi gos pa'o //
NK058(si)001:12847: ting nge 'dzin gsum sngon du song bas nam mkha'i
NK058(si)001:12848: dkyil 'khor rab tu dwangs pa'i dbyings ye shes kyi
NK058(si)001:12849: gzhal yas khang 'od dang bcas pa'i nang na nyi
NK058(si)001:12851: ye shes rgyal po kun tu bzang po stangs dpyal
NK058(si)001:12852: gnyis zung du sbyor bas rdo rje'i skyil krung mnyam
NK058(si)001:12853: bzhag dang bcas pa'i sku las 'od zer du ma
NK058(si)001:12855: de'ang thun mong gi theg pas sangs rgyas rnams la
NK058(si)001:12856: rgyud tha dad zhing tha dad dus tha dad tshul
NK058(si)001:12857: tha dad par 'dod pa las khyad par du bstan
NK058(si)001:12858: te / de'ang de ltar snang ba'i sprul pa'i sku rnams kyang gdul bya'i snang ngor yin gyi /
NK058(si)001:12859: thun mong ma yin pa'i theg pas gzhal na chos sku skye ba med pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12860: longs sku 'gag pa med pa 'og min na bzhugs
NK058(si)001:12861: pa dag gis bsdus pas de'i phyir rang bzhin gyi
NK058(si)001:12862: sku gang mos shig bsgoms pas thams cad 'grub cing
NK058(si)001:12863: / khyad par du sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rang
NK058(si)001:12864: bzhin nam byed po kun tu bzang po yab yum
NK058(si)001:12865: zung cig bsgom pas rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad
NK058(si)001:12866: kyang ma lus par ni bsgom par 'gyur te /
NK058(si)001:12867: lha'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kyang sku gsung thugs dang
NK058(si)001:12868: dbyings rang bzhin gyis dag pa gcig tu 'du ba'i
NK058(si)001:12869: phyir ro // de'i 'thad pa dgod pa ni /
NK058(si)001:12870: de ltar bsgoms pa'i lha de rang gi sems yin pas ji ltar 'grub snyam pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12871: yang lha'i rang bzhin gzhan zhig nas 'ongs pas dngos
NK058(si)001:12872: grub ster ba yin nam snyam pa'i the tshom spang
NK058(si)001:12873: ba'i phyir / 'das pa la sogs pa'i dus bzhi
NK058(si)001:12874: dang shar la sogs pa'i phyogs bcu po gang nas
NK058(si)001:12875: kyang rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sems las logs su gyur
NK058(si)001:12876: pa'i rang mtshan pa zhig sgrub rgyu'am /
NK058(si)001:12878: sems kyi rang bzhin ji ltar gnas pa de nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas yin gyi /
NK058(si)001:12879: phyogs gzhan nas sangs rgyas 'di lta bu zhig ce'am /
NK058(si)001:12880: sems 'di nyid da lta sangs rgyas kyi sa bon
NK058(si)001:12881: nam rgyu yin pa sbyangs pas nam zhig na sangs
NK058(si)001:12882: rgyas su 'gyur gyi da lta sangs rgyas ma yin
NK058(si)001:12883: no snyam pa ste yul dus gzhan du phye ba
NK058(si)001:12884: rnams kyis sangs rgyas rnyed par mi 'gyur bas /
NK058(si)001:12885: de'i phyir sangs rgyas sems las gzhan du ma 'tshol zhig ces gdams so //
NK058(si)001:12886: de skad du brgyad stong pa las /
NK058(si)001:12887: byang chub sems dpa' rtag tu ngu'i mdun du sangs
NK058(si)001:12888: rgyas kyi sku zhig bzhugs pa des lung bstan nas
NK058(si)001:12889: mi snang bar gyur pa de'i tshe /
NK058(si)001:12890: rtag tu ngu 'di snyam du sems te /
NK058(si)001:12891: de bzhin gshegs pa de ni gang nas byon /
NK058(si)001:12895: rigs kyi bu de bzhin gshegs pa de ni gang
NK058(si)001:12896: nas byon pa'ang med cing gang du'ang bzhud pa med
NK058(si)001:12897: do // de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK058(si)001:12899: dper na la la zhig gi rmi lam du de
NK058(si)001:12900: bzhin gshegs pa byon nas mi snang bar gyur na
NK058(si)001:12901: / de gang nas byon pa'am bzhud pa yod dam /
NK058(si)001:12903: de ni ma mchis te gnyid kyis log pa las gzhan med do //
NK058(si)001:12905: de bzhin du sems las gud na med de chos
NK058(si)001:12906: thams cad rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa'i phyir
NK058(si)001:12908: sems rtogs na sangs rgyas yin pas /
NK058(si)001:12909: sangs rgyas gzhan du mi 'tshol ba'i 'du shes rab tu bskyed par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:12911: gnyis pa tshul des dkyil 'khor kun 'grub pa ni /
NK058(si)001:12912: dkyil 'khor kun tu bzang po gcig gi bskyed rdzogs
NK058(si)001:12913: la rab tu sbyor zhing bsgom par byas pas de
NK058(si)001:12914: las 'phros pa'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad
NK058(si)001:12916: nyi zla grub pa na de'i 'od zer ma lus pa thams cad 'grub pa bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:12917: gsum pa nyes pa phra mos mi gos pa ni
NK058(si)001:12918: thams cad sems kyi rang bzhin du shes pas spang
NK058(si)001:12919: blang gnyis su med pa de lta bu don rtogs
NK058(si)001:12920: nas rdzogs rim la dbang 'byor bas bskyed rim gyi
NK058(si)001:12921: cho ga phra mo rnams la lhag gam ma tshang
NK058(si)001:12922: na'ang / cho ga'i yan lag nyams pa'i skyon nyid
NK058(si)001:12923: dag ste de'i nyes pa med pa dngos grub la
NK058(si)001:12926: chos nyid dag pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK058(si)001:12927: bskyed pa'i cho ga las rab dag /
NK058(si)001:12928: lhag dang ma tshang nyes bral cing //
NK058(si)001:12929: dngos grub ya mtshan chen por 'grub //
NK058(si)001:12931: de'ang mtshan bcas bskyed pa dang mtshan med rdzogs pa'i rim par spyi la grags kyang /
NK058(si)001:12932: rnal 'byor pa'i blo dngos po dang mtshan mar 'dzin
NK058(si)001:12933: pa de'i tshe gang bsgoms kyang mtshan bcas las mi
NK058(si)001:12934: 'da' zhing / blo mtshan 'dzin med pa'i tshe ci bsgoms kyang mtshan med yin te /
NK058(si)001:12936: des na rnal 'byor skyes bu yis //
NK058(si)001:12937: mtshan med ngang la gnas bcas nas //
NK058(si)001:12938: mtshan ma'i rnal 'byor bsgom par bya //
NK058(si)001:12939: mtshan ma med dang mtshan ma yang //
NK058(si)001:12940: tha dad min par shes par bya //
NK058(si)001:12941: de ltar rig pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK058(si)001:12942: de nyid nga yi sa thob yin //
NK058(si)001:12943: sangs rgyas zhes kyang de la bya //
NK058(si)001:12946: ji srid mtshan mar 'dzin yod pa //
NK058(si)001:12947: de srid mtshan bcas 'jig rten pa //
NK058(si)001:12948: nam zhig dngos po mtshan ma med //
NK058(si)001:12950: spyod yul kun tu bzang po'i zhing //
NK058(si)001:12951: nyon mongs ye shes gnyis su med //
NK058(si)001:12953: gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni de skad
NK058(si)001:12954: ces rang snang dag pa'i 'khor la ched du brjod
NK058(si)001:12955: pas / ting nge 'dzin gyi rol mo'i sprin bkod
NK058(si)001:12956: pa'i mchod pa phyogs bcur mi sgrib par gsal ba'i
NK058(si)001:12957: rgyan phun sum tshogs pa rang snang ba nyid kyis
NK058(si)001:12958: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mnyes par gyur to
NK058(si)001:12959: pas / // thabs kyi rol pa mchog tu gsang
NK058(si)001:12960: ba'i snying po snang bcas tshogs kyi de kho na
NK058(si)001:12962: lam bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs bsgrub pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:12964: // don gnyis pa snying po'i don la 'jug pa rdzogs pa'i rim pa la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:12969: lam bskyed pa'i rim pa bstan pa de nas rdzogs
NK058(si)001:12970: pa'i rim pa bstan pa'i phyir phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i
NK058(si)001:12971: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung
NK058(si)001:12972: dang thugs rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor thams cad gcig tu
NK058(si)001:12973: 'dus nas gnas pa'i ston pa kun tu bzang po
NK058(si)001:12974: ye shes bla na med pa'i dgyes pa chen pos
NK058(si)001:12975: rol te / snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i
NK058(si)001:12976: chos thams cad ye nas rdzogs pa chen por lhun
NK058(si)001:12977: gyis grub pa'i dam tshig ni snod du ma gyur
NK058(si)001:12978: pa rnams pa shin tu gsang ba'i rang bzhin de
NK058(si)001:12979: kho na nyid kyi snying po'i sprin skal ba mchog
NK058(si)001:12980: dang ldan pa rnams la bkod pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK058(si)001:12981: la snyoms par zhugs nas man ngag dam pa'i ched
NK058(si)001:12982: du brjod pa 'di dag brjod par mdzad do zhes
NK058(si)001:12983: rol te / so // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:12984: don gsang ba rdo rje slob dpon gyi thugs la gnas tshul spyir bstan pa dang /
NK058(si)001:12985: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:12987: don ngos bzung ba ni spyir theg pa so so'i
NK058(si)001:12988: don mthar thug rang rang gi ston byed slob dpon
NK058(si)001:12990: khyad par du rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don
NK058(si)001:12991: mthar thug pa rgyud lung gi gzhung tshig la gab
NK058(si)001:12992: cing sbas pa rnams bla ma'i thugs la gnas pa
NK058(si)001:12993: gdams ngag 'dod pas bla ma mnyes par bya ba
NK058(si)001:12994: la thug go // de'ang theg pa bsam gyis mi
NK058(si)001:12995: khyab cing brjod las 'das pa sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK058(si)001:12996: dang sems can gyi gnas ris grangs med pa na
NK058(si)001:12997: yod pas ma nges mod kyi /
NK058(si)001:12998: da lta'i bskal pa bzang po 'di dag mi mjed
NK058(si)001:12999: kyi 'jig rten 'dir sangs rgyas kyi sgron ma bkod
NK058(si)001:13000: cing / dman pa dang mchog dang phyin ci log
NK058(si)001:13001: gi theg pa dang gzhung lugs kyi tshul rnams re
NK058(si)001:13003: dang po yang dag pa'i don ma rtogs pa ni
NK058(si)001:13004: grub pa'i mtha' la ma zhugs pa'i skye bo phal
NK058(si)001:13005: pa ste / legs pa tsam zhig don du gnyer
NK058(si)001:13006: bas bde 'gro bsgrub pa sor bzhag lha dang mi'i
NK058(si)001:13007: pa ste / theg pa'o // de'i don dge ba bcus 'dod pa'i lha dang mir 'phen cing /
NK058(si)001:13008: bsam gtan gzugs med kyi khams gong ma bsgrub pa ste /
NK058(si)001:13010: 'jig rten pa yi yang dag lta //
NK058(si)001:13011: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK058(si)001:13012: 'di la kha cig phyal ba dang rgyang 'phen pa
NK058(si)001:13013: gnyis la 'dod pas ni snga phyi'i 'brel ma 'grig
NK058(si)001:13014: cing theg pa'i rnam dbye ma phyed par zad do
NK058(si)001:13015: // de'ang sngar theg pa lnga'i skabs su lha mi'i theg pa gsungs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:13016: theg pa srid do cog gi don 'dir bsdus pas sor bzhag gi theg pa la brjod do //
NK058(si)001:13017: phyal ba dang rgyang 'phen ni phyin ci log tu
NK058(si)001:13018: rtog pa'i mu stegs kyi nang tshan yin pas 'dir
NK058(si)001:13019: ma 'brel lo // yang dag pa'i don las phyin
NK058(si)001:13020: ci log par rtog pa ni mu stegs byed de
NK058(si)001:13021: ma 'brel lo // / lta ba log pa'i grangs
NK058(si)001:13022: kyis de'i dbye ba bsam gyis mi khyab kyang bsdu
NK058(si)001:13023: na rtag par lta ba sde bzhi chad par lta
NK058(si)001:13024: ba dang bcas pas tir ti ka sde lngar grags
NK058(si)001:13025: ma 'brel lo // / so // rtag pa bzhi ni /
NK058(si)001:13026: dbang phyug rtag par smra ba'i rig pa can dang /
NK058(si)001:13027: khyab 'jug rtag par smra ba khyab 'jug pa dang /
NK058(si)001:13028: gtso bo rtag par smra ba grangs can pas dang /
NK058(si)001:13029: rdul phran rtag par smra ba bye brag pa'o //
NK058(si)001:13030: de dag kyang drang srong ser skya dang /
NK058(si)001:13034: chad par lta ba ni rgyang 'phen pa'am /
NK058(si)001:13035: tshu rol mdzes par smra ba'am /
NK058(si)001:13036: nam mkha'i gos can pa zhes bya ste /
NK058(si)001:13038: de thams cad kyang bdag tu smra ba ste /
NK058(si)001:13039: rtag par lta ba rnams ni bdag gam gtso bo rtag pa gcig pu rang dbang can yin zhing /
NK058(si)001:13040: 'byung ba rnams la dbang byed pa khyab pa'i rang
NK058(si)001:13041: bzhin sems can kun gyi snying la gnas par 'dod
NK058(si)001:13042: cing / dbang phyug khyab 'jug la sogs pa'i lha
NK058(si)001:13043: rtag pas mtho ris sam ngan song du 'phen par
NK058(si)001:13044: cing / 'dod la / chad pa pos ma'i mnga' du bdag glo bur du byung nas gnas pa /
NK058(si)001:13045: shi ba'i tshe bdag rgyun chad pas na snga phyi'i mur thug ste tshe lnga phyi dang /
NK058(si)001:13046: thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa med par 'dod pas mur thug pa'am rgyang 'phen pa zhes bya'o //
NK058(si)001:13047: bsdu na rtag chad gnyis su 'adu'o //
NK058(si)001:13048: yang dag pa'i don gyi phyogs tsam rtogs pa ni nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:13049: bdag med gcig dang phyed dang gnyis rtogs shing 'khor ba las grol ba'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:13050: nyan thos la dbye na rtsa ba'i sde bzhi gyes pa bco brgyad do //
NK058(si)001:13051: de'ang gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba'i sde las phye ba bdun te /
NK058(si)001:13057: rnam par phye ste smra ba'i sde /
NK058(si)001:13058: rtsa ba'i gyes gzhi dang bdun po 'di dag ni
NK058(si)001:13059: rgyal rigs sgra gcan 'dzin rab tu bzang po bcom
NK058(si)001:13060: ldan 'das kyi sras su gyur pa de'i slob brgyud
NK058(si)001:13061: / sam skri ta'i skad du smra zhing /
NK058(si)001:13062: snam sbyar gyi snam phran dgu yan chad nyi shu rtsa lnga man chad de /
NK058(si)001:13063: rtags su ut+pala dang pad+ma dang rin po che 'byung ba'o //
NK058(si)001:13064: phal chen pa'i sde la phye ba /
NK058(si)001:13068: 'jig rten las 'das par smra ba'i sde /
NK058(si)001:13070: 'di dag ni bram ze'i rigs gnas brtan 'od srungs chen po'i slob brgyud /
NK058(si)001:13071: pra kri ta'i skad du smra ba /
NK058(si)001:13072: snam sbyar gyi snam phran dgu yan chad nyi shu
NK058(si)001:13073: rtsa gsum man chad de rtags su g.yung drung 'khyil
NK058(si)001:13075: gnas brtan pa'i sde la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:13076: rgyal byed tshal na gnas pa'i sde /
NK058(si)001:13077: 'jigs med ri la gnas pa'i sde /
NK058(si)001:13078: gtsug lag khang na gnas pa'i sde'o //
NK058(si)001:13079: 'di dag ni smyug ma mkhan gyi rigs las rab
NK058(si)001:13080: tu byung ba 'phags pa k+aa ta y+aa na chen
NK058(si)001:13081: po'i slob brgyud / a wa bri sha'i skad du smra ba /
NK058(si)001:13082: snam phran ni dgu yan chad nyi shu rtsa gcig man chad la rtags su dung bris pa'o //
NK058(si)001:13083: mang pos bkur ba la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:13087: 'di dag 'dregs mkhan gyi rigs las rab tu byung ba 'phags pa nye ba 'khor gyi slob brgyud /
NK058(si)001:13088: bi sha tsi'i skad du smra ba /
NK058(si)001:13089: snam phran ni gnas brtan pa dang mthun pa'o //
NK058(si)001:13090: de dag gis gang zag gi bdag dang nga dang nga yir 'dzin pa phung po dang /
NK058(si)001:13091: de las gzhan na'ang med par rtogs pas 'bras bu mngon du byed pa'o //
NK058(si)001:13092: rang sangs rgyas la dbye na /
NK058(si)001:13095: bse ru lta bu gsum mo //
NK058(si)001:13096: lta ba ni gang zag gi bdag med dang /
NK058(si)001:13097: phyi gzung ba rang bzhin med par rtogs pas phyed dang gnyis dang /
NK058(si)001:13098: srid pa tha ma'i dus su rang gi byang chub
NK058(si)001:13099: 'grub pa bla ma la dngos su mi ltos par
NK058(si)001:13100: rten 'brel gyi chos nyid rang shar du rtogs nas
NK058(si)001:13101: grol te / brda'i chos ston gyi ngag gis mi smra ba yin no //
NK058(si)001:13102: gnas lugs kyi don yang dag pa nyid lhag ma
NK058(si)001:13103: ma lus par ma rtogs pa ni rgyu mtshan nyid
NK058(si)001:13105: rgyu sems can gyis tshogs gnyis bsgrubs pas 'bras bu
NK058(si)001:13106: bskal pa grangs med pa du ma nas sangs rgyas
NK058(si)001:13111: de la phyi snod du snang ba sems su khas blangs nas /
NK058(si)001:13112: sems de yang rang rig pa gzung 'dzin gnyis su
NK058(si)001:13113: med pa'i ye shes don dam par bden pa dang
NK058(si)001:13114: brdzun par 'dod pas rnam bden brdzun gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:13115: dbu ma spyan ras gzigs kyi brtul zhugs las /
NK058(si)001:13116: gang dag dngos po sna tshogs su snang ba rang gi sems su khas blangs nas /
NK058(si)001:13117: sems de yang don dam par so so rang gi
NK058(si)001:13118: rig pa'i ye shes gzung ba dang 'dzin pa gnyis
NK058(si)001:13119: med pa bden pa'am brdzun par smra ba'i rang bzhin
NK058(si)001:13120: gyis phyogs gnyis po dgag par bya ste zhes so
NK058(si)001:13122: rang rgyud pa ni sna tshogs su snang ba 'di dag kun rdzob sgyu ma ltar grub cing /
NK058(si)001:13123: don dam par de yang grub pa med pa'i rang bzhin nam mkha' ltar 'dod pa'o //
NK058(si)001:13124: dbu ma thal 'gyur ba ni dus thams cad du
NK058(si)001:13125: rang bzhin med pas sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad dang 'dra
NK058(si)001:13126: bar snang ba de nyid spros pa'i mtha' thams cad
NK058(si)001:13127: dang bral bas gang du'ang grub pa med cing mtha'
NK058(si)001:13128: bzhi'i dri ma las 'das par 'dod do //
NK058(si)001:13129: de thams cad kyang lta ba bdag nyid kyis stong
NK058(si)001:13130: pa'i chos nyid du thag bcad nas lam mi dge
NK058(si)001:13131: ba 'dor zhing dge ba sgrub la 'bras bu phyis
NK058(si)001:13133: theg pa gong mas gzhal dus de dag chos thams
NK058(si)001:13134: cad bdag med cing mnyam pa nyid du rtogs par
NK058(si)001:13135: 'dod kyang / chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par mnyam pa'i don ma mthong ba dang /
NK058(si)001:13136: las nyon mongs pa nyid ye shes su shar bar
NK058(si)001:13137: spang blang med pa'i rang bzhin ma rtogs pa dang
NK058(si)001:13138: thabs nyung zhing dka' tshegs dang bcas pas dus ring
NK058(si)001:13139: mo zhig na 'bras bu 'grub par 'dod pa'i phyir
NK058(si)001:13140: yang dag nyid ma rtogs pa zhes bya'o //
NK058(si)001:13141: kha cig shes rab khyad med kyang thabs kyis 'phags so zhes 'dod pa'ang 'dres pa yin te /
NK058(si)001:13142: thabs khyad zhugs shing gong du 'phags pas thabs des bzhag pa'i shes rab kyang khyad 'phags shing /
NK058(si)001:13143: chos thams cad dkyil 'khor du gnas pa dang /
NK058(si)001:13144: da lta'i sems 'di nyid spu ma barjesa pa nas
NK058(si)001:13145: sangs rgyas su grub par 'dod pa'i shes rab pha
NK058(si)001:13146: rol tu phyin pa'i theg pa la ga la yod
NK058(si)001:13147: / des na thabs dang shes rab gnyis kas 'phags te /
NK058(si)001:13148: tshul gsum gyi sgron ma las /
NK058(si)001:13149: don gcig na yang ma rmongs dang //
NK058(si)001:13150: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK058(si)001:13151: dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas pas //
NK058(si)001:13152: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK058(si)001:13154: de'i phyir pha rol tu phyin pa'i tshul la rmongs pa'i sgrib pa phyogs gcig yod par bshad do //
NK058(si)001:13155: gzhan yang theg pa gsum rnam par bzhag pa las kyang /
NK058(si)001:13156: dmigs pa rnam par dag pa dang //
NK058(si)001:13157: grogs kyi mthu dang spyod pa yis //
NK058(si)001:13158: blo ldan rnams kyi theg pa ni //
NK058(si)001:13159: chen po'i chen por yongs su bsgrags //
NK058(si)001:13162: gsang sngags tshul chen shin tu rmad byung ni //
NK058(si)001:13163: lam gyi nang nas nye lam chen po ste //
NK058(si)001:13164: thabs kyi nang nas ma nor dam pa nyid //
NK058(si)001:13165: shes rab nang nas shes rab khyad par can //
NK058(si)001:13167: gtsang sbra dang dka' thub gtso bor byed pas sgo
NK058(si)001:13168: gsum gyi nyes spyod 'dul ba ni bya spyod kyi
NK058(si)001:13169: rgyud de / dbye na sems bskyed tsam la brten nas lha bsgrub pa dang /
NK058(si)001:13170: dka' thub dang smyung gnas tsam la brten nas lha bsgrub pa dang /
NK058(si)001:13171: rig gtad rjes gnang tsam la brten nas lha bsgrub pa ste gsum du yod do //
NK058(si)001:13172: de'ang gza' skar dang dus tshigs bzang po la sgrub
NK058(si)001:13173: pa'i mgo brtsam zhing 'jug pa dag grol tu byed
NK058(si)001:13174: do // dgongs pa ni rnal 'byor gyi rgyud de /
NK058(si)001:13175: a p+ai pra ya'i sgra las sems kyi dgongs pa la 'jug cing /
NK058(si)001:13176: sems rtse gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin gtso bos lha bsgrub bo //
NK058(si)001:13177: de'ang dbang ma thob par lha bsgrub pa'i lugs med do //
NK058(si)001:13178: sku gsung thugs kyi gsang ba gsal por ston pa ni rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud de /
NK058(si)001:13179: dngos po la mngon par zhen pa'i blo can theg
NK058(si)001:13180: pa 'og ma rnams la bstan par bya ba ma
NK058(si)001:13182: dbye na bskyed rim gtso bor ston pa pha'i rgyud dang /
NK058(si)001:13183: rdzogs rim gtso bor ston pa ma'i rgyud dang /
NK058(si)001:13184: zung 'jug gtso bor ston pa gnyis su med pa'i rgyud do //
NK058(si)001:13185: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin gsang ba'i
NK058(si)001:13186: don rmad du byung ba ni rdzogs pa chen po
NK058(si)001:13187: sems dang ye shes rang snang bar ston pa sgyu
NK058(si)001:13189: kun gyi spyod yul ma yin pa ngo bo nyid
NK058(si)001:13190: dang rang bzhin dang thabs khyad par gyis gsang ba
NK058(si)001:13191: ste / dbye na sems dang ye shes gnyis med
NK058(si)001:13192: du ston pa bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gi rdzogs pa
NK058(si)001:13193: ste / chen po / sems gtso bor ston pa sems klong ye grol gyi rdzogs pa chen po /
NK058(si)001:13194: ye shes gtso bor ston pa 'od gsal chos nyid kyi rdzogs pa chen po'o //
NK058(si)001:13195: de ltar theg pa so so'i tshul rnams ni rtogs par bya ba'i don yin no //
NK058(si)001:13196: gnyis pa don de gang gi dbyings na gnas tshul
NK058(si)001:13197: bstan pa ni theg pa de dag gi don rnams
NK058(si)001:13198: rjod byed kyi gzhung la gnas shing /
NK058(si)001:13199: gzhung yang yi ge sil bu'i khong na gnas te /
NK058(si)001:13200: dbyangs dang gsal byed kyi sgra tha snyad btags pa
NK058(si)001:13201: a dang ma 'dus pa las rang gi mar mtshon
NK058(si)001:13203: ming du ma tshogs pa'i spyi la tshig rnams brten
NK058(si)001:13204: pa'i tshig gis sh+lo ka dang rab tu byed pa
NK058(si)001:13205: dang / bstan bcos sam rgyud sde so so'i lus grub cing /
NK058(si)001:13206: so so'i gzhung des rang rang gi brjod bya'i don rab tu mtshon te gnas so //
NK058(si)001:13207: gsum pa don de ma nor par gang gis ston
NK058(si)001:13208: pa ni de lta bu'i gzhung tshig so so'i khong
NK058(si)001:13209: na rang rang gi brjod bya'i don gnas shing /
NK058(si)001:13210: khyad par du rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di
NK058(si)001:13211: rgyud tshig so so'i khong na chos thams cad ye
NK058(si)001:13212: nas sangs rgyas pa la sogs pa rang bzhin gyis
NK058(si)001:13213: rtogs par dka' ba'i don rnams gab cing /
NK058(si)001:13214: tha mal ba'i spyod yul du bsgrag tu mi rung
NK058(si)001:13215: ba'i gsang ba zab mo rnams skal med rnams kyis
NK058(si)001:13216: mi go bar bya ba'i phyir brda la sogs pas
NK058(si)001:13218: +aa li k+aa li'i phyag rgya yis //
NK058(si)001:13219: zhes pa lta bu'i don rnams mngon sum du 'byin
NK058(si)001:13220: pa ni rgyud kyi don phyin ci ma log par
NK058(si)001:13221: ston pa rdo rje'i slob dpon gyi thugs la gnas
NK058(si)001:13222: pas de la thug cig pa'o //
NK058(si)001:13223: kha cig 'og min du ston pa kun tu bzang pos 'byin la /
NK058(si)001:13224: tha mal ba rnams la rdo rje slob dpon gyis
NK058(si)001:13226: te / rgyud 'di'i khong nas don 'byin pa rgyud
NK058(si)001:13227: gsung pa po las gzhan zhig bstan pa yin gyi
NK058(si)001:13228: te / / kun tu bzang po nyid kyis 'chad nyan byed cing don 'byin pa ga la rigs /
NK058(si)001:13229: de bas don ma go bar zad do //
NK058(si)001:13230: gnyis pa rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don bye brag tu bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:13231: snying po'i zab don dngos bstan pa //
NK058(si)001:13232: de gzhan las khyad par 'phags tshul //
NK058(si)001:13233: gang la gdams pa'i snod bstan pa'o //
NK058(si)001:13239: thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa ni phung po khams dang
NK058(si)001:13240: skye mched kyis bsdus pa 'khor ba dang mya ngan
NK058(si)001:13241: las 'das pa'i chos thams cad ye nas sku gsung
NK058(si)001:13242: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas te rang bzhin
NK058(si)001:13243: gyis rnam par dag pa las /
NK058(si)001:13244: phyis lam gyis sngar sangs rgyas ma yin pa sangs rgyas su bsgrub pa lta bu ma yin te /
NK058(si)001:13245: 'gro ba kun la ye nas de ltar gnas pa
NK058(si)001:13246: ni gzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor rang chas
NK058(si)001:13247: su ldan pa'i rang bzhin te /
NK058(si)001:13248: de ltar rtogs nas ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:13249: gyis ye nas yin pa'i dkyil 'khor la ni yin
NK058(si)001:13250: par shes pa'i dkyil 'khor du gsal 'debs shing bsgom
NK058(si)001:13251: par bya'o // de ltar chos thams cad kyi rang
NK058(si)001:13252: bzhin de lta bu yin yang yin pa tsam gyis
NK058(si)001:13254: gzhi de ltar yin kyang lam gyis bsgrub dgos te /
NK058(si)001:13255: gser dang dngul gyi rdo'i khams la gser dngul du yod kyang /
NK058(si)001:13256: bzhu btul ma byas na mi snang ba dang /
NK058(si)001:13257: dung dkar por gnas kyang bad kan ma sbyangs kyi
NK058(si)001:13258: bar ser por snang bas bad kan sbyong dgos pa
NK058(si)001:13259: bzhin no // gnyis pa shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim
NK058(si)001:13260: pa ni bde gsal rnam par mi rtog pa'i dkyil
NK058(si)001:13261: bzhin no // 'khor / rtog tshogs nyon mongs su
NK058(si)001:13262: snang ba thabs kyis zin pa'i dkyil 'khor las byung
NK058(si)001:13263: bzhin no // 'khor / ba ste / de nyid
NK058(si)001:13264: ma spangs rang sar dag pa'i rang bzhin yin pas
NK058(si)001:13265: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor zhes bya ste dkyil 'khor thams
NK058(si)001:13266: cad kyi nang nas mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK058(si)001:13267: gsum pa gnyis med 'od gsal gyi rim pa ni /
NK058(si)001:13268: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo la sogs pa na
NK058(si)001:13269: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa sku dang ye shes
NK058(si)001:13270: kyi rang bzhin du gnas pa ni gsang ba'i thig
NK058(si)001:13271: le rmad du byung ba ste /
NK058(si)001:13272: rkyen bla ma'i man ngag gis nyams su blangs na
NK058(si)001:13273: sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i
NK058(si)001:13274: dkyil 'khor thams cad 'byung ba'i dbyings yin no //
NK058(si)001:13275: tshul 'di ni rgyud 'dir shin tu gab cing sbas
NK058(si)001:13276: pas sngon gyi sgyu 'phrul mkhan po phal gyis ma
NK058(si)001:13278: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
