NK058(si)001:16119: badz+ra lo ka rdo rje 'jig rten snang byed ma ste dred gdong ma'o //
NK058(si)001:16120: b+ha smi pa la ya ba ti ni thal bar byed pa ste spyang gdong can no //
NK058(si)001:16121: mtha' rten gyi dzahmh'u bam hohbzhi ni sa bon no //
NK058(si)001:16122: lnga pa dbang phyug ma rnams kyi sngags ni /
NK058(si)001:16123: b+h+yo nyi shu rtsa brgyad de /
NK058(si)001:16124: de'ang b+ha g+ai ni sring mo /
NK058(si)001:16126: de dag gi sgra bsdus te b+h+yo zhes sa bon du byas pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16127: las bsgrub pa'i tshe ma nu rak+sha s+ai b+h+yo dgra
NK058(si)001:16128: bo m+aa ra ya h'u phata ces pa la sogs
NK058(si)001:16129: pa so so'i sngags dang sbyar ro //
NK058(si)001:16130: gnyis pa ye shes pa spyan drang ba'i sngags ni
NK058(si)001:16131: ru lu ru lu ru lu h'u ni khro bo
NK058(si)001:16133: de'ang sngon las kyi srin po'i dam tshig gi gdug pa'i glu dpal chen pos byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16134: e h+ye hi ni tshur spyon tshur spyon no //
NK058(si)001:16136: dzahmh'u bam hohni tshad med bzhis sems can gyi las la bskul ba'o //
NK058(si)001:16137: ram ni dam tshig pa dang ye shes pa spyan
NK058(si)001:16138: drangs pa'i me ri 'dab 'byor tsam du bzhugs pa'o
NK058(si)001:16139: // bla ma rong pa ni rig pa'i me tog
NK058(si)001:16140: dor ba ste bdag dang lha rang bzhin dbyer med
NK058(si)001:16141: du rtogs nas gnyis su med pa la phyogs pa'o
NK058(si)001:16142: // zhes 'chad do // gsum pa rig pa'i me
NK058(si)001:16143: tog dor ba'i sngags ni badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma
NK058(si)001:16144: ya h'u ni khro bo dam tshig la 'dus shig
NK058(si)001:16145: // zhes 'chad do // pa'o // bzhi pa dngos grub kyi don du gsol ba gdab pa ni //
NK058(si)001:16146: gdul bya las kyi khro bo ma rungs pa 'dul
NK058(si)001:16147: ba la ye shes kyi rang bzhin de bas kyang
NK058(si)001:16148: khros par snang bas gdul bya'i rgyud zhi bar mdzad
NK058(si)001:16149: pa thugs rje ngang gis khro bor sprul pa ni
NK058(si)001:16150: 'gro ba'i dpal chen po rab tu rngams pa'i tshogs
NK058(si)001:16151: / sku gsung thugs ye shes kyi rang bzhin 'bar
NK058(si)001:16152: ba'i byin rlabs rmad du byung ba chen po de
NK058(si)001:16153: dus da lta nyid du ni bdag la sku gsung
NK058(si)001:16154: thugs kyi dngos grub ma lus pa rtsol cig pa'o
NK058(si)001:16155: / // sa ma ya s+t+wam dam tshig la nos shig /
NK058(si)001:16156: sa ma ya phata dam tshig spros shig /
NK058(si)001:16157: sa ma ya hohdama tshig yin no zhes pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16158: lnga pa phrin las kyi don du gtor ma sbyin
NK058(si)001:16159: pa'i sngags ni a li u li bza' ba dang
NK058(si)001:16160: btung ba / ta li ta ba li de dag gi yan lag go //
NK058(si)001:16161: damsh+ta goo na roo tri mche ba can rdo rje drag po'i tshogs /
NK058(si)001:16162: kha ram yo gi ni kh+aa hi hohzhala 'bar ba rnal 'byor ma'i tshogs gsol cig pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16163: de dag gang gi zhal du gsol snyam na h'u ha he phata lha sum cu'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK058(si)001:16164: de'ang 'di ltar rig par bya ste /
NK058(si)001:16165: gsang sngags 'di dag bod skad du ma bsgyur ba
NK058(si)001:16166: ni gsung pa po'i bden tshig 'grub par bya ba'i
NK058(si)001:16167: phyir ro // gal te bsgyur nas bzlas na dngos grub med de /
NK058(si)001:16168: bod skad du sngon gyi gsang sngags gsung ba pos byin gyis ma brlabs pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:16169: skad so sor shan sbyor ma shes kyang nyes pa med de /
NK058(si)001:16170: dad pa dang mos pa rtse gcig pas bzlas na
NK058(si)001:16171: dngos grub chen po ji lta ba bzhin 'byung ngo
NK058(si)001:16172: // sgra sbyor shes na'ang phan yon yod de /
NK058(si)001:16173: tshig don go bas don gyi gzungs 'grub pa dang tshig la rmongs pa med pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:16174: gsum pa ltas khyad par can gyis mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK058(si)001:16175: de skad ces brjod pas 'jig rten drug gi phyogs
NK058(si)001:16176: bcu thams cad kyi snod ma dag pa'i dngos po
NK058(si)001:16177: dang bcud kyi sgrib pa'i tshogs las /
NK058(si)001:16178: lus kyi mi dge ba rnams tshig /
NK058(si)001:16180: sems kyi kun tu rab tu tshig go //
NK058(si)001:16181: de ltar tha mal gyi dngos po sgrib pa dang
NK058(si)001:16182: bcas pa tshig nas snang ba snod kyi 'jig rten
NK058(si)001:16183: ye shes kyi snang bar 'bar zhing gdul bya'i sgo
NK058(si)001:16186: thugs kyi kun tu rab tu 'bar ro //
NK058(si)001:16187: de'i tshe snang srid snod bcud nam mkha'i mthas gtugs
NK058(si)001:16188: pa thams cad du 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs
NK058(si)001:16189: rigs lnga'i rang bzhin gyis nam mkha'i dbyings thams cad
NK058(si)001:16190: sku'i dkyil 'khor gyis gang zhing sku de dag las
NK058(si)001:16191: gsang sngags kyi rang sgra 'brug stong tsam gyis khyab
NK058(si)001:16192: par rab tu gang ba thams cad kyang thugs rje
NK058(si)001:16193: chen po'i sprul pa dang 'od dang gzi brjid kyis
NK058(si)001:16194: gsal la chos skus khyab pa'i thugs kyi rang bzhin
NK058(si)001:16195: gnyis su med pas kun tu gang na gyur to
NK058(si)001:16197: yang dkyil 'khor gsum gyis nam mkha' dang sa gzhi
NK058(si)001:16198: dang bar snang gsum du gang rab tu gang kun
NK058(si)001:16199: tu gang ngo // yang rang snang lhun stug po
NK058(si)001:16200: bkod par 'od dang gzi brjid dang ye shes kyi
NK058(si)001:16201: bkod pas gang rab tu gang kun tu gang ba'o
NK058(si)001:16202: tu gang ngo // // gsung mchog tu gsang ba'i
NK058(si)001:16203: snying po ye shes kyi rang sgra'i de kho na
NK058(si)001:16205: ye shes kyi khro bo'i tshogs chen po'i gsung gi
NK058(si)001:16206: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dkyil 'khor mtha'
NK058(si)001:16207: dbus med par spros pa'i le'u ste bcu drug pa'i
NK058(si)001:16210: // spyi don gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rten gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:16212: dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin rgyas par bshad /
NK058(si)001:16213: ngo mtshar gyi ltas snang ba'o //
NK058(si)001:16215: gsung gsang sngags kyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas
NK058(si)001:16216: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos khro bo'i sprin
NK058(si)001:16217: phung gsang sngags dang bcas pa de dag gi rnam
NK058(si)001:16218: pa gsal bar byed pa na dmigs pa'i rten dgos
NK058(si)001:16219: pas phyi rabs kyi gdul bya la phan pa'i don
NK058(si)001:16220: du gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i phyir ched
NK058(si)001:16221: du brjod pa 'di dag brjod do //
NK058(si)001:16227: ye shes lnga mtshon pa'i phyir phyi nang med par
NK058(si)001:16228: me dpung 'bar ba'i klong pho brang gi 'og gzhi
NK058(si)001:16229: lte ba mu khyud dang bcas pa'i 'khor lo rtsibs
NK058(si)001:16230: bzhi pa ni rigs lnga'i rang bzhin gyi barda'o //
NK058(si)001:16231: de'ang tshad med pa bzhi dang bden pa bzhi mtshon
NK058(si)001:16232: pa'i phyir gru chad bzhi yis rnam par brgyan pa'o
NK058(si)001:16233: // de'i steng du ye shes kyi gzhal yas khang
NK058(si)001:16234: yon tan rgyas pa'i brdar gru bzhi pa rnam par
NK058(si)001:16235: thar pa bzhi'i mtshon byed du sgo khyud bzhi dang
NK058(si)001:16236: ldan pa'i dbus sku lnga'i brdar 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi
NK058(si)001:16237: gru chad dang bcas pas mdzes pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16238: des mtshon pa rnam thar brgyad kyi rta babs dang
NK058(si)001:16239: bden pa gnyis kyi don mtshon pa ye shes 'bar
NK058(si)001:16240: ba'i bar khyams phyi nang gnyis kyi mdzes shing ban+d+ha'i
NK058(si)001:16241: rtsig pa chen pos lhun mtho ba'o //
NK058(si)001:16242: gnyis pa de mdzes par byed pa'i rgyan ni /
NK058(si)001:16243: phal cher gong dang mtshungs shing /
NK058(si)001:16244: khyad par du thod pa skam rlon gyi rtsig pa la sbrul nag gi chun pos dkris shing /
NK058(si)001:16245: thod pa sbrul gyi zar tshags dang /
NK058(si)001:16246: nyi ma dang zla ba'i mthong khung dang /
NK058(si)001:16248: mchog chen gyi ka ba dang /
NK058(si)001:16249: rus sbal gyi ka gdan dang /
NK058(si)001:16251: mchog phran gyi dral ba dang /
NK058(si)001:16254: don snying gi d+r+wa phyed dang /
NK058(si)001:16255: sgo bzhi rus sbal gyi ma them dang /
NK058(si)001:16256: chu srin gyi ya them dang /
NK058(si)001:16257: sbrul nag gi skyes bu dang /
NK058(si)001:16258: zhing chen gyi sgo glegs la sogs pa sna tshogs pas brgyan cing /
NK058(si)001:16259: nyi ma dang zla ba dang gza' skar gyi kha
NK058(si)001:16260: bad dang rgyan gyis brjid cing me dpung 'bar ba'i
NK058(si)001:16261: rtse las me'i tsha tsha phyogs bcur 'phro ba'i phreng
NK058(si)001:16262: ba mang po dang 'od zer 'khrugs pas mdzes pa'o
NK058(si)001:16263: // gsum pa gdan gyi khyad par ni 'gro ba zil gyis gnon pa khyu mchog dang /
NK058(si)001:16264: gzi brjid che ba ma he dang /
NK058(si)001:16265: gdug pa che ba gzig dang /
NK058(si)001:16266: dpa' brtul che ba stag dang /
NK058(si)001:16267: rang bzhin gyis gtum pa'i dom rnams kyi sbar bas ni btegs pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16268: mi shes pa dag sder mos lha chen po bzung zhes 'chad pa ni ma yin te /
NK058(si)001:16269: 'di dag gi khri'i steng du dregs pa pho mo bsnol ba la bzhugs pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:16270: de'i steng du dregs pa'i dbang phyug lha chen po la sogs pa khyo shug zung du bsnol ba'o //
NK058(si)001:16271: bzung ni yi ge ma dag pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16272: srog chags 'di dag kyang sku gsung thugs ye shes lnga'i mtshon byed du rang snang ba'o //
NK058(si)001:16273: gnyis pa brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:16277: sku mdog dang zhal phyag gi rnam pa las /
NK058(si)001:16278: sku mdog gi gti mug gnas su dag pas gtso bo smug nag /
NK058(si)001:16279: zhe sdang dag pas badz+ra he ru ka sngo nag /
NK058(si)001:16280: nga rgyal dag pas rat+na ser nag dang //
NK058(si)001:16281: 'dod chags dag pas pad+ma dmar nag /
NK058(si)001:16282: phrag dog dag pas karma yab yum ljang nag ste rtsa zhal dang bcas pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16283: dbus dang shar nub byang bzhi'i he ru ka'i g.yas dkar zhing /
NK058(si)001:16285: dbus dang lho dang byang gi g.yon dmar zhing /
NK058(si)001:16286: shar dang nub kyi g.yon ser po'o //
NK058(si)001:16287: de'ang drag po'i phrin las mthar phyin pa'i rtags su thams cad la nag po'i sgra smos so //
NK058(si)001:16288: gdul bya gdug pa can gyi snang ngor rab tu 'jigs pa'i sku ste /
NK058(si)001:16289: zhal phyag gi gnas lugs ni dug gsum dag cing
NK058(si)001:16290: sku gsum mnga' ba'i phyir thams cad kyang dbu gsum
NK058(si)001:16291: pa / ye shes drug la dbang sgyur zhing pha
NK058(si)001:16292: rol tu phyin pa drug gis 'gro ba drug sgrol
NK058(si)001:16293: ba'i phyir phyag drug pa rdzu 'phrul bzhi dang bdud
NK058(si)001:16294: bzhi 'dul ba'i brdar zhabs bzhi brkyang bskum du bgrad
NK058(si)001:16295: pa / pa'o // gnyis pa rgyan chas dang gsung gi nga ro la /
NK058(si)001:16296: rgyan chas ni dpal gyi chas brgyad de /
NK058(si)001:16297: theg pa chen po'i don la mnga' brnyes pa'i mtshon byed du glang chen spags pa'i stod g.yogs /
NK058(si)001:16298: dregs pa dbang du sdud pa zhing gi g.yang gzhi'i stod g.yogs /
NK058(si)001:16299: gzung 'dzin gyi mtha' las grol ba stag lpags kyi
NK058(si)001:16300: sham thabs te ko rlon gyi gos ni rnam pa
NK058(si)001:16302: sbrul ni rgyal rig dkar po'i dbu rgyan /
NK058(si)001:16303: rje rigs ser po'i snyan cha dang mgur chu /
NK058(si)001:16304: bram ze'i rigs dmar po'i do shal dang dpung rgyan /
NK058(si)001:16305: rmongs rigs ljang gu'i sked rag /
NK058(si)001:16306: gdol ba'i rigs nag po'i phyag zhabs kyi gdu bu'o //
NK058(si)001:16307: thod phreng ni mi mgo skam po'i dbu rgyan /
NK058(si)001:16309: rlon pa lnga bcu rtsa gcig gi do shal lo //
NK058(si)001:16310: nyi ma dang zla ba'i chas ni phrag pa g.yas
NK058(si)001:16311: g.yon nas 'od 'gyed pa ste thabs dang shes rab
NK058(si)001:16316: thal chen gyi tshom bu dang brgyad do //
NK058(si)001:16323: thal ba rnams dur khrod chas brgyad do //
NK058(si)001:16324: gsung gi nga ro ni rngams pa'i sgra skad chen
NK058(si)001:16325: po 'jigs par sgrogs pa 'brug stong ldir ba tsam
NK058(si)001:16326: mo // gsum pa phyag mtshan dang btsun mo'i sbyor tshul la /
NK058(si)001:16328: sangs rgyas gsang ba phyag g.yas g.yon gyi dang po gnyis na rdo rje dang 'khor lo /
NK058(si)001:16329: bar ba na ral gri dang dung chen /
NK058(si)001:16330: tha ma gnyis na dgra s+t+wa dang thong gshol la sogs kyi sgra dbyug to //
NK058(si)001:16332: bee con la sogs pa'o zhes gsungs shing /
NK058(si)001:16333: rong pa ni g.yas dang po rang rang gi phyag mtshan /
NK058(si)001:16334: g.yon dang po ban+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba /
NK058(si)001:16335: gzhan rnams rim pa bzhin sbyor bar bzhed kyang /
NK058(si)001:16336: 'dir sgyu 'phrul rdo rje dang mthun par sbyar na /
NK058(si)001:16337: g.yas dang po rnams rang rang gi phyag mtshan 'dzin pa ste /
NK058(si)001:16338: de'ang badz+ra he ru ka'i g.yas dang po rdo rje rtse dgu pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16339: rigs lnga ga'i g.yas bar ma rdo rje rtse lnga pa dang /
NK058(si)001:16340: g.yon bar ma dung chen te thod pa lcang lo med pa khrag gis gang ba'o //
NK058(si)001:16341: karma he ru ka'i g.yas dang po ral gri /
NK058(si)001:16342: de bzhin gshegs pa'i g.yon dang po dang /
NK058(si)001:16343: rin po che'i g.yon tha ma gnyis na dgra s+t+wa /
NK058(si)001:16344: las kyi g.yon dang po thong gshol /
NK058(si)001:16345: rdo rje'i g.yon tha ma dang /
NK058(si)001:16346: las kyi g.yon tha ma gnyis stong gi 'jig rten
NK058(si)001:16347: khor yug dang bcas pa mtshon pa'i phyir rnge chung
NK058(si)001:16348: ngo // la sogs kyis bsdus pa /
NK058(si)001:16352: bud+d+ha'i g.yon tha ma kha t+w+aam ga /
NK058(si)001:16353: rin po che'i g.yon dang po rgyu zhags /
NK058(si)001:16354: rdo rje dang pad+ma'i g.yon dang po dril bu /
NK058(si)001:16355: pad+ma'i g.yon tha ma rnge chung /
NK058(si)001:16356: thams cad kyi g.yas tha ma ti ra ste zhing dbyug gdengs pa ste /
NK058(si)001:16357: rang gi lag cha sna tshogs bsnams pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16359: rdo rje rdo rje dril bu dang //
NK058(si)001:16361: de bzhin 'khor lo dgra s+t+wa dang //
NK058(si)001:16363: nor bu rin cen rgyu zhags dang //
NK058(si)001:16364: rdo rje dgra s+t+wa rab tu bsdebs //
NK058(si)001:16365: chags mchog pad+ma chen po dang //
NK058(si)001:16366: dril bu rnga yi sgra sgrogs pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16367: las kyi ral gri gshol chen dang //
NK058(si)001:16369: bar ma rdo rje dung dmar 'khrug /
NK058(si)001:16370: ti ra chen po rab bsdebs pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16372: btsun mo'i 'khril tshul ni rang rang gi rigs kyi
NK058(si)001:16373: btsun mo lnga ni zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma 'jigs
NK058(si)001:16374: pa'i tshogs g.yas yab la 'khyud cing g.yon thod khrag
NK058(si)001:16375: gtso bo'i zhal du stob pa dang 'khril ba'o //
NK058(si)001:16376: gnyis pa 'khor gyi bkod pa la gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:16377: dang po khro mo nyi shu'i bkod pa ni /
NK058(si)001:16378: gnas kyi ma mo brgyad ni /
NK058(si)001:16379: de'ang rnam shes tshogs brgyad 'khor ba bskyed pa'i gnas yin la /
NK058(si)001:16380: de rnams gnas su dag par byed pa'i phyir gnas kyi phyag rgya zhes bya'o //
NK058(si)001:16381: de la goo r+ai dkar mo zhing dbyug dang b+han dmar /
NK058(si)001:16382: tsoo r+ai ser mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa /
NK058(si)001:16383: bra mo h+aa dmar mo phyag gnyis chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan bsgreng ba /
NK058(si)001:16384: beet+ta l+ai nag mo rdo rje 'phyar zhing b+han dmar thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK058(si)001:16385: puk+ka s+ai dmar ser byis pa'i rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK058(si)001:16386: gasma ri ljang nag dung dmar dkrug cing gsol ba /
NK058(si)001:16387: sma sha n+ai mthing nag byis pa'i snying za ba /
NK058(si)001:16388: tsan+da l+ai ser skya bam gyi mgo lus 'dral ba'o //
NK058(si)001:16389: yul gyi phyag rgya phra men brgyad la /
NK058(si)001:16390: de'ang sgo lnga'i rnam shes kyi yul gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya /
NK058(si)001:16392: nyon mongs pa can gyi yul kun gzhi /
NK058(si)001:16393: kun gzhi'i yul phyi nang gi chos thams cad gnas su dag pas yul gyi phyag rgya'o //
NK058(si)001:16394: de'ang seng ha ser mo lag pas ro bsnol nas kha'i thad du 'dzin pa /
NK058(si)001:16395: b+y+aa gri dmar mo ro la mig 'bru tshugs su blta ba dang /
NK058(si)001:16396: sri la nag mo zhing la 'dag pa dang /
NK058(si)001:16397: shwa na mthing ga ro'i lto ba 'dral ba dang /
NK058(si)001:16398: kri ta dmar mo ro'i rgyu ma 'dren pa dang /
NK058(si)001:16399: kang ka ser mo zhing chen phrag la khur ba dang /
NK058(si)001:16400: k+aa k+aa nag mo b+han gri thogs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:16401: hu lu mthing ga lcags kyu 'debs pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16402: sgo ma bzhi'i phyag rgyas rab tu mdzes pa ni /
NK058(si)001:16403: phyin ci log gi bdud bzhi 'joms shing ye shes bzhi yis rgyas 'debs pa ste /
NK058(si)001:16404: rta gdong dkar mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK058(si)001:16405: phag gdong nag mo zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK058(si)001:16406: dred gdong dmar mo lcags sgrog 'dzin pa /
NK058(si)001:16407: spyang gdong ljang gu dril chen 'dzin pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16408: gnyis pa dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi bkod
NK058(si)001:16409: pa ni slas chung ma dang byi mo mdza' mo
NK058(si)001:16410: dang bran mo'i tshogs ni g.yog gi las byed pa'i
NK058(si)001:16411: cha nas btags te de ltar bcu phrag gnyis dang
NK058(si)001:16412: ni brgyad kyis mdzes par bskor ba'o //
NK058(si)001:16413: de dag rang rang gi 'og na ro'i gdan dang
NK058(si)001:16414: thod rlon la sogs pa'i lag cha dang bcas te
NK058(si)001:16415: phrin las ci bgyi zhes ni chas te 'khor bar
NK058(si)001:16416: gnas so // ji ltar gnas na /
NK058(si)001:16417: srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang ba dang /
NK058(si)001:16418: tshangs pa dmar ser pad+ma 'dzin pa dang /
NK058(si)001:16419: 'khrug mo dkar ljang tri shul 'dzin pa dang /
NK058(si)001:16420: rtogs 'dod sngon mo 'khor lo thogs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:16421: gzhon nu dmar mo mdung thung 'dzin pa dang /
NK058(si)001:16422: dbang mo dkar mo rdo rje 'dzin pa dang /
NK058(si)001:16425: zla ba dkar mo pun+da ri ka /
NK058(si)001:16426: bee con ljang gu dbyug to //
NK058(si)001:16427: srin mo dmar nag dung khrag 'thung ba /
NK058(si)001:16428: za ba ljang nag ro yi rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK058(si)001:16429: dga' ba dmar mo gri gug /
NK058(si)001:16431: gcig pur spyod ma ser mo spu gri /
NK058(si)001:16433: grub mo dkar mo bum pa /
NK058(si)001:16434: rlung lha sngon mo ba dan /
NK058(si)001:16435: gsod byed dkar mo ral gri /
NK058(si)001:16436: me mo dmar mo gsal shing /
NK058(si)001:16437: phag mo nag mo mche zhags /
NK058(si)001:16438: rgan byed nag mo zhing za ba dang /
NK058(si)001:16439: sna 'phyang dkar mo thod khrag 'thung ba /
NK058(si)001:16440: chu lha dmar mo sbrul zhags /
NK058(si)001:16441: nag mo chen mo lcags kyu /
NK058(si)001:16445: le'u 'di ni bri ba dang sgom pa la sogs
NK058(si)001:16446: pa spyi'i don du smos kyi gcig kho na'i phyogs
NK058(si)001:16447: su chad pa ni ma yin no //
NK058(si)001:16448: gsum pa ngo mtshar gyi ltas snang ba ni de
NK058(si)001:16449: skad ces brjod pas 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu
NK058(si)001:16450: thams cad du ye shes kyi khro bo me dpung
NK058(si)001:16451: 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor zhing gi rdul snyed nam mkha'i
NK058(si)001:16452: dbyings dang chos kyi dbyings kyis khyab pa kun tu
NK058(si)001:16453: sku gsung thugs kyi snang bas gang bar gyur to
NK058(si)001:16454: // rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po dkyil 'khor gyi de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK058(si)001:16455: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi rnam dbye bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu bdun pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16457: // spyi don gsum pa der mchod pa ji ltar bya ba'i tshul la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:16462: dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas bcom ldan 'das mchod
NK058(si)001:16463: sprin gyi rol pa la dgyes pa chen pos phyi
NK058(si)001:16464: nang gsang ba'i rang bzhin gyis mnyes pa'i mchod pa
NK058(si)001:16465: chen po 'di dag ched du brjod do //
NK058(si)001:16467: sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa spyir bstan /
NK058(si)001:16468: dam rdzas 'dod yon gyi mchod pa bye brag tu bshad /
NK058(si)001:16469: de'i phan yon dngos grub 'grub pa'i tshul brjod pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16472: de la rgyal ba mchod pa dang sems can la
NK058(si)001:16473: sbyin pa bya ba'i tshul ni bsod nams kyi tshogs
NK058(si)001:16474: yin la / de dag gi nang nas mchog dam
NK058(si)001:16475: pa ni sems nyid ye nas dag pa mchod bya
NK058(si)001:16476: dang mchod byed med pa don gyi mchod pa ste
NK058(si)001:16477: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po yin pas na /
NK058(si)001:16478: thog mar bdag nyid kyis 'khor ba'i gnas 'dir ma
NK058(si)001:16479: rig pa'i log par rtog pas dngos po dang mtshan
NK058(si)001:16480: mar goms pa'i phyin ci log spros pa'i mtha' brgyad
NK058(si)001:16481: dang gzung 'dzin du zhen pa'i blo ngan thams cad
NK058(si)001:16482: gdod nas skye ba med pa'i ngang du bsgral te
NK058(si)001:16483: / phyi nang gi chos thams cad nam mkha'i rang bzhin can du bsgom par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:16484: de skad du'ang rgya mtsho las /
NK058(si)001:16485: mchod pa'i phyag rgya che mchog ni //
NK058(si)001:16486: sems kyi rtog tshogs kun bsgral te //
NK058(si)001:16487: mchod dang mchod bya mi dmigs pa'i //
NK058(si)001:16488: rang bzhin nam mkha'i ngang du bsgom //
NK058(si)001:16490: kha cig lta ba rtogs pa goms pa'i sgom par
NK058(si)001:16491: sbyor ba ni ma rtogs pa'i rnam 'gyur du snang
NK058(si)001:16492: ngo // mchod pa spyi'i sngon 'agro'am rdzogs rim du sbyar yang 'gal ba med mod /
NK058(si)001:16493: 'on kyang sgrol mchod la sgra nye ba'i phyir bshad de /
NK058(si)001:16494: thog ma med pa nas bdag gzhan du rtog pa
NK058(si)001:16495: goms pa de yod pas zhe sdang rang ga ma
NK058(si)001:16496: 'byung ba'i phyir / sgrol ba'i tshe gnyis su med
NK058(si)001:16497: pa'i don dang dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje'i ngang
NK058(si)001:16498: nas rang gi gzung 'dzin gyi zhen pa dang bsgrub
NK058(si)001:16499: bya thabs shes kyi ngang nas bsgral ces bya ba
NK058(si)001:16500: 'byung ba'i phyir / yin no // ji ltar bsgral ba dngos ni /
NK058(si)001:16501: rang gi gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog pa chos dbyings su
NK058(si)001:16502: bsgral ba de nas bsgral ba'i yul dang sgrol byed
NK058(si)001:16503: bdag nyid gnyis su med pa'i blo yis ni shes
NK058(si)001:16504: rab mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa'i ngang las /
NK058(si)001:16505: thabs snying rje chen pos bsgral bar bya ste /
NK058(si)001:16506: zhing bcu lta bu'i sems can blo ngan srid pa'i
NK058(si)001:16507: 'jig rten 'og mar brgyud pa 'di dag snying re
NK058(si)001:16508: rje snyam du byams pa dang snying rje tshad med
NK058(si)001:16509: pa bsgoms nas / bdag nyid sgyu ma dang yul
NK058(si)001:16510: mig yor gyi tshul tsam du shes par bya ste
NK058(si)001:16511: pa bsgoms nas / / kun rdzob tu snang yang
NK058(si)001:16512: don dam par gnyis su med par rtogs pas bsgral
NK058(si)001:16513: pa bsgoms nas / / bar bya'o // de'ang skabs
NK058(si)001:16514: dang sbyar te bya zhing rgyas par le'u bcu gcig
NK058(si)001:16515: pa bsgoms nas / / bar bya'o // pa dang
NK058(si)001:16516: / nyi shu ba'i skabs drag po'i phrin las ltar
NK058(si)001:16517: pa bsgoms nas / / bar bya'o // pa dang
NK058(si)001:16518: / bya'o // gnyis pa sbyor ba'i mchod pa ni
NK058(si)001:16519: gong du bshad pa ltar bdag dang yum lhar bskyed
NK058(si)001:16520: pa'i gsang bar dkyil 'khor spyan drangs la yab yum
NK058(si)001:16521: gnyis su med par 'khril ba'i bde ba byang chub
NK058(si)001:16522: kyi sems kyi mchod rdzas chen po rdo rje dang
NK058(si)001:16523: pad+ma mnyam par sbyor ba las skyes pa'i ngo bos
NK058(si)001:16524: bdag nyid mnyes pa de yis de bzhin gshegs pa
NK058(si)001:16526: gnyis pa dam rdzas 'dod yon gyi mchod pa bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:16527: dang po dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i mchod pa ni bdag
NK058(si)001:16528: gzhan 'khor 'das mnyam pa'i dngos grub sgrub pa'i rdzas
NK058(si)001:16529: chen po bdud rtsi lnga la sogs pa dag bdag
NK058(si)001:16530: gi phung po khams dang skye mched ye nas dkyil
NK058(si)001:16531: 'khor du gnas pa la ting nge 'dzin zab mos
NK058(si)001:16532: gsal btab pa dang bdag dang mnyam pa ye shes
NK058(si)001:16538: byang chub kyi sems lnga ni ngo bo ye nas dag pa chos kyi dbyings /
NK058(si)001:16539: rang bzhin de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs la sogs pa rigs lnga dang /
NK058(si)001:16540: ye shes lha'i ngo bor gnas shing /
NK058(si)001:16541: byin gyis brlabs te longs spyod pas dug lnga dang /
NK058(si)001:16542: 'byung ba'i nad rnams sel ba'i phyir sman gyi mchog ste /
NK058(si)001:16544: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK058(si)001:16545: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK058(si)001:16546: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK058(si)001:16547: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK058(si)001:16548: rgyud lnga'i sems can kun sgrol ba'i //
NK058(si)001:16549: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi mchog /
NK058(si)001:16551: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba ni de dag gi
NK058(si)001:16552: ye shes lnga lnga la sogs par phye na de
NK058(si)001:16554: gnyis pa 'dod yon gyi mchod pa la gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:16555: mchod rdzas ni sha dang mar la sogs pa'i bza'
NK058(si)001:16556: ba dang shing tog la sogs pa'i bca' ba dang
NK058(si)001:16557: ja dang rgud chang la sogs pa'i btung ba dang
NK058(si)001:16558: li chu dang za ba ber la sogs pa'i bgo
NK058(si)001:16559: ba dang / gzhan yang lha dang mi'i longs spyod
NK058(si)001:16560: 'dod yon lnga dang ldan pa thams cad kun ji
NK058(si)001:16562: mchod yul ye shes kyi lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal
NK058(si)001:16563: ba ni mchod rdzas 'dod yon gyi lha'i dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:16564: thim pa'i tshul gyis dbul zhing bdag yab tu shes
NK058(si)001:16565: pa la rdzas yum du rol pas longs spyod par
NK058(si)001:16566: bya'o // de skad du'ang mnyam sbyor las /
NK058(si)001:16567: sha dang chang du ldan pa yi //
NK058(si)001:16568: bza' ba sna tshogs grub pa ni //
NK058(si)001:16569: dga' ba'i longs spyod skal mchog ste //
NK058(si)001:16570: che ba'i dam pa rab tu 'grub //
NK058(si)001:16572: gsum pa de'i phan yon la gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:16573: thun mong gi dngos grub la'ang 'thad pa'i tshul dgod
NK058(si)001:16574: pa ni phyogs bcu dus bzhir sems can gyi don
NK058(si)001:16576: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi yon tan rmad po
NK058(si)001:16577: che thams cad kyang sems goms pa las gzhan na
NK058(si)001:16579: thun mong gi dngos grub lha srin bran du 'khol
NK058(si)001:16580: ba dang las phran tshegs zhi rgyas dbang drag la
NK058(si)001:16581: sogs 'grub pa lta smos kyang ci dgos zhes pa
NK058(si)001:16582: ni 'thad pa grub pa'i don dngos so //
NK058(si)001:16583: gnyis pa mchog gi dngos grub ni rnal 'byor pa
NK058(si)001:16584: rtogs pa dang ting nge 'dzin las su rung ba
NK058(si)001:16585: rnams kyis mtshan bcas lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po
NK058(si)001:16586: me long nang gi gzugs brnyan lta bu'i bskyed rim
NK058(si)001:16587: rdzogs par gyur cing mtshan med rdzogs pa chen po
NK058(si)001:16588: bya rtsol med pa'i ngang la 'adi'o zhes spros pa'i
NK058(si)001:16589: mtha' dang 'dzin zhen du gsal ba'i yid gnyis gang
NK058(si)001:16590: yang med pa na de bzhin nyid kun tu bzang
NK058(si)001:16592: sku gsum 'du 'bral med pa'i dkyil 'khor chen po
NK058(si)001:16593: phrin las dang bcas pa 'bar zhing thob par 'gyur
NK058(si)001:16594: ro // de'ang chos thams cad sems kyi cho 'phrul yin zhing /
NK058(si)001:16595: sems kyang ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin thabs kyi grub
NK058(si)001:16596: rdzas kyis mtshon nas lam du byas pa las gnas
NK058(si)001:16597: skabs dang mthar thug gi don gnyis rdzogs par gyur
NK058(si)001:16599: dngos po ma lus sems nyid phyir //
NK058(si)001:16600: mtshan nyid bral ba chos kyi dbyings //
NK058(si)001:16601: rang bzhin med pa ye shes lnga //
NK058(si)001:16602: byed pa med par rang snang ba'o //
NK058(si)001:16603: shes rab ting 'dzin thabs dag gis //
NK058(si)001:16605: 'di lta'i lam la gang gnas pa //
NK058(si)001:16606: sangs rgyas ma lus thams cad kyis //
NK058(si)001:16607: phyogs dus kun nas byin gyis rlobs //
NK058(si)001:16610: gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK058(si)001:16611: de skad ces brjod pas phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod
NK058(si)001:16612: sprin rgya mtsho'i mnyes pa'i mchod pa chen pos phyi
NK058(si)001:16613: nang gi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad
NK058(si)001:16615: ye shes gsang ba'i snying po kun la khyab pa'i de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK058(si)001:16616: bla na med pa'i yo byad kyis rgyal ba mchod
NK058(si)001:16617: cing sems can la sbyin pa dam pa bstan pa'i
NK058(si)001:16618: le'u ste bco brgyad pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16620: // spyi don bzhi pa dam tshig dang ldan pas 'grub pa dam tshig gi rim pa la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:16625: mchod sbyin bshad pa de nas bcom ldan 'das dam
NK058(si)001:16626: tshig chen po'i rang bzhin la dgyes pa chen pos
NK058(si)001:16627: gsang sngags 'chang ba'i rnal 'byor pa rnams 'bras bu
NK058(si)001:16628: myur du 'grub cing log par mi ltung bas smon
NK058(si)001:16629: pa'i don yod par bya ba'i phyir gsang chen rgyal
NK058(si)001:16630: po'i dam tshig chen po 'di ched du brjod par
NK058(si)001:16631: mdzad do // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:16635: bsrung bya dam tshig gi rang bzhin /
NK058(si)001:16636: dam tshig dang sdom pa'i khyad par /
NK058(si)001:16637: bslab gsum mi 'gal bar 'dus tshul lo //
NK058(si)001:16645: sa ma ya zhes pa'i sgra las dam tshig tu bshad de /
NK058(si)001:16647: bsrungs na phan yon 'thob pas dam tshig tu gzhag pa ni /
NK058(si)001:16649: dam pa rnams kyi dgongs pa la //
NK058(si)001:16650: dbang dang byin rlabs thob pa yis //
NK058(si)001:16651: dam pa'i tshul bzhin nges spyad na //
NK058(si)001:16652: mi mthun phyogs rnams tshig par 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:16654: nyams na nyes dmigs 'thob pas kyang de skad ces bya ste /
NK058(si)001:16656: dam pa rnams kyi bka' bcag cing //
NK058(si)001:16657: byin rlabs dmod por rang bzhin grub //
NK058(si)001:16659: rdo rje can yang tshig bar 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:16661: thun mong dam baca'i tshul gyis kyang de skad ces bya ste /
NK058(si)001:16663: rgyal ba'i gsang chen rmad kyi chos //
NK058(si)001:16664: ma nyams dam du 'dzin pa'i phyir //
NK058(si)001:16665: bla mas ji skad bstan pa bzhin //
NK058(si)001:16666: dam bcas tshig ni brtan 'dzin pa //
NK058(si)001:16667: dam tshig ces su bshad pa yin //
NK058(si)001:16669: mdor na spang bya spong zhing bsgrub bya sgrub par
NK058(si)001:16670: dam bcas pa las mi nyams par byed pa'i sgo
NK058(si)001:16671: gsum gyi brtson pa'i rang bzhin dge ba cha dang
NK058(si)001:16672: bcas pa la de skad ces bya'o //
NK058(si)001:16673: gnyis pa dbye ba la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:16676: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dbye ba'o //
NK058(si)001:16681: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:16682: de'ang ljon shing gi rtsa ba ltar bsrungs shing bskyed
NK058(si)001:16683: na yon tan gyi 'byung gnas yin zhing ma bsrungs
NK058(si)001:16684: na mi 'byung bas rtsa ba'i dam tshig ces bya
NK058(si)001:16685: la / de bsrung ba'i thabs dang grogs su gyur pa'i phyir yan lag gi dam tshig ces bya'o //
NK058(si)001:16686: gnyis pa de'i dbye ba la bco lnga ste /
NK058(si)001:16692: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcod pa /
NK058(si)001:16693: yang dag pa'i lam du zhugs pa la byams pa /
NK058(si)001:16694: gsang ba'i don gzhan du mi bsgrag pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16696: dkon cog gsum nam yang mi spang ba'o //
NK058(si)001:16697: dbye na gzhi sems can thams cad ye nas dkon mchog gsum du gnas pas mi spang ba dang /
NK058(si)001:16698: lam bskyed rdzogs gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin don
NK058(si)001:16699: dam pa dang kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems gnyis
NK058(si)001:16701: 'bras bu bla na med pa'i sangs rgyas sku gsum /
NK058(si)001:16702: de'i gsung mdo rgyud lung dang rtogs pa'i chos /
NK058(si)001:16703: de'i don la slob pa'i dge 'dun dkon cog gsum mi spang ba'o //
NK058(si)001:16704: de'ang sems can gyi sems nyid ye nas dag pa'i sangs rgyas su bshad de /
NK058(si)001:16705: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas pas //
NK058(si)001:16706: sangs rgyas gzhan du ma 'tshol cig /
NK058(si)001:16708: de'i yi ge 'khor lo las byung ba'i ngag kyang chos su bshad de /
NK058(si)001:16710: +aa li k+aa li las byung ba'i //
NK058(si)001:16711: 'gro ba'i sgra skad dam pa'i chos //
NK058(si)001:16713: bsod nams dang dge ba bsgrub pa'i zhing du gyur pas dge 'dun du'ang bshad de /
NK058(si)001:16715: sbyin sogs bsod nams rnam 'phel zhing //
NK058(si)001:16716: de dge'ang bsgrub pa'i rigs yod phyir //
NK058(si)001:16717: rnam pa gnyis kyis chos 'grub pas //
NK058(si)001:16720: yang kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i ngo bo sems nyid rang bzhin kyis dag pa'i sangs rgyas /
NK058(si)001:16721: bden pa gnyis dang bskyed rdzogs chos /
NK058(si)001:16722: nyams su len pa po dge 'dun te ye shes d+r+wa ba las /
NK058(si)001:16723: bden don bden pa'i rang bzhin de nyid 'dzin //
NK058(si)001:16724: rnal 'byor pa de dkon cog gsum dngos nyid //
NK058(si)001:16726: 'bras bu'i gsum yang rgyud bla ma las /
NK058(si)001:16727: ston pa bstan pa slob don gyis //
NK058(si)001:16728: skyabs gsum rnam par gzhag pa yin //
NK058(si)001:16730: kha cig bla med mi spang ba phyogs re kho nar 'chad pa ni mi 'thad de /
NK058(si)001:16731: dkon cog gi rang bzhin ma shes pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:16732: bla ma bkur ba la'ang gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:16736: 'dren pa'i bla ma ni chos kyi sgor 'dren pa rab byung gi mkhan po lta bu ste /
NK058(si)001:16738: mkhan po mthong ma thag tu stan las ldang bar bya'o //
NK058(si)001:16741: bla ma gnas pa'i sgo glegs la //
NK058(si)001:16742: lag pas dal gyis brdung bar bya //
NK058(si)001:16743: nang zhugs gus pas bla ma la //
NK058(si)001:16744: khams bde mi bde la sogs dri //
NK058(si)001:16746: shes rgyud 'grol ba'i bla ma ni chos 'chad pa'i slob dpon lta bu ste /
NK058(si)001:16747: mdo sde thar pa chen po las /
NK058(si)001:16748: chos smra ba'i dge slong la gus pas bla mar bya ste /
NK058(si)001:16751: chos smra ba ni bla ma'i mchog rab ste //
NK058(si)001:16752: rgyal ba'i mchod sdong chen po de bkur ro //
NK058(si)001:16754: man ngag ston cing lung 'bogs pa'i bla ma ni
NK058(si)001:16755: sems bskyed pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen lta bu ste
NK058(si)001:16757: de ni bdag gis thog ma med pa nas sems bskyed pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen yin te /
NK058(si)001:16759: nyams chags skong ba'i slob dpon ni sdig pa bshags pa'i yul du gyur pa ste /
NK058(si)001:16760: su si ti ka ra'i rgyud las /
NK058(si)001:16761: bshags pa'i yul du gang gyur pa //
NK058(si)001:16762: de yang de yi bla ma yin //
NK058(si)001:16764: dam tshig dbang gi bla ma ni /
NK058(si)001:16766: dbang bskur mchog thob rdo rje yi //
NK058(si)001:16767: bla ma la ni de bzhin gshegs //
NK058(si)001:16769: de dag gi steng du kun gyis dam par bkur zhing /
NK058(si)001:16770: bka' drin cung zad thob pa spyi'i bla ma dang drug tu'ang bshad de /
NK058(si)001:16772: spyi dang 'dren dang dam tshig dang //
NK058(si)001:16773: chag nyams skong dang shes rgyud 'grol //
NK058(si)001:16774: man ngag gi lung gi slob dpon rnams /
NK058(si)001:16776: gnyis pa bkur thabs ni thun mong gi bla ma
NK058(si)001:16777: rnams bsod nams dang mchod pa'i zhing la sogs pa
NK058(si)001:16778: dam pa'i yul du blta bas bdag nyid nad pa
NK058(si)001:16780: nyams su len pa de rgyud la bsten pa /
NK058(si)001:16781: dge ba'i bshes gnyen sman pa mkhas pa'i tshul gyis bsten te /
NK058(si)001:16783: rigs kyi bu khyod kyis bdag nyid la nad pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK058(si)001:16785: nyams su len pa la nad nye bar 'tsho ba dang /
NK058(si)001:16786: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la sman pa mkhas pa'i 'du shes rab tu bskyed par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:16788: khyad par du gsang sngags rdo rje'i slob dpon la tshul gsum gyis bkur te /
NK058(si)001:16789: de'ang dkon cog bzhi par gsungs pa ni /
NK058(si)001:16791: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun dang //
NK058(si)001:16792: slob dpon yang ni bzhi pa yin //
NK058(si)001:16794: sangs rgyas dang mnyam par yang rnam snang sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las /
NK058(si)001:16795: sangs rgyas kun dang bla ma mnyam //
NK058(si)001:16797: lhag par yang thugs kyi rgyud dpal gsang ba 'dus pa las /
NK058(si)001:16798: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad pas //
NK058(si)001:16799: bla ma'i ba spu khung gcig mchog /
NK058(si)001:16800: ces pa'i tshul gyis ji ltar mnyes pa'i rim pas bkur bar bya'o //
NK058(si)001:16801: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcod pa la'ang gnyis
NK058(si)001:16802: las sngags ni lha so so'i dngos grub sgrub pa'i
NK058(si)001:16803: thabs kyi rim pa ste lha'i de kho na nyid
NK058(si)001:16804: la sogs pa lngas bzlas pa dang /
NK058(si)001:16805: phyag rgya ni dngos grub bsgrub pa'i grogs kyi yan lag ste /
NK058(si)001:16806: bsam pa chos kyi phyag rgya /
NK058(si)001:16807: brjod pa dam tshig gi phyag brgya /
NK058(si)001:16808: bsgyur ba las kyi phyag rgya /
NK058(si)001:16809: lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po'o //
NK058(si)001:16810: rgyun mi gcad pa rab chu bo'i rgyun lta bu /
NK058(si)001:16811: 'bring nyin mtshan gyi thun la gnas pa /
NK058(si)001:16812: tha ma'ang nya stong brgyad la sogs pa zla ba
NK058(si)001:16813: dang lo'i dus su ma chag par byed pa ste
NK058(si)001:16815: rab kyis chu bo'i rgyun bzhin nam //
NK058(si)001:16816: nyin gsum mtshan gsum nyin mtshan du //
NK058(si)001:16817: ma yengs pa yi ngang gis bzla //
NK058(si)001:16818: 'bring gis zla gcig dus drug dang //
NK058(si)001:16819: dus bzhi bar du mi gcad cing //
NK058(si)001:16820: tha mar brtson pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK058(si)001:16821: zla re'am ra ba'i dus dag tu //
NK058(si)001:16822: brtson par 'bad de mi byed pa //
NK058(si)001:16823: byang chub sa bon brlag pa yin //
NK058(si)001:16824: tshogs dang gtor ma'ang de bzhin te //
NK058(si)001:16827: yang dag pa'i lam du zhugs pa la byams pa ni mched la brtse gdung bya ba ste /
NK058(si)001:16828: spyir mched lcam rnam pa drug ste /
NK058(si)001:16829: sems can thams cad ye gdod ma nas bdag gi spun yin pa'i phyir spyi'i mched do //
NK058(si)001:16830: sangs rgyas kyi chos la zhugs so cog ni bstan pa gcig pa'i mched do //
NK058(si)001:16831: lta spyod gcig pa ni mthun pa'i mched do //
NK058(si)001:16832: bla ma gcig pa ni mdzes pa'i mched do //
NK058(si)001:16833: chos lhan cig tu nyan pa ni nye ba'i mched do //
NK058(si)001:16834: dbang lhan cig tu zhus pa ni 'dres pa'i mched de rdo rje'i spun no //
NK058(si)001:16835: 'dir ni spyir thar ba'i lam dang theg pa chen por zhugs pa la brtse ba ste /
NK058(si)001:16837: byang chub sems brtan theg chen zhugs la byams //
NK058(si)001:16839: khyad par du rdo rje'i spun la brtse gdung bya ba ste /
NK058(si)001:16841: rdo rje'i spun la gdung sems kyang //
NK058(si)001:16843: yang dag lam du zhugs pa la //
NK058(si)001:16844: rngam dang bcas kyi sems tsam yang //
NK058(si)001:16845: rtag tu spang bar bya ba yin //
NK058(si)001:16846: brtse zhing gdung ba'i shugs phyung la //
NK058(si)001:16847: gcig la gcig ni mig bzhin blta //
NK058(si)001:16848: mdor na srog la'ang mi chags par //
NK058(si)001:16849: spun dang ming sring dgos pa bsgrub //
NK058(si)001:16850: ci phyir rdo rje spun rnams ni //
NK058(si)001:16851: 'di nas byang chub bar dag tu //
NK058(si)001:16855: gsang ba mi bsgrags pa'i dam tshig kyang gsang sngags
NK058(si)001:16856: kyi lta sgom spyod 'bras zab mo rnams snod ma
NK058(si)001:16857: yin pa'i 'gro ba la shin tu gsang ba ste
NK058(si)001:16859: spyi dang bar gsang bzhi bzhi dang //
NK058(si)001:16860: 'os dang gnyer gtad gdams pa bcu //
NK058(si)001:16861: lta zab spyod pa barlang po dang //
NK058(si)001:16862: lha ming gzungs dang grub rtags rnams //
NK058(si)001:16863: spyir gsang rnam pa bzhir bshad do //
NK058(si)001:16864: sgrub pa'i gnas dus grogs dang rdzas //
NK058(si)001:16865: bar du gsang nas bsgrub par bya //
NK058(si)001:16866: gsang bar 'os pa'i dam tshig ni //
NK058(si)001:16867: phud dang gtor ma tshogs dag dang //
NK058(si)001:16868: ban+d+ha phur pa mar me'i snod //
NK058(si)001:16869: rdzas dang lag cha dkyil 'khor rnams //
NK058(si)001:16870: skye bos mthong bar yongs mi bya //
NK058(si)001:16871: dril bu rnge'u chung la sogs sgra //
NK058(si)001:16872: skye bos thos par yongs mi brdung /
NK058(si)001:16873: grogs kyi skyon dang mtshang rnams dang //
NK058(si)001:16874: sems can kun gyi ngan spyod rnams //
NK058(si)001:16875: kun la gnod pa'i spyod pas rnams //
NK058(si)001:16876: shin tu gsang na byang chub rgyu //
NK058(si)001:16877: gnyer gtad pa ni gdams pa ste //
NK058(si)001:16878: sngar bshad slob dpon mched kyis so //
NK058(si)001:16883: grub pa'i rtags te spyir gsang bzhi /
NK058(si)001:16888: phud dang gtor ma la sogs pa mthong du mi rung ba'i dam rdzas rnams gsang bar 'os pa /
NK058(si)001:16889: bla ma dang mched lcam gyis 'di ltar gyis shig
NK058(si)001:16890: la sogs pa gnyer du gtad pa ste bcu po
NK058(si)001:16893: dam nyams dam las log pa dang //
NK058(si)001:16894: dam med dkyil 'khor ma mthong dang //
NK058(si)001:16898: snod ma yin pa'i gang zag la //
NK058(si)001:16899: dus dang gnas skabs kun tu gsang //
NK058(si)001:16900: snod dang ldan pa rnams la yang //
NK058(si)001:16901: dbang ma thob par bshad pa min //
NK058(si)001:16903: ji ltar gsang na de las /
NK058(si)001:16904: sems kyis bstan par mi bsam zhing //
NK058(si)001:16905: lus kyis thams cad sbas la spyad //
NK058(si)001:16906: ngag gi rdo rje'i lce yod kyang //
NK058(si)001:16907: brjod par bya ba ma yin no //
NK058(si)001:16909: de ltar rtsa ba'i dam tshig gi lha mi spang ba dang /
NK058(si)001:16910: dngos grub kyi 'byung gnas bla ma bkur ba dang /
NK058(si)001:16911: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad pa ni yon
NK058(si)001:16912: tan khyad par can sgrub pa'i dam tshig yin la
NK058(si)001:16913: / de'i yan lag tu yang dag pa'i lam du zhugs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:16914: mched lcam la gus pa ni bla ma'i thugs dang 'gal ba bsrung zhing /
NK058(si)001:16915: gsang ba gzhan la mi smra ba ni lha dang
NK058(si)001:16916: sngags dang phyag rgya'i de nyid dang 'gal ba bsrung
NK058(si)001:16917: ba yin no // kha cig lha dang sngags phyag rgya gnyis sgrub pa /
NK058(si)001:16918: de dag gi thugs dang 'gal ba bsrung ba'i phyir bla ma dang mched la gus pa /
NK058(si)001:16919: gsang ba mi smra ba gsum srung ba'o zhes pa ni ma yin te /
NK058(si)001:16921: sgrub pa'i dam tshig chen po ni //
NK058(si)001:16922: lha dang bla ma mi spang zhing //
NK058(si)001:16923: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad //
NK058(si)001:16925: dngos grub sgrub pa'i rtsa ba bla ma yin la /
NK058(si)001:16926: de mnyes na dngos grub 'byung ba de las /
NK058(si)001:16927: mchod pa thams cad yongs spangs la //
NK058(si)001:16928: bla ma mchod pa yang dag brtsam //
NK058(si)001:16929: de mnyes pa las kun mkhyen gyi //
NK058(si)001:16930: yon tan mchog ni ma lus 'byung //
NK058(si)001:16933: dkyil 'khor dbang phyug bla ma nyid //
NK058(si)001:16934: ces pas lha'i dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo bla mar gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK058(si)001:16935: de mnyes pa 'ba' zhig bsgrub dgos pas /
NK058(si)001:16936: sgrub pa'i dam tshig kho nar bshad pa'i lung dang 'gal lo //
NK058(si)001:16937: de ltar lnga po yang sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin gsum gsum las ma 'das pas /
NK058(si)001:16938: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig gsum du gnas te /
NK058(si)001:16939: dper na bla med mi spang ba'ang lus kyis bkur zhing /
NK058(si)001:16941: sems kyis gus par bya ba dang /
NK058(si)001:16942: bla ma la'ang tshul de dang mched la'ang sgo gsum gus pa dang /
NK058(si)001:16943: sngags dang phyag rgya'i dam tshig la'ang sgo gsum tshang ba dang /
NK058(si)001:16944: gsang ba yang sgo gsum gyi bya bas gsang zhing sbed pa'o //
NK058(si)001:16945: kha cig bla ma dang mched lcam la gus pa
NK058(si)001:16946: ni gzhi ma lus kyi bya ba yin pas sku'i
NK058(si)001:16947: dam tshig lha mi spang zhing sngags dang phyag rgya
NK058(si)001:16948: rgyun mi gcod pa ni bzlas brjod kyi yan lag
NK058(si)001:16950: gsang ba mi smra ba ni yid la brnag par
NK058(si)001:16951: bya ba yin pas thugs kyi dam tshig go zer
NK058(si)001:16952: ba de yang rigs par ma mthong ste /
NK058(si)001:16953: 'don pa bsgyur na mtshungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:16954: gnyis pa yan lag gi dam tshig bcu la /
NK058(si)001:16959: de'ang rang bzhin shes pas mi spang ba /
NK058(si)001:16960: thabs kyis zin na lam gyi grogs yin pas mi spang ba /
NK058(si)001:16961: sku dang ye shes yin pas mi spang ba'o //
NK058(si)001:16963: sangs rgyas kyi rigs sam gdung yin pas mi spang ba ni /
NK058(si)001:16965: rmongs pa'i sems kyi de bzhin nyid ni rdo rje sems dpa'i de bzhin nyid do //
NK058(si)001:16966: rdo rje sems dpa'i de bzhin nyid ni de kho na nyid do //
NK058(si)001:16968: dri ma med par grags pa las kyang /
NK058(si)001:16969: nyon mongs pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i gdung ngo //
NK058(si)001:16970: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK058(si)001:16971: rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa yin pas spang
NK058(si)001:16972: blang med pa'i phyir mi spang ba la'ang kun rdzob
NK058(si)001:16973: tu nyon mongs pa smig rgyu dang 'dra ste /
NK058(si)001:16974: skad cig gis mi rtag pas rang gis rang spangs shing /
NK058(si)001:16975: de'ang snang la ngos bzung gi dngos po dang ngo
NK058(si)001:16976: bo bden pa'i chos su ma grub pa'i phyir spang
NK058(si)001:16977: byar med de / rdo rje las /
NK058(si)001:16978: nyon mongs rnams ni sgyu 'dra ngo bos stong //
NK058(si)001:16979: rang gis mi rtag rang bzhin shes pas grol //
NK058(si)001:16981: don dam par gang gi dngos por yang ma grub
NK058(si)001:16982: cing kun tu btsal na mi rnyed pas kyang spang
NK058(si)001:16983: du med de / phyir mi ldog pa 'khor lo'i mdo las /
NK058(si)001:16984: ma rig nam mkha' ji bzhin te //
NK058(si)001:16985: chos rnams thams cad mtshan nyid med //
NK058(si)001:16986: 'dod chags med cing zhe sdang med //
NK058(si)001:16987: nga rgyal dang ni phrag dog kun //
NK058(si)001:16988: sgyu 'dra ngo bo nyid med de //
NK058(si)001:16989: yod med mi dmigs rten dang bral //
NK058(si)001:16992: nyon mongs rnams ni yul na mi gnas phyogs na
NK058(si)001:16993: mi gnas dbang sogs la min de dag bar na'ang
NK058(si)001:16995: ye nas stong pa'i dngos 'di la //
NK058(si)001:16996: thob pa ci yod shor ci yod //
NK058(si)001:16997: mi dgar ci yod dgar ci yod //
NK058(si)001:16998: thams cad nam mkha' 'dra bar ni //
NK058(si)001:16999: bdag 'dras yongs su gzung bar gyis //
NK058(si)001:17001: gnyis pa thabs kyis zin na lam gyis grogs yin pas mi spang ba ni /
NK058(si)001:17002: nyon mongs pa lnga ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin yin la /
NK058(si)001:17003: de nyid man ngag gis nyams su blangs pas nye lam du 'gyur te /
NK058(si)001:17005: nyon mongs lam ni dag pa che //
NK058(si)001:17006: thabs kyi 'dod yon rgyan gyi mchog /
NK058(si)001:17007: thams cad thams cad rol pa yis //
NK058(si)001:17008: myur du he ru ka dpal 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:17010: tshul 'di mdo sde las kyang gsungs te /
NK058(si)001:17012: ji ltar grong khyer rnams kyi mi gtsang lud //
NK058(si)001:17013: de ni bu ram shing ba'i zhing la phan //
NK058(si)001:17014: de bzhin byang chub sems dpa'i nyon mongs lud //
NK058(si)001:17015: de ni rgyal ba'i chos kyi zhing la phan //
NK058(si)001:17018: thabs chen rnams dang ldan pa la //
NK058(si)001:17019: nyon mongs byang chub yan lag 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:17021: gzhan yang spang bya nyon mongs pa med na spong
NK058(si)001:17022: byed gnyen po mi 'byung bas kyang spong bar mi
NK058(si)001:17023: rigs pa dang / nyon mongs pa'i chos can yod
NK058(si)001:17024: na de rang gis ngo bos stong pa'i chos nyid
NK058(si)001:17025: yod pas kyang chos nyid mngon du bya ba'i phyir
NK058(si)001:17027: nyon mongs pa la brten nas sems can gyi don
NK058(si)001:17028: 'grub pa'i yan lag du 'gyur bas kyang mi spang
NK058(si)001:17029: ba yin no // 'o na nyon mongs pa ma
NK058(si)001:17030: spangs na yon tan mi skye zhing sangs rgyas mi
NK058(si)001:17032: lam dang 'bras bu'i yon tan ni nyon mongs pa'i rgyu kho na las 'thob ste /
NK058(si)001:17033: ye shes yin zhing de goms par byas pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:17034: ngan 'gro la sogs par brgyud cing 'ching ba ma yin nam zhe na /
NK058(si)001:17035: nyon mongs pa'i rang bzhin shes nas goms na de'i
NK058(si)001:17036: nyes pas mi gos shing bde 'gro'i lus dang 'bras
NK058(si)001:17038: kha cig na re nyon mongs pa lam du byed pa na thabs kyi zin dgos sam mi dgos /
NK058(si)001:17039: dgos na nyon mongs pa lam du byas pa ma yin te /
NK058(si)001:17040: thabs lam du byas pa'i phyir /
NK058(si)001:17041: mi dgos na tha lam pa dang khyad med par thal lo zhe na /
NK058(si)001:17043: nas la zan byed par 'dod mod /
NK058(si)001:17044: barngo ba dang btags pas byas na nas kyi zan du'ang mi 'gyur te /
NK058(si)001:17045: phye'i zan yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK058(si)001:17046: ma byas na zan du'ang mi 'grub bo zhes pa 'di la lan ci yod /
NK058(si)001:17047: de'ang rgyu nas la rkyen barngo ba dang btags pas zan du 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK058(si)001:17048: 'dir yang rgyu nyon mongs pa la rkyen thabs kyi lam du byed pa kho na'o //
NK058(si)001:17049: 'di ltar nyon mongs pa'i dngos po gcig la nyan
NK058(si)001:17050: rang gis spang byar mthong ba dang byang chub sems
NK058(si)001:17051: dpas spyad byar mthong ba dang /
NK058(si)001:17052: gsang sngags thun mong bas dag byar mthong ba dang /
NK058(si)001:17053: thun mong ma yin pas blang byar mthong ba ni
NK058(si)001:17054: dper na gser las byas pa'i rang bzhin gcig la
NK058(si)001:17055: / chol zangs su byas pa'i tshe btsog pa dang /
NK058(si)001:17056: gzhong par byas pa'i tshe gtsang ba dang /
NK058(si)001:17057: gdu bur byas pa'i tshe rgyan dang /
NK058(si)001:17058: lha'i sku gzugs su byas pa'i tshe mchod pa'i rten du byed pa bzhin du /
NK058(si)001:17059: rkyen gyis theg pa so so'i de ltar mthong yang
NK058(si)001:17060: ngo bo ye nas dag pa'i ye shes yin pas
NK058(si)001:17061: / gzhi lam 'bras bu'i chos su nyon mongs pa
NK058(si)001:17062: de nyid 'gyur ba'i spang bar bya ba ma yin
NK058(si)001:17063: pa'i rgyu mtshan 'thad pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK058(si)001:17064: gsum pa sku dang ye shes yin pas mi spang ba ni /
NK058(si)001:17065: dam tshig nyer brgyad pa las /
NK058(si)001:17066: phrag dog la sogs nyon mongs lnga rnams ni //
NK058(si)001:17067: ye nas rigs lnga'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir //
NK058(si)001:17069: gti mug chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes de bzhin
NK058(si)001:17070: gshegs pa'i rigs te rnam par snang mdzad kyi dam
NK058(si)001:17071: tshig go // zhe sdang me long lta bu'i ye
NK058(si)001:17072: shes rdo rje'i rigs te mi bskyod pa'i dam tshig
NK058(si)001:17073: tshig go // go // nga rgyal mnyam pa nyid
NK058(si)001:17074: kyi ye shes rin po che'i rigs te rin chen
NK058(si)001:17076: 'dod chags so sor rtog pa'i ye shes pad+ma'i rigs te snang ba mtha' yas kyi dam tshig go //
NK058(si)001:17077: phrag dog bya ba grub pa'i ye shes las kyi rigs te don yod grub pa'i dam tshig go //
NK058(si)001:17078: des na 'gro ba'i sems so cog tu 'char ba
NK058(si)001:17079: nyon mongs lngar snang dus nas sku dang ye shes
NK058(si)001:17080: su grub pa'i phyir mi spang bar gdams so //
NK058(si)001:17081: gnyis pa dang du blang ba'i dam tshig lnga ni bdud rtsi lnga ste /
NK058(si)001:17082: de'ang ye nas blang dor med pa'i chos nyid kyi rol pa yin pas kyang dang du blang ste /
NK058(si)001:17084: bdud rtsi ye nas dag pa'i chos //
NK058(si)001:17085: blang dor med pa kun las 'das //
NK058(si)001:17086: ye bsrung chen po'i dam tshig tu //
NK058(si)001:17087: mkhas pas dang du blang bar bya //
NK058(si)001:17089: rigs lnga'i rang bzhin yin pas kyang dang du blang dgos te /
NK058(si)001:17091: bdud rtsi lnga ni rigs lnga'i dngos //
NK058(si)001:17092: dri chen dri chu byang chub sems //
NK058(si)001:17094: dngos grub sgrub pa'i rdzas yin pas kyang dang du blang ste /
NK058(si)001:17096: sha chen dam tshig chen po ni //
NK058(si)001:17098: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK058(si)001:17099: yang bdud rtsi lnga dang sha lnga brten na mkha'
NK058(si)001:17100: 'gro 'du zhing dngos grub nye bas kyang dang du
NK058(si)001:17102: ba lang khyi dang rta sha dang //
NK058(si)001:17103: mi sha glang chen sha la sogs //
NK058(si)001:17104: zos na yon tan thams cad 'grub //
NK058(si)001:17105: bdag cag rnams kyi dam tshig lags //
NK058(si)001:17107: sngon gyi rgyal ba grangs med kyis //
NK058(si)001:17108: brtul zhugs 'di lnga gtsor spyad na //
NK058(si)001:17109: dam tshig dam par bzung bas na //
NK058(si)001:17110: sngon gyi dam tshig yin par grags //
NK058(si)001:17111: zhes pas brtul zhugs spyod pa'i grogs su gyur pas kyang dang du blang bar bya ba yin no //
NK058(si)001:17112: gnyis pa yan lag gi dbye ba ni sum brgya drug cu ste /
NK058(si)001:17113: de'ang dam tshig ni lha'i rang bzhin yin la /
NK058(si)001:17114: lha thams cad kyi rtsa ba ni thabs dang shes
NK058(si)001:17115: rab yin pas rtsa ba'i bla med mi spang ba
NK058(si)001:17116: la sogs pa lnga po'i gang rung gcig la'ang rtsa
NK058(si)001:17118: de gnyis la sku gsung thugs su phye bas drug /
NK058(si)001:17119: de dag la'ang sku gsang thugs yon tan phrin las lnga lnga ste sum cu /
NK058(si)001:17120: rtsa ba'i thabs shes gnyis bsnan pas sum cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK058(si)001:17121: de ltar lnga ga las phye bas brgya drug cu'o //
NK058(si)001:17122: yan lag gi dam tshig nyis brgya ni yan lag
NK058(si)001:17123: gi bcu'i 'dod chags mi spang ba lta bu gcig
NK058(si)001:17124: la'ang thabs dang shes rab gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:17125: thabs la ye shes lnga dang yul lnga ste bcu /
NK058(si)001:17126: shes rab la'ang ye shes lnga dang yul lnga ste bcu phrag gnyis la nyi shu'o //
NK058(si)001:17127: de ltar nyi shu tshan pa bcu la nyis bargya'o //
NK058(si)001:17128: rong pa ni yan lag gi dam tshig ni yan lag nas dbye bar bya ste /
NK058(si)001:17129: gcig la'ang sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi yan lag rnam pa lnga dang /
NK058(si)001:17130: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos gzhi gsum yang de nyid du zhig ste yan lag gi gzhi med /
NK058(si)001:17131: rtsa ba thabs dang shes rab gnyis kyang thabs shes rab dang ldan /
NK058(si)001:17132: shes rab thabs dang ldan pas rtsa ba gnyis po zhig ste yan lag bzhir 'gyur bas /
NK058(si)001:17133: de yang sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i cha shas su 'gyur pas na /
NK058(si)001:17134: rtsa ba'i 'phro gzhi med de yan lag dang cha
NK058(si)001:17135: shas nyi shu nyi shur 'gyur ro zhes dkon cog
NK058(si)001:17137: dam tshig 'di dag ni yon tan gyi cha chas dbye ba yin gyi /
NK058(si)001:17138: mtshan nyid tha dad pa'i rnam grangs ni so sor bshad pa med /
NK058(si)001:17140: gsum pa bsam gyis mi khyab par dbye ba ni
NK058(si)001:17141: sems can gyi rtog tshogs ji snyed pa'i gnyen por
NK058(si)001:17142: dam tshig gi dbye ba'ang de snyed yin pas grangs
NK058(si)001:17143: 'di kho na'o zhes gcig tu chad pa med de
NK058(si)001:17145: dam tshig rnam pa'i grangs dag ni //
NK058(si)001:17146: sems can grangs dang log rtog grangs //
NK058(si)001:17147: rtog 'dul gnyen por dam tshig grangs //
NK058(si)001:17148: rgyal ba nyid kyis brjod las 'das //
NK058(si)001:17150: gsum pa dam tshig bsrungs ba'i phan yon ni /
NK058(si)001:17151: gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi don thams cad 'grub pa ste /
NK058(si)001:17153: gsang sngags rdo rje'i dam la gnas //
NK058(si)001:17154: de yis smon pa kun 'grub cing //
NK058(si)001:17155: lha rnams kyis kyang rtag tu bsrung //
NK058(si)001:17156: rgyal ba rgyal mchog sras bcas kyis //
NK058(si)001:17157: bu bzhin dgongs pa dam pa mdzad //
NK058(si)001:17158: ting 'dzin yon tan dpag yas shing //
NK058(si)001:17159: kun bzang rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK058(si)001:17161: bzhi pa ma bsrungs pa'i nyes dmigs ni /
NK058(si)001:17162: rang nyid kyi legs pa las nyams shing gzhan la nyes pa ngang gis sbyin pa ste /
NK058(si)001:17164: dam tshig las ni 'das gyur na //
NK058(si)001:17165: 'di phyir bde legs nyams pa dang //
NK058(si)001:17166: yid du mi 'ong sna tshogs myong //
NK058(si)001:17167: sa spyod me yis sdug bsngal la //
NK058(si)001:17168: bskal pa bye ba grangs med gnas //
NK058(si)001:17171: ji ltar 'o ma rul pa dag /
NK058(si)001:17172: rul pas 'o ma kun rul ltar //
NK058(si)001:17173: rnal 'byor nyams gyur gcig gis ni //
NK058(si)001:17174: rnal 'byor can kun ma rungs byed //
NK058(si)001:17177: de'ang nyan thos ltar ma yin gyi /
NK058(si)001:17178: gsang sngags ni gsor rung ba'i thabs yod de /
NK058(si)001:17180: dam tshig nyams par gyur pa na //
NK058(si)001:17181: mgon btsun mnyes pa'i don rtogs na //
NK058(si)001:17182: de nyid bskang ba'i gnas su 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:17183: bla ma spun la smad gyur na //
NK058(si)001:17184: tshe 'di nyid la mnyes byas te //
NK058(si)001:17185: mthol bshags drag pos 'gyod byas na //
NK058(si)001:17186: de ni bskang ba'i mchog tu 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:17187: gal te bdag gam bla ma spun //
NK058(si)001:17188: ma bskang bar du tshe 'phos na //
NK058(si)001:17189: de ni bskang ba'i tshad las 'das //
NK058(si)001:17190: gsung gi tha tshig ral gyur na //
NK058(si)001:17191: rdo rje chos su bdag bsgom ste //
NK058(si)001:17193: thugs kyi tha tshig ral gyur na //
NK058(si)001:17194: rdo rje sems dpar bdag bsgom la //
NK058(si)001:17195: lo gsum bar du mi smra bar //
NK058(si)001:17196: bsam gtan sbyor ba rab tu bya //
NK058(si)001:17197: yan lag tha tshig ral gyur na //
NK058(si)001:17198: so so rang rang rigs kyis bskang //
NK058(si)001:17199: zhes pas sku gsung thugs kyi nyams chag gi gtso
NK058(si)001:17200: bo sgo gsum dang sbyar la brtson pas bskang bshags
NK058(si)001:17202: 'di ni thabs kyi dam pa ste 'og ma dag las 'phags so //
NK058(si)001:17203: de'ang nyan thos kyi sdom khrims ni 'chab sems ma
NK058(si)001:17204: skyes na lan bdun gso bar snang zhing skyes na
NK058(si)001:17205: lan gcig la'ang gsor mi rung bas rdza be'u chag
NK058(si)001:17206: pa dang 'dra'o // byang chub sems dpa' ni rin
NK058(si)001:17207: po che'i snod chags pa dang 'dra ste dge ba'i
NK058(si)001:17208: bshes gnyen la brten nas nyams pa gso bar rung
NK058(si)001:17209: pa dang 'dra'o // ste / mgar ba mkhas pas
NK058(si)001:17210: snga ma las lhag pa'i snod byar rung ba bzhin
NK058(si)001:17211: pa dang 'dra'o // ste / no // gsang sngags
NK058(si)001:17212: ni rin po che'i snod gzhom pa dang 'dra ste
NK058(si)001:17213: rang gi stobs kyis gsor rung bas na /
NK058(si)001:17214: mgar ba mi dgos par rang gi rtsol bas gzhom pa bsrang du yod pa dang 'dra'o //
NK058(si)001:17215: gnyis pa dam tshig dang sdom pa'i khyad par ni /
NK058(si)001:17216: de'ang rang gi rgyud sdom pa'i cha nas sdom pa'ang yin la /
NK058(si)001:17217: sangs rgyas kyi gsang ba'i rdo rje gsum 'dzin zhing
NK058(si)001:17218: mi nyams par byed pas dam tshig kyang yin te
NK058(si)001:17219: / bum pa gcig nyid byas pa'ang yin la mi rtag pa'ang yin pa bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:17220: des na ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad de /
NK058(si)001:17222: de ltar sum brgya drug cu rnams //
NK058(si)001:17223: bdag gi rdo rje mchog gsum pos //
NK058(si)001:17224: log par mi ltung sdom pa'i dngos //
NK058(si)001:17225: sa gzhi lta bur gsungs pa yin //
NK058(si)001:17228: chos kun ye nas dag pa'i phyir //
NK058(si)001:17229: log rtog ye nas rnam par dag /
NK058(si)001:17230: de bas sdom pa rnam par dag /
NK058(si)001:17231: dam tshig 'di ni rmad po che //
NK058(si)001:17233: de'ang sdom pa'i ngos nas gzhal na gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:17236: rig pa 'dzin pa'i sdom pa ste /
NK058(si)001:17238: so so thar dang byang chub sems //
NK058(si)001:17242: dge slong byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK058(si)001:17245: de'ang so so thar pa'i sdom pa ni rang nyid
NK058(si)001:17246: gcig pu zhi bde 'dod pas ji srid 'tsho'i bar
NK058(si)001:17247: du rigs bdun gang yang rung ba bsrung zhing /
NK058(si)001:17248: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa gnyis don du sdom pa'i tshul khrims kyis rgyud sdoms /
NK058(si)001:17249: dge ba chos sdud kyis rtogs pa dang yon tan khyad par can rnams bsgrub /
NK058(si)001:17250: sems can don byed kyis gzhan la phan 'dogs pa'o //
NK058(si)001:17251: rig pa 'dzin pa'i sdom pas gzhan don rlabs po
NK058(si)001:17252: che sgrub cing nyon mongs ye shes su bsgyur ba
NK058(si)001:17254: de ltar sdom pa gsum po yang //
NK058(si)001:17255: rang dang gzhan don phan pa che //
NK058(si)001:17257: dam tshig ni rdo rje gsum gyi rang bzhin nyams
NK058(si)001:17258: pa med par bsrungs pas gzhan la phan pa 'ba'
NK058(si)001:17259: zhig lhur len pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:17260: gsum pa bslab gsum mi 'gal bar 'dus tshul bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:17264: 'di ltar nyan thos kyi phas pham pa bzhi bsrung bya'i rtsa ba dang /
NK058(si)001:17265: de'i yan lag chang mi 'thung ba la sogs pa yin zhing /
NK058(si)001:17266: byang chub sems dpa'i sems can la 'tshe ba cha
NK058(si)001:17267: dang bcas pa las ldog pa ltar snang bas sdom
NK058(si)001:17268: pa gsum tshang ba dang 'gal lo snyam na /
NK058(si)001:17269: mi 'gal bar ston pa la gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:17270: dang po nyan thos kyi so so thar pa'i sdom pa dang mi 'gal ba'i tshul ni /
NK058(si)001:17271: de'ang srog gcod pa'i pham par gyur pa la /
NK058(si)001:17272: gzhi mi yin pa bsam pa de nyid las gzhan
NK058(si)001:17273: du ma 'khrul par zhe sdang rang ga mas gsod
NK058(si)001:17274: par rtsom pa / dngos gzhi mtshon la sogs par srog gi dbang po 'gag pa /
NK058(si)001:17275: rjes yi rang ba ste chos bzhi tshang dgos pa la /
NK058(si)001:17276: 'dir sgrol ba'i skabs su rnam pa h'u du gsal
NK058(si)001:17277: zhing ngo bo ma skyes pa yin pas mi dang
NK058(si)001:17278: mi las gzhan dud 'gro la sogs pa'i 'gro ba
NK058(si)001:17279: pha ma yin pas gzhi'i yan lag ma tshang ngo
NK058(si)001:17280: // de'i sdug bsngal dang bral 'dod kyi snying rje
NK058(si)001:17281: yod kyi gsod sems rang ga ma med pas bsam
NK058(si)001:17282: pa'i yan lag kyang ma tshang ngo //
NK058(si)001:17283: gsad bya dang gsod byed du 'dzin pa med pas
NK058(si)001:17284: srog kyang med cing de gcad ba'ang med pas dngos
NK058(si)001:17285: gzhi'i yan lag kyang ma tshang ngo //
NK058(si)001:17286: rjes zhe sdang gis kun nas bslang ba'i yi rang
NK058(si)001:17287: med pas yongs su rdzogs pa'i yan lag kyang ma
NK058(si)001:17288: tshang bas nyes pa gang yang med do //
NK058(si)001:17289: de bzhin du ma byin par len pa'i tshe'ang gzhi mis bdag tu bzung ba'i rdzas dgos pa la /
NK058(si)001:17290: 'dir bdag gzhan gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs pas
NK058(si)001:17291: rang snang gi rdzas rmi lam lta bu len pa'i
NK058(si)001:17292: phyir dang / bsam pa brku ba'i sems dgos pa las /
NK058(si)001:17293: 'dir rang sems kyi snang ba tsam la rang snang rol gyis brku sems med pa dang /
NK058(si)001:17294: dngos gzhi rin thang tshang ba spros te bdag gir byed pa las /
NK058(si)001:17295: de yang ma tshang ste sgyu ma dang rmi lam
NK058(si)001:17296: ltar gnyis su med pas spros pa med pa dang
NK058(si)001:17297: / rjes thob blo dgos pa las /
NK058(si)001:17298: thob bya dang thob byed du zhen pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:17299: mi tshangs par spyod pa'i pham par gyur pa la yang /
NK058(si)001:17300: gzhi mi'i bud med la sogs pa dgos pa las /
NK058(si)001:17302: dngos po zag byed du nor bu bcug nas bgas rim 'das pa dgos pa las /
NK058(si)001:17303: rdo rje dang pad+mara gsal bas de gnyis rang mtshan pa ma tshang ba dang /
NK058(si)001:17304: bsam pa ma 'khrul bas bde ba myong bar 'dod pa yang /
NK058(si)001:17305: dkyil 'khor gsum du shes pas bsam pa'i yan lag ma tshang ba'i phyir nyes pa med de /
NK058(si)001:17306: brdzun du smra ba yang pha rol po'i 'gro ba
NK058(si)001:17307: la 'du shes gzhan du bsgyur bas lha la sogs
NK058(si)001:17308: pa ma mthong bzhin du mthong ngo zhes pa la
NK058(si)001:17310: chos thams cad rdzun snyam du shes nas gzhan la
NK058(si)001:17311: phan pa'i yan lag tu smras pa'i phyir na nyes
NK058(si)001:17312: pa med do // de bzhin du chang btung ba'ang
NK058(si)001:17313: bdud rtsir bsgyur ba'i phyir na longs spyod du mi
NK058(si)001:17314: rung bar bshad pa dang mi 'gal lo //
NK058(si)001:17315: de thams cad kyi skabs su bdag nyid dge slong yin pa /
NK058(si)001:17317: 'du shes gzhan du ma gyur pa rnams dgos pa las /
NK058(si)001:17318: 'dir lha'i dkyil 'khor du gnas gyur pa'i phyir nyan
NK058(si)001:17319: thos kyi so so thar pa'i sdom pa dang 'gal
NK058(si)001:17320: ba med do // gnyis pa byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa dang 'gal ba med de /
NK058(si)001:17321: gzhan la phan 'dod kyi snying rje dang thabs khyad par can gyis zin pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:17322: de gnyis dang ldan pa ni sems dpa' rnams la'ang gnang ba yin te /
NK058(si)001:17324: yang dag sems can don 'gyur ba'i //
NK058(si)001:17325: thabs de rgyal sras bslab pa'i mchog /
NK058(si)001:17326: sprin las char chen 'bab pa yis //
NK058(si)001:17327: lo tog phun sum tshogs par byed //
NK058(si)001:17329: gnyis pa 'dus tshul la'ang gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:17330: nyan thos kyi tshul ni gtso bor rang don sgrub
NK058(si)001:17331: pa'i sdom pa de yang 'dir rnal 'byor pas rang
NK058(si)001:17332: gi sdug bsngal las thar pa'i phyir rgyud sdom par
NK058(si)001:17333: 'dus te / srog gcod dus nyid na sems kyi
NK058(si)001:17334: zhe sdang la sogs pa'i mi dge ba med pas
NK058(si)001:17335: rang gi zag pa rang mtshan pa bsdam pa'i phyir
NK058(si)001:17336: srog gcod pa spong ba'i sdom pa'ang bsdus so //
NK058(si)001:17337: de bzhin du lhag ma rnam la'ang sbyar te zag
NK058(si)001:17338: pa rang mtshan pa bsdams pas na thabs kyi spyod
NK058(si)001:17339: pa barlang po ltar snang yang ngo bo nyan thos
NK058(si)001:17340: kyi sdom pa 'dus pa kho na'o //
NK058(si)001:17341: dper na sman pa kha cig tsha ba'i nad la bsil sman byed pa na /
NK058(si)001:17342: la las ldog ste bcos pas myur du phan pa
NK058(si)001:17343: gnyis 'gal ba ltar snang yang don la 'gal ba
NK058(si)001:17344: med pa ltar / lam gyi thabs 'gal bar snang yang /
NK058(si)001:17345: don la rang rgyud kyi nyon mongs pa spong zhing dge ba bsgrub par don mthun pa kho na'o //
NK058(si)001:17346: gnyis pa byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa'i 'dus tshul ni /
NK058(si)001:17347: spyod pa gang la sbyor ba de'i tshe tha mal
NK058(si)001:17348: gyi nyon mongs rang ga ma'i 'jug pa sdom pas
NK058(si)001:17350: de la brten nas lam gyi yon tan gong du
NK058(si)001:17351: 'phel bas dge ba chos sdud kyi tshul khrims so
NK058(si)001:17352: // thabs des gzhan la phan 'dogs shing rjes su
NK058(si)001:17353: 'dzin pas sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims so
NK058(si)001:17354: // // de bzhin du gsang sngags kyi sdom pa'ang ji snyed thams cad 'dir 'dus te /
NK058(si)001:17355: rgyud sdom zhing nyon mongs pa dag par tshul mtshungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:17356: gnyis pa gzhung gi don la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:17357: dam tshig chen po'i ngo bo spyir bstan pa dang /
NK058(si)001:17358: sgrub bsrung gi rnam gzhag bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:17360: dang po gsang ba'i dam tshig gzhan las 'phags pa'i
NK058(si)001:17361: tshul ni gang zag gang zhig gsang chen bla na
NK058(si)001:17362: med pa'i theg pa 'dir zhugs te don phyin ci
NK058(si)001:17363: ma log par rab tu nges pa ste nyams su
NK058(si)001:17364: blangs na 'dod chags la sogs pa'i nyon mongs pa
NK058(si)001:17365: dug lnga dang des bskyed pa'i las rnams kun la
NK058(si)001:17366: spyad kyang / sgyu ma'i sprul pas spyad pa ltar
NK058(si)001:17367: las de nyid byas par snang la de'i sgrib pa
NK058(si)001:17368: dang bag chags mi gsog pa'i steng du bsod nams
NK058(si)001:17369: dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs par 'gyur te
NK058(si)001:17370: spyad kyang / / spyod pa de nyid kyi ngo
NK058(si)001:17371: bo la so sor thar pa'i tshul khrims dang byang
NK058(si)001:17372: chub sems dpa'i sdom pa dang gsang sngags kyi dam
NK058(si)001:17373: tshig rnams phun sum tshogs pa'i don tshang zhing rdzogs
NK058(si)001:17374: spyad kyang / / pa'i phyir ro // gnyis pa
NK058(si)001:17375: gsang ba'i dam tshigs tu 'dul sdom thams cad 'dus
NK058(si)001:17376: par bstan pa ni gsang chen bla na med pa'i
NK058(si)001:17377: mchog gi dam tshig tu nyes spyod 'dul ba'i dbang
NK058(si)001:17378: gis rnam par bzhag pa'i tshul khrims so so thar
NK058(si)001:17380: des mtshon nas byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa dang /
NK058(si)001:17381: sngags phyi pa gsum nang pa dang bcas pa ji
NK058(si)001:17382: snyed pa'i sdom pa bsam yas yod pa ma lus
NK058(si)001:17383: pa'i yon tan kun yar ldan du 'dus shing 'og
NK058(si)001:17384: ma'i skyon gyi phyogs phra mo tsam yang rnam par
NK058(si)001:17385: dag pa'o // gsum pa rtsa ba'i dam tshig chen po'i rnam par gzhag pa la bzhi las /
NK058(si)001:17386: dang po srog gcad pa ni don dam par chos
NK058(si)001:17387: yod pa rtag pa'i mtha' dang med pa chad pa'i
NK058(si)001:17388: mtha' dang mtha' gnyis dang bral ba'i dbu ma'ang mi
NK058(si)001:17389: dmigs shing / kun rdzob tu bdag nyid sgyu ma
NK058(si)001:17390: dang sems can mig yor lta bu'i tshul gyis sgrol
NK058(si)001:17392: snang dus de nyid na sems can rang mtshan du
NK058(si)001:17393: ma grub pas srog bden pa ba med cing srog
NK058(si)001:17394: rang bzhin ma grub pas srog kyang gcod du med
NK058(si)001:17396: srog dang srog ldan gyi skyes bur snang ba'ang rang
NK058(si)001:17397: sems 'khrul pa'i log rtog tsam las don la gnyis
NK058(si)001:17399: yul 'khor skyong gis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK058(si)001:17400: bdag dang gzhan dang srog dang skyes bu rnams //
NK058(si)001:17401: med par snang la rang bzhin gnyis su med //
NK058(si)001:17402: phyin ci log tsam nyid las gzhan med de //
NK058(si)001:17403: yang dag ma yin kun brtags sgyu ma'i tshul //
NK058(si)001:17405: dkon cog brtsegs pa'i nye ba 'khor gyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK058(si)001:17406: ji ltar sgyu ma mkhan gyis 'jig rten na //
NK058(si)001:17407: sems can brgya phrag mang po sprul byas te //
NK058(si)001:17408: sprul pa de dag thams cad bsad gyur kyang //
NK058(si)001:17409: sgyu ma de dag gsod pa yod min ltar //
NK058(si)001:17410: 'gro ba 'di dag sgyu ma'i rang bzhin te //
NK058(si)001:17411: 'di la mtha' ni nam yang dmigs su med //
NK058(si)001:17412: gang dag de ltar mtha' yas mos byed pa //
NK058(si)001:17413: de dag 'jig rten na ni tshor ba med //
NK058(si)001:17414: gang dag rang bzhin med chos 'di shes pa //
NK058(si)001:17415: dpa' bo de dag 'jig rten mya ngan 'da' //
NK058(si)001:17416: 'dod pa'i yon tan spyod kyang chags med cing //
NK058(si)001:17417: chags pa rnams spangs sems can 'dul bar byed //
NK058(si)001:17418: mi dbang rnams ni sems can phan pa mdzad //
NK058(si)001:17420: dgos pa ni nges brjod las /
NK058(si)001:17421: sangs rgyas bstan la gnod byed dang //
NK058(si)001:17422: bla mar smod brtson ma rungs dang //
NK058(si)001:17423: rtag tu sems can gnod brtson pa //
NK058(si)001:17424: mkhas pas bsgrims te gsod par bya //
NK058(si)001:17426: de ltar bsgral ba'i dgos ched kyang /
NK058(si)001:17427: byang chub spyod 'phel sems can bde //
NK058(si)001:17428: lha mnyes bdag gi dam skong zhing //
NK058(si)001:17429: las ngan bar chad sdug yun thung //
NK058(si)001:17432: e ma ho gsod pa 'di ni bzang //
NK058(si)001:17433: gsod pa gsod pa ma yin te //
NK058(si)001:17435: gnyis pa ma byin par blang ba ni chos thams
NK058(si)001:17436: cad don dam pa dang kun rdzob kyi bden pa
NK058(si)001:17437: gnyis kar rang bzhin dbyer med pas don la ma
NK058(si)001:17438: grub cing / tha snyad du'ang ma grub ste 'phrul
NK058(si)001:17439: dag'i lha rnams rang gis sprul pa'i longs spyod la
NK058(si)001:17440: len pa'i tshul te gzhan du snang ba'i rdzas dang
NK058(si)001:17441: len pa po bdag nyid don la tha dad min
NK058(si)001:17442: pa'i rang bzhin du shes nas /
NK058(si)001:17443: rang snang gi rdzas la rang snang len pa'i tshul
NK058(si)001:17444: gyis ma byin par len dus de nyid na'ang blang
NK058(si)001:17445: bya'i yul sems can gzhan dang des bdag tu bzung
NK058(si)001:17446: ba'i rdzas rang mtshan pa ma byin par blang rgyu
NK058(si)001:17447: med pa'i phyir ma byin par blangs pa yang med
NK058(si)001:17448: de / blang bya'i yul blang rgyu'i rdzas len pa
NK058(si)001:17449: po bdag nyid kyi mtshon pa'i chos thams cad ye
NK058(si)001:17450: nas rnam par dag pa nam mkha' lta bu'i de
NK058(si)001:17451: bzhin nyid kyi dbyings yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:17452: ji skad du dkon cog brtsegs pa las /
NK058(si)001:17453: ji ltar sgyu mas sgyu ma'i nor blangs te //
NK058(si)001:17454: rmi lam nang bzhin dgos pa de spyad kyang //
NK058(si)001:17455: de la las med rnam par smin pa med //
NK058(si)001:17456: de bzhin chags med ye shes 'di bslabs te //
NK058(si)001:17457: mya ngan 'das pa dam pa mchog zhir 'gro //
NK058(si)001:17459: blang ba'i dgos pa yang phyug po de dag gi
NK058(si)001:17460: tshogs rdzogs la bkren pa dag gi 'dod pa 'grub
NK058(si)001:17462: 'jungs pa rnams la nor blangs la //
NK058(si)001:17463: sems can bkren la sbyin par bya //
NK058(si)001:17464: de phyir mi yi bdag po dang //
NK058(si)001:17465: phyug po rnams kyi nor 'phrog go //
NK058(si)001:17467: gsum pa rdzun du smra ba ni gzhan don du
NK058(si)001:17468: 'gyur ba'i dgos pa khyad par can yod na ji
NK058(si)001:17469: ltar phan pa de ltar smras kyang nyes pa med
NK058(si)001:17470: de / 'di ltar 'khor 'das kyi bsdus pa'i chos
NK058(si)001:17471: rnams kyi rang bzhin sgyu ma lta bu dang rmi
NK058(si)001:17472: lam lta bu la sogs pa yin la /
NK058(si)001:17473: de dag so so'i ming dang tshig tu btags pa
NK058(si)001:17474: de yang so so'i rtog pas glo bur du btags
NK058(si)001:17475: pa'i phyir brdzun pa nyid de /
NK058(si)001:17477: rab 'byor chos thams cad ni rang bzhin gyis dngos po med pa ste /
NK058(si)001:17478: gang brjod cing snang la btags pa de dag ni glo bur ba yin pa'i phyir brdzun pa'o //
NK058(si)001:17480: de ltar rtogs na gtong bya'i yul brdzun pa nyid
NK058(si)001:17481: la gtong byed bdag ni brdzun pa'i ngag tu yod
NK058(si)001:17482: med la sogs pa'i brdzun spyod cing gtong ba de'i
NK058(si)001:17483: tshe / gtong dus de nyid nas brdzun zhes bya
NK058(si)001:17484: ba'i chos su grub grub po ming tsam btags pa
NK058(si)001:17485: tsam du'ang yod pa ma yin te /
NK058(si)001:17486: sgra de nyid phyi nang gang na'ang med pa dang
NK058(si)001:17487: de'i ngo bo grags stong skye med yin pa'i phyir
NK058(si)001:17488: ro // de skad du'ang nye ba 'khor gyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK058(si)001:17489: ji ltar 'chang ba bcangs te byis pa la //
NK058(si)001:17490: ston zhing ngag tu yod ces brjod byas nas //
NK058(si)001:17491: de yis 'chang ba stong pa mthong nas ni //
NK058(si)001:17492: byis pa de ni cho nges ngu ba ltar //
NK058(si)001:17493: de bzhin sangs rgyas bsam gyis mi khyab par //
NK058(si)001:17494: sems can tshul la mkhas shing mkhyen pa rnams //
NK058(si)001:17495: chos rnams 'di kun gsog gsob mkhyen gyur nas //
NK058(si)001:17496: 'jig rten dag la yod dang med ces ston //
NK058(si)001:17498: dgos pa ni ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK058(si)001:17500: sems can rnams la phan spyod pas //
NK058(si)001:17501: rtag tu dam tshig bla ma'i nor //
NK058(si)001:17502: sems can srog ni bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK058(si)001:17503: brdzun du yang ni smra bar bya //
NK058(si)001:17505: bzhi pa mi tshangs par spyod pa ni /
NK058(si)001:17506: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin gang du'ang ma chags
NK058(si)001:17507: pa dngos po dang mtshan mar grub pa cung zad
NK058(si)001:17508: kyang med pa'i gnas lugs stong pa nyid la blos
NK058(si)001:17509: de ltar rtogs pa ni chags pa dang ste shes
NK058(si)001:17510: rab kyis mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa'i ngang nas
NK058(si)001:17511: yab yum snyoms par zhugs pa'i ye shes la chags
NK058(si)001:17512: pa nyid nas tha mal gyi 'dod chags med pa
NK058(si)001:17513: de ni thabs snying rje chen po'i rang bzhin te
NK058(si)001:17514: / tha mal rang gi 'dod chags las mchog tu
NK058(si)001:17515: gyur pa bde stong gnyis su med pa'i ye shes
NK058(si)001:17516: kyi rgyal po ste tshangs par spyod pa'i dam pa
NK058(si)001:17517: shin tu rnam par dag pa'i chags pa chen po
NK058(si)001:17518: pad+ma'i rigs sems can la thugs rje 'byung ba'i ngang
NK058(si)001:17519: / tshul yin no // ji skad du dkon cog brtsegs pa las /
NK058(si)001:17520: ji ltar rmi lam sgyu ma'i rang bzhin du //
NK058(si)001:17521: skyes bu 'dod bsten de yang de 'dra ste //
NK058(si)001:17522: ngo bo nyid kyis stong la dngos po med //
NK058(si)001:17523: las med rnam par smin pa de yod min //
NK058(si)001:17527: sangs rgyas rnams ni mnyes bya dang //
NK058(si)001:17528: dam tshig rnams ni bsrung ba dang //
NK058(si)001:17529: gsang sngags rig pas bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK058(si)001:17530: gzhan gyi bud med bsten par bya //
NK058(si)001:17532: gnyis pa sgrub bsrung gi rnam gzhag bye brag tu bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK058(si)001:17533: ngo bo nges tshig dang bcas pa //
NK058(si)001:17534: phan yon nyes dmigs dang bcas pa //
NK058(si)001:17535: rang bzhin dbye ba dang bcas pa //
NK058(si)001:17536: phan yon chen po bshad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:17538: ngo bo dang nges tshig go //
NK058(si)001:17540: rtsa ba'i dam tshig ni gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum
NK058(si)001:17541: gyi bla na med pa'i dkon cog gsum mi spang
NK058(si)001:17542: ba dang po'o // chos dang dam tshig gis 'brel
NK058(si)001:17543: ba'i bla ma rnams dang khyad par du gsang sngags
NK058(si)001:17544: rdo rje'i bla ma bkur ba gnyis pa'o //
NK058(si)001:17545: de'ang dbang bskur ba rgyud bshad pa gdams pa bstan
NK058(si)001:17546: pa ni gsum ldan te de las gnyan pa'i bla
NK058(si)001:17547: ma med do // dbang bskur ba la sogs pa gang rung gnyis ni gnyis ldan te bar ma'o //
NK058(si)001:17548: gang rung re re ni gcig ldan te cung zad mi gnyan no //
NK058(si)001:17549: bkur ba'i rim pa'ang de bzhin du bya zhing /
NK058(si)001:17550: re re'am gnyis ldan lta bu la /
NK058(si)001:17551: dbang dang bshad pa dang man ngag gsum ni snga ma snga ma las gnyan no //
NK058(si)001:17552: dbang la'ang rim pa gong ma gong ma gnyan pas bla ma yang de bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:17553: dkyil 'khor gang du zhugs pa'i lha rnams kyi rgyu
NK058(si)001:17554: ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags la sogs pa yan
NK058(si)001:17555: lag lnga'i sgo nas bzlas shing dam tshig chos las
NK058(si)001:17556: phyag rgya chen po dang bzhi'i sgo nas lha so
NK058(si)001:17557: so'i phyag rgya 'chang ba rnams rgyun mi gcod par
NK058(si)001:17558: dus dang brtson pa'i rim pas byed pa ni gsum
NK058(si)001:17559: pa'o // yang dag pa'i lam du ste theg pa
NK058(si)001:17560: chen por zhugs pa'i gang zag rnams la byams pa
NK058(si)001:17561: pa'o // ni bzhi pa'o // gab pa dang sbas
NK058(si)001:17562: pa'i lta spyod gsang ba'i don rnams phyi rol snod
NK058(si)001:17563: du ma gyur pa la smra bar mi bya ba
NK058(si)001:17564: pa'o // ni bzhi pa'o // ni lnga pa'o //
NK058(si)001:17565: don de dag rnams ni dam tshig gi rtsa ba
NK058(si)001:17567: dang po gsum sgrub pa'i dam tshig dang phyi ma
NK058(si)001:17568: gnyis de dag gi thugs dang 'gal ba bsrung ba'i
NK058(si)001:17569: dam tshig gi mchog yin no //
NK058(si)001:17570: gnyis pa yan lag gi dam tshig la'ang gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:17571: mi spang ba'i dam tshig lnga ni gti mug gang
NK058(si)001:17572: du mi rtog pa dang 'dod chags bde ba chen
NK058(si)001:17573: po dang zhe sdang gsal ba chen po dang phrag
NK058(si)001:17574: dog khro ba chen po rnams ni gzhi ye nas
NK058(si)001:17575: dag cing thabs kyi lam du 'gyur ba la 'bras
NK058(si)001:17576: bu sku dang ye shes su 'char ba'i rang bzhin
NK058(si)001:17577: yin pas nam yang mi spang ngo //
NK058(si)001:17578: dang du blang ba'i dam tshig lnga ni dkar rtsi
NK058(si)001:17579: byang chub kyi sems dang dmar rtsi pad+ma rak+ta dang
NK058(si)001:17580: dri chen dri chu dang sha chen lnga'i dwangs ma
NK058(si)001:17581: rnams ni / kha cig gis btsog par 'dzin pas
NK058(si)001:17582: de dang mthun pa'i blo spang byar shes pa ni
NK058(si)001:17583: dam rdzas kyis dag cing dben pa'i snod yin pas
NK058(si)001:17585: 'di la kha cig ye nas dag pa'i snod bcud du gnas pas mi dor zhes pa dang /
NK058(si)001:17586: la la dam rdzas dag pa dang de'i snod ka
NK058(si)001:17587: p+aa la mi dor zhes zer bas ma shes par
NK058(si)001:17588: snang ste gzhung de nyid bklags pas shes so //
NK058(si)001:17589: de dag ni rtsa ba'i grogs sam thabs su byung
NK058(si)001:17590: bas na yan lag rnam pa bcu yi dam tshig
NK058(si)001:17591: ste rang dgar spyad na tha mal ba bzhin 'gyur
NK058(si)001:17592: bas / ye nas dag pa gsum dang mnyam pa
NK058(si)001:17593: bzhir gnas pa'i don rtogs pas rang bzhin shes par
NK058(si)001:17594: byas la rang rang gi thabs kyis zin pa'i tshul
NK058(si)001:17596: gnyis pa nges tshig la'ang gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:17597: rtsa ba'i nges tshig ni bsrung zhing bsgrub pa'i dam
NK058(si)001:17598: tshig rnam pa lnga ni gsang sngags bsgrub pa'i rtsa
NK058(si)001:17600: ljon shing gi rtsa ba ltar bsrungs na dngos grub
NK058(si)001:17601: 'byung zhing nyams na theg pa chen po'i rigs te
NK058(si)001:17602: mngon par byang chub pa'i skal ba med par 'gyur
NK058(si)001:17603: ro // de'ang gnas skabs rgyangs bsrings pa tsam la
NK058(si)001:17604: de skad bya yi gtan du rigs sam skal pa
NK058(si)001:17606: thar pa'i sa bon bskrun pa'i phyir dang /
NK058(si)001:17607: rigs chad mi srid pa'i phyir ro //
