NK058(si)001:17608: rigs zhes pa ni mtshan nyid kyi theg pas thog
NK058(si)001:17609: ma med pa'i chos khams dge ba sa bon gyi
NK058(si)001:17611: snying po bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK058(si)001:17612: thog ma med pa'i dus kyi dbyings //
NK058(si)001:17613: chos rnams kun gyi gnas yin te //
NK058(si)001:17621: gter dang 'bras bu'i shing bzhin du //
NK058(si)001:17622: rigs de rnam gnyis shes bya ste //
NK058(si)001:17623: thog med rang bzhin gnas pa dang //
NK058(si)001:17624: yang dag blangs pas mchog nyid do //
NK058(si)001:17626: dang po 'di ni sems nyid don gyi kun gzhi
NK058(si)001:17627: ye nas rang bzhin gyis dag cing 'od gsal ba
NK058(si)001:17629: de bzhin yid kyi nang chud rin cen gter //
NK058(si)001:17630: dri med bsal dang gzhag med chos nyid kyang //
NK058(si)001:17632: chos can ni don gyi kun gzhi'i steng na ljon
NK058(si)001:17633: pa'i sa bon ltar sangs rgyas kyi mtshan dpe 'od
NK058(si)001:17634: zer dang bcas pa 'byung rung gi dngos po shin
NK058(si)001:17635: tu phra ba'i rang bzhin du thog ma med pa
NK058(si)001:17636: nas yod pa sbyangs pa las gzugs sku 'byung bar
NK058(si)001:17638: ji ltar a mra la sogs shing 'bras la //
NK058(si)001:17639: yod pa'i sa bon myu gu 'jig med chos //
NK058(si)001:17640: sa rmos chu sogs ldan pas ljon shing gi //
NK058(si)001:17641: rgyal po'i dngos por rim gyis 'grub pa ltar //
NK058(si)001:17642: sems can rnams kyi ma rig sogs 'bras kyi //
NK058(si)001:17643: pags sbubs nang chud chos khams dge ba yang //
NK058(si)001:17644: de bzhin dge ba de la de brten nas //
NK058(si)001:17645: rim gyis thub pa'i rgyal po'i ngo bor 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:17647: de'ang rigs dang pos chos sku dang /
NK058(si)001:17648: gnyis pas gzugs sku bskyed par /
NK058(si)001:17650: rigs 'di gnyis las sangs rgyas kyi //
NK058(si)001:17651: sku gsum thob par 'dod pa yin //
NK058(si)001:17652: dang pos sku ni dang po ste //
NK058(si)001:17653: gnyis pa yis ni phyi ma gnyis //
NK058(si)001:17655: de ltar gzhi la yod pa'i rigs sad pa na
NK058(si)001:17656: sems bskyed dang lam bsgrub pa'i skal pa yod pas
NK058(si)001:17657: rigs dang po sad pa'i rtags su /
NK058(si)001:17659: so so skye bo'i dus na'ang stong pa nyid thos nas //
NK058(si)001:17660: nang du rab tu dga' ba yang dang yang du 'byung //
NK058(si)001:17661: rab tu dga' ba las byung mchi mas mig brlan zhing //
NK058(si)001:17662: lus kyi ba spu ldang bar 'gyur ba gang yin pa //
NK058(si)001:17663: de la rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas blo yi sa bon yod //
NK058(si)001:17664: de nyid nye bar bstan pa'i snod ni de yin te //
NK058(si)001:17665: de la dam pa'i don gyi bden pa bstan par bya //
NK058(si)001:17667: gnyis pa sad pa'i rtags ni /
NK058(si)001:17669: sbyor ba'i sngon du snying rje dang //
NK058(si)001:17670: mos pa dang ni bzod pa dang //
NK058(si)001:17671: dge ba yang dag spyod pa ni //
NK058(si)001:17672: rigs kyi rtags su yang dag bshad //
NK058(si)001:17674: de lta bu'i rigs de nyid gsang sngags pa ltar na /
NK058(si)001:17675: nyi ma sprin gyis bsgribs pa'am 'dam gyis gos pa'i
NK058(si)001:17676: nor bu ltar sku dang ye shes dang zhing khams
NK058(si)001:17677: ye nas lhun grub tu yod par 'dod cing chos
NK058(si)001:17678: thams cad ye nas sangs ma rgyas pa med par
NK058(si)001:17679: 'dod de / rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni //
NK058(si)001:17680: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:17681: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan pa'i chos //
NK058(si)001:17682: sangs rgyas nyid kyis mi brnyes so //
NK058(si)001:17684: de lta na'ang glo bur kun tu brtags pa'i dri
NK058(si)001:17685: ma nyid chag rom chu ru zhu ba ltar ye
NK058(si)001:17687: nyon mongs lnga ni ye shes lnga //
NK058(si)001:17688: srid pa gsum ni bde ldan zhing //
NK058(si)001:17689: zhes rdo rje las bshad pa bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:17690: tshul 'di nyid bka' tha ma nges pa don gyi mdo sde las kyang gsungs te /
NK058(si)001:17691: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po'i mdo las /
NK058(si)001:17692: ji ltar mi yi gser gyi gar bu ni //
NK058(si)001:17693: nyal nyil rnam pa'i nang du lhung gyur la //
NK058(si)001:17694: der de lo ni mi nyung ba zhig tu //
NK058(si)001:17695: de ltar gnas kyang mi 'jig chos can no //
NK058(si)001:17696: lha yis lha yi mig gis de mthong nas //
NK058(si)001:17697: rnam par sbyang phyir gzhan la smras pa ni //
NK058(si)001:17698: 'di na rin cen mchog gi gser yod la //
NK058(si)001:17699: rnam par sbyongs la de nyid bya ba gyis //
NK058(si)001:17700: de bzhin ngas ni sems can thams cad kyang //
NK058(si)001:17701: nyon mongs rnams kyis yun ring rtag non mthong //
NK058(si)001:17702: de dag gis ni glo bur nyon mongs shes //
NK058(si)001:17703: rang bzhin sbyang phyir thabs kyi chos ston to //
NK058(si)001:17704: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK058(si)001:17705: des na de lta bu'i rigs las nyams pa ma yin kyang /
NK058(si)001:17706: rnal 'byor sems tsam pa ltar re zhig lam sgrub
NK058(si)001:17707: pa'i rigs las nyams par 'ag+r+yura pas de skad ces
NK058(si)001:17708: bya'o // yan lag gi nges tshig ni mi spang
NK058(si)001:17709: ba dang mi dor ba'i dam tshig lnga tshan gnyis
NK058(si)001:17710: ni rtsa ba sgrub pa'i grogs su dgos pas yan
NK058(si)001:17711: lag gi dam tshig ces bya ste /
NK058(si)001:17712: de dag kyang rtsa ba dang gnyan mi gnyan dgos
NK058(si)001:17713: pa'i dbang gis mnyam pas na de las shin tu
NK058(si)001:17715: ra ba mtshams kyi 'obs dang 'dra bas so //
NK058(si)001:17716: gnyis pa phan yon nyes dmigs dang bcas pa la'ang gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:17717: dam tshig la gnas pa'i phan yon ni chos thams
NK058(si)001:17718: cad ye nas sku dang ye shes su sangs rgyas
NK058(si)001:17719: par mnyam nyid kyi don la lam thabs dang shes
NK058(si)001:17720: rab zab mos mnyam par sbyor ba yi rang bzhan
NK058(si)001:17721: ni mnyam pa'i dam tshig chen po de nyid la
NK058(si)001:17722: gnas na 'bras bu sku gsum 'du 'bral med par
NK058(si)001:17723: mnyam pa nyid kyi yon tan lhun rdzogs chen po
NK058(si)001:17724: sangs rgyas thob par 'gyur bas na dam tshig bsrung
NK058(si)001:17725: bar bya'o // dam tshig las 'das na sangs rgyas
NK058(si)001:17726: thob pa ma yin pas 'da' bar mi bya ste
NK058(si)001:17727: bar bya'o // / rgyal po'i khrims la gnas pas
NK058(si)001:17728: bde ba byung zhing 'das pas chad pa 'byung ba
NK058(si)001:17729: bar bya'o // / bzhin no // gnyis pa nyams pa'i nyes dmigs la gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:17730: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams pa'i nyes pa la'ang nyams
NK058(si)001:17731: grib gzhan la gnod pa ni rtsa ba'i dam tshig
NK058(si)001:17732: nyams pa'i gang zag bslab sdom phyal bar dor ba
NK058(si)001:17733: dag dam tshig gso ba'i thabs la nye bar mi
NK058(si)001:17734: brtson na de dang skad cig tsam yang mi 'grogs
NK058(si)001:17735: shing yud tsam gcig tu'ang phan tshun gtam smra bar
NK058(si)001:17736: ma byed cig / ci'i phyir zhe na tshe 'dir
NK058(si)001:17737: nad dang gnod pa la sogs pa mi 'dod pa'i
NK058(si)001:17738: rkyen sna tshogs 'byung zhing phyi mar de dang mnyam
NK058(si)001:17739: du dmyal bar 'gro dgos pas dam tshig nyams pa
NK058(si)001:17740: las gyur pa'i nyes pa brjod kyis mi lang ba
NK058(si)001:17742: de'ang zlas nyams pa zhes bya'o //
NK058(si)001:17743: kha cig de dang lung pa gcig gi chu la'ang
NK058(si)001:17744: mi btung zer ba ni dgongs pa ma yin te
NK058(si)001:17745: / 'di ltar gsang sngags 'og ma 'og ma rnams
NK058(si)001:17746: dog cing gong ma gong ma de las yangs pas
NK058(si)001:17747: dam tshig bsrung mtshams kyang de bzhin te kri ya
NK058(si)001:17748: bas lung ba gcig gi chu la'ang mi btung bar
NK058(si)001:17749: / bshad de / dam tshig bkod pa las /
NK058(si)001:17750: kri ya rnams las khyad par du //
NK058(si)001:17751: lung gcig chu la mi btung dang //
NK058(si)001:17753: u pas lung pa gcig tu gnas kyang mthong bar mi bya ba dang /
NK058(si)001:17754: yo ga bas mthong yang 'phrad par mi bya ba dang /
NK058(si)001:17755: ma h+aa dang a nu a ti gsum gyis 'phrad kyang gtam mi smra bar bya yi /
NK058(si)001:17756: gnas gcig tu 'dug pa tsam la nyes pa de tsam ma gsungs so //
NK058(si)001:17757: gnyis pa nyams pa'i nyes pa rang la 'byung ba
NK058(si)001:17758: ni rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams par gyur na char
NK058(si)001:17759: phab na than pa 'byung ba'am mthu btang na rang
NK058(si)001:17760: la log pa ltar gang sgrub pa thams cad de
NK058(si)001:17762: kun gyi yid du mi 'ong ba dang /
NK058(si)001:17763: tshe 'dir phongs pa dang nad dang gdon dang 'tshe
NK058(si)001:17764: ba dang tshe thung ba la sogs pa mi 'dod
NK058(si)001:17766: phyi mar dmyal bar ltung zhing bskal pa du mar
NK058(si)001:17767: sdug bsngal ba la sogs pa rang gi yid du
NK058(si)001:17768: mi 'ong ba rnam pa sna tshogs pa'i rang bzhin
NK058(si)001:17769: rgyu dam tshig nyams pas bskyed pa'i gnas skabs dang
NK058(si)001:17770: mthar thug gi 'bras bu sdug bsngal du ma mi
NK058(si)001:17771: 'dod bzhin du rang dbang med par 'du bar byed
NK058(si)001:17772: do // gnyis pa yan lag gi dam tshig nyams pa'i nyes pa ni /
NK058(si)001:17773: yan lag gi dam tshig nyams par gyur na tshe
NK058(si)001:17774: 'dir sgrub pa'i 'bras bu mchog dang thun mong gi
NK058(si)001:17775: dngos grub gang yang med cing phyi ma ngan song
NK058(si)001:17778: dam tshig nyams pas thur du 'gro //
NK058(si)001:17781: gsum pa rang bzhin dang dbye ba bshad pa la gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:17782: dam tshig gi rang bzhin ni rtsa ba dang yan
NK058(si)001:17783: lag gi dam tshig rnams ni sku gsung thugs kyi
NK058(si)001:17784: rdo rje chen po'i ngo bo sangs rgyas kun gyi
NK058(si)001:17785: bdag nyid dam pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:17786: de'i phyir bsrungs na phan yon dang nyams na nyes
NK058(si)001:17787: dmigs chen po 'byung ba 'thad pa dang bcas pa'o
NK058(si)001:17788: // gnyis pa dbye ba la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:17789: rnam grangs kyi dbye ba dang /
NK058(si)001:17790: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dbye ba'o //
NK058(si)001:17792: rtsa ba'i dbye ba ni rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga
NK058(si)001:17793: po la ni bla med mi spang ba lta bu
NK058(si)001:17794: gcig la'ang rtsa ba thabs dang /
NK058(si)001:17795: shes rab gnyis dang de gnyis la sku gsung thugs
NK058(si)001:17796: gsum gsum ste drug dang de re re'ang yon tan
NK058(si)001:17797: phrin las sku gsung thugs lnga lnga ste bsdoms pas
NK058(si)001:17799: yan lag gi dbye ba ni yan lag gi dam
NK058(si)001:17800: tshig lnga gnyis te bcu la 'dod chags mi spong
NK058(si)001:17801: ba lta bu gcig la'ang thabs dang shes rab las
NK058(si)001:17802: / thabs la ye shes lnga dang yum lnga /
NK058(si)001:17803: shes rab la ye shes lnga dang yul lnga ste
NK058(si)001:17804: bcu phrag gnyis su dbye bas nyi shu yod do
NK058(si)001:17805: // gnyis pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dbye ba la gnyis las /
NK058(si)001:17806: chos can bsam gyis mi khyab pas dam tshig bsam gyis mi khyab pa ni /
NK058(si)001:17807: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig de dag ni ngo mtshar rmad po che yin te /
NK058(si)001:17808: 'gro ba'i khams rnams ye shes chen por 'dul ba'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:17809: de'ang sems can mtha' yas pa ltar de re re
NK058(si)001:17810: la ltos pa'i dam tshig sum brgya drug cu'ang de
NK058(si)001:17811: snyed du 'gyur bas mtha' yas so zhes bstan pa
NK058(si)001:17812: ni / 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na srid
NK058(si)001:17813: pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i 'gro ba ji snyed yod
NK058(si)001:17814: pa de dag gi rnam par rtog pa ji snyed
NK058(si)001:17815: yod pa 'dul ba'i phyir rtsa ba dang yan lag
NK058(si)001:17816: gi dam tshig kyang de snyed du spro bas nam
NK058(si)001:17817: mkha'i dbyings dang chos kyi dbyings ltar bsam gyis mi
NK058(si)001:17818: ni / khyab pa'o // kha cig sems can gyi
NK058(si)001:17819: rtog pa mang ba bzhin dam tshig kyang rigs mi
NK058(si)001:17820: 'dra ste de snyed du 'chad pa ni dgongs pa
NK058(si)001:17821: ni / khyab pa'o // ma yin te / dam
NK058(si)001:17822: tshig de ni zhes rtsa ba dang yan lag gi
NK058(si)001:17823: dam tshig bshad ma thag pa de la snyegs pa
NK058(si)001:17824: ni / khyab pa'o // ma yin te / dang
NK058(si)001:17825: 'gal lo // gnyis pa chos nyid bsam gyi mi
NK058(si)001:17826: ni / khyab pa'o // ma yin te / dang
NK058(si)001:17827: 'gal lo // khyab pas / dam tshig bsam gyis
NK058(si)001:17829: de ltar chos can rnam grangs kyi dam tshig bstan
NK058(si)001:17830: pa las gzhan yang snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK058(si)001:17831: thams cad ye nas blang dor med pas spang blang
NK058(si)001:17832: bsrung mtshams las 'das pa rgyal mchog kun tu bzang
NK058(si)001:17833: po bya rtsol med pa'i mchog gi rol par chos
NK058(si)001:17834: thams cad ma lus par 'dus shing gnyis su med
NK058(si)001:17835: pa'i phyag rgya nam mkha' lta bu yin pas na
NK058(si)001:17836: / gang gis kyang bcos shing rtsol sgrub re dogs med pa'i rang bzhin te /
NK058(si)001:17837: dam tshig thams cad kyi snying po'i mchog dam pa
NK058(si)001:17838: ma lus la kun de yin pas na de bzhin
NK058(si)001:17839: nyid la bcos bslad dang re dogs med pa'i gnas
NK058(si)001:17840: lugs rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang du shes par bya'o
NK058(si)001:17841: // de skad du'ang kun byed las /
NK058(si)001:17843: ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po nga //
NK058(si)001:17844: rtsa ba byang chub sems su kun gcig pas //
NK058(si)001:17845: kun kyang snying po'i dam tshig gcig yin te //
NK058(si)001:17846: bsrung dang mi bsrung don las 'das par rtogs //
NK058(si)001:17848: kun byed rgyal po lta ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK058(si)001:17849: skye med nam mkha' lta bur phyogs 'das pas //
NK058(si)001:17850: gang gis de dag legs par rtogs pa de //
NK058(si)001:17851: kun byed rgyal po'i dam tshig rtogs pa yin //
NK058(si)001:17853: chos rnams rtsa ba sems su gcig pa ltar //
NK058(si)001:17854: dam tshig rtsa ba bsrung du med par gcig /
NK058(si)001:17856: kun byed nga yi dgongs pa'i dam tshig ni //
NK058(si)001:17857: ma yengs dran pas dngos po ye shes su //
NK058(si)001:17858: ma bcos sus kyang ma byas rang byung ste //
NK058(si)001:17859: rig pas dbang sgyur bsrung dang mi bsrung med //
NK058(si)001:17860: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK058(si)001:17861: rang byung snying por gsal bas dbang bsgyur nas //
NK058(si)001:17862: kun byed rgyal pos byas pa'i chos rnams la //
NK058(si)001:17863: rig dang ma rig gnyis ka'i yul las 'das //
NK058(si)001:17864: 'da' nyams bsrung mtshams med pa'i dam tshig yin //
NK058(si)001:17866: des na gnas lugs don gyi dam tshig ni brjod
NK058(si)001:17867: du med pa dang bstan du med pa dang mtshan
NK058(si)001:17868: ma med pa dang ye ji bzhin pa'i chos nyid
NK058(si)001:17869: dus gsum 'pho 'gyur med pa'i ting nge 'dzin te
NK058(si)001:17870: / de la sogs pa bsam brjod dmigs pa'i yul
NK058(si)001:17871: las 'das pas dam tshig gi ngo bo mtha' yas
NK058(si)001:17872: pa'i mchog rdzogs pa chen po don gyi gnas lugs
NK058(si)001:17873: / su gnas pa'o // de lta bu'i dam tshig
NK058(si)001:17874: tu dam tshig thams cad ma bsgrubs kyang ngang gis
NK058(si)001:17876: nam mkha' klong yangs kyi rgyud las /
NK058(si)001:17877: nor bu rin cen rnyed pa'i mis //
NK058(si)001:17878: 'jig rten so nam mi dgos bzhin //
NK058(si)001:17879: ma bsgoms sems kyi don rtogs na //
NK058(si)001:17880: yon tan ma lus lhun gyis grub //
NK058(si)001:17881: de las mi 'da' dam tshig yin //
NK058(si)001:17883: bzhi pa phan yon chen po rgya cher bshad pa la lnga las /
NK058(si)001:17884: dang po 'jig rten pas bstod cing bkur ba ni /
NK058(si)001:17885: rgyal ba'i rigs kyi mchog gsang sngags 'dzin cing dam
NK058(si)001:17886: tshig la gnas pa de la tshangs pa dang brgya
NK058(si)001:17887: byin la sogs pa 'jig rten pa'i gtso bo dang
NK058(si)001:17888: de'i 'khor gyis bstod cing bkur sti dang phu dud
NK058(si)001:17890: gnyis pa 'phags pas byin gyis rlob pa ni /
NK058(si)001:17891: lha dang mi'i skye rgu rnams kyi nang nas dam pa mchog gtso bo sangs rgyas rnams dang /
NK058(si)001:17892: de'i sras dam pa sar gnas kyi byang chub sems
NK058(si)001:17893: dpa' yis rim pa bzhin sras kyi thu bo dang
NK058(si)001:17894: spun gyi dwangs mar dgongs shing /
NK058(si)001:17895: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las dang bcas pas byin gyis rlob pa'o //
NK058(si)001:17896: gsum pa rgyal ba'i spyod yul thob pa'i phan yon ni /
NK058(si)001:17897: dam tshig la gnas pa de nyid bde bar gshegs
NK058(si)001:17898: pa nyid kyi spyod yul sar chud pa sa la
NK058(si)001:17899: gnas pa sa yongs su smin pa'i rig 'dzin gsum
NK058(si)001:17900: la zhugs pa'i mthar chos thams cad la 'jigs pa
NK058(si)001:17901: med pa'i mchog kun tu bzang por sbyor zhing thob
NK058(si)001:17902: par byed do // de'ang sgrib pa gnyis dang /
NK058(si)001:17905: shes bya gang la'ang 'jigs pa med pas 'jigs med
NK058(si)001:17906: kun tu bzang po 'bras bu'i sangs rgyas su bshad
NK058(si)001:17907: do // sar chud pa'i rig 'dzin ni dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:17908: du zhugs te bskyed rdzogs dang por mnos pa dag
NK058(si)001:17909: do // go // sa la gnas pa'i rig 'dzin
NK058(si)001:17910: ni rtogs pa dang ting nge 'dzin thob nas de
NK058(si)001:17912: sar smin pa'i rig 'dzin ni thob pa de las kyang stobs cher gyur te /
NK058(si)001:17913: rnam smin tshe dbang phyag rgya thob nas lhun gyis
NK058(si)001:17914: grub pa'i rig 'dzin la sbyor zhing thob par byed
NK058(si)001:17915: pa'o // bzhi pa sdom pa dang dam tshig gi yon tan 'dus pa'i phan yon ni /
NK058(si)001:17916: bla na med pa'i dam tshig gi nang du chos
NK058(si)001:17917: thams cad kyi gnas lugs ji bzhin pa'i chos nyid
NK058(si)001:17919: sems can 'dul ba'i thabs theg pa mtha' dag gi don dang /
NK058(si)001:17920: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK058(si)001:17921: dpa' dang rig pa 'dzin pa la sogs pa ji
NK058(si)001:17922: snyed pa de dag gi sdom pa bsam yas kyi
NK058(si)001:17923: rigs gang yin pa ma lus pa kun yar ldan
NK058(si)001:17924: gyi tshul bre mig tu phul ltar 'dus shing de
NK058(si)001:17925: dag gi yon tan ma lus pa lhun gyis grub
NK058(si)001:17926: pa yin no // lnga pa nyams kyang gsor rung
NK058(si)001:17927: ba'i phan yon ni rtsa ba dang yan lag gi
NK058(si)001:17928: dam tshig nyams pa na nyan thos kyi 'dul khrims
NK058(si)001:17929: rdza be'u chags pa ltar gso mi rung ba ma
NK058(si)001:17930: yin gyi dbang nod pa dang bshags pa la sogs
NK058(si)001:17932: snga ma bzhin sor chud cing rdzogs par 'gyur ba
NK058(si)001:17933: dang de la sogs pa'i phan yon mtha' yas pa'i
NK058(si)001:17934: mchog gsang sngags la yod do //
NK058(si)001:17935: gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK058(si)001:17936: de skad ces brjod pas rang snang gi de bzhin
NK058(si)001:17937: gshegs pa'i tshogs nyid de bzhin gshegs pa kun tu
NK058(si)001:17938: bzang po dkyil 'khor gyi mnga' bdag de nyid la
NK058(si)001:17940: dam tshig gsang ba'i snying po kho na nyid nges
NK058(si)001:17941: pa las rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig
NK058(si)001:17942: gi don bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu dgu pa'i rnam
NK058(si)001:17944: spyi don lnga pa dam tshig can gyis phrin las ji ltar bsgrub pa'i tshul la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:17949: dam tshig gi rim pa bshad pa de nas dam
NK058(si)001:17950: tshig can gyis phrin las 'grub pa'i phyir bcom ldan
NK058(si)001:17951: 'das ye shes kyi dgyes pa chen po nyid ye
NK058(si)001:17952: nas rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dam tshig phrin
NK058(si)001:17953: las su byin gyis rlob pa zhes bya ba'i ting
NK058(si)001:17954: nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas las thams cad
NK058(si)001:17955: 'grub pa'i ched du brjod pa 'di dag brjod do
NK058(si)001:17957: phrin las bzhi'i rim pa spyir bstan /
NK058(si)001:17958: las kyi rjes su bka' bsgo zhing bro gar gyi phan yon bye brag tu bshad pa /
NK058(si)001:17959: las bzhi sgrub pa'i gnas dang ting nge 'dzin gyi khyad par ro //
NK058(si)001:17966: bsreg pa me'i las ni drag po'i thab khung gru
NK058(si)001:17967: gsum e'i rnam pa can mtshan nyid rnams tshang ba'i
NK058(si)001:17968: tshogs kyi dbus su lha so so'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK058(si)001:17969: mchog dam tshig pa bskyed la ye shes pa bcug
NK058(si)001:17970: ste / gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin drag po'i
NK058(si)001:17971: me dpung 'bar ba'i me lha gtum chen rngams pa'i
NK058(si)001:17972: cha byad can la sngags mkhan bsgrub bya la rab
NK058(si)001:17973: tu khros pa'i yid kyis drag po'i mchod pa dang
NK058(si)001:17974: bsreg rdzas sbyin par byas na /
NK058(si)001:17975: tshogs gnyis las grub pa'i sangs rgyas bsod nams brgya'i
NK058(si)001:17976: mtshan gyis brgyan pa'i sku yang 'jig na 'jig rten
NK058(si)001:17977: phal pa rnams lta ci smos pa'o //
NK058(si)001:17978: yang na sems can thams cad sangs rgyas su bshad pas bsgrub bya de nyid 'jig ces sbyar ro //
NK058(si)001:17979: gnyis pa gdab pa phur bu'i las ni ling ga'i
NK058(si)001:17980: rgyu bdud rtsi lnga'am yang na nya sha bu ram
NK058(si)001:17981: til nag sbrang rtsi 'bras te zas lnga de'i gseb
NK058(si)001:17982: tu bsgrub bya'i dri ma rkang rjes kyi sa dang
NK058(si)001:17983: bcas pa la bsgrub bya'i mtshan ma ste /
NK058(si)001:17984: gzugs la dpral bar ming snying gar rus 'doms su
NK058(si)001:17985: bla btags gang yod dang m+aa ra ya phata dang
NK058(si)001:17986: bcas par bri zhing mtha' ma 'gugs byed kyi yi
NK058(si)001:17987: ge dzahs bskor ba gro ga'am ras sam shog bu
NK058(si)001:17988: la bris te de'i nang du gzhug pa'am mdun rgyab
NK058(si)001:17989: gang rung du glan par bya'o //
NK058(si)001:17990: de la bsgrub bya sngags ting nge 'dzin phyag rgya
NK058(si)001:17991: gsum gyis bkug nas lcags la sogs pa rdo rje
NK058(si)001:17992: phur pa badz+ra k+ai la yar bskyed pas snying ga
NK058(si)001:17993: la sogs pa'i gnas su gdab par bya ste /
NK058(si)001:17994: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du byas par bsams nas karma he ru ka'i tshogs sam /
NK058(si)001:17995: snga ma'i thab khung du drag po'i lha bskyed pa'i tshogs la 'bul zhing sbyin sreg bya'o //
NK058(si)001:17996: gsum pa mnan pa bro'i las ni e'i tshogs kyi
NK058(si)001:17997: ste drag po'i dkyil 'khor ram thab khung de'i khor
NK058(si)001:17998: yug tu rnal 'byor pa des gung srin gnyis mthe
NK058(si)001:17999: bos mnan mdzub mo gnyis brkyangs pa bkan pa'i mathe'u
NK058(si)001:18000: chung gnyis lu gu rgyud du sbrel zhing bsdams nas
NK058(si)001:18001: / phyag rgya de ltar bcings par gyur pas lus
NK058(si)001:18002: bskyod nas rdo rje'i 'gros su gom pa dor zhing
NK058(si)001:18003: lus dang phyag rgya phyogs bcur g.yo bas /
NK058(si)001:18005: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor bcas pas //
NK058(si)001:18007: skad cig yud la brlag mdzad de //
NK058(si)001:18008: brlag par ma gyur gang yang med //
NK058(si)001:18009: m+aa ra ya phata ces brjod cing /
NK058(si)001:18010: ling ga'i steng du rkang pas bro brdungs pas bsgrub bya rdul du song bar bsam mo //
NK058(si)001:18011: des ni gang dmigs de nyid dran pa myos nas
NK058(si)001:18012: snying gas te lus tshig cing dngos po med par
NK058(si)001:18013: 'gyur ro // kha cig sngar gyi sbyin sreg gi las zin pa dang sa gzhi bsubs la /
NK058(si)001:18014: de'i steng du rnal 'byor pho mo rnams gral gru
NK058(si)001:18015: gsum du byas te me dpung gi dbus su karma
NK058(si)001:18016: he ru ka'i rnam par bskyed la /
NK058(si)001:18017: thams cad srin lag sbrel te dbus su ling ga bzhag pa'i mthar bro brdung zhes zer ro //
NK058(si)001:18018: de'ang sreg mnan bro gsum po 'di gang rung re res kyang las 'grub la /
NK058(si)001:18019: gsum ga tshang na mchog tu 'grub bo //
NK058(si)001:18020: gnyis pa dbang gi las la'ang gsum las /
NK058(si)001:18021: dang po sreg pa me yi las ni wam gyi
NK058(si)001:18022: dbyibs dang des mtshon zhing bris pa'i thab khung zla
NK058(si)001:18023: gam mo // tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog ni thab
NK058(si)001:18024: kyi mtshan nyid dang lha'i gtso 'khor gnyis ka la
NK058(si)001:18025: 'jug ste thams cad la de bzhin du sbyar ro
NK058(si)001:18026: gam mo // // de'i nang du thab kyi me
NK058(si)001:18027: dang me lha rab tu 'bar ba dbang gi cha
NK058(si)001:18028: byad can gzi brjid che zhing sku bong gi lhun
NK058(si)001:18029: chen po bzhugs pa la sngags mkhan bsgrub bya la
NK058(si)001:18030: rjes su chags pa'i yid kyis dbang dang mthun pa'i
NK058(si)001:18031: rdzas me la mchod sbyin byas na rdo rje gsung
NK058(si)001:18032: ste snang ba mtha' yas yang dbang du 'gyur ro
NK058(si)001:18033: gam mo // // // gnyis pa gdab pa phur bu'i las ni /
NK058(si)001:18034: bdud rtsi lnga'am yang na zas lnga bsgrub bya'i gos
NK058(si)001:18035: dang dri mar bcas pa la gang dbang du bya
NK058(si)001:18036: ba de'i mtshan ma gzugs byas pa'i nang du shog
NK058(si)001:18037: bu la sogs pa'i byang bu la ming rus mtshan
NK058(si)001:18038: gsum du bcas pa bris la gzhug par bya zhing
NK058(si)001:18039: / zangs la sogs pa'i phur pa rdo rje chags
NK058(si)001:18040: pa ste pad+ma k+ai la yar bskyes pas gdab cing
NK058(si)001:18041: / / btab pa'i ling ga de nyid chags pa'i
NK058(si)001:18042: tshogs pad+ma he ru ka 'khor bcas sam sngar gyi
NK058(si)001:18043: thab kyi lha la gnyis su med par thim par
NK058(si)001:18044: / / dbul lo // gsum pa mnan pa bro'i las ni /
NK058(si)001:18045: wam gyi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor thab khung gi mtha'
NK058(si)001:18046: 'am dbang gi dkyil 'khor du rnal 'byor pa lu
NK058(si)001:18047: gu rgyud du sbrel nas bsdams te bro byas na
NK058(si)001:18048: 'gro ba thams cad 'gugs par 'gyur ba'i rdo rje
NK058(si)001:18049: pad+ma dang dbang chen mdzes pa'ang phyi bzhin 'brang na
NK058(si)001:18050: mi'i 'gro ba phal pa rnams lta smos kyang ci
NK058(si)001:18051: dgos te / yid la ci 'dod pa de bzhin 'ong bar 'gyur ro //
NK058(si)001:18052: gsum pa rgyas pa'i las la'ang gsum las /
NK058(si)001:18054: ma yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog ste thab gru
NK058(si)001:18055: bzhi par me dang me lha gnyis po 'od zer
NK058(si)001:18056: 'bar ba'i tshogs nang du 'du bas longs spyod sdud
NK058(si)001:18057: cing phyir 'phro ba'i gzi brjid chen pos re ba
NK058(si)001:18058: bskong bar bsam pa la sngags mkhan dga' zhing spro
NK058(si)001:18059: ba'i yid kyis rgyas pa'i mchod spyin byas na /
NK058(si)001:18060: tshe dang dpal dang 'byor ba 'phel ba la sogs
NK058(si)001:18061: pa'i yon tan nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa 'thob
NK058(si)001:18063: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga gang rung gi gseb tu
NK058(si)001:18064: 'bru dang rin po che la sogs pa bsres la
NK058(si)001:18065: nor bu gser dngul mu tig rta glang la sogs
NK058(si)001:18066: pa gang rgyas shing 'phel bar 'dod pa de'i gzugs
NK058(si)001:18067: kyi mtshan ma ming spel bris pa dang bcas pa
NK058(si)001:18068: byas te / 'dod pa'i yon tan gang dgos 'byung
NK058(si)001:18069: ba yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che'i gter
NK058(si)001:18070: du bsgom pa ni brtag pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18071: de la gser la sogs pa'i phur pa nga rgyal
NK058(si)001:18072: dga' spro ste rat+na k+ai la ya dngos grub kyi
NK058(si)001:18073: char 'bebs par bskyed la phur pa gdab cing /
NK058(si)001:18074: yon tan rdo rje'i gzi brjid chen po 'phel bar
NK058(si)001:18075: rat+na he ru ka'i tshogs sam gong gi rgyas pa'i
NK058(si)001:18078: ma yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du rgyas par byed
NK058(si)001:18079: pa'i dkyil 'khor ram thab khung gi mtha' mar rnal
NK058(si)001:18080: 'byor pa lu gu rgyud du sbrel zhing bsdams pa
NK058(si)001:18081: phyogs bcur bskyod nas bro brdungs pa'i 'od zer gyis
NK058(si)001:18082: longs spyod sprin phung dpal dang gzi brjid 'bar ba'i
NK058(si)001:18083: rnam 'phrul chen po rang gi gnas der char du
NK058(si)001:18084: 'bab pa'i ting nge 'dzin spro zhing des sems can
NK058(si)001:18085: gyi dbul ba bsal bar bsams na /
NK058(si)001:18086: yon tan 'dod dgu 'byung ba'i yid bzhin gyi nor
NK058(si)001:18087: bus nam mkha' gang bar 'gyur zhing bsam pa thams
NK058(si)001:18088: cad 'grub pa'o // bzhi pa zhi ba'i las la'ang gsum las /
NK058(si)001:18090: ya yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog ste thab khung
NK058(si)001:18091: zlum po'i nang du me dang me lha gnyis ka
NK058(si)001:18092: 'od gsal ba'i gzi brjid 'tsher ba zhi ba'i rnam
NK058(si)001:18093: par bskyed la sngags mkhan sems rab tu dwangs pa'i
NK058(si)001:18094: yid kyis nad dang gnod pa dang 'jigs pa zhi
NK058(si)001:18096: shin tu ma rungs pa'i gtum chen rngam pa bdud
NK058(si)001:18097: dang r+au tra la sogs pa'ang sems rab tu zhi
NK058(si)001:18098: ba byang chub kyi sems su lhan ner 'gyur na
NK058(si)001:18099: 'jig rten phal pa rnams lta ci smos pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18101: bdud rtsi lnga dang zas lnga'i gseb tu gang zhi
NK058(si)001:18102: bar 'dod pa de'i gos dang dri ma la sogs
NK058(si)001:18103: pa bsres la sngar bzhin ling ga byas pa de
NK058(si)001:18104: nyid lus gtum ngag rngam sems 'khrugs pa'i rnam pa
NK058(si)001:18105: can dagra'am bgegs la sogs pa gang yin pa de'i
NK058(si)001:18106: ngo bor brtag cing dngul la sogs pa'i phur bu
NK058(si)001:18107: de nyid lhan ner gsal ba bud+d+ha k+ai la yar
NK058(si)001:18108: bskyed pa'i phur bu gdab cing dpal dang gzi brjid
NK058(si)001:18109: 'bar ba lhan ne'i tshogs bud+d+ha he ru ka 'khor
NK058(si)001:18110: bcas sam zhi ba'i me lha la dbul lo //
NK058(si)001:18112: ya yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du zhi ba'i dkyil
NK058(si)001:18113: 'khor ram thab khung gi mthar rnal 'byor pa rnams
NK058(si)001:18114: lu gu rgyud du sbrel nas bsdams te bro byas
NK058(si)001:18115: na / pha rol khro ba'i me 'bar ba yang
NK058(si)001:18116: zhi bas lhan ne'i byin brlabs kyis khyab nas sdig
NK058(si)001:18117: pa dang gdug sems thams cad yid la cung zad
NK058(si)001:18118: kyang mi 'gyu bas g.yo ba med par byed pa'o
NK058(si)001:18119: na / // de ltar e wam m+aa y+aa bzhi
NK058(si)001:18120: ni yi ge'i dbyibs kyis thab khung gi dbyibs mtshon
NK058(si)001:18121: na / // par byed pa'o // bla ma rong
NK058(si)001:18122: ba ni bam ban na'i sgra sdud cing 'ching bas
NK058(si)001:18123: zhi ba dang dbang du sbyor ba ni yul tha
NK058(si)001:18124: dad kyi yi ge'i dbyibs mi 'dra ba rnams la
NK058(si)001:18126: gnyis pa las kyi rjes su bka' bsgo zhing bro gar gyi phan yon bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:18127: dam can la bka' bsgo ba dang /
NK058(si)001:18128: bro gar gyi phan yon bstan pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18130: dang po las la bsgo ba'i tshul brjod pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18131: de ltar phrin las bzhi po gang yang rung ba'i
NK058(si)001:18132: rjes thog tu tshogs kyi 'khor lo la longs spyod
NK058(si)001:18133: de / bza' btung gi lhag ma bsdus la rdo
NK058(si)001:18134: rje slob dpon gyi kha phrus byin gyis brlabs te
NK058(si)001:18135: de / / dpal chen po'i dkyil 'khor du 'dus
NK058(si)001:18136: pa'i slas lha chen po rnams kyi chung ma dang
NK058(si)001:18137: byi mo mdza' mo dang bran mo'i tshogs rnams lhag
NK058(si)001:18138: ma'i mchod sbyin 'dod pa'i mgron yin pas sbyin te
NK058(si)001:18139: za lam bdun cu'i sar bskyal zhing sngon dpal chen
NK058(si)001:18140: po'i spyan sngar khas blangs pa'i rang rang gi dam
NK058(si)001:18141: tshig rnams rab tu bsgrags nas zhi ba la sogs
NK058(si)001:18142: pa gang 'dod pa'i las de byed par bsgo bar
NK058(si)001:18143: de / / bya'o // gnyis pa ji ltar bsgo ba dngos ni /
NK058(si)001:18144: sngon dregs pa'i dbang phyug rnams btul ba'i tshe dpal
NK058(si)001:18145: chen po he ru ka shin tu gdug cing gtum
NK058(si)001:18147: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad kyi dregs pa ma
NK058(si)001:18148: lus pa rnams 'dul bar mdzad pa'i dbang phyug dang
NK058(si)001:18149: byin rlabs rmad po che mnga' bas lha dbang phyug
NK058(si)001:18150: chen po la sogs pa thams cad dbang du bsdus
NK058(si)001:18151: nas de dag gi 'khor dang chung ma dang bu
NK058(si)001:18152: mo dang ma dang phu nu mo ma lus pa
NK058(si)001:18153: rnams longs spyod kyi phyir dbang phyug dang slas su
NK058(si)001:18154: byin gyis brlabs pa byas te /
NK058(si)001:18155: dgugs pa dang bcing ba dang gsod pa la sogs
NK058(si)001:18156: pa'i so so'i las rnams dpal chen pos rang rang
NK058(si)001:18157: la bsgos pa de nyid sngon ji ltar dam bcas
NK058(si)001:18158: shing khas blangs pa'i lugs bzhin skad cig kyang ma
NK058(si)001:18159: thogs par las kyi 'bras bu myur du mngon par
NK058(si)001:18161: rang rang gis dam bca' pa bzhin du ma byas
NK058(si)001:18162: na sngon ji ltar dam bcas shing rang rang gi
NK058(si)001:18163: mna' tshig bor ba'i sdom pa dam bcas pa de
NK058(si)001:18165: gal te dam tshig de las 'das par gyur na
NK058(si)001:18166: khyed cag gi mgo lus dang snying yang tshal pa
NK058(si)001:18167: bdun du yak+sha me 'bar gyi khro bos dum bur
NK058(si)001:18169: rgyu mtshan de bas na rnal 'byor sngags 'chang bdag gis ji ltar bcol ba bzhin du byos shig /
NK058(si)001:18170: gal te las de mngon du ma byas na rang
NK058(si)001:18171: rang gis mna' bor zhing khas blangs pa'i dmod pa
NK058(si)001:18172: bzhin rul myags tshig nas rdo rje'i dmyal bar 'gro
NK058(si)001:18173: bar 'gyur ro // des na rnal 'byor pa dam
NK058(si)001:18174: tshig la gnas par gyur pa'i phrin las ci 'dod
NK058(si)001:18175: pa rnams yongs su bya ba dang rnal 'byor pa
NK058(si)001:18176: bdag cag gi 'khor rnams kyang rang gi bu gcig
NK058(si)001:18177: pa bzhin du skyongs shig dang /
NK058(si)001:18178: de'i mthus khyed cag phra men ma yang mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub 'thob par 'gyur ro //
NK058(si)001:18179: de bas na rnal 'byor bas ji ltar bcol ba'i las rnasama mngon du byos zhes bka' basgo'o //
NK058(si)001:18180: gnyis pa bro gar gyi phan yon la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:18184: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor sgrub pa'i phrin las kyi gtso bo ni bro gar 'di yin no zhes pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18186: gtso bo lnga'i bro gar gyi phan yon ni //
NK058(si)001:18187: khrag 'thung chen po bud+d+ha he ru ka la sogs
NK058(si)001:18188: pa btsun mo dang bcas pa'i bro gar las bzhi'i
NK058(si)001:18189: skabs su bstan pa ltar glu tshig gi nga ro
NK058(si)001:18190: chen mos ni zhi rgyas la sogs pa thun mong
NK058(si)001:18191: gi dngos grub thams cad dang mchog gi dngos grub
NK058(si)001:18192: thams cad ci 'dod par phrin las thams cad dang
NK058(si)001:18193: dngos grub thams cad 'grub par byed pa yin no
NK058(si)001:18194: // gnyis pa gnas kyi ma mo brgyad kyi bro gar gyi phan yon ni /
NK058(si)001:18195: koo r+ai'i sgra las bsgyur bas mdzod ldan te dkar
NK058(si)001:18196: mo chen mo la sogs pa phyogs ma bzhi'i rnam
NK058(si)001:18197: par gsal ba'i bro gar dang glu tshig chen mos
NK058(si)001:18198: ni skye 'gro dbang du 'du bar 'dod na dbang
NK058(si)001:18199: du 'du bar byed cing tshe dang yo byad la
NK058(si)001:18200: sogs pa 'phel bar 'dod na 'phel bar byed do
NK058(si)001:18201: // sbos mo chen mo puk+ka s+ai la sogs pa
NK058(si)001:18202: mtshams ma bzhi'i bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni
NK058(si)001:18203: dgra bgegs la sogs pa lhan ne ste zhi bar
NK058(si)001:18204: 'dod na zhi zhing lhan ner byed la sems rmugs
NK058(si)001:18205: shing mi gsal bar 'dod na rmugs par byed do
NK058(si)001:18206: // // gsum pa yul gyi phra men brgyad kyi bro gar gyi phan yon ni /
NK058(si)001:18207: seng gdong chen mo la sogs pa phyogs ma bzhi'i
NK058(si)001:18208: bro gar dang glu tshig chen mos ni gdug pa
NK058(si)001:18209: can thams cad de dgra bgegs kun gyi lus srog
NK058(si)001:18210: la za bar byed cing rdul phra rab kyi cha
NK058(si)001:18211: shas tsam yang med par byed do //
NK058(si)001:18212: bzhad gdong chen mo la sogs pa mtshams ma bzhi'i
NK058(si)001:18213: bro gar dang glu tshig chen mos ni gdug pa
NK058(si)001:18214: can thams cad kyi lus kun las nang khrol dang
NK058(si)001:18215: don snying 'byin par byed cing de dag gi srog
NK058(si)001:18216: la sogs pa phun sum tshogs pa kun las rab
NK058(si)001:18218: bzhi pa dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi bro gar gyi phan yon ni /
NK058(si)001:18219: slas dang byi mo bran mo yi bro gar dang
NK058(si)001:18220: glu tshig chen mos ni pho nya dgra la rbad
NK058(si)001:18221: cing mngag gzhug las la gtang bar bya ba ste
NK058(si)001:18222: phyir 'gal byed cham la 'bebs pa'i las thams cad
NK058(si)001:18223: dang / nang du dngos grub yid bzhin du 'grub pa'i las thams cad byed pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:18224: gsum pa las bzhi bsgrub pa'i gnas dang ting nge 'dzin gyi khyad par ni /
NK058(si)001:18225: shing ljon pa'i nags tshal dang ni lcug phran gyi tshal skyed shing gi ra ba dang /
NK058(si)001:18226: shing sdong gcig gi drung dang ni mes reg ste
NK058(si)001:18227: nags mes tshig pa'i gnas rnams su zhi ba dang
NK058(si)001:18228: rgyas pa dang dbang dang drag po rnams bsgrub pa'i
NK058(si)001:18229: phyir dwangs pa dang dga' ba dang chags pa dang
NK058(si)001:18230: khros pa'i yid bzhi rim pa ltar ldan pas k+aa
NK058(si)001:18231: li ste thabs kyi phrin las bzhi po rab tu
NK058(si)001:18232: bsgrub par bya'o // kha cig yum bzhi dang sbyar
NK058(si)001:18233: nas 'chad pa na +aa li'i sgra la 'jug pa
NK058(si)001:18235: gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK058(si)001:18236: de skad ces brjod pas gtso bo de bzhi na
NK058(si)001:18237: gshegs pa nyid la 'khor gyi de bzhin gshegs pa
NK058(si)001:18238: nyid phrin las rnam pa bzhi'i don rtogs pa ste
NK058(si)001:18239: lung nod pa'i tshul gyis bsgrub par gyur to //
NK058(si)001:18240: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po ye shes kyi de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK058(si)001:18241: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa chen po ye nas lhun
NK058(si)001:18242: gyis grub pa'i phrin las rnam pa bzhir gnas pa
NK058(si)001:18243: de nyid gdul bya'i don du byin gyis rlob pa
NK058(si)001:18244: zhes bya ba'i le'u ste nyi shu pa'i rnam par
NK058(si)001:18246: spyi don gsum pa 'bras bu sku dang ye shes la bstod pa'i tshul la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:18247: bstod tshul mdor bstan pa dang /
NK058(si)001:18248: bstod pa dngos rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18250: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi mdzad pa rdzogs pa de
NK058(si)001:18251: nas rang snang gi sku dang ye shes la bstod
NK058(si)001:18252: pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po'i tshogs
NK058(si)001:18253: khrag 'thung rigs lnga 'khor dang bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK058(si)001:18254: gyi snang ba chen po de nyid la shin tu
NK058(si)001:18255: rngam pa'i mdangs kyis dgyes pa'i glu 'di skad ces
NK058(si)001:18256: blangs so // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:18257: rigs dang rigs kyi bdag po la bstod pa dang /
NK058(si)001:18258: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18260: rigs lnga la spyir bstod pa dang /
NK058(si)001:18261: dkyil 'khor gyi dbang phyug la bye brag tu bstod pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18263: sku'i rigs kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad la bstod pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18264: h'u zhes pa rnams ni khro bo'i glu rnams re
NK058(si)001:18265: re zhing sku lnga ye shes lnga ldan du mtshon
NK058(si)001:18267: de'ang sku ni bdud dang r+au tra la sogs pa
NK058(si)001:18268: dregs pa can rnams 'dul bar byed pas gtum po
NK058(si)001:18269: chen po ste / bskal pa 'jig pa'i me ltar
NK058(si)001:18270: 'bar zhing me dpung gi klong na bzhugs pa'i sku
NK058(si)001:18271: las ye shes kyi 'od zer nyi ma 'bum gyi
NK058(si)001:18272: gzi brjid phyogs gcig tu bsdus pa dang mtshungs pa
NK058(si)001:18274: gdug pa can bsdigs pa'i khro gnyer glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin 'khyug pa /
NK058(si)001:18275: gdug pa can tshar gcod pa'i mche ba zangs yag
NK058(si)001:18276: rno dkar bzhis ma rungs pa za bar byed pa'i
NK058(si)001:18278: ho ni ngo mtshar ba'i gad mo ste 'og ma rnams la yang sbyar ro //
NK058(si)001:18279: gnyis pa gsung gi rigs kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad la bstod pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18280: khro bo'i gsung rngam pa'i nga ro 'brug sgra stong
NK058(si)001:18281: dus gcig la ldir ba lta bu'i gtum chen dang
NK058(si)001:18282: drag shul ri rab 'bum dus gcig tu bsnyil ba'i
NK058(si)001:18284: a a dang ha ha dang a la la'i gad rgyangs chen po dgod pa /
NK058(si)001:18285: dbugs kyi shugs las bshug pa'i 'thor rlung chen pos
NK058(si)001:18286: gdug pa can rnams 'jigs pas g.yeng ba byed pa
NK058(si)001:18287: ni dus mtha'i rlung bas kyang che'o //
NK058(si)001:18288: gsum pa thugs kyi rigs kyi dkyil 'khor la bstod pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18289: shes bya ma lus pa mkhyen pa ni ma rig
NK058(si)001:18290: pa'i tshogs la khros pa'i shes rab kyi 'od zer
NK058(si)001:18292: ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor kun tu gsal bas gnas
NK058(si)001:18293: skabs dug lngar 'bar ba'i ngo bo ye shes su
NK058(si)001:18294: gnas pa'i nyon mongs pa rang mtshan gyi rtsal kun
NK058(si)001:18295: tu 'joms pa'i ye shes de yang sprul sku la
NK058(si)001:18296: ltos nas ji lta ba dang ji snyed pa mkhyen
NK058(si)001:18298: longs sku la ltos nas me long lta bu la
NK058(si)001:18299: sogs pa sna tshogs kyi ye shes rnams ngo bo
NK058(si)001:18300: gnyis su med pa'i thig le chen po chos nyid
NK058(si)001:18301: don gyi ye shes su ro gcig pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18302: bzhi pa yon tan gyi rigs kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad la bstod pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18303: gdug pa can 'dul ba'i yon tan mnga' bas khro bo'i rgyal po yin zhing /
NK058(si)001:18304: de las sprul pa du ma'i char 'bab pa'i gzhi byed pas sprin chen po zhes bya la /
NK058(si)001:18305: thugs khros pas khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi char chen po 'bebs shing /
NK058(si)001:18306: gdul bya'i don du gang la gang 'dul gyi dkyil
NK058(si)001:18307: 'khor yid bzhin gyi nor bu ltar bsam pa bzhin
NK058(si)001:18308: du 'byung ba'i gter las sprul pa sna tshogs pa
NK058(si)001:18309: khros pa'i gzugs su nam mkha' khyab par 'byung ba
NK058(si)001:18310: thams cad kyang gnas lugs thig le chen po gcig
NK058(si)001:18311: tu gnas so // lnga pa phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad la bstod pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18312: phung po la sogs pa'i bdud bzhi po kun gyi stobs 'joms pas na bdud chen po yin zhing /
NK058(si)001:18313: sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa ni 'khor bar
NK058(si)001:18314: 'du byed pas bdud kyi dbang po rnams kyang 'dul
NK058(si)001:18315: bar byed pa'i phyir bdud de las dang nyon mongs
NK058(si)001:18317: bdud dang gshin rje la sogs pa 'jigs pa'i tshogs
NK058(si)001:18318: pa'i tshogs kyang rab tu 'jigs shing skrag par byed
NK058(si)001:18319: pa chen po he ru ka rnams ni rang bzhin
NK058(si)001:18320: spros pa'i mtha' dang bral bas thig le chen po'o
NK058(si)001:18321: // yang na gzhan 'phrul dbang byed la sogs pa'i
NK058(si)001:18322: bdud kun gyi ni bdud chen po dga' rab dbang
NK058(si)001:18324: bdud de'i bdud ni dregs pa'i r+au tra yin pas
NK058(si)001:18325: 'jigs pa'i tshogs chung ma dang bcas pa 'jigs par
NK058(si)001:18326: byed pa ni 'jigs byed che mchog nyid de spros
NK058(si)001:18327: pa med pa'i ngo bor bzhugs pas thig le chen
NK058(si)001:18329: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor gyi dbang phyug la bye brag tu bstod pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18330: che mchog yab yum gyi sku ni skye shi 'pho
NK058(si)001:18331: 'gyur med pas rdo rje'i brag chen po nyid de
NK058(si)001:18332: 'jig 'bral med pas rab tu sra ba chen po
NK058(si)001:18334: gsung dang yon tan ni ye shes rdo rje'i chu
NK058(si)001:18335: bos gdul bya'i tshogs sdud cing tshim par byed pa
NK058(si)001:18336: po yin la / thugs ni thams cad mkhyen pa'i
NK058(si)001:18337: rdo rje ye shes kyi me 'od gsal ba ste
NK058(si)001:18338: shes bya'i yul ma lus pa mngon sum du gyur
NK058(si)001:18339: cing thugs rje'i 'od zer rab tu 'bar ba chen
NK058(si)001:18340: pos 'gro ba'i ma rig pa'i mun pa sel bar
NK058(si)001:18341: po yin la / byed pa'o // phrin las ni
NK058(si)001:18342: lhun gyis grub pa rdo rje'i bdag nyid gdul bya
NK058(si)001:18343: la khyab cing g.yo bar byed pas rlung ste bdud
NK058(si)001:18344: dang mu stegs la sogs pa 'thor zhing las bzhi'i
NK058(si)001:18345: don rnams yongs su rdzogs pa chen por lhun gyis
NK058(si)001:18346: po yin la / byed pa'o // grub pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18347: gnyis pa rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor la bstod
NK058(si)001:18349: brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor la bstod pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18351: gtum chen dus mtha'i zhes pa nas 'jigs byed chen po thig le che hoh'i bar te /
NK058(si)001:18352: he ru ka rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor la so sor bstod pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18353: rten gzhal yas khang la bstod pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18354: rdo rje'i brag chen keng rus kyi ri rab dang /
NK058(si)001:18355: chu bo rak+ta'i rgya ma tsho dang /
NK058(si)001:18356: me ye shes kyi me ri dang /
NK058(si)001:18357: rlung 'og gzhi rlung gi dkyil 'khor la sbyar te bshad do //
NK058(si)001:18358: de skad ces de bzhin gshegs pas ched du gleng ngo //
NK058(si)001:18359: 'bras bu gsang ba'i snying po sku dang ye shes kyi de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK058(si)001:18360: rang snang ye shes kyi khro bo la bstod pa'i le'u ste nyer gcig pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18362: // spyi don gsum pa rgyud dam par gdams nas rjes 'jug la gtad pa'i tshul la gsum ste /
NK058(si)001:18367: sgyu 'phrul rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs par bstan pa
NK058(si)001:18368: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po dpal
NK058(si)001:18370: de'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs la /
NK058(si)001:18375: rdo rje 'chang chen po la sogs pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18376: ston pa des rang snang lhun stug po bkod pa'i
NK058(si)001:18377: rigs lnga sems dpa' brgyad la sogs pa'i de bzhin
NK058(si)001:18378: gshegs pa nyid la gsang sngags kyi rgyal po 'di
NK058(si)001:18379: nyid mi nub cing 'gro ba la phan gdags pa'i
NK058(si)001:18380: phyir brtan par zungs shig ces pa 'di ched du
NK058(si)001:18381: brjod cing khyad par du rig pa'i sems dpa' gsang
NK058(si)001:18382: bdag la gdams par mdzad do //
NK058(si)001:18383: kha cig ni gsang bdag 'chad pa'i skyes bu yin gyi /
NK058(si)001:18386: kun nas snang ba'i dpal la gdams pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18387: zhes pa'ang rigs par ma mthong ste /
NK058(si)001:18388: 'di ltar phyag na rdo rje la gdams pas gzhan la ma gdams par mi 'gyur pa dang /
NK058(si)001:18389: 'og min du kun bzang nyid rigs lnga'i gtso bo
NK058(si)001:18390: rnam par snang mdzad du snang bas ston cing 'chad
NK058(si)001:18392: gsang bdag 'khor du snang bas 'dzin pa po yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:18394: lam kun gyi 'bras bur gdams pa dang /
NK058(si)001:18395: gsang ba kun gyi mchog tu gdams pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18397: gdams bya rgyud kyi rang bzhin dang /
NK058(si)001:18398: gang la gdams pa snod kyi che ba'o //
NK058(si)001:18400: 'bras bu rgyud dngos bstan pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18401: rang snang gi 'khor thabs dang shes rab gnyis su
NK058(si)001:18402: med pa'i rang bzhin yab yum du snang ba rnams
NK058(si)001:18403: la kye kye zhes bos nas snang srid 'khor 'das
NK058(si)001:18404: kyi chos phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i rang
NK058(si)001:18405: bzhin 'di dag thams cad de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs
NK058(si)001:18406: lnga yab yum dang sems dpar bcas pa ste zhi
NK058(si)001:18407: khro gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor du ye nas sangs rgyas
NK058(si)001:18408: pa'i ngo bo nyid du gnas pa ni gzhi gsang
NK058(si)001:18410: des mtshon nas lam dang 'bras bu gsang ba'i snying po ni rgyud kyi ngo bo'o //
NK058(si)001:18411: gnyis pa lam gzhan de'i rkang stegs su bstan pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18412: phyi gzung ba'i yul dang nang 'dzin pa'i sems kyi
NK058(si)001:18413: spros pa la blo 'chel nas srid pa gsum por
NK058(si)001:18414: 'khyams pa'i 'gro ba yis phyi nang gzhan la sogs
NK058(si)001:18415: pa'i rnam par rtog pa mi bzad pa'i zhags pas
NK058(si)001:18416: so sor zin te sdug bsngal pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18417: slob dpon phyogs kyi glang pos 'jam dpal la bstod pa las /
NK058(si)001:18418: rnam par rtog las ma gtogs pa'i //
NK058(si)001:18419: 'khor ba zhes bya ci yang med //
NK058(si)001:18422: dang por nga zhes bdag la zhen gyur cing //
NK058(si)001:18423: bdag gi 'di zhes dngos la chags pa skyes //
NK058(si)001:18424: zo chun 'phyan ltar rang dbang med pa yi //
NK058(si)001:18425: 'gro la snying rjer gyur gang de la 'dud //
NK058(si)001:18426: ces pa'i tshul gyis 'khor bar 'khyams pa'i sems can
NK058(si)001:18427: gyi dbang po'i rim pa dang sbyar te theg pa
NK058(si)001:18428: so so'i sa rnams dang lam gyi khyad par gong
NK058(si)001:18429: 'og tu bkod pa yang rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying
NK058(si)001:18430: por 'gro ba'i lam stegs yin gyi lam tshang la
NK058(si)001:18431: ma nor ba dngos ma yin te /
NK058(si)001:18432: de dag gi mthar 'dir 'jug dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:18433: gsum pa rnam grangs du ma gsungs pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18434: de lta na gsang ba'i snying po gcig pu gsungs pas chog mod /
NK058(si)001:18435: theg pa'i rnam grangs mtho dman mang po bstan ci dgos she na /
NK058(si)001:18436: sems can rnams ni dbang pos rim pa sna tshogs
NK058(si)001:18437: su gnas skabs gnas pas gang la gang 'tshams kyis
NK058(si)001:18439: 'di nyid dang po nas go ba'am 'phrad pa shin tu dka' bas sngon 'agro'am stegs su bstan te /
NK058(si)001:18440: phyis 'di dang 'phrad cing spyad pa bya ba'i phyir
NK058(si)001:18441: spangs pa dang rtogs pa'i ye shes ngo mtshar ba
NK058(si)001:18442: rab 'byams mnga' ba'i ston pa kun tu bzang po
NK058(si)001:18443: nyid kyi rang byung gi thugs rje sprul pa'i sku
NK058(si)001:18444: 'jig rten du snang bas gsungs pa'i chos thams cad
NK058(si)001:18445: kyang sems can gyi don du mi 'gyur zhes bya
NK058(si)001:18446: ba ni gang cung zad cig kyang yong ste dus
NK058(si)001:18447: rnam pa thams cad du ma gsungs pa yin no
NK058(si)001:18448: // de skad du'ang legs byin gyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK058(si)001:18449: 'jig rten rnams la phan pa mdzad pa'i phyir //
NK058(si)001:18450: rgyal ba rnam 'dren de yis chos gsungs te //
NK058(si)001:18451: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug zhi mdzad cing //
NK058(si)001:18452: mya ngan 'das pa'i lam la 'god par mdzad //
NK058(si)001:18453: nam yang don du mi 'gyur mi mnga' ste //
NK058(si)001:18454: nyes zad rdzun gyi tshig spangs drang srong che //
NK058(si)001:18456: des bstan pa'i chos ni shes bya ma lus pa
NK058(si)001:18457: mngon sum gyis gzigs shing sgrib pa mtha' dag spangs
NK058(si)001:18458: pa sangs rgyas kyi gsung yin pa'i phyir na don
NK058(si)001:18460: de la ye shes kyi gzigs pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18462: mkhyen pa'i skad cig gcig gis kyang //
NK058(si)001:18463: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor kun khyab can //
NK058(si)001:18465: sgrib pa mtha' dag dang bral ba ni sangs rgyas
NK058(si)001:18466: te rdzun spangs pa'i skyes bu tshad mar gyur pa
NK058(si)001:18468: nyes pa spangs pas brdzun gyi tshig /
NK058(si)001:18469: smra bar mi 'gyur rgyu med phyir //
NK058(si)001:18470: nyes zad lung du shes par bya //
NK058(si)001:18472: de ltar sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa don du 'gyur
NK058(si)001:18473: ba bzhin du de'i sras dang slob ma dag gis
NK058(si)001:18474: rgyal ba'i bka'i rjes su 'brangs te rnam bshad mdzad
NK058(si)001:18477: gang zhig rgyal bas bstan pa 'ba' zhig gi //
NK058(si)001:18478: dbang byas rnam g.yeng med yid can gyis bshad //
NK058(si)001:18479: thar pa thob pa'i lam dang rjes mthun pa //
NK058(si)001:18480: de yang drang srong bka' bzhin spyi bos blangs //
NK058(si)001:18482: gnyis pa gang la gdams pa snod kyi che ba ni /
NK058(si)001:18483: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK058(si)001:18484: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las phun sum
NK058(si)001:18485: tshogs pa'i phyag rgya dam pa ni gzhi lam 'bras
NK058(si)001:18486: bu'i gsang chen chos thams cad kyi snying po 'di
NK058(si)001:18487: yin no // de'ang brjod bya don dang rjod byed
NK058(si)001:18488: rgyud kyi gzhung gnyis ka de bzhin gshegs pa'i phyag
NK058(si)001:18489: rgyas btab pa'i phyir de las 'da' bar dka' bas
NK058(si)001:18490: phyag rgyar bshad de dper na rgyal po'i bka' rtags
NK058(si)001:18491: kyi phyag rgyas btab pa bzhin te /
NK058(si)001:18493: 'da' dka' de bzhin mi shigs pa //
NK058(si)001:18494: rgyal po'i phyag rgya mchog gi rtags //
NK058(si)001:18495: bdag nyid chen po'i mtshan ma'i gzugs //
NK058(si)001:18496: de bas phyag rgya zhes bya'o //
NK058(si)001:18498: de lta bu'i tshul ni rgya du mas btab cing
NK058(si)001:18499: rang bzhin dang gnas skabs kyi gsang ba'i don de
NK058(si)001:18500: nyid phyin ci ma log par rang gis rtogs nas
NK058(si)001:18501: skal pa ldan pas gzhan la smra bar gang byed
NK058(si)001:18502: pa'i gang zag de nyid rgyud kyi ston pa phun
NK058(si)001:18503: sum tshogs pa nga kun tu bzang po yin zhing
NK058(si)001:18504: / phan pa dang nus pa'i dbang yang ye nas ngang ngam lhun gyis rdzogs pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:18505: tshig 'dis rgyud 'chad pa de la ston pas thog
NK058(si)001:18506: ma med pa'i dus su dbang bskur zin pas tshe
NK058(si)001:18507: 'di la ma mnos kyang rgyud la dbang bas bdag
NK058(si)001:18508: don dang gzhan don byos shig /
NK058(si)001:18509: nga kun tu bzang po dngos kyi byin gyis brlabs
NK058(si)001:18510: shing ye nas sangs rgyas pa dang gsang ba zab
NK058(si)001:18511: mo'i don la mos shing mi skrag par gyur pa'i
NK058(si)001:18512: phyir ro zhes bya bar bstan to //
NK058(si)001:18513: gnyis pa gsang ba kun gyi mchog tu gdams pa la gnyis te /
NK058(si)001:18515: de 'dzin pa'i gang zag dam par lung bstan pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18517: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK058(si)001:18518: la sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi gsang ba mthar
NK058(si)001:18519: thug pa rgyud kyi dam pa 'di las gzhan cung
NK058(si)001:18520: zad kyang mi mnga' ba yin pas mchog dam par
NK058(si)001:18522: de'i don yang chos thams cad ye nas mnyam pa
NK058(si)001:18523: nyid gsang ba'i snying por sangs rgyas pa ni gzhi'i
NK058(si)001:18524: rgyud de / rgyal ba thams cad kyis gtan la dbab bya'i don mthar thug pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18525: de nyid ston pa gzhung gi tshogs la'ang don zab
NK058(si)001:18526: mo yod pa rtag pa'i mthar sgro 'dogs pa dang
NK058(si)001:18527: med pa chad pa'i mthar skur pa 'debs pa dang
NK058(si)001:18528: / yod med gnyis yin pa dang min pa la
NK058(si)001:18529: sogs pa'i spros pa thams cad nye bar zhi ba
NK058(si)001:18530: yi rang bzhin ye nas stong zhing bdag med pas
NK058(si)001:18531: blo yi yul las 'das pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18532: gsang ba'i snying po chos thams cad kyi de kho
NK058(si)001:18533: na nyid de chos nyid bsam brjod med pa nges
NK058(si)001:18534: pa'i dbyings nas brjod pa'i don du ston pas byung
NK058(si)001:18535: ba'o // de skad du'ang mngon rtogs rgyan las /
NK058(si)001:18536: zab pa nyid de sgro 'dogs dang //
NK058(si)001:18537: skur ba'i mtha' las grol ba nyid //
NK058(si)001:18540: gzhan las shes min zhi ba dang //
NK058(si)001:18541: rnam rtog med don tha dad med //
NK058(si)001:18542: spros pa rnams kyis ma spros pa //
NK058(si)001:18543: de ni de yi mtshan nyid do //
NK058(si)001:18545: ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi mdo las /
NK058(si)001:18546: chos rnams ma skyes mkha' ltar rab zhi ba //
NK058(si)001:18547: don dam gzigs pa rnams kyi spyod yul te //
NK058(si)001:18548: rgyal ba rnam 'dren zag pa med zhi ba //
NK058(si)001:18549: de bzhin nyid dbyings nas ni bstan par mdzad //
NK058(si)001:18551: rjod byed kyi tshig le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis po
NK058(si)001:18552: 'di dag kyang de bzhin nyid kyi rang bzhin sgro
NK058(si)001:18553: 'dogs dang skur pa zhi ba yi don gyi lta
NK058(si)001:18554: ba zab mo dang spyod pa barlang po rnams snod
NK058(si)001:18555: min la gsang zhing snod ldan la bstan pa'i rang
NK058(si)001:18556: bzhin chos thams cad kyi snying po gzhi lam 'bras
NK058(si)001:18557: bu'i de kho na nyid de ni /
NK058(si)001:18558: kun tu bzang po'i thugs kyi dbyings rum nges pa'i
NK058(si)001:18559: dbyings nas phyung ste lhan cig pa'i 'khor la skal
NK058(si)001:18560: ldan gyi gdul bya'i don du gsungs pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18561: gnyis pa de 'dzin pa'i gang zag dam par lung bstan pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18562: rgyud 'di 'dzin cing ston pa'i gang zag de ni
NK058(si)001:18563: nges pa kho nar gzhan la ston pa rig pa'i
NK058(si)001:18564: skyes bu dang rang nyid grol ba skye ba gcig
NK058(si)001:18565: gis mi thogs par sangs rgyas su lung bstan te
NK058(si)001:18566: / de ni nga yin dbang yang rdzogs //
NK058(si)001:18569: chos tshul 'di la gang spyod pa //
NK058(si)001:18573: rang rig ye shes don ston phyir //
NK058(si)001:18574: rang snang rig pas mngon byas la //
NK058(si)001:18575: rig 'dzin mchog ste lhun grub pa'i //
NK058(si)001:18576: ting 'dzin nus pa'i mthu med kyang //
NK058(si)001:18577: sa sbyong sems dpas bskyod du med //
NK058(si)001:18578: bde gshegs nyid dang spyod yul gcig /
NK058(si)001:18579: rig pa'i skyes bu'i lung thob pa'o //
NK058(si)001:18581: de lta bu'i gang zag de ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sras po ni dam pa yin te /
NK058(si)001:18582: thugs kyi gsang ba rmad du byung ba 'di lta bu las skyes pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK058(si)001:18583: dper na 'khor los sgyur ba'i bu thu bo rgyal tshab tu skyes pa bzhin no //
NK058(si)001:18584: de nyid gnas skabs su sar chud pa /
NK058(si)001:18586: sar smin pa gsum la gnas shing /
NK058(si)001:18587: mthar thug 'bras bu'i sa rab mchog tu gyur pa rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa zhes bya /
NK058(si)001:18588: thabs dang shes rab mchog gi sa zhes bya /
NK058(si)001:18589: rig pa 'dzin pa'i sa zhes kyang bya /
NK058(si)001:18590: mthar thug pa de la gnas par 'gyur ro //
NK058(si)001:18591: de ni nga yin zhes pa dang sbyar na da
NK058(si)001:18592: lta nyid nas rig pa 'dzin pa'i sa la gnas
NK058(si)001:18593: par bstan te / 'chad pa'i ston pa kun bzang dngos su gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:18594: de'i yon tan yongs su ma rdzogs par snang yang don la rdzogs par yod de /
NK058(si)001:18595: sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor du ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:18596: dper na mi dbul po'i sa 'og gam khyim na
NK058(si)001:18597: rin po che'i gter yod pa 'byin pa'i rtsol ba
NK058(si)001:18599: dus de nas longs spyod mig lam ma 'gyur bas
NK058(si)001:18600: dbul por brjod kyang gter chen dngos su dbang bar
NK058(si)001:18601: thag chod pas 'byor pa can yin pa bzhin du
NK058(si)001:18602: / sa rab rig pa 'dzin pa rang la gnas
NK058(si)001:18603: pa de nyid mngon du byed pa'i rtsol ba la
NK058(si)001:18604: zhugs pas na sa rab rig pa 'dzin pa gnas
NK058(si)001:18605: zhes kyang bshad par bya ste /
NK058(si)001:18606: 'di kho nar nges so zhes phyogs gcig tu rtag
NK058(si)001:18607: pa mtha' bzung gis rgyud sde chen po bshad par
NK058(si)001:18608: mi bya ste / rdo rje'i tshig barlinga zhing gang du'ang sbyar du yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK058(si)001:18609: gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK058(si)001:18610: rgyud kyi ston pas mdzad pa chen po'i bshad pa rdzogs nas ji ltar bzhugs tshul ston pa ste /
NK058(si)001:18611: de'ang mdo dang rgyud sde kha cig gis ni bshad
NK058(si)001:18612: pa rdzogs nas 'khor rnams rjes su yi rang zhing
NK058(si)001:18613: mngon par bstod pa tsam ston zhing /
NK058(si)001:18614: de nas spyod lam gzhan gyis bzhugs par mngon par dus res 'ga' bar bstan la /
NK058(si)001:18616: nyid kyi thugs kar zhugs nas mi snang bar gyur to //
NK058(si)001:18617: zhes dkyil 'khor bsdu bas mi snang bar gsungs shing /
NK058(si)001:18623: ston pa nyid las gzhan du gyur pas dman pa dang /
NK058(si)001:18624: chos kyang sna tshogs pa dang /
NK058(si)001:18625: gnas kyang gdul bya'i snang bas bsdus pa ste /
NK058(si)001:18626: thun mong du gyur pa rnams las ches gsang zhing
NK058(si)001:18627: khyad par du 'phags par bstan pa'i phyir rgyud kyi
NK058(si)001:18628: don de skad ces brjod pas rang snang 'od gsal
NK058(si)001:18629: du bkod pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga til
NK058(si)001:18630: gyi gong bu ji snyed kyis nam mkha'i dbyings kyi
NK058(si)001:18631: mtha' dbus khyab pa de dag thams cad gnyis su
NK058(si)001:18632: mi dmigs shing / ngo bo dbyer med par dgyes
NK058(si)001:18633: nas dus gsum 'pho 'gyur med pa'i ngang gzhir rdzogs
NK058(si)001:18634: lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin dus bzhi chos nyid
NK058(si)001:18635: kyi 'khor lo mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings mtha' dbus
NK058(si)001:18637: snang zhing bkod pa thams cad ston pa nyid kyi
NK058(si)001:18638: sku dang gsung dang thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi
NK058(si)001:18639: 'khor lo'i rang bzhin las lhun stug po bkod pa'i
NK058(si)001:18640: rgyan nyid du sngon ji lta bar phyis kyang de
NK058(si)001:18641: bzhin nyid de / nam mkha' bzhin du rang bzhin
NK058(si)001:18642: 'pho 'gyur dang 'phel 'grib med pa'i tshul gyis bzhugs
NK058(si)001:18643: bzhin nyid de / so // zhing khams gsang ba'i
NK058(si)001:18644: snying po ye shes kyi rang snang de kho na
NK058(si)001:18646: mdzad pa rdzogs nas dgongs pa la bzhugs pas mnyes
NK058(si)001:18647: pa dang rgyud mi nub par gtad pas 'khor gyis
NK058(si)001:18648: yongs su bzung ba'i le'u ste nyi shu rtsa gnyis
NK058(si)001:18651: // spyi don gsum pa yongs su rdzogs pa mjug gi don la gsum las /
NK058(si)001:18652: dang po rgyud gang gi khongs su gtogs pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18653: brjod bya gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa bden
NK058(si)001:18654: pa dbyer med kyi don ye nas sangs rgyas par
NK058(si)001:18655: ston pas rjod byed tshig gi rgyud la'ang 'phags pa
NK058(si)001:18656: zhes brjod do // 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las
NK058(si)001:18657: 'das pa'i dngos grub sgrub pa'i thabs kyi rgyud thams
NK058(si)001:18658: cad la rtog pa zer la /
NK058(si)001:18659: 'di ni de dag thams cad kyi mchog tu gyur
NK058(si)001:18660: pa'i phyir rtog pa'i rgyal po rdo rje sems dpa'
NK058(si)001:18661: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud chen po le'u stong phrag
NK058(si)001:18662: brgya yod pa las de'i khongs su gtogs so //
NK058(si)001:18663: gnyis pa le lag gang yin pa de ni /
NK058(si)001:18664: de'i nang nas 'di ni rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg
NK058(si)001:18665: pa dang 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi rgyud thams cad
NK058(si)001:18666: kyi 'phro gazhi'am byung khungs yin pas lung gi spyi
NK058(si)001:18667: zhes bya'o // de nyid phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de
NK058(si)001:18668: bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs rdo
NK058(si)001:18670: mchog tu 'phags shing rab tu zab la rgya che
NK058(si)001:18671: ba'i gnas ston pa'i phyir gsang ba'i snying po gzhi
NK058(si)001:18672: lam 'bras bu'i de kho na nyid rnam par nges
NK058(si)001:18673: pa'i le'u zhes bya ba yin te /
NK058(si)001:18674: 'di las theg pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams
NK058(si)001:18675: cad ma lus par 'phros te bstan pas na kun
NK058(si)001:18676: gyi rtsa bar gyur pa yin no //
NK058(si)001:18677: gsum pa 'bras bu mchog tu bstan pa ni /
NK058(si)001:18678: rgyal ba rnams kyis 'gro ba'i don du sgyu 'phrul
NK058(si)001:18679: stong phrag brgya pa la sogs pa chos kyi 'khor
NK058(si)001:18680: lo dpag tu med pa bskor ba de dag gi
NK058(si)001:18681: nang nas 'bras bu gsang sngags bla na med pa'i
NK058(si)001:18682: mchog rtsa ba'i rgyud chen po rdzogs so //
NK058(si)001:18683: zhes legs par gtan la phab zin to //
NK058(si)001:18684: de ltar rgyud don zab cing rgya che 'phags blo'i spyod yul gangs can mtsho //
NK058(si)001:18685: mkha' ltar rab zhi rnyog pa kun bral gdod nas 'od gsal 'dus ma byas //
NK058(si)001:18686: ji snyed ji bzhin gzigs pa'i gsang chen shin tu rmad byung mtha' yas gang //
NK058(si)001:18687: rgyal ba'i thugs rjes 'gro la snang byas gangs ri'i khrod 'dir cung zad gsal //
NK058(si)001:18688: de don mkhas rnams rim par legs bshad gser gyi d+r+wa bas mdzes byas na'ang //
NK058(si)001:18689: tshig don brgal daka'i chos tshul rgya mtsho da dung cung zad yongs mi gsal //
NK058(si)001:18690: 'di ni shin tu rtogs dka' rlabs chen gsang ba'i mdzod yin phyir //
NK058(si)001:18691: kun gyi yul min mchog gsang rab ni rigs ldan 'gro ba'i thugs la gnas //
NK058(si)001:18692: gang 'dir bdag blo'i mtsho skyes tshal du tshig don rnam bkra'i gzugs snang ba //
NK058(si)001:18693: kun dag'i cha shas zla ba'i gzugs brnyan dwangs pa'i rdzing bur shar ba bzhin //
NK058(si)001:18694: gsal zhing yongs dag dkyil 'khor gang bas chu nang kun tu mdzes pa ni //
NK058(si)001:18695: lha yi thugs rje shin tu rmad byung ches dkar rol ba'i zung gis brgyan //
NK058(si)001:18696: tshul 'di skal bzang slob ma'i mchog gyur pa //
NK058(si)001:18697: blo bzang dge ba'i 'byung gnas dam pa dang //
NK058(si)001:18698: dad ldan gtong phod sri zhu'i mchog gyur pa //
NK058(si)001:18699: sh+aakya ye shes bzang pos bskul ba'i ngor //
NK058(si)001:18700: ji bzhin don nyid spyod pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK058(si)001:18701: rgyud don zab mo'i rang bzhin mngon phyungs nas //
NK058(si)001:18702: gangs ri thod dkar rin cen snying po'i mgul //
NK058(si)001:18703: o rgyan rdzong zhes bya ba'i gnas su bkod //
NK058(si)001:18704: ji bzhin don nyid de ltar phye yang rgyud don rdo rje'i tshig barlinga bas //
NK058(si)001:18705: 'gal 'khrul nor ba'i rang bzhin mchis srid 'phags pa'i go 'phang ma thob phyir //
NK058(si)001:18706: rgyal dang rgyal sras bla ma'i tshogs dang blo mchog mnga' ba ji snyed dang //
NK058(si)001:18707: ye shes las grub mkha' 'gro'i sprin phung dam can rgya mtshos bzod par mdzod //
NK058(si)001:18708: sngon rabs skye bar kam ru'i shar phyogs b+he la he ta'i nags khrod du //
NK058(si)001:18709: ma h+aa mi tra pad+ma'i rjes slob phyi nang grub pa'i don kun shes //
NK058(si)001:18710: de las 'dir 'ongs mdo rgyud gsal ba'i blo gros dam pa ngang gis grub //
NK058(si)001:18711: zab don snying po'i bdud rtsis rab brlan nges gsang snying po'i tshul 'dir mos //
NK058(si)001:18712: da ni rgyal ba'i bstan pa rin cen gter //
NK058(si)001:18713: phan bde'i 'od stong mnga' ba'ang nub tu nye //
NK058(si)001:18714: legs ldan 'gro ba'i mig kyang phal cher zum //
NK058(si)001:18715: gang na'ang chos tshul 'di 'dra dkon pas na //
NK058(si)001:18716: thos bsam snying po'i don la nan tan bskyed //
NK058(si)001:18717: nam yang mi rtag skyes bu'i tshe 'gro ste //
NK058(si)001:18718: lbu ba brdol 'dra so sor 'jig gyur cing //
NK058(si)001:18719: srid pa'i bde sdug khor mor 'khyams pa na //
NK058(si)001:18720: 'khor ba'i grong las zhi bde'i nags khrod du //
NK058(si)001:18721: rang bzhin 'da' bas brtson pa'i go bgos shog /
NK058(si)001:18722: de bas rab tu thar pa'i lam zhugs te //
NK058(si)001:18723: de ring nyid nas srid la skyo ba yis //
NK058(si)001:18724: do mod tsam yang gnas pa'i mthu med ces //
NK058(si)001:18725: da lta nyid nas nges par bsam 'tshal lo //
NK058(si)001:18726: mdzod ldan rnams kyi ye shes gangs can mtsho //
NK058(si)001:18727: mtsho gter zab mo shin tu rmad byung dwangs //
NK058(si)001:18728: dwangs pa'i 'od kyi yon tan phun tshogs kun //
NK058(si)001:18729: kun nas brtson pas legs grub 'bad par mdzod //
NK058(si)001:18730: dus rnams kun tu dus gsum rgyal ba'i mdzad pa can //
NK058(si)001:18731: bla na med pa'i bla ma dam pa mnyes bya zhing //
NK058(si)001:18732: dam las mi 'da' dam tshig sdom pa tshul bzhin bsrung //
NK058(si)001:18733: lhag bsam rnam dag lhag pa'i ting 'dzin zab mo bsgom //
NK058(si)001:18734: de ltar legs gsungs zhi ba'i chos tshul tshangs pa'i rnga sgra snyan po yis //
NK058(si)001:18735: ma rig gnyid myos 'jig rten gsum rnams skad cig de las rab sad de //
NK058(si)001:18736: ye shes dam pa'i go 'phang la gnas gdod ma'i gzhi la mthar phyin nas //
NK058(si)001:18737: chos sku'i mkha' dbyings dri ma med la gzugs sku'i dkyil 'khor snang bar shog /
NK058(si)001:18738: phyi nang snod bcud rigs lnga'i zhing du ma lus rang bzhin rnam dag cing //
NK058(si)001:18739: nyon mongs ye shes dri ma med la dran rig thugs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK058(si)001:18740: ye nas yin la de ltar gsal bas glo bur sgrib gnyis rnam dag cing //
NK058(si)001:18741: gang na'ang srid ces ming tsam med la thams cad kun bzang nyid gyur cig /
NK058(si)001:18742: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rang bzhin gnyis med dpal ldan dga' ba'i skyed mos tshal //
NK058(si)001:18743: gdod nas mngon par byang chub tshul 'di gsal bar bkod pa'i legs byas des //
NK058(si)001:18744: 'gro bas rang bzhin 'bad pa med par zhi ba'i dbyings su legs gzhol te //
NK058(si)001:18745: sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pas sangs rgyas pad ma 'dzum par shog /
NK058(si)001:18746: dpal ldan yon tan sprin gyi bzhon pa'i bla re shin tu gsal ba can //
NK058(si)001:18747: mdzad pa'i rnam 'gros nam mkha'i 'khor khyab phan bde'i char gyi tshogs mang ba //
NK058(si)001:18748: legs gsungs rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po rgya cher bshad pa'i bsod nams des //
NK058(si)001:18749: nam mkha'i mtha' klas skye rgu yongs kyi kun tu bzang po'i gnas 'thob shog /
NK058(si)001:18750: las dang nyon mongs srid pa'i mtsho las brgal bar shog /
NK058(si)001:18751: sa dang lam dang gzungs dang ting 'dzin 'grub par shog /
NK058(si)001:18752: gnas skabs mthar thug re ba thams cad rdzogs par shog /
NK058(si)001:18753: dag pa'i zhing rnams rgyal bas yongs gang mthong bar shog /
NK058(si)001:18754: bgegs dang srin po mkha' 'gro'i gdon gyi tshogs zhi zhing //
NK058(si)001:18755: tshe dang dpal dang skal pa bzang pos legs 'byor te //
NK058(si)001:18756: zhi dang rgyas dang dbang dang mngon spyod 'grub pa yis //
NK058(si)001:18757: 'gro ba'i don gnyis rin cen mchog legs 'byung bar shog /
NK058(si)001:18758: chos tshul 'di yang ji srid nam mkha' gnas kyi bar //
NK058(si)001:18759: 'gro ba'i don du de srid gnas pa'i don byed cing //
NK058(si)001:18760: nyi zla'i mchog dang nor bu dpag bsam bum mchog bzhin //
NK058(si)001:18761: lhun gyis grub pa'i mdzad pa chen pos phyogs rnams kun tu khyab par shog /
NK058(si)001:18762: gad+g+aa'i chu bo rgyun ring ji bzhin 'dis kyang gzhan phan rgyun ring zhing //
NK058(si)001:18763: 'od ldan rnams kyi bdud rtsi'i mchog bzhin nyon mongs gdung ba sel ba dang //
NK058(si)001:18764: yid bzhin rin cen sprin gyi tshogs bzhin 'dod dgu'i re ba rnams skong zhing //
NK058(si)001:18765: sa chen gling bzhi snang byed mchog bzhin yid mkha'i mun pa sel bar shog /
NK058(si)001:18766: chos tshul ston ka'i ri bong 'dzin gzugs legs bshad rgyu skar phreng ba can //
NK058(si)001:18767: don rnams gsal ba'i 'od dkar gyis mdzes blo gsal kun+da'i kha 'byed pa //
NK058(si)001:18768: nyes pa'i cha shas sgrib pa med can ma rig mun pa sel ba'i dpal //
NK058(si)001:18769: blo gros rta lnga'i bzhon pas rab bskyod skal ldan 'gro ba'i snang byed yin //
NK058(si)001:18770: gang rnams phyi nang don rnams shes 'dod gzhung lugs rgya mtshor gnas bcas te //
NK058(si)001:18771: ji bzhin don nyid rnam dpyod mig gis de bzhin legs par lta 'dod pa //
NK058(si)001:18772: de dag gis kyang tshul 'di mthong na dga' ba'i blo gros cher 'phel cing //
NK058(si)001:18773: grags dang ma grags tshig don rnam bkra'i tshul la shin tu mkhas par 'gyur //
NK058(si)001:18774: rgyud don rgya mtsho'i pha rol brgal 'dod pas //
NK058(si)001:18775: legs bshad rin cen gru bo 'dir zhugs te //
NK058(si)001:18776: don zab ba dan gshog yangs brkyang byas nas //
NK058(si)001:18777: tshig don ji bzhin don gnyis blang bar rigs //
NK058(si)001:18778: 'dir ni rgyud don 'o ma'i chu gter mchog /
NK058(si)001:18779: bdag blo'i rnam dpyod bzang pos legs bsrubs te //
NK058(si)001:18780: snying po'i rang bzhin bcud du rab bsdus nas //
NK058(si)001:18781: phyi rabs 'gro ba rnams la snang bar byas //
NK058(si)001:18782: phyogs tsam ma yin don kun gsal ba yin //
NK058(si)001:18783: grags phyir ma yin gzhan phan brtse ba yin //
NK058(si)001:18784: rnyed phyir ma yin chos don mthong phyir yin //
NK058(si)001:18785: nyes bshad ma yin legs bshad rgyam tsho yin //
NK058(si)001:18786: ye shes rnam bkra nor bu'i khang bzang dbang po'i gzhu dang dus mtshan dang //
NK058(si)001:18787: nyi ma rnam bkra dkar ba'i mchog dang zla zer bdud rtsi'i skyed mos tshal //
NK058(si)001:18788: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i de nyid legs mtshon mchog gsang rdzogs pa chen po'i don //
NK058(si)001:18789: ma lus rang bzhin gcig tu bstan pa gsang ba'i snying po dam pa yin //
NK058(si)001:18790: 'od ldan rnams kyi snying po la reg pad+ma'i d+r+wa bas cher mdzes shing //
NK058(si)001:18791: bdud rtsi'i lha dang mi'am cis mchod shin tu gsang ba'i mdzod mnga' ba //
NK058(si)001:18792: rgyal ba'i yum gyur kun gyi 'bras bu gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK058(si)001:18793: de nyid legs gsungs rgya che'i tshul la chen po rnams kyis mchog tu basngagasa //
NK058(si)001:18794: lam 'dir zhugs rnams kun las mchog gyur sa rab rig pa 'dzin la gnas //
NK058(si)001:18795: lha mi'i 'jig rteen mchog gi gtso dang drang srong grub pas phyag byas shing //
NK058(si)001:18796: don gnyis 'bras bu tshe 'dir 'byor pas zhing gi dam pa rgya che ba //
NK058(si)001:18797: de phyir de dag 'byung ba'i mdzod ni rnam bshad rgya mtsho 'di yin pas //
NK058(si)001:18798: thar 'dod rnams kyis chos tshul mchog 'di gtsug gi rgyan du gus pas bzung //
NK058(si)001:18799: dge legs yid bzhin ston ka'i sprin ni 'jug pa'i snang ba rgya che ba //
NK058(si)001:18800: 'od zer sna tshogs kun nas 'khrug cing zhing rnams bye ba gsal bar byed //
NK058(si)001:18801: ma lus de dag lam ldan 'dir brten legs pa'i 'bras bu mchog 'grub ste //
NK058(si)001:18802: phyogs bcu'i mgon pos rab tu dgongs shing kun nas basngagasa par mdzad pa yin //
NK058(si)001:18803: dpal gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i rgyud kyi rgyal po /
NK058(si)001:18804: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rnam bshad nyi zla'i sprin gyi
NK058(si)001:18805: snang ba chen pos phyogs bcu'i mun pa thams cad
NK058(si)001:18806: nges par sel ba zhes bya ba /
NK058(si)001:18807: sngags dang pha rol tu phyin pa'i tshul rgya mtsho
NK058(si)001:18808: la mang du thos shing legs par sbyangs pa'i me
NK058(si)001:18809: tog rgyun chags pas blo'i pad mtsho gang bar byas
NK058(si)001:18810: pa'i rang bzhin / theg pa mchog gi rnal 'byor
NK058(si)001:18811: pa rdo rje gzi brjid kyis sngon gyi 'grel chen
NK058(si)001:18812: pa'i rang bzhin / du ma dang / bla ma
NK058(si)001:18813: rnams kyi legs bshad mngon par snang ba'i tshogs dang
NK058(si)001:18814: pa'i rang bzhin / du ma dang / / rgyud
NK058(si)001:18815: lung man ngag du ma'i snying po bsdus te gzhan
NK058(si)001:18816: la phan pa'i blos shin tu gsal bar phye nas
NK058(si)001:18817: pa'i rang bzhin / du ma dang / / /
NK058(si)001:18818: 'brug gi lo ston zla ra ba'i tshes bco lnga
NK058(si)001:18819: bkra shis kyi nyi ma shar ba la gangs ri
NK058(si)001:18820: thod dkar gyi mgul du legs par sbyar ba 'di
